user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Crissy Geco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuJ3S3izzKvCA0KHhbGxhqv1Pfwi-klzp3LuC46IS8Eck67vNB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Usually stop by there for the earl grey tea and the spinach feta bistro pastry!

Today i tried the black rose garden tea and (despite how long I’ve been going here, this visit was the only time I’ve been ever asked if i wanted my tea steeped or a tea bag be given).

I prefer to have steeped tea always!

This visit they also ran out of the chocolate ganache cake which is my favourite so feeling a bit sad they ran out (it’s only early afternoon in the week when I visited).

Met someone on a scooter and they mentioned it was nice there’s ample street parking on Kingsway (in front of the café) and specially on the side streets as there are trees for shade 🌳","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMb2M9wN17nzcpghHtLYPv9cwZryRkLJnWvjxwJ&fid=0x0:0x466206b57e209b12"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Alyssa Alexandera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV95VpKh_Tdijxwf_FmdOEYfNLTLHWEG3UIMyC3BunlgTP-0qg-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We come in almost daily but the South Asian girl (her name escapes me at this time but I will update!) often gets the order incorrectly. Each time we order the same thing, Waves size medium roast coffee with cream and 2packets sugar (they recently began withholding sugar packets and changed the drink making station to be on a weird small ledge that only one person can stand at compared to the actual counter right behind it.. incredibly uncomfortable and inconvenient).

She keeps giving the regular size instead of the Waves size, and this time when we called out the mistake, charged us an extra 50 cents for the cup change?? Even though it was not our mistake. Just seems silly as a long line was forming if impatient customers as she couldn’t figure out how to charge us just for the cup..

Coffee is great, love it, but service has recently gone down a bit since the newer hires happened. Still love waves and still support them! And despite what I wrote above they’re very friendly. We can’t imagine going anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blue Grandsport","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk7UWkL-LuISkgeYx5QrsWrqDGyL4SrrqyIOe2gPa-OKIfCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a long time customer (10+ years) I offered up my congrats to this particular Waves store for being the top cafe in Burnaby. I've been going to this same location since 2014. Seen so many staff come and go. And now Dennie the current team lead is doing an excellent job with everything here as well!

I have even been around during its renovation period when they completely changed the floor tiling and rearranged the kitchen / front counter location within the store.

So congratz to my favorite Waves store for the win!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6zExCS7O4N86DgzhrCMEd3KfATOC5sPUcBaly&fid=0x0:0x466206b57e209b12"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Jas Chauhan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5uDW42XKiVzbO61dFqJZ8mAnhNnpL6GW8UuwZVgntI4gopg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there today around 3:30. It’s a really great and nice coffee shop for everyone to visit. The girl in the front was super friendly and she helped me with the menu as I have never been to waves coffee before and the coffee tasted really good as well. Will recommend again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mohammed Danish Shaikh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXL_2EBKbS3tzuR33VUJ70dWWQIVmaIikBg5e3McHnfzvmltQQr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I tried their Vegetarian Samosa and Nanaimo Bar. The samosa was okay, Nanaimo Bar was better. Lots of seating inside, lots of street parking around and in a very good location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNx87D4V0Iff3Vx8v2nzpsjKK-jT-O0laxQuyYY&fid=0x0:0x466206b57e209b12"],"When":"2023-12-31"},{"Name":"Sash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsEN8LESXHdVUHALQ4S3DxVR2gfd5knlpOhRGZTjLzMJeMHtuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s a nice location with plenty of street parking available nearby.  My favourite go to drinks are : milk hot chocolate and dark hot chocolate. (Apart from their regular coffee)
They have a lot of dessert options available as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJdBKD4G6kbZqxOtslI4HCIr9E4SzYPcq2oSVe&fid=0x0:0x466206b57e209b12"],"When":"2023-12-26"},{"Name":"Riya Negi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlRtMgYfhEe4Evzg3lqCZhfhhuBUs_joQ7qjut3Z2AkGIBcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited Waves Kingsway this evening.I accidentally spilled my drink but the staff was very nice and they cleaned it up without any complaints.The drink was very tempting and tasty.Would highly recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good amount of both indoor and outdoor seating at this location, lots of light, and a full menu offered at this Waves location. Nearby to Patterson skytrain station, Metrotown, and Central Park, it’s a very convenient location to go and grab a coffee with a friend or date. On street parking only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnsXRUnlLZg1-URYk0gU9MsMcJP-nzLAgwmuGt&fid=0x0:0x466206b57e209b12"],"When":"2023-7-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX11ANDfpnFU7GmCeaVtU5cBwuWRqquWAK3F9_AUyciKpah0H5L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After how many years of wishing and hoping, Tealips has finally opened up a second location. They have wisely chosen to open this location at Metrotown, which should pretty much guarantee its success.

Absolutely beloved for their incomparable waffles, I was thrilled that I could now make my way over there whenever I pleased. Their Highgate location is really out of the way, especially for someone who doesn't drive.

I assume that the owners must have struck up a bargain with the former tenants, as Tealips was displaying the exact same miniature desserts as Mr. Mustache.

More spacious than their flagship store, this Metrotown location offers up more charm in the way of quirky knick knacks for you to ponder, as well as a fair amount of vegetation.

The quality of the food and drinks is on par with the Highgate location, which is a huge relief.

If you're looking for a cute off to the side Café where you can have your fill of bubble tea, iced desserts, and sinfully delicious waffles, detour over here and make your lips happy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcVPCCImMRKhLwj9owblAzWq8DTkNfWfPVzmxb&fid=0x0:0x8e619ade2d75b38f"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Kristy Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEfZ2rjxNiODjhooQ3vu4wU52UFmMssx1nBEw-QrGtiP3D8nPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A tad overpriced for what It is, I paid $4 for like 2 strawberries… But the cake and the waffle here is absolutely delicious, would definitely recommend. I did not love their bubble waffle though, it sounded interesting but is not much different from a regular bubble waffle.
Service is standard, cafe is not very big.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmlZ_5mayX1TIRHi0dRAKpx2-YBqr0bzKtT5z4&fid=0x0:0x8e619ade2d75b38f"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Used to visit the Edmonds location frequently years ago. Their new spot close to Metrotown was fairly quiet when we visited.

Had the mango slush and passionfruit green tea along with the chocolate waffle pop. Pretty standard stuff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHsGfESkbPy1WYpsxO2FUJQ8RufOpw2DOR5w7E&fid=0x0:0x8e619ade2d75b38f"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Matthew Zhao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqEC97UBlOW8ksbjeGIzyTGP5HoUSJ2msd1UoNVDokj0KiMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cozy cafe is the perfect study spot on a rainy day! The food is amazing and the workers are very kind as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwodLuRYjyhTT8HjkxHY7Vpa-0ZaYXYqQrAwYb&fid=0x0:0x8e619ade2d75b38f"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"ann bc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViaOsh3TXlBEKoJMyDpdVLP8Ypi4uozX-MbqTb8FC4tJO81Tc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough about how much I love this cafe! The sandwiches? Absolutely delicious—so full of flavor and just perfect! But the real standout is the service. The staff are incredibly friendly and welcoming, like they’re genuinely happy to see you. The whole atmosphere feels light and joyful, and the space… wow!
It’s rare to find such a spacious cafe in Burnaby. I was thrilled to find a cozy spot to snap pictures when I met up with friends I hadn’t seen in ages—it was the perfect reunion spot! I also love the overall vibe—sipping tea, relaxing, and chatting without feeling rushed.
My first visit was on a rainy Vancouver day, but as soon as I stepped inside, it felt like a burst of sunshine! This cafe gives me such a peaceful, happy feeling, like a little escape from the hustle and bustle outside. Now, I visit all the time and would definitely recommend it to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY_qIX-Alu7CtPDFDUtTkSlRT1hVzcFbm9j9HEOogCz6HKZgzElw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently tried the oolong tea latte at Tealips Cafe and was disappointed with the flavor profile. The drink was incredibly light, almost like drinking diluted milk with a hint of tea. It was so subtle that it was difficult to detect any distinct oolong flavor.

While it's possible that the oolong tea used in this latte is simply not a good match for milk, I've never encountered this issue with other oolong tea lattes. I'm willing to give the benefit of the doubt and assume that this particular combination just didn't work.

Unfortunately, based on this experience, I won't be ordering the oolong tea latte again at Tealips Cafe. If you're looking for a strong, flavorful tea latte, I recommend exploring other options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrnQE4RK7KNfEoHYN2PTgEq6Bh0NtsVfBoWvZr&fid=0x0:0x8e619ade2d75b38f"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Betty Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkHKO0FNXUjcVpSdEmjVpTrBPRFq89QuZ-Z5xXnZc-tQBI6ZrG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"3.5, rounded up.

the service was great, the cashier was very nice and explained the drink menu options clearly. I ordered a hojicha milk tea with coconut jelly, but I felt that it was way too sweet (it might've been because of the jelly), and the hojicha flavour was not very present. however, the atmosphere was cozy and pleasant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tina Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGNz6BMlXQZVg2D_Ca3s8J_KgA4K4jfm3cCr_4ej6TgbqsYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited the shop with my friend today to try the new promotion menu. Unfortunately, the cashier hurriedly informed us that the jasmine flavor was unavailable and only the original was offered. She also mentioned that the dessert waffle promotion would start next week. Her rushed and unfriendly demeanor, without even a hint of a smile, made us feel quite unwelcome. We decided not to place an order and left, which is quite a shame considering it was your grand opening. We were looking forward to supporting your new shop, but it seems like customer service isn't much of a priority. Hopefully, things will improve for other customers in the future.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"damanpreet singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGPfy_mVg1Vr2ejgkkdAoGKdIS4zV6nFJVU7nUKxx4-uGHpklS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first time at Coffee Loft and it was delightful.

Staff is very courteous and friendly and greet you with smiles.

I ordered the egg and cheese on English muffin without bacon and they made a delicious sandwich and made some excellent replacements.

The coffee is good as well and will try some other items next time I am in the neighborhood.

Much better experience than other chain coffee shop places which are in Metrotown.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1AKRYTelSRj2QJSiXTUayGcfhVly83jJlNyfv&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"y sa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFngQqa2F90OIpbxkUL3vQVcASx5xoE2gyFjE4kMR1ydjk_2M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered a chestnut latte and a chocolate hazelnut croissant. The latte was great, but the croissant felt a bit too moist and heavy, possibly because of the oil. The atmosphere can vary depending on the time of day, but the vibe is calm (when it's not too busy).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa7EPoE-9raa8vm-YyzXTZs2hrRhE_yZa0ox64&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Shaianne Casasis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVflTGm8iJItU5OIi2vvnAmt0aeNAsLE9-Rruq437_EqjqkFaHH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm enchanted by this place.

The atmosphere was incredibly cozy and inviting. The soft indie music playing in the background enhanced the ambiance, playing loud enough to be enjoyable yet quiet enough not to disturb my reading. This place offers various seating options including standard chairs and tables, high stools, and a comfortable sofa. I ordered an iced brown sugar latte, which had the perfect balance of ice to avoid dilution and was not overly sweet. Both the cashier and the barista were exceptionally pleasant and quickly prepared my order.

I would definitely recommend this spot to a friend looking for a great place to unwind!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abhay Verma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrV_6i4dbcDuraV7ft63f2m_fuGbXlt4ooiSAA_Az5gxTkAzw0Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried their Spanish latte on the way to metropolis mall and was very happy with the product. The coffee was perfect and what I expected in a Spanish latte, my only minor complaint was the coffee could be a little stronger (not sure if it was the beans or # of espresso shots in a 16oz coffee).

Was completely packed when we came here, it's a popular place for students to get a coffee or pastries and study. They have a lot of seating.

Recommended if you live nearby and like good coffee!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLzx64GRbgWYD_RhLumeDdVHabN3WnJ_SoN890&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"Matt K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbsZ43tiHJA5LPIasgCFxc-_Vmad6SXxBlx2Vc4G6V_jKEHJbR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cafe is amazing, the coffee is excellent and full of flavor. The pastries are always fresh and delicious. The staff are super friendly and make you feel welcome. The cozy atmosphere makes it the perfect spot for relaxing with your buddies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDM2Q_8a7oa_BcoC8rhH-pqCeeEqnZ8VEm9v47&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Kelly L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLX9T8NjUEkpLRVZ79xh3zOY94cv5DeZoWU5Jr6AQRHOuuC0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their sandwiches are amazing ! Good portions, and it comes with chips, which i like 👍  but there are so many studying people (always) , it's hard to find a table to sit and enjoy coffee.
The staff, she's friendly, but the lady( i think the owner) is not, though ...
Overall, it's a cozy cafe in Metrotown !

They have a washroom and also some tables outside(2 tables).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcF-JeKp3K2bOy58bi4PMqi6fPwWVoeiOmBNLK&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Leah Kloeble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyDWKAUYa5KA0SGP07rwL6ye3Xptn57rUEru5oqAWQw274UalgiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Really good dark chocolate peppermint mocha, London fog wasn't very milky (more like a tea with milk). Overall it's a good cafe. 3.5/5 stars Nice atmosphere with high ceiling and cute coffee shop vibes in an easily accessible area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicky G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbWjpLgBln8DnFCHZy58YMKyUW1zX1_ln-Kz0kxGh5SneXRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They are great! But always busy, students just kind of sit and stay there forever. There should really be a table rule during busy times where people can only stay for 1 hour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkXn4db9CRQkSkGql2ZJDJhTLDbXJo04-hsns&fid=0x0:0xf85963ff3c587445"],"When":"2024-11-23"}]

[{"Name":"Keith Ver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVdqxLCf1LEt0AU82myo-eUqDcb2LcbdnfhupJTEW0sPAQ-qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their Hainanese Chicken Rice is just okay. Probably enough for a quick grub given that the store is inside a mall. And I love Hong Kong style coffee and tea so I felt it was pretty good. I also see they have a two topping noodle deal that comes with a drink for $15.95 which seems pretty reasonable. I haven't tried the food, only the bubble tea.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1LnBxqi9z1wke2oMF345uESZG7dedtvQxks6j&fid=0x0:0x45c6ad37c6427e2c"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Jacinda K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0xoGeCDSw5DVJ3YNgzQb_o4aJOLzQdAQ3syqD9WiYy7lJqCATJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Having been to multiple locations, the Metrotown one is the most challenging:  long lines at peak times, hard to find available seats/table, and the menu is slightly higher than the other locations.  Service was surprisingly quick though!

Drinks are not included in the combos (extra $1 for basic beverages like milk tea or lemon tea).  But it’s still good value for what you get comparatively.  Hainanese chicken with rice $15.95, plus $1 for drink, plus $2.50 for waffle.  The waffle was made to order, hot, fresh, and crispy.  The meal was solid, but the chicken portion seemed smaller.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPt76GkDyRJHAjxLKoL2gFmSwv5CMVvNCTxrRSL&fid=0x0:0x45c6ad37c6427e2c"],"When":"2023-11-12"},{"Name":"Frank","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV32Dl3aDuecVTKkUVDILvrpBYb8ATjyfxIGWGxKJriKTeCzCiJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst bubble waffle, a lot broken tiny rice noodle(half inch length)and only 2 slices of beef inside. Spicy soup was way too spicy! All for $18! What a waste of my money! Never gonna visit here ever!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIkTtNe0cP15yaaAHqz-RpzCqvz6KTHODGa_kA&fid=0x0:0x45c6ad37c6427e2c"],"When":"2024-1-21"}]

[{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently visited Single V Coffee and was a bit disappointed. To start off parking was so difficult to find. There is a huge pay parking lot but everything was so full, I drove around for 5 minutes trying to find a spot. While the atmosphere was nice, I found that their coffee options were quite basic, lacking variety. The food selection was also limited, with only four pastries and a croissant available. I was hoping for more “lunch” choices to enjoy with my coffee. Overall, it was an okay experience, but I wish there were more options to choose from.
Customer service was great and efficient","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1Ym-wFZWLA_4qRH9L9bE_571XY84J6Iv7rv2f&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Rajwant Minhas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhLrVtRe3AjcYdFMzuxUzJYT9GZYipB1ZOxjqlnJU7Sq_TSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time at the cafe. Flat white was amazing - the taste was great as the coffee was not bitter at all. The service was good..loved their cute mugs..so glad they have that option for sustainability. I would encourage the business to have signs up for customers to encourage customers to bring their own coffee cups/mugs for take out coffee to promote sustainability especially if they offer discount for the same. Good ambience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtqZig9vbMqvI92yUbcta-P8NvakrlKRzI7XD-&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Erica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiBiehVBMqDRcQQk3J28lEnqLVQ-p5tIOA0Zlj3wvs65IUmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here on a Sunday afternoon, they were out of brew coffee so I got an Americano with Oat Milk (Americano $4.5 + $1 for Oat Milk).
I also tried the Chocolate Cream Cheese muffin ($5), it was pretty good but a tad dry. The outside is like a dry Japanese-style cheesecake, and the inside is a regular chocolate cake, but the combo together is quite interesting.
I'm not a coffee connoisseur, but I do enjoy coffee and need my daily dose, so I did find their coffee overall a bit acidic for my tastes. To each their own.

There's a small Specialty Menu on the side that I didn't realize until after I paid, I  would want to dry the Espresso Tonic or Orange Espresso. They also sell beans by the cashier. You pay at the cashier, and there's no screen to tip which I appreciate. I personally rather pay for a more expensive cup of coffee than tip, as I usually only sit for 15-30min, and take my own cup/plates away before leaving.

Small cafe, about 4 small seats and a few by the bar so it does fill up fast. There's a large parking lot for the plaza, but it's paid parking only. Prices are pretty standard for a small local coffee shop. Overall, I'd recommend this place in Burnaby, walkable for both Royal Oak or Metrotown Skytrain station. It's a cute place to check out if you're ever craving a non-chain coffee shop in Burnaby!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbOuj3gbTcj9acCPqWdnx3kX2STza0i0QMdfPd&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Cindy Xu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkWnRcqRwVg_mpqM7f4VioaCJHawOmYOsqXy6htya5AhFjkbgY1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Hojicha tea latte has a very smooth taste and was served by Diana, who is so friendly to customers coming into this corner coffee shop. Their shop also has a good selection of coffee and pastries that could be worth checking out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqj5bQ4JRkc8ORZOhP6Q5OWH0VFpVMJBihjXMi&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Danilo Teodoro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_rV4_xok36vIezJ6uAhpzSfyECA8ogmjA4ehyXVTr4dBqIAFv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Pour over and the Latte were superior! And the Strawberry cake was a good surprise. I decided to get their whole beans package home after that. It would be great if they had more brunch options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR7nhKEycTfno6YAhUigxdZPQkkZ8AANrQNhNL&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Nara Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhvqYviVmNRdUs4hBsTj9aEeMEUIUtVFXoe8f3rZFhfWT27yat=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A small cafe with around 16 seats. The matcha 🍵latte was very authentic and smooth. Would definitely come back to try other drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7PnyCEUHZr76xHLODN2s8VCbMPVuNw-n2Y9WU&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Anthony Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXljEKK4QPlqb0LvSutuMH9-Ibtf8vhPBv3YlPTlMYvh2tczTL3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clean and pleasing aesthetic. We were lucky to see the croissants come out of the oven - very tasty! Espresso was slightly tart but with medium body. Overall enjoyed my experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxt2fR0lUS546Z60aThaYT2VA-0e-s2bwa-3Ve&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both the drip coffee and the iced passion fruit coffee were absolutely fire. Single V is sophisticated without being stuck up, a beautiful gem with probably the cutest mugs I have ever seen (all made by a local artist, one of a kind). Very attentive service from the barista (arigato!), indeed a place to go back to. Quality coffee either character.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpZYcEQeCPeyskb43zn8Sb-Brm_ouVi80f3coq&fid=0x0:0xda7ea3a05cbeab79"],"When":"2024-8-6"}]

[{"Name":"Joanna Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWolcjmld9gF3v6DkaAWVH8shgENhbGrrRuqb_2RSUD8H4muTAvMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried the ebi mayo, the meat topped gyoza, and the deluxe mazesoba.

The atmosphere was really nice, service was great. Very attentive. The food was delicious.

They're very busy during dinner time, so plan accordingly!

Will come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCwQQsL9MN8Cc3ZtdB_yS19XRlEzwf-_GPI0sT&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved dining here, beautiful layout and delicious food! Ordered off the tablet at the table, food and drink came in decent time. Mazesoba was absolutely delicious! Plum wine is a must try. Friendly and good customer service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCxmXyacNMNGHoDIg5W0F_KOVKl9i6ApDgq_r4&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Leon Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPOnBvlGz2k_WzxOhCiURR3aRaAE5ffHXfUBJJ4GP7GBC5Wn8K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and great atmosphere! They have some very good portion sizes, and they even do rice refills in case the carbs aren’t enough, which is complements the Mazesoba very well. My only complaint is that they used to put their bubble tea in cute bags, and the rice refill portions have gotten smaller, but I still highly recommend this place, especially their Hokkaido milk tea :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOw_O88UgeIP7Oq_q2EWK3cy_NLBgrBzm_WbJiK&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Christine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMbb4rSx2yeLvBgC1qs9Q3xv5M2ENLkGN0MgNur7yErOCX2LNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I visited this place because I’m a big fan of soba, and I was especially curious to try their mazesoba, which isn’t something you find everywhere. Unfortunately, I don’t think I’ll be returning.

The interior is spacious, with plenty of seating, so there was no wait at all—we were seated immediately. Each table had a monitor for ordering, which was incredibly convenient since we didn’t need to wait for a server.

However, the taste of the food was quite confusing. I found myself adding small amounts of every seasoning available at the table, trying to make each bite more enjoyable. Unfortunately, it felt like a search for flavor with every mouthful (and not in a good way). They do offer free rice to mix with the remaining sauce after finishing your soba, but in my case, there wasn’t enough sauce left to make it worthwhile.

Overall, while the service and convenience were great, the food just didn’t meet my expectations. I don’t think I’ll be visiting again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBK6Lxerfy8BFuE1VvXLBIlNV7ji1lpU8Q1k_9&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"M. A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLB10KqeIl0fqiL0pGNdfKbos8ZnoBDkwk_kgO3yJezaC8LhTs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've never eaten at this Metrotown location before, and I truly enjoy the atmosphere. I placed an order for the Tamago ramen with level 1 spicy. It tastes good and is delicious. The pricing, in my opinion, is also fair. The staff is incredibly helpful and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrX8luZNgGDjpHxYBDa7XHbPv45hW4bmB9vmgf&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Daria Liukin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkJyqUukJ1Tp32CT1Y60hgwO8TEu98t8UrHjC4vSHU3XhtZR-hfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time trying mazesoba, and I highly recommend this place for anyone new to it. The waiter was incredibly helpful, explaining the menu and the ingredients in each dish. They genuinely recommended good options for first-timers, especially for those who are sensitive to spicy food. We thoroughly enjoyed the experience and the atmosphere, and we would definitely go again, especially on cozy days when you can watch the rain through the glass and enjoy a warm meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUvch9MxzytQHsnX5F7kfg5G6XDPvPxZYwu7nj&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Andrea Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaHmtb_7S3QMBAvPDyTDdmbnTM8PZJFItNseE9VGIP9mdJXWbN0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We order the carbonara and zenbu mazesoba, appetizer is chilli sauté shrimp. The one star is because of the shrimp dish, too oily. I understand sauté is you stir fry food with oil, but as you can see all the dish is oily, and the bread also absorb the oil from chili. The ebi mayo usually the best appetizer but this dish is the worst. We have to move the shrimp to the empty plate because this oily chili completely fed up with. The main dish is mazesoba, always creamy and delicious, but adding with this appetizer, I really don’t recommend. If the chili oil is spicy then have more flavor, but this chili didn’t taste spicy, it just dry chili deep in oil.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9yWONVxSM8e2ODhgRTrWXmieGYazVdrRgGRNM&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Franklin Liao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrGFaQEoVKTERfUvRAWQCImcuaAWW4G55EVRkYegV3eRBq6fzG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kokoro Mazesoba serves up Taiwan Mazesoba that hails from Nagoya in 2008, while the chain from Tokyo came to be in 2013. The bite, chew, presentation, portion, and the richness of the sauce all hit it off with me. Free noodle upside, free rice as is customary with this mazesoba make the experience an impeccable bang for the buck.

Having said that, the decor, the staff, and the location are all superb. Within an easy 5 minute walk from Metrotown station, at the newly expanded Station Square, this spot is an easy recommendation from me to visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPH8Xdl6noHpJUlSDMCtdjILBFm4arRq4zSDAqo&fid=0x0:0x194bae6812444fe2"],"When":"2024-10-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dana Sliman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLCGVuOanB5fZdK4mDXVlNu1FRWwlivE-0dO5Jtxe0XvekGJ21jg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Plenty of options and beautiful menu to choose from. As you enter the space it smells amazing like home cooking. I ordered a breakfast wrap. It was very delicious and oozing with sauce (to rich to my liking). I’m glad that I didn’t take it to go because it was dripping. I will try to come back and try something different and experience more of the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6TRgSSAWe6Gi5i3bP7VpvYn8j6B-_4mlJvQB5&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Anthony Plaxen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0TosyGAQWTqM_XvTHaXfq2jDGHv6ifKWBgTGcJKYnap3ceipL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great spot to hit up for decent good eats and brunch. Decided to give their special of the day a try and it was good, solid and what you would expect from a cafe.

It’s nothing too special but it fill you up well. Came with some chips and soup which was nice. It’s a nice quaint little cafe in an industrial area with decent eats and overall I was quite satisfied. I’d come back again for a decent sandwich. Staff are very friendly and they’re open till 3 most days. I’d give their Benedict a try next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKGgSQEfVitCPRyAUV4ztglT_6YE6HgX0jlLYi&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Mohammad M Islam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuRqeYa0qeQvQy57V-9LRvbVMV5FXbbaQqt8771B7XbII3uUko6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been hearing great things about Oneway Café, and I finally had a chance to try it out. Based on the positive reviews online, I had high expectations, and they were mostly met! This little café is located in what looks like an office block.

The atmosphere is cozy and inviting, with a bohemian vibe that's perfect for a relaxed breakfast, brunch, or lunch. It’s nicely decorated, and the menu offers a handful of delicious options, from classic breakfast dishes to creative lunch plates.

I ordered the avocado toast with a poached egg, and it was okay. Maybe I have different taste buds. I’ll need to give it another try. The presentation was very nice, though.

The service was friendly and attentive, and the staff were happy to answer any questions I had about the menu.

There was plenty of parking around, at least on the weekend when we visited. It might be different on weekdays when the offices are open.

Overall, we had a good experience at Oneway Café and would recommend it to anyone looking for a delicious and cozy brunch or lunch spot in Burnaby.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU1q_FYN2Z3CJf-bVxdhOGJ6cMbOI9jrXTe2Q1&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Jessica Aranas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUG8N5f3Wd4GKt8zT_qaGsKHP4OREkobtyE2Xefb2cmdEv-KSHu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best brunch we’ve had so far, it is not as fancy as other restaurants but the food is so delicious. We ordered the Bulgogi Benedict but next time I’m gonna try other food on their menu. Maybe, they can design the place where you would want to stay and relax. Anyway, giving 5 star for good food, good service, and nice ambiance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhqGsOzOFuDa8MJNV7PBEDq-g3GuU3DdX7kJRe&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Kun Ho Yoon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7a_TkQUEpAcdGGNy9qU2vuDm2_Ypkj7DPW3ASPBDUd0z4TSse=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is simply amazing, I visited for the first time and I couldn’t have asked for better.
The service was really good and friendly. It was very welcoming. I ordered avocado Benedict and with the lentil soup and it was simply amazing, delicious. I’d love to visit again, you must try it in the cafe instead of take out because the vibe and the environment here is very relaxing and pleasing. I would love to visit again in the future, definitely recommended 10/10. Thank you so much!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0UPiGNH0-MWY3UI2P1K5KDL_c8aKMY1MNaAk3&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Stephy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV09N9nFBWqArIiOZROODXFgWotqMzNAOWY7bfqNJM_q_rhJ8yu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was excellent! Staff are very friendly and everything is very fairly priced! Will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1btgaJ5BIR3VHBGX9Rsrz1iR2BDIRm94BKQ-4&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Fluffy Squirrel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2-eZIWh01U6JMyfsAly6kLgc0p4QySV9zmMG41-1unvk4QA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was introduced to this place by my relatives and I can say I was really impressed. We ordered tomato soup, avocado toast, Wednesday special BLT and veggie bibibop. All dish had fresh ingredients, yummy flavour and no flavours were an overkill. The staff were very friendly and checked in with us a couple times to see how we were doing. Overall, it’s a place where I can comfortably bring anyone for a nice brunch / lunch and have a good warm meal. Highly recommend giving this place a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyCuX0uUpjqF4OOkmesBFJQs0r_hZD6_x-dzGn&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-1-17"},{"Name":"AH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbSDTBRb0i5Z-O9Llx_f4jUDvaC36Rpc_Ai8VCzOt_tM08rlqM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was looking for brunch near Coquitlam and found this place online. It was delicious! We tried the Bulgogi benedict and the shashu grilled panini. Both dishes were filling and very good! The taro slush was not fresh but I liked their pearls. Prices are kinda expensive but it’s worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOE2AQvy74mCjiYS3AA3iiRbOmc5ylV3lCW-Ucg&fid=0x0:0x3332f77d0ceb5860"],"When":"2024-7-15"}]

[{"Name":"Emilia Muirragui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVbrBdWMJwAdDmTKF2rqn3OE2f7BKVf4ff7Eui90G41UPNKe7l=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good Cactus Club location, conveniently within walking distance of Metrotown. The restaurant was clean and not too busy for a Friday afternoon, and the bathrooms were well-maintained.

The food was delicious: we tried the Tuna Stack, Bolognese pasta, and Lava Cake. Since we mentioned we’d be sharing the pasta, they brought it out already divided into two plates, which was a thoughtful touch. However, they didn’t remove the appetizer dishes, which made the table feel a bit cramped.

Our server was super nice and friendly, which added to the positive experience overall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpO2QnSIfZcqzB6wUbH4of6fu_orY0ZGC-jHKX&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Isha Motani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIW4POr2CnFe8xGZwSQ3o1VsIIzKAt5a0D-U1KW9FjBnuY1fQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I am a vegetarian and always struggle to find good food in these type of restaurants. Why do you guys hate vegetarians!!
I had no option but to have Falafel bowl. Even the Thai curry had fish sauce! Please keep some vegetrarian options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlWrBma5YkeYCrpIwFPhjmYlYJHFWlXJEv0DqX&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Chantel Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhUBNkL0dFJIMe46Hc5ZOh4M4Rb_kRrqjOnOpE53jr3rAZmMY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"we went there during the happy hour time.
The burger was great, but the steak was overcooked and hard to eat. We asked for medium but it might close to well done.
I think it might be close to the closing time (11:00), so the service was really slow. The service was nice, however, he never filled up our empty water glass.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnqkZV9PAajcT9m5OmbK3tD-CWAVToPUvotTs&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Melissa Meng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfi_MaQwJQjr5awFnfBadZv0UHcxu-wrWjT5PFn9oDD0gq0vU3JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New location in Burnaby, new environment inside and outside. Spacious inside. Food is still kept high end level. Fresh food material. Service is professional. Suitable for friends , family and company gathering here. Worthy to come . You can park your car at square station parking lot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfJUJGkGekeAnUysz0mCaySi_fYYPXG-tHxEg9&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Yanniandi C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSuq2O6lPgjTyeeK5I0-HvsIcyZNK163GH31jkT6zHPryGZbnbnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've been there a few times for employee appreciation dinners and have had a wonderful experience each time, the meals are all delicious, and if the servers are able to be around they can speed up the serving of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkX-koel7eyOWFF8CZUFsXxkpADHndKOV6Tnhd&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Lost in Flax Blog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnuEdz0exGAqoaKWuU3YZ60m50P5j2VjB_aqaZVW3VnTtNws28=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been fortunate enough to be a patron of Cactus Club Cafe for more than 20 years. I first started off being obsessed with their gardenburger and sweet potato fries back in my youth when I was courting vegetarian hood. Later, I would grow to love their calamari with tzatziki dip (since discontinued…) and various pasta dishes (many discontinued).

Despite their ever evolving menu, Cactus Club never disappoints and always satisfies my cravings. More recently, I tried their spaghetti portofino, Baja fish tacos with a side of truffle fries, chipotle chicken tacos, and New York cheesecake. All were sublime but my favorites were the spaghetti and fish tacos. Will be back to try their salmon aburi, chicken Parmesan with potato gnocchi, and hot chicken with pickles!

Keep on rocking and winning, Cactus. You are always a good idea 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻

P.S. waterfront and station square branches are my fave so far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjIkiPRMXcrDBgB0XGFgOID5mP4fqfRT89NyJB&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Carol Wal.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmaEoaKXJ-LJbZu9x6VXOl8dM3-bKZExckrX8F7_7T88DDxKbn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our server, Christina (back to my memory…),was awesome! Very friendly and patient. A nice place for dine in with friends!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwgtgPoxZEDoFt00WDWIOU0ZvHke1gnq4Fa01m&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Berenice Baeza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9NjTRE1lVaLFkorLOHsrwcd4Ar03FlEkQdbO7B2xq0ZkfNKVyWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great option for birthday celebrations, the personal is very friendly they made my celebration special. Also, they are very efficient we don’t have reservation and our party was a little bit big, however we didn’t have to wait too much for our table. 10/10 experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDPAcQLq26Z8LUner9IlEX4g0SxpgaUZBqAfKB&fid=0x0:0x41a3a1261e77e59d"],"When":"2024-11-12"}]

[{"Name":"Vem Fell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwkPSV3Go5MeUNG2num_FvOxxkl2soaYDTRAJLJyvuZfHkM2xy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Special shout out to our server extraordinaire, Sharin! She was continually checking in on us, making food recommendations and subs---attentive and positive demeanor throughout our dining time. Best of all, she surprised me with a birthday choco-banana waffle on the house! It's our first time here, visiting from Seattle, with no reservation on a Saturday morning. Will def come back the next time we're in town!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8VhF0xv2lUsVs73IwX5csx-SrHdgeMKMGhs0D&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Daria Liukin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkJyqUukJ1Tp32CT1Y60hgwO8TEu98t8UrHjC4vSHU3XhtZR-hfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been there twice and can't get enough!
My husband and I absolutely love this place! First off, their coffee is amazing especially for a coffee lover like me. They serve it in a bowl size, which is a perfect 10/10 in my opinion!

The food is always presented in an eye-pleasing manner and is very filling. Their potatoes are the best I’ve ever had!

As for the service, the staff always greet you with a smile and a welcoming attitude. It can get busy on the weekends, so sometimes there’s a bit of a wait to get in, but it's definitely worth it!
This place is definitely going to be our new favorite!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODfNaLPefrkQlD0BcSGceOTls-F1V9JSOjlYrV&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Very disappointed
Quality of food really below average
Burger patty very dry
I have potato allergy and they substitute at $1.5 for salad but the salad not fresh and only some chopped veggie with onion ( I could have paid $4 to upgrade to fruit salad)
I requested sour dough in place of bun my wish was granted
Presentation of food is nice
Next table gifted us the fruit on toast as they didn’t want the sauce very generous of them
Free 3 hours underground  parking at Station Sqaure but they do ticket fast if park over 3 hours","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuoefrV8Tz8jnZbBNyjPQLSQnyubv-3BvNqpC3&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Cat King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs0w4Gi6wbbwHozHIMXCxGOYXWgHMRV7NGZtPTmRmCUIubsOlj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just dropped by here with my little toddler and my girlfriend for brunch. The prices were pretty decent, and the quality of food was pretty good too. I ordered the crêpes and fruit, an island spritz and junior kids meal for my toddler. My girlfriend ordered a skillet. Overall, it was solid  Breakfast. Nothing was Nasty. The drink wasn't that great. Think I could've skipped that. Didn't finish it. I think I should try their different menu items to really see if this place stands out more than other regular brunch spots. The junior for my toddler seemed to be a meal of good value so I liked that. It came with milk. For now, I thought it was clean and pretty straight forward. Service was alright though. Nothing to write home about. When they got busy, they kind of forgot you but when they came around, they were very nice. If I'm around, I wouldn't mind visiting again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlNrJs_9hO0skFpAqAyZPp9FrXCgjhe4xEXBsa&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Anne Reimchen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1BebgngGXnOdE_L-yoUylD52GWAlXy8f3wfJI7Evtsu_zBUPrSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service was exceptional. Hameek did his best to let my friend have an amazing birthday brunch. Even tho whole team came to sing with a little dessert and candles. My vegan toast was amazing and huge and also my friend loved the vegetarian skillet. We def come back!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM04Goy2vBSj3bUm2P_8hDABAFHLKC4N_F79PUf&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Harmony Hodge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjEcB71glc9XoGzAlvpfEkLF80DU1ajN-Vzz27Hv5DYyKOznI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved the atmosphere and the service! The food presentation and taste was superb. Great menu selection and yummy smoothies. Our server Om provided exceptional service. I will definitely be coming back again soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuVZZXvRJdrdDHZlTdNWqy6EgIbdiSGpO9SRd_&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"samira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwkQGMre8jgbaip4E0o2r4QwZ6hsRUFGFhUhbAr4O--khz6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food here is great! Menu got a good variety of brunch options to choose from. Location is very convenient next to the mall and the interior design is quite nice. The only major problem with this place is that they are way too short staffed. We were on a waitlist that took an hour and even when we got seated at our table it took them a long time to get our food. They had like a few empty tables while ppl were waiting but actually no free staff to take care of them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsZ8eOkZnakn1vTmD9f-JdMD1pLGwAaDHgX4ic&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"camillia Verbena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7XSwryagnko87z4Nq17RiWXSBJKLG9tumm0l46SSWFLtMDn8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Came here the other day for brunch and it was such a disappointment.  With the wait time and good ratings,  I expected it to be decent.

The food and service was mediocre.  I was shocked by the lack of effort put in for the dishes. I got the avocado lox and the avocado wasn't even cut and spread out onto the toast properly.  I just found half an avocado placed on the toast,  and the layers of smoked salmon all clumped together on top.  You can be busy but this was plain laziness and i expect more from a restaurant this popular.  On top of that,  the pricing was pretty standard.  I can forgive this lack of attention if they actually had cheap prices.

Would not go back and don't  recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_ef55XpN3ud7EIrHKyFkptqsVqInc3NKahoDy&fid=0x0:0x46ad4bf21998be2f"],"When":"2024-9-10"}]

[{"Name":"Micahel Rupisan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJm8I4ki07gu4RRJY-_8s1XDFKf7mDmzv8CFmkU0_OIQr7POA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good and tasty food.  Good portions that could be shared if you are a moderate eater.  Very accommodating servers who gives you option if needed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDXxJOxbh4hVbuE_0dEkvkh6OWY_HUxFaN3nAs&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Alexa Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRyxk7sfm3OPU9JtxS536XsKHV42RFY-PqVVLiGC8U8BwuFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for a couple of years and think it's the best shawama in the area. The food is healthy and made onsite (kudos to the woman in the back who's always preparing and bringing out more salads, etc.!). A nice change from typical mall food.
Favourite dish is the chicken shawarma salad plate. You get to choose four salads such as tabbouleh, fattoush, dolmades, and so on. I always add the pickled turnips yum :) Posted a photo but it's hard to see - the salads are underneath all the chicken.
The ladies who work there are kind and always smile and wave at my 1- year old daughter.
Hope they're there for a long time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVFR1dNFamAjytOhK-u9ig3cLg7EBOCvUQTzLc&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Melissa Albano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHEx4g1_Qmx297PBmzL-VHqJXywquOlItQDaqeAmjGdDu1eQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm absolutely loving Basha! The servers are incredibly kind, especially Aziz - he's exceptionally friendly, goes above and beyond, and truly provides top-notch service! Plus, the food is EXCELLENT and the portions are generously big! Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2VNXLmxFXz4iHd2imyL6kBmvleGJQiCl0eCl9&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Monica Nguyen Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZBeMwSkt7l1K2HVfyeAFOoXFwnBn78IKEly42V3HGsujhC8gu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love eating here whenever I have a work break or drag my bf here. Plates are very filling and I love their garlic potatoes. Just a small box filled with garlic potatoes is very filling. I will say thought the package they use for the wraps is disappointing. I held it in my hand for like 5min and when I was opening it the wrapping kept sticking to the burrito. Not worth getting a burrito but I hope they change the packaging then maybe I will try it again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_UAODAHOH5GMqD_Xs7c4hI6obu6lnu8vhBtGf&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Ehsan Ansari Dezfouli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBuctSfCC7I6o7Wmf5_NwMSKZW4VU-hHdVx9puXgtFqHggGVM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at this restaurant. The food was amazing, and the staff were incredibly kind and friendly. I asked for some extra sauce, and they brought it to me without charging anything, which was such a nice gesture. Overall, I was very satisfied and would highly recommend this place. Also, there was a staff member named Aziz who was super kind and helpful—his kindness made my visit even better!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWy2gopVQKKOPp0yZ0h3WVl0GENR-SZqM2r9OLc3rowdUnaAt0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately, my experience at this restaurant was quite disappointing. There was a staff member, referred to as Azi or Azir by another employee, who behaved very unprofessionally. He spoke to customers in a loud and disrespectful manner, which was extremely unpleasant. Customer service is everything in a restaurant, but sadly, it was completely lacking here. I strongly suggest the management reassess their staff to improve the overall service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAJAdS8x58YUiX8uOuJxMOg8H4Diond0h_fpLl&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"syed jabir (jabi)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP9nX8GVPPrANlU6g7-R_R2dmHT7JuRB3X3vHIrCFep-sUXsRU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was taste 4/10, but the chicken had alot of fats. Its doesn’t look quality chicken though","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwBLBgv6WSw6ioNJW0h6iGqyeJqeV3pQrYyTlV&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"P P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrqQn2R7yD4XVDPK-c61om1uFohhWM5nSQHwFsInaye-f9-dDwGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good Lebanese food! Will visit again! Good portion size and quality.

Edit 29 March 2024:
Portion size changed to smaller, seems they are using new plates and bowls, no longer great value, 5 stars -> 3 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlDWNRCaXmkFNkGbo9AVie7Bsx3wFI28vgN1r6&fid=0x0:0xb415152e4fdbcb53"],"When":"2024-2-18"}]

[{"Name":"Albert Teng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-nTWIs_AvduA4K0dYLiWKazmh1Q7KIidiI00NDZrUefslOS4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I passed by this place the other day and wanted to try it out.   Came here today with a friend to try it and was not disappointed!  The portions are large and delicious.  I got a Chaska platter and my friend got the waffles set.  Also the Masala Chai was really good!  The owner is very friendly and hospitable and it looks like everyone in the family was helping out today.  I love these types of businesses!  Thanks again and will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUYhuOCcrGwLcedTPRGpHOIQbaJxEgyC6-vQmN&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Tifa Mai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUY0a4aza7yCzK5UKhYbMTpb1757qfJGKRWOVn3HwWNXhFB3lbe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great local restaurant with an amazing menu! Highly recommend if you’re looking for a quick breakfast wrap or even a full meal 😊 Good mix of Indian and Canadian food so there’s something for everyone - even vegetarians! Owner is so nice and welcoming. 🎉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwwtAZdQDbVYc6_4HtI8FZfTWSorvh09L345m4&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Zain Sattar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFfrSoEFfdUlTAEpaJufTkEEj1Hvgw0Vj7UCpPTI9WC2NtfqXt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing chai and the sausage muffin and sausage bagel were excellent. Update: came back a week later and order the same items. Quality remained high and consistent. Excellent chai!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMekT33dnx-zQysJAAaIZ93p2Z3vyDqchSZKF34&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Hassan Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUQjGAmJ4PVWk5E9bHJPOxbmU5vqAkoCRdK6Qav07M1xFn-G-Bsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely hospitable service and the food was simply amazing. We ordered the Chaska platter and chicken pesto panini. They were both amazing. Seating is kind of tight but we went early morning to skip some of the rush. Will definitely be returning again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzTbN1qIguQIVWjqM7lNnMhqGS68xxFdECJRy2&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Hina Butt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqqzrEx8HAHzJ9we4YEcA9SwAHWacTYolqXcl0f21tT7u4E_WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the pleasure of checking this spot out today and it was such a great experience. The food was even better than we thought it would be. We got to try the sausage croissant, avocado BLT, pepperoni pizza pocket, refresher, and matcha frappe and all were delicious - especially the avocado BLT.

We really appreciated the kind service and warm environment - my toddler really enjoyed dining in and getting spoiled with a free cookie. Will definitely be coming back whenever we’re in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYuM2-umzikmPeU5iHIHvVwYWSxnFRODdk-RE&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Charlie Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxfQIYfMiKUcM7bkE87BV9W2vRwnWStbft5J_s8_CBViiwklE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second time coming back in 3 days. We ordered a Coconut Latte, an Americano, a Shami Kebab Panini, a side of fries and a Sausage Bagel. Total was around $38 which is very reasonable for me.

They're all delicious, I really like the bagel here. The chicken sausage tastes good and the panini size/portion is great. The Coconut Latte is a bit sweet for my taste so I'll make sure to adjust it next time.

Would come back again as we love supporting local businesses!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOsV9gSdkfclsxhwLWlGv6pLUoGi_eD5JAEdg&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"sahar poloiyan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqOweYEv7zIhUU1qcdca8uy8QwBgdPu7vCye5kmcCGwd-KJCCq0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time here, and I needed a customized breakfast in a hurry. The owner was incredibly friendly, asking for details to ensure I’d be happy with the meal. They prepared it quickly, and it tasted delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp6417UEXAg7CT7fhGCDNV8O1-dx49ZWPZDnSb&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Shuja Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEBorCT1xB53Ohf-r3sasYNY3f1aLK2cvkUGn0blmUthajlwZj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This newly opened restaurant is a must try. I went for a breakfast on Sunday and wasn’t disappointed. Ordered an All American and chaska platter. All American had 2 eggs, 2 chicken sausages, 2 chicken strips, hash brown with choice of 2 roasts, French toasts or pan cakes, we chose French toast. Chaska had omelette, 2 shami kabab, paratha yogurt and achar, I ordered Karak chai too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZ1VZWkG9iK78XUdNzOOPSsUjwU2feoCsQuq6T&fid=0x0:0x3b4243b8ea9e86b7"],"When":"2024-8-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Olha Diachek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKapYGpIaHHL_bYwAq1JBs_HDSsE2Hp1SZ1O_3KZuVv9Zypvs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was surprised by how spacious this place is. On a Saturday afternoon, it was quite busy and noisy, but that’s exactly what gives it its unique vibe. I was particularly impressed that your order is brought to you by waitstaff. The team is very friendly. There’s a huge selection of desserts, which seemed to sell out quickly. I ordered the waffles platter, but the portion was so generous that I couldn’t finish it all. I ended up taking two waffles home with me.

The interior deserves special mention. The abundance of fairy lights brightens up the mood, even on the gloomiest, rainiest day.

This place is definitely worth a visit. I’ll be coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5-SdGkXj3GbWivZzbkY_2IlQXOp-GBo11NQ83&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Alysa Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcgTm0ud5IEy5AFweNCtfAx_NW6IUKANq244urxoakJ5YPzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cake shop has a beautiful interior design that makes you feel comfortable as soon as you walk in. The atmosphere is cozy and welcoming, and the overall vibe of the shop is relaxing. The staff are incredibly friendly, always greeting customers with a smile and making you feel at home. Their warm and attentive service really adds to the experience, making it even more enjoyable. The cleanliness of the shop is also worth mentioning, as everything is spotless and well-maintained, which makes the place even more inviting.

Of course, the highlight is the food itself. The cakes and other treats are absolutely delicious, made with fresh ingredients and a lot of care. Whether you're there for a simple snack or a special occasion, everything on the menu is prepared to perfection. It's clear that a lot of attention goes into both the presentation and taste of their offerings. Overall, this cake shop is a fantastic place to relax, enjoy great food, and be treated with excellent service. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQlkV62UIFpdE8hs2hwu1ckZA2mGJag-ImqovN&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Lucy Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuwCjTEBDQem6hcfmmxSA0I0nNlJPkS88N0KyjwlMUZAjI_Jdm8w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally tried this place out and it did not disappoint! We went on a Sunday around 2pm and it was packed, but there were a couple tables available so we didn’t have to wait. Recommend reserving to avoid the wait during peak hours. I got the bulgolgi sandwich with squid ink buns, and it was so yummy. The food also comes with salad as well. The interior of the place is also super aesthetic and there are a lot of seats, and it’s a great place to study! The pastries are also really delicious and we tried the red velvet Oreo cake :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNip0Qa07f4r-TlKrE6qKhz5mGJwAH1aOqBPNgV&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Minsu Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeQw_YhBoAI2Nw8r0LMwW0nIB7-k0xmL7wVLR2dXlH04ac3BEx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee was great, they make it with lots of love.
I had a cookie which was very good, many people in seats around me were having heavier meals and they all looked good as well.
The tables are wide, good for studying or working, but after sunset it’s a bit too dark for reading.
Highly recommend a visit!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBXBYe_LYyLjs7bhCJqvipCXDux8aJl7sDFKZC&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Angeline Rafael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNIjGFt3AwM_dbBlrzN87xEqd8MR6IorQ07Mu1L2X8Ih11nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is always busy and packed but their service is fast. Once you placed your order, one of their staff will help you get a table. We got their chicken platter but not a fan of their soy&garlic chicken. But their desserts and drinks are really good. We liked the tiramisu roll and their matcha latte. 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtkwPk3bDK3tLOAy1n3F8pNttR_FbsDjRBJjoc&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Elaheh Mahraban","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM7Oi6ZA5Fr6MkruIzoopb-zB6aVtEKxKffUhhlHzjMxNIqDrL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a really nice and relaxing time at this bakery. The mango waffle was delicious, and the high ceilings along with the well-thought-out interior design created such a chill atmosphere. Perfect spot to unwind and enjoy a sweet treat!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmj1dEDAV0h4hXUMfuaOLxsuAcGqL2mpHbS5Nw&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Cap Holz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPyOU4gu8e0VDkbUMnKwJdDhYwFFnSKwX2msPVNIE1ol0wz4i8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food is really great looking,  but when it comes to taste, it's just but there. Service is fast but theyre always very full.

Also, 90 dollars breakfast for 2","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO201plN8k843wl1PqhX3BWdkrO8cjU8MAEvZI&fid=0x0:0xee497c0e629fc581"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"AIZY A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW63HuUeCCv9sgK_rgm18cZfVwLP0r1WfmUCdIu1jqRWz_XpAFKzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful ambience, everything look appetizing. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVijg2B2FKhHEO0daffmmkqtpWCzt3aDQdnZOIHflF7afjJd1G7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"9/10: fried cabbage (fresh, crunchy, well seasoned, not overdone, simple but yummy).

8/10: fried chicken (well executed, crispy not oily, tender inside, kept the skin on, dark meat - a bit sweet though, presumably from sweet potato flour dredge).

7/10: Beef satay noodles (not enough satay heat, veg a bit mundane like fast food style).

Service super nice. Restaurant small, feels a bit cramped.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHpu_z14Z-U56vu7cJpCz5b_f9wPxQufxowxVi&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Amy Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvtm7hBqZHDYxXgP_oxkelx2FGhwfW-EuwTv9rdyjxo-_-_8Nq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here and will be coming back again. Great deal for homey Taiwanese food! I got the fried Sweet and Sour Fish and the batter was super light and the fish was tender and moist. The fried tofu side was light with a nice sauce. The Special combo for two is very worth it as it’s a larger portion of meat for just a few dollars more. Good portions. Service is friendly and very Taiwanese. Love it. I NEED to come back for the salt and pepper chicken.

My friend and I shared the Special combo and it came to $46 between us.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR7VpPglq3ZyjTroxhKTMzbAwu9wPM42_TyQKD&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Jonny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJShSgCHbmme6GLETHZczdb6MWGsJKCwpKUqZlkj3SXYWukfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Never been to Aroma Eatery before. Small Taiwanese spot outside of Crystal Mall.

- Special combo for two ($39.50) - Taiwanese sausage and sichuan boiled fish. Combo came with fried tofu, seasonal vegetable (garlic yu choy), two bowls of rice and two black teas. Sausage wasn't anything special but liked the sliced pickled garlic. The Sichuan fish was tender but very mild. Vegetables were excellent, tofu lightly deep fried.
- Wonton with spicy sauce ($9.00) - standard.
- Crispy pork noodle soup ($15.75) - pork came separately on the side. Decent.

Debit or cash only. 3.5 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP25ZnByvJO2PiiZlBE_5cVZZx9keDn-DN4-U6f&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"D Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4D0pnJRuugp7xtOoI9Okhc1IdtNuzKocuzhsSBj3gUdos57g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very homey taiwanese food.  Beef noodle was great. We went on a day that wasn’t very warm so i don’t know if they have air conditioning on a hot day. Otherwise the food definitely met expectations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO7euZi1J7sizu1wP-QjPNnIkTbF-n7DOZLAqN&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Ellie K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1Bvfhw59U6hW1Dmjhl5XuenKr5q-LKNQDB91SK_lnnqhqiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here! Really Taiwanese style! The price is reasonable and staff are really nice. Just a bit salty and deep fried technique can be better, other than that is good!! Will come back again and will recommend it to my friends!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPP4JBC9D7rjaSjPvflsE16ZUFwt3MyJzH0WuW3&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Vancouver Foodie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8w6jkWQhHhs1Z246avVvoKQqrR4N6KZDvvFaklq629YACSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very authentic Taiwanese food at the outskirt of Crystal Mall.
Roughly $17-19 per combo.
Combo includes a drink and two sides.
Big portion meal.
It's a small shop but people have a quick turnaround.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnnQclvY4jza-0v_7erB3CDSMoAz6q5Cy5-tjI&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"J. T.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_sa5RAC1-7vSaf7XilM5IG_MJjFsqYnws9ROJ1rmG68gmT1Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My co-worker took me here for lunch yesterday. The service was great. Food was fantastic. As for the value of the food, you are getting the most bang for your buck here during this financial tough time when everyone is struggling to put food on the table. Unbeatable price for their combo meal. Many thumbs up and I highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpPiGe1weebNI81yRt14tnjx9V6ffYmrnjmFRg&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-4-26"},{"Name":"Eva Tong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbdn1JwTeGwTMz4zaH_aM0s2MjqUg4f-ith9g4COdwAGXFieA4Ow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hubby and I ordered lunch special for two people. The food was delicious and flavourful. Love the salt and pepper chicken, the Kung-Pao beef is spicy, my husband likes to eat. They also provide two additional side dishes, veggie and fried tofu (nicely done, crisp and crusty outside, soft inside). They have either tea or soup to choose for drinks. The overall is great, but the store is small with it takes long time to wait for seats. Recommend to go early for lunch instead of 1pm that needed to wait 3-5 parties ahead.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh2BL2-INHXLBD7ilVSLe5DRndySwIsmPKXog6&fid=0x0:0x8455285560aa645f"],"When":"2024-2-11"}]

[{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Service is awesome here.. som of staff know my order.. always clean.. fast service.. food and the coffee is the same as any other Starbucks..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhkjSrkYh8GZ-QmRonQ89zUKTuD5ORSxVMHVqn&fid=0x0:0x408f10147f771ba2"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX11ANDfpnFU7GmCeaVtU5cBwuWRqquWAK3F9_AUyciKpah0H5L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was craving Starbucks after having lunch at Happy Lamb and it turns out that there was one located conveniently just down the block. Who knew? Wasn't I just saying in another review how there are so few Starbucks around these days?

I stuck to my usual Java Chip Frappuccino, and it was heavenly.

If you're at Metrotown and don't fancy waiting in line at the food court Starbucks, make a trip out to this one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDnfyvQ7Yu2eDcRdo2GPVPragUzruTjKxIcVAJ&fid=0x0:0x408f10147f771ba2"],"When":"2024-2-28"},{"Name":"Z Zhao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs-pJ1HJcJcEs9CvV5lP2Uh95o0TMQA_oMLKcGyRZlHrF1s475OA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered multiple times from this store, every single person smile like angle/male angle/trans angle, you what I meant. The coffee is just a Starbucks coffee, nothing more and nothing less. The store is clean and very well organized. Appropriately staffed and I always get my coffee super fast. Normally there is a short line in the afternoon, but don’t really have to wait long because everyone is so productive and professional I guess. Love this location! I would recommend everyone order your coffee here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4YfzTkCfbtSmwlgCHN4dnmXo_9hooFpTgn2fZ&fid=0x0:0x408f10147f771ba2"],"When":"2023-3-30"},{"Name":"Sadaf Amiri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPHc2xTnS12CBehzwzDFEmwlfSIrGQainQFAOK2JxHKratI7mL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my everyday spot and I love spending time here for studying, setting my meetings and just being here!
The staff are really nice and friendly and welcoming!
I wanna thank all of them for their hard work and their beautiful attitudes🫶🏽","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JV Yiu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURaW1e5G2BuTB8BBonhhezWSO1Vc30CBAmArCz-oEdJ4ny_Uf06w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very clean and convenient coffee shop! Employees are friendly and helpful.  Got my drink on time and they taste good.
