Everything from coffee, breakfast and delicious pastries. The customer service is top notch and all the food/drinks are so yummy! You must stop here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNseGx7NiGG2lyI0FdJYEuYm8Mb2FcERP6euo04\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"El B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1Jp_yyor94dWcxEABRdR-csu7LJ3E6mAmEDdXvZyVkvxhIa10=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee place. On of my favorite. The croissant was fresh and flaky. Service was great. People who work here were all in good mood and friendly. They all deserve a raise.☺️. Plenty of seating. The place was clean and not super busy in the morning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTgcUmqAgNARa2ROk7uIm_BSYtt7Tsv01_v9Bh\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Jorge Enrique Marciales Acosta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs9G5ZpQ_qTBOsbd8J0VpmKWERzXHqzAq0CocOXlhPv9vZOWo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The coffee here is absolutely delicious! They could improve the quality of their pastries, but I keep coming back thanks to the amazing coffee and the friendly staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhcUBboucO9qCdafpIwlE8o5l56MZafeAZLQsd\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Hiep Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMRHHZ7t798igHqhwEObqqiXXBYRe7_vTRRS3-gXG7fOgZlXSH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here at any JJ Bean! I usually go to Starbucks cause they have so many locations and it's more convenient.  So glad they offer Matcha Latte since I don't drink coffee! My latte and friends coffee came out within 2 min so quite efficient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kalkidan Berhanu (Kali)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwG91QfSOTlmWxrAuB_p_OYFEJGLPgwgdqAlCklQT3xXMLtELr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very cute cafe by Metrotown! I love their Cajun chicken sandwich and London fog. Their bakery items are delicious also. Fair bit of space if you wanna do some work, but it gets quite busy and seats can be limited during peak hours as expected. Dining in gives you a discount also :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOG9slvN5nJi18pYpn5aPVYZeuOO4UdWpIjO-mx\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"candy L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgq2OgnXFRsC1icGye-CTgUf_6kEV0cPoOgzI7ANMes5eDT-Xz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today, my friend invited me to meet at this branch of JJ Bean. This particular location is situated at the corner and has a wider space, with much more beautiful interior design compared to other branches. It is very modern, especially with those lovely hanging lights. Perhaps because it's already evening, the pastries didn't look very fresh. I ordered a cup of espresso, which was very aromatic and rich. My favorite thing about this company is that every branch provides oat milk or soy milk for you to add to your coffee at the counter. Overall, I highly recommend this place as it's a great space to meet and chat with good friends or enjoy some alone time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0tIDYk0hV1hC7ztFdEzGfyc1CobSVMyNQZiQT\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2023-6-2"},{"Name":"Y S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTmtWUtCZcs7qDdNKdjVbtcx5f5BcDfDU3YRp4zcFsXHKu1_WS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This location is convenient and busy. I came on a weekday morning and it’s already busy with people working or meeting. There’s a small lineup but the line moved quickly. Their coffee was better than Starbucks, not as watered down.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKDP_aT8aDudlfq4C6zUo4IsLQpL4n85RYTPKe\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Larry YVR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuTv093wbMx-W_HREHfZgp4qwBRPVQElu44Abax3eT7gG680u3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Much much better now than when it first opened years ago .. staff are very friend and their systems are now in place … the single origin coffee they had (I am an Ethiopian coffee geek), Ethiopia ACACIA was very good and the peanut butter cookie :-) well done to the manager and staff .. give them a raise Mr. John Neate!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfPwMo8hAVbk_o2mtKBIGdYkMM-ZD5qWfNMl4S\u0026fid=0x0:0x798dbaeca30f0b9b"],"When":"2024-4-6"}]

[{"Name":"Penguinz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDSeZlcEU1qo8PHZvMYCV0si_olLu3nUl_RY0wYLXZcgQjYnWI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve had numerous instances of when my drink was not to the quality that I was wanting. Call me picky, but when my Frappuccino starts tasting like flavoured water, I will not be able to enjoy it at all! I want to give this place a higher rating, but the quality doesn’t match my wishes.

Definitely not a place I will be frequenting.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emilia Muirragui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVbrBdWMJwAdDmTKF2rqn3OE2f7BKVf4ff7Eui90G41UPNKe7l=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at this Starbucks. The place was clean, and there’s plenty of parking available. I ordered ahead, and my drink was ready for easy pickup with everything perfectly prepared. The baristas were friendly and kind, and they were happy to add a little extra cinnamon powder to my drink upon request—such great service! Although the store seemed busy around midday, there were no delays with my order.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dayeon Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLm7jhYuUm7w4XfDYaFhZh8jyFnRGedzYsk52-74IUgzAXogQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best Starbucks in Vancouver!
I often go there on my way to work :)
Vilma is the sweetest person
I appreciate all their service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORnmi84G1fz74O9pldJegShD1utDcLYHduSnzX&fid=0x0:0x43f58ed58d130d5f"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Eunice S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS9soOUCZ9ekI0vaGOiLQWPKC2U-QbHqY51JG9ueHHlLQZTb5VzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had the worst customer service experience at Starbucks for the first time. I bought a few gift cards and asked for separate receipts, but the staff didn’t seem to know how to do it and shook her head right in front of me. Another staff member helped, and I finally got the receipts. This has never happened to me before.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Ian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXJEY-nIJbGr1aoJ2B_gnJF4-mXIdQwbEefkiviuafPbwPMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was having a running stomach and I had to use the toilet. Then I asked for a cup of warm water. I was not confronted at all. The lady in glasses was very nice and friendly and handed me the water for free. Definitely would come back and buy coffee from this store. ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkgI8d8IjS5dl7nqRLdRn6tfCxMJUvpUrfnxUxM-aNYxU-m0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"‼️ Door Dash Order- This keeps happening- where is the consistency? Sometimes the cups are full of milk and sometimes they look like this!!! Would you pay full price for a carton of milk if the clerk at the check out stand poured out more than a quarter of the milk before handing it to you to take home⁉️❓ *NO*
So why does this Starbucks expect me to pay almost $7 for each venti soy milk but not fill the cup? Please have a discussion with your staff and do better, this has happened at least 5 times out of 10 orders. We are obsessed with the soy milk and can’t find it anywhere and we are willing to pay the steep price— BUT NOT WHEN YOU DONT FILL THE $&@!! Cups!! 🤦🏻‍♀️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEPZ8MzmDFy3mqmrEjb9h9LtRJek93gWnrsFkg&fid=0x0:0x43f58ed58d130d5f"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Meral","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZgJDSBQQNKp8dP0oLNQ0hDG3ysmSYlwA2fle373dORaWJmgoR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The staff here is unbelievably rude and condescending . I have never heard from any of the Starbucks stores that I couldn’t get a refill from a Venti Matcha tea latte for a simple  tall black tea while i was sitting there in tbe store. It was my first time in this store and I just assumed she was having a bad day but doesn’t mean she could be condescending.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darcey Kaspick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOtaBFZwINbXq2e7vHEzuMhGJcmm-gQI1RQ-yFD5cs8tN4AU6T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A friend took us there to treat us for drinks on a Friday and said we were the for the promo of 25% off  cold drinks. Instead of being welcoming the cashier, Chris was abrasive. He said there was no such deal. When our friend presented the promo from her Starbucks app he still was saying there was no promo. Thankfully another worker, Maddy came over and told him it was and how to process it. He was reluctant and then did it and then rudely proceed to blame on it an American Starbucks app. He never bothered to say sorry for not being familiar with the promo. We felt very unwelcomed and not impressed considering he is the first contact person there. Maddy was the only thing that made the difference.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Carlos Ajoy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj56wBY1xLPQ20bqQNpwgjeSO2V5tNX7g2abXXBavTb3s8Iinv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently visited Eggstatic and tried their bubble tea and waffles. The bubble tea was delicious and refreshing. The waffles were also quite good, but I found that the flavor can become a bit overwhelming after a while. Because of this, one portion of waffles can easily be shared between two people. The overall experience was pleasant, and the staff were friendly and efficient. I would definitely recommend this place for a nice snack and a drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQZ8QL1bXxltK_NMhZt8wQVN3wQZQeLedgi0py&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"kawaii hatchiko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLtom4JJghW2UnkOsI7GKr-J96yxZfSX4SBdkTaAQaNBfKVBVT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Bubble waffles lacking flavour. Drinks as well. We ordered the honeydew slush and milk tea as well as regular bubble waffle.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJqqFXgzEzN1pYWavO_pVak3N6dMe7YW3qal5k&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Joey Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIncJBLfbVzRO24PRdfxE4-hovZn6C_s4RV_vqsGslULP8YEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They have the better egg waffle in the Greater Vancouver Area. Their quality is fairly constantly. I think I only had one time that egg waffle was not that great but just okay.

I tried this Christmas special before the Christmas season. It was quite special and tasty. Its price was the high end side, so it was a special treat for myself.

They also offer drink, but I am usually
here just for the egg waffle.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoiCCQxjAlR-il0qPt2q7ACeLx7peCkR_L8gEc&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Flo Lii","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtRnz3GaTcevfTQqnG6soE-sT_V-eROwUBjNwbiFxrdvUuqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As the egg-waffle chef lovingly (I’m assuming) spread the Portuguese egg tart filling into the waffle iron, I was already drooling.

We went to Eggtastic after lunch planning to order the OG egg waffle but the Portuguese waffle caught our eye so we got that along with a Hojicha Milk Tea with pearls ($6.50) - 30% sweet was just right. I liked that they had a non-caffeinated tea option.

After a 5-6 minute wait, the egg waffle was piping hot and ready. I’m glad we got some photos because we inhaled it in about 60 seconds. The outside was crispy while inside each bubble was some sweet (but not too sweet) and hot fresh egg custard. I don’t know much about food trends or if Portuguese egg waffles are a thing but if they aren’t, they should be!

It’s a bit pricey at $7.25 but I’m already planning on when to go again and this time I don’t plan to share!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrFKMw-nyqgTky0JfhmptKqXDEDKaINvQaDCW6&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2023-9-20"},{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is rare to go to Crystal Mall, and found out this on the lower level, and it has bubble tea and Hong Kong Style Egg Crepes.

The crepes are in Heart shapes, it was very nice and delicious.

The bubble tea was very good as well.

They have daily special too, remember to look for the sign in front of the store.

They have couple combos that have the hong kong style crepes with bubble tea.

It is very nice and would recommended to everyone to have a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM27w_2bYrrscdIIO6WxPBupM4l1-TiP3C8E0Ze&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"Winnie ThePooh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb2RrdHMIPUzUgI4nwzJWm1ScRCOhwLujq204SDkdRG6DBkgAt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious matcha mochi bubble waffles. Excellent texture. Just the right amount of depth of matcha-ness and a mochi in every bubble.

Also appreciate their hygienic food handling by using a clean glove to place the mochi in the waffle pan.  Probably can be done with a spoon and chopsticks, but at least they did not use a gloved hand that touch everything to touch food, like another place that we tried.

Two thumbs up.  We wanted to try the Portuguese custard bubble waffles, but it was already sold out on the days that we went to get it.  Next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0U0obSVV7gaZg9j6_6ITKqqpKGQ9bUzi_sb8_&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Cindy Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6jlJ2-_-6GHAppZsg7B4koHj8fbUdf_fVuTHQwAItU4JSFfPc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Do not order matcha mochi bubble waffle, it’s mostly tasteless with a bit of sugar flour flavour. I am very unimpressed with it. I have not tried their classic Hong Kong flavour yet, but not sure I will give another chance.

When I came in to order the classic bubble tea, the store also ran out of bubble. I’ve never had a bubble tea store run out of bubble before. So again, very unimpressed with their store.

Lastly, the order took much longer than I expected.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhJpR57VJJ8LiQoHvXfywkAJe98hvElwH0AcRN&fid=0x0:0x82e882dec7402aa2"],"When":"2020-9-26"},{"Name":"J M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_zGAMOi7_Krrx5NX5BJ9UVs_EJI5hzWeZwPdr6_X5_p0_KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This business starts closing their day about 30 mins before closing time so go early or you will experience disappointment. We were there at 6PM (business hours show 6:30 as closing time) and they told us they weren't selling egg waffles because it takes a while to clean.  I think management should schedule them extra time so that the staff can begin cleaning when the store is closed - not when their store is still open. Not cool.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Selina Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl1Xdwkrhcn348KF_kAAKRb07OtRHuXqFNqAaHShsjdgXloDJaXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We googled the restaurants around south Burnaby and found this treasury. The place is small. It was a raining and cold day. Only two people inside but we imagined that it’ll be busy during working hours or brunch hours.

We ordered chicken enchiladas and Burrito. The size is big, taste good. Definitely will come again to try their brunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_BKG0xTw0QqMqFEEbJbVwULGWlP3EkP6Wx8cb&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Erik Leong (gd6noob)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFn08Dkw-Vc2VUS4RFPPEWldYIwPrAvH4xtkXnIoGrVB2Is6a4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cozy little cafe and the food tasted great. Definitely worth a visit if you have never been here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY288kvmFFHIs25VtN_6BMJCT7reO11MImjzTg&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"What a lovely joint tucked in a business complex. We came for brunch and it didn’t disappoint, we got there around 10 on a Sunday morning and no one was there. Then around 11 am it got really busy! The baha fish taco was perfectly crispy and flavourful but not greasy.

The big breakfast burrito was huge and the Benedict’s came with 3 poached eggs, tater tots and coleslaw. The kids didn’t like the coleslaw much since it was bitter. But everything was cooked and flavoured well.

We will need to visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDDM5eLhqxO80lgLZxF1fXfEMgMtKs6NW-ewy-&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-4-7"},{"Name":"Emilia Muirragui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVbrBdWMJwAdDmTKF2rqn3OE2f7BKVf4ff7Eui90G41UPNKe7l=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a little hidden gem and I love that about this place. I haven't tried any of the food just yet, but I've bought a couple of drinks and bakery items and they've all been pretty good. I personally recommend the Hibiscus Water (Agua de Jamaica) - it was SO refreshing and it's so rare to find that it was a lovely surprise!
The staff is very friendly, but are usually quite busy which can make interactions feel brief and sharp at peak hours. There is plenty of seating space and the music is great. Would highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJsSj-DZsV05SxRqB5Htj9yFMlSlNgqg20UNB9&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Jade S-T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt8D3Wbam1mlvwn8z7VPlAaeVuiJetfJ4opr154dNUfSfiD-sJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super cute little cafe with super yummy food and unique drinks! I loved the smoked salmon eggs benny (3 eggs!!) and my sister enjoyed the chilaquiles. But be careful with the chilaquiles, they were a little spicy for us! But we’re not spice people. Bright and inviting space with friendly staff. Highly recommend, will be back for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFkXxCx4B4-e2_RNo_X-5u-Be7mJTbxWjoS4f-&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-4-29"},{"Name":"Diandra Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrV3qPJoVEtA9rkDz4RRCP6sOJp9qqBiWsoaOl1V_rtuqFD07TKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am beating myself up for not trying this place sooner! This place is GREAT. After spending a fortune at Lucky Taco at River Distinct last weekend, I would rather go here ten times over. The portions are excellent for the pasta and very flavourful. We were here for when they had the Bites of Burnaby going on - three courses for $35. We got the tortilla soup, three tacos and a craffle. The soup was so good man. Super hearty. Tacos had double fajitas so you can make them into six tacos.

Atmosphere is so cute. Love all the custom painted murals and portraits of local scenic spots along the Fraser River.

Customer service is absolutely on point. The girl at the front has the best customer service I’ve seen in a while.

Will be back many many more times :) to try for brunch next.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuwYA7I7Z5fMZMgU-1N0OQebGFd6yxEsNc2_Cz&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-3-29"},{"Name":"Vancouver Foodie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8w6jkWQhHhs1Z246avVvoKQqrR4N6KZDvvFaklq629YACSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Little hidden gem in the industrial area for a great brunch.

Ordered their eggs benedicts and it was great.  They also have a lot of taco selections if you love tacos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7OzHDBrOupLvFCHGDWWxnCTQn6IMBD-L_eo2v&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"M L'Esperance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZqUBTP-65WyvMXDylpShFuRceNg0tDp5M3yyClpT9KjBeCmg4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We stopped for Sunday brunch to try out a new place for breakfast/brunch. It was not too busy and we were able to order pretty quickly. Friendly service!
I ordered the Chilaquiles and my wife got the Classic Eggs Benedict. The food did not take long to come to the table, but the sides on my plate were not very warm, I would have preferred them hotter. The flavours however were excellent. The beans rich and tasty, the rice spiced nicely for flavour. I asked for eggs medium poached and that’s how they were done. The eggs were fairly hot so it seems maybe the sides sat for a while and cooled before the eggs were done and went on the plate last. The home made hot sauces were also very tasty.
The Benedict was a bit unusual, the Hollandaise sauce was not the usual type but was made in house and tasted good just different.
We will come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRy4-H-qy_pvyIPPpwXDYpl8LgqE2RbmKQlGPr&fid=0x0:0x3bfdaebc3898d562"],"When":"2023-10-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Marina Shcherbakova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyLcc8GZsJdQZpxpX6MKq7M68TDSvo70nMESQn_e-1N4B3YVk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Three stars for this coffee shop. While the food offerings like the chicken pesto sandwich, lemon loaf, and cappuccino were just average, nothing particularly wowed me. The lukewarm cappuccino was a bit of a letdown, and the self-service pickup system could use some improvement—I almost missed my sandwich sitting on the counter. On the bright side, the place has a cozy atmosphere with stylish furniture, fitting well into the community vibe it aims for. Plus, the spacious layout and large tables make it a great spot for group gatherings. However, the parking situation can be a hassle. Although there's a lot in front of the community center, it tends to be busy, so be prepared to circle around to find a spot. Overall, it's a decent place to hang out, but don't expect to be blown away by the food or service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyTeLhpKCdLV7thF7OvpRPe2Yl0R5X2zNHPX3O&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Josephine Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4ctBP8R2rm9S8Aa5NyuULMapTvyTQYakS6AvI9Cd025oSy86H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One would never guess that you could find such wonderful eats inside a community centre of all places and yet that's where we got this incredible Lobster Melt sandwich and Chocolate Lava Cake! Situated inside Christine Sinclair Community Centre is Bastion Coffee + Kitchen. I couldn't believe it when I read that they served a Lobster Melt sandwich, and that it was only $8.95. At that price, what did we have to lose? Wow, this Lobster Melt was no joke! It was affordable and delicious. My husband and I agreed to share a Lobster Melt sandwich with each other, but it only took about two bites at most for him to decide that he wanted to buy another one so that he could have it all to himself!

The Chocolate Lava Cake was also quite impressive. It's always so satisfying to see that soft, gooey chocolate centre spilling out when I cut through the middle of a molten lava cake. I have had better Chocolate Lava Cakes than this, but for a $5.95 cake from a community centre cafe, this was really nicely done!

Would you come and try out this hidden gem?

Service: Good
Parking: Plentiful and free
Location: 3713 Kensington Ave., Burnaby, BC","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYIkIqejMvzGzV560ES6M95X3OnfCrlnMOIUdj&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"Sarah Kosari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRKJF1Yntnp-zRLmumvc9e-i3Wwazxmkif9r_MkSiD9JZJ8ngfpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Indulge in a truly delightful experience at this charming coffee shop, where you'll find the most delicious and aromatic coffee roasted right on-site. Whether you're looking to kickstart your day or take a much-needed break from work, this place has it all. Among their tempting offerings, the sandwiches stand out as the ultimate comfort food. Trust me when I say that the Turkey bacon sandwich is an absolute winner, with its mouthwatering combination of savory turkey, crispy bacon, and delectable ingredients that will leave your taste buds in awe.

What sets this coffee shop apart is its hidden gem status, nestled within the Christian Sinclair Community Centre. It's a place that locals hold dear, a little secret oasis of culinary delights. The warm and friendly staff make you feel right at home from the moment you step through the door, providing excellent service and ensuring your visit is nothing short of fantastic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2DNwfdEUwF2I2IoLoSZd-Wg-lCus0WWOTED7-&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2023-5-13"},{"Name":"JB K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWly2PKypJ4esl-D83GYkWwd-9Yh4K8DViyxJnf76i-vR26b6kW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"quality pastries.  good collection of espresso drinks to order from.  labeling in cups and beans look result great.   space and parking are very nice. how works well.  very much like this cafe!!  service was also excellent.   will return definitely","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWGZc09yR1vstNuaefoTCLYr1ec8F0BpYk-tZM&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2022-8-1"},{"Name":"Abdallah Ouda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDCxH2dBsdWhzi2rHa8CpgxoxKgmmdnEjFmKfe7rf3St_1zWrb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reasonable prices and delicious food. Oat milk cappuccino was so good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt304lyenVGppPz1Q2qSadB8ReqyB9loDm7OF0&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Vancouverite111","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjCLNB8OHposl1jn_syPr10S-VZ7DlTNmaTgV5nPF1IIbSNwkU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A nice public place for having a bite and a local delicious coffee.

Pros :

- amble parking.

- drop in activities in the centre for adults and kids.

- nice atmosphere.

- luxurious tables and chairs.

- opens 7 days a week.

- very close to burnaby park facilities

Cons: (hardly found any thing I would complain about)

- they close at 7 pm, would be nice if they stayed a bit longer at night especially on weekends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIH51Lp4htRUAqv5uS0y-84ENbTaVRsNOdcLwL&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2022-5-27"},{"Name":"Elsa Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgBtFYCkWTkjtefII4egxADlhVRhaG7pRnzQoESC-LbjFzCviaGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love this cafe that is located inside the community centre. The coffee is decent (price is a bit high), the pastries are good, the service is not bad. Overall, good cafe!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAbQwS_tm6HIaoEWq4oJmr1ZURrFLJ-HFYe-Cz&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2022-12-6"},{"Name":"J W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo-Cmrc1HZduOPETsbTPLkBkL6YnB-OGT_-IXnca5j7zZRJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Unexpected gem for a cafe in a community centre. The vibe is on point for a feeling of something classic from the decor, taste of coffee to the smooth jazz music.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYqYuHtWPcj3HB5FVU-w7zBdpphX4QAa_MlugC&fid=0x0:0x442073c957d1721"],"When":"2024-5-29"}]

[{"Name":"Sandy Y. (CameraGourmet)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQ9J8ig1HwUQBJbXRdKDIwR0OrTw3YtQtyHDEaRuCN8XnUDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We recently visited ZUBU at their Metrotown location to satisfy our ramen cravings while shopping at the mall.  This spot is conveniently located outside the mall, right across from Walmart and next to the parking area, making it super accessible.

We are regular members of ZUBU and are familiar with their Happy Hour menu, which usually offers excellent variety and value.  The food and service at this location were consistent with the standards we've experienced at other ZUBU spots.  However, we were slightly disappointed with the ramen noodles — they were soft and overcooked. This was unexpected since ZUBU typically delivers on quality.  We also noticed a steady stream of takeout orders, which may have impacted the kitchen's focus.

On a brighter note, we redeemed our ZUBU rewards points for their 5-piece Crispy Chicken and Pan-Fried Pork Gyoza, both of which were delicious!  If you're a fan of ZUBU, downloading their app is a must — it’s an easy way to earn rewards and enjoy perks during every visit.

Overall, ZUBU Metrotown is a decent option for a casual bite during a shopping trip, but we hope they can improve consistency, especially with their ramen.

📝📝

Food: 🍜🍜🍜 Can Try!
Service: 👩‍🍳👩‍🍳👩‍🍳👩‍🍳
Kids: 👶👶👶👶 Yay!  The kid’s menu has various kinds of food.
Price: 💲 $20-$30 spend each person (Happy Hour)
Presentation: 📷📷
Parking:  🚗🚗🚗🚗 Free parking available in the mall parking lot, but it is not easy during busy time or shopping season.
Tips:
📝 can get a free hand roll when signing up for their ZUBU app.
📝 serve Happy Hour Sunday-Thursday from 2-5 PM and 9 PM-close.
📝 can join the ZUBU app to rack up points and make your visits even more rewarding.
📝 have an outdoor patio in warmer weather.
Would I Return: Yes 👱‍♀️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJMzWgerMFMhfJSINDtkCitgohgEn_lV5uWMgm&fid=0x0:0xd3b9dc93123922f"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a chain restaurant which has another location in downtown. The food was about what I expected compared to what we had in downtown. The ramens were still very good. But brussel sprout tempura was a bit disappointing because it wasn’t seasoned enough for me, and there wasn’t any sauce. But the truffle fries were quite tasty and would love to have it again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMu59sIZKAiGrVUZje7A6y8qa3JOMM5aWSdQMyX&fid=0x0:0xd3b9dc93123922f"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Oceanid S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILFoBYTPTB6JAB2W82GMAbE1dVJUby3rG9nTZ9Q57ut0Ti-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Service is on the slower side even though the restaurant is half empty. Some of the servers were just on their phones. But when they do attend, they are friendly and courteous.

Food portions: Husband had the ramen set which came with a mini size ramen (set type), an Appy and desert (ice cream) good value if you are a small eater.

I had the ramen flight as I was interested to try the different ramen types. Individual portions are even smaller than a mini and the cumulative size of all three is probably similar to that of a mini ( by weight/volume) which doesn't seem to be worth the price as I could get a regular sized ramen for cheaper. See picture of empty bowls for size comparison between mini and those in the flight ( keep in mind that the it's typically filled to slightly below the zubu word on the bowl and that is the narrowest parts of the bowl which creates an optical illusion that it's alot larger than it actually is). Most But good option for those that just can't choose.

Taste wise:
Tonkotsu soup was a let down. Not much bone broth flavour. Noodles were good. Not much toppings. Mainly soup and noodles so we were both hungry not long after.

Overall: Being located in Metrotown.. I'd rather go elsewhere for good ramen. Cute atmosphere for those that like to combine alcohol/ modern bar vibes and ramen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZzKw-JdSi2n8BpmuzjymdJqA9rayZp0wVCNr7&fid=0x0:0xd3b9dc93123922f"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Jayson J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh5xePACHGFMrujGyu-HBmelU_P6fuccz4VSAVxS0935C9YQ3k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"2024 update: ⭐️⭐️

[{"Name":"HYEIN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUNyZrmLJeqYX_sTsyo3T3b-P6Te7oShhYK7RSRPBvIDN5QyY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this cafe💗💗 (한국분들 산미 없고 고소한 커피 여기예요!!!) every time the boss and staff are always kind and coffee flavor is also perfect!! And desserts are also cheap. I ordered chicken panini, and super delicious! Please Long live the business😆","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5J52O0AipaWkt7ZgS365fhHEQhSTM9iHMPvbE&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"ARSHDEEP BRAR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-1Tv9-EDl2oD-vznzqIuasHzQz2h5a_Lo9apRS2kk4M0uw8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This my second time and again its really good place to study and have some coffee with a perfect meal. Really like the people who work here one guy and girl. They provide me the best customer service😊 thank you 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZg5XqY4sSwraBHpH4wcVJXFhIrpFi5b24IYgk&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Tommy Byun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQhlW94B8T2fhww-HWh0iFh-RYIvFitfF4mjJX2E5t_heAv3Lb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I decided to check this place out on aa Saturday afternoon after a friend's recommendation & good reviews on the owner being super friendly & food being amazing. I didnt get to try the food, but just 2 drinks, so I will review on the drinks only today. Possible update on the next visit.

We ordered cold brew vanilla cream & tiramisu latte. The cream topping on both drinks were less sweet than similar drinks that you would get at starbucks, which was a plus. However, the cold brew itself was rather bland compared to other cold brews I had before. Because of that, I liked tiramisu latte more than cold brew vanilla cream.

The inside was surpringsly quiet & cozy, whereas I thought it would be pretty loud & busy located right in front of a busy street. It was quite relaxing while we were there.

I dont know who the owners are exactly, but I had a rather different experience with the service. Considering the numerous reviews commenting on their utmost service, the staff we dealt with provided just a bare minimum service we had, rather subpar. We said thank you as we left, and the lady staff barely said thank you back.

I would visit again to check out their food & other drinks, as well as to check out that their level of service lives up to others' reviews.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPC9w_hO3thKKQQlQ0jkDZgv4t6t-EPVaZ0LcwC&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Dana Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQIw-0oOUNgoyniYugTscGkgpKJS8tpx4V0tAajn3ZGkNIfqEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delightful delightful place. A quiet environment with soothing music, very clean with tables wiped down after each customer. Customers were mixed in age and ranged from laptop users to families/couples chatting. The man who took my order was very kind.
A range of tempting pastries and sandwiches were on display. I chose the butter paneer wrap, a slice of strawberry NY cheesecake, and a strawberry matcha bubble tea. The wrap was huge! The filling was very flavourful, spicy but not extremely "hot". The cheesecake was very dense, which is definitely the right way to do a NY cheesecake but after the paneer wrap it was almost too much for me... that's my own fault for not thinking through what I was ordering. I really liked the strawberry topping, which tasted like homemade strawberry jam with big strawberry slices. The strawberry matcha also was great, it had a nice layer of sweet and vibrant strawberry compote on the bottom, which combined nicely with the unsweetened matcha for a balanced taste. $22 total, which was a good price for a hefty serving of quality food.
If I come back, which I'm very tempted to, I will have to try one of their housemade cookies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6twCj7ekvrl2jXMCKnEtyTwgvnHTGzTjzpGlX&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Stella Oh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvqyQ2KS_YIN6XYOMkDtQZO2ezjEJLWRODsOzNFIWuIhCYtAL-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I stopped by out of curiosity. We've only tried the iced americano, but I've got to say, they know how to make a mean iced americano! It was seriously so good! I can't wait to come back to try their other drinks.

The owners greeted us with wide smiles when we entered and walked out. That's not something you see every day. I sincerely hope their business continues to grow and flourish in this neighbourhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBpDteIlLwj-mtqkTnijPeXV8IVbKK-TbCHxjk&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Anna Armitage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW167LDjPh-2gRccaMmZlISBWI2l2wuI5r0DAJu_qnguqLBPsLN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic first visit. Coffee was good and the apple fritter delicious. Service was excellent and super friendly. Lovely atmosphere on a Sunday afternoon. Worth returning to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane (Dineoutwithdee)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJfHVJSjIKAcPEXNIfUcWAtOeYHaXavqJYPtVJZ3lhCbCbpeo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful coffee shop that serves up good coffee and tasty food! I have tried their box cakes and oat latte and really enjoyed them! The cakes are made in-house (like everything else) and make a really great treat that’s easy to take home or gift to someone!

Their menu also listed bubble tea and a bunch of other sandwiches and goodies that I must go back for. What a great addition Ruka Coffee is! If you’re looking for a new coffee shop to check out, give them a try. Their space is also nice and bright and conveniently located on E Broadway and Nanaimo!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQwrxganVffJJFFStwWnGwpoTKEX0PotYpPqJx&fid=0x0:0x6c89ce2572269409"],"When":"2021-9-3"},{"Name":"Cathy Si","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDlpRs03x4WI6FNSeNA-oTAUFMvmlM6SYwbJfP7MWuWEQU_hU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to this cafe after summer school with my friends a few times, and it has been a great experience each time! The cafe owners are incredibly kind with their greetings, and their service is amazing. I had their earl grey cookie and their matcha latte, which were both the perfect consistency. This place is also the perfect spot for studying. My friends and I will definitely be coming back and I would love to try their matcha cookie!!!

P.S. Thanks for the free freezies on such a hot day!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Thomas Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUITuDRjw9J9Us45xAUXKSfp8lG2sJ2s04TW_lNAi_G6a5d62ur=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I thought the food was very tasty and had good value. The wait took a while. We waited about 45 mins for a table for four. The only dish I didn’t enjoy was the fried rice. It was very average that’s all. The chow mein noodles were excellent and so was were the chow fun noodles. They had a delicious smoky flavour. Service was fine. I would go back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-oJnSAc9ML1779Ft_0B4RRAE5QJioTXfTQh4i&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid HK Style cafe with your usual Cantonese “fast food” menu. Breakfast set combos are an excellent choice here. Can be pretty popular on weekend mornings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOG_y0SjmZQRmyV2F1q94KSBhAyQ_b6YAsfdkMY&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Karen Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVy7IKDgoBu5-GpgCOSD4cGeZrgQ2WNTZ5s54ZY-vysf5NoRKzIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid Hong Kong restaurant, they have system for a getting where you get a number ticket from the machine and look on the screen for it to announce your number to get seated.

It’s nice they close at 8pm on Sundays even though the mall closes at 7pm. Eat dinner here after going shopping.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoxDD5gWqSz7vJYwVKctZgNn80yGxnukWzEMvE&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2023-8-13"},{"Name":"Thedishdetective Lala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD_tj6k6xpF8R8uVmPtHQuGBgjvefVOKaKmqeE1mkWnmvdyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The Boss Restaurant
Located in : Metropolis at Metrotown
Address : 4700 Kingsway, Burnaby, BC V5H4M5

**Satay Beef Soup**
The satay beef soup is good, with a rich and flavorful broth that pairs well with the tender beef slices. Definitely a comforting dish.
8/10

**Oyster Congee**
The oyster congee is thick and creamy, making it a hearty option. The oysters are fresh and plentiful, adding a pleasant brininess to the dish. 8/10

**Omelet**
The omelet is decent, featuring a generous amount of mushrooms. However, it could benefit from a bit more seasoning to enhance the overall flavor. 7/10

**Satay Skewer**
I was very disappointed with the satay skewer. The lamb pieces were too large and tough, and the lack of seasoning made the dish quite bland. 2/10

**Lamb**
The lamb is juicy and flavorful, though the portion size is somewhat thin. It’s well-seasoned, which makes it enjoyable, but the accompanying vegetables were bland and lacked seasoning. 7/10

**Service**
The service is poor and inattentive staff, which detracts from the dining experience.

**Ambience**
The restaurant is located inside a mall, which gives it a casual vibe. The place is okay, but nothing special.

The pricing is affordable, making it a reasonable choice for a quick meal. 2/5

**Verdict**
Despite some disappointments, I would consider coming back due to the extensive menu. There are many other dishes I’m curious to try, and hopefully, the overall experience will be better next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1uWFVQ8Lva418-2QHdbHfgLTovwv0gVQbdkAf&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"chan Cindy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaeOXV6kT2G98yuvkhh00Ns9a0SyZ7N-CPIvk93SlbI2dHg53blA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was very disappointed. I know me and my friend may have chat late till 21:50, while i only left half cup of my ice lemon tea. The staff spray detergent the table next to me madly and spread all over my left arm, while my lemon tea is near my left hand, means that detergent is all into my cup.

Staff was keep asking like third time whether we make our decision on our order in 5 mins. What a bad dinning experience.👎🏻👎🏻👎🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhm9qmm5j1L1aS0IPnVJIYKTl2OR6aXEo--Tok&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"mlvn cgndhn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyQ_4N38tzwgbvk9ME_YzYZifN3k2gci6ujiPZVaKX59iCiCObxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A friend brought me here for he first time and I like it! Service was fast, food was good and staff are friendly. It can be very busy during lunch hours but I’d say it’s worth it. You should try this place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTvT7CGYZ21YC0r6CVAFvcwVMCyCY4RdCRsujj&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Stephen Chiu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyvDfgr2u_SVXCbenwncr5m_lbx3hXSedpR8trbIomLSD6ruw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The Boss offers a clean, modern updated setting. The food is decent and is always served quickly. And the portions have gotten better again over the past year. The breakfast combos and set menu specials remain a good value even with the price increases.

This is a popular restaurant, so wait times can be long when the mall is busy. And they still only take cash payment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHtxyuNpxW-VKvReIrSX9rnrIszGOg8Yj-LLs6&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2022-9-24"},{"Name":"Gina Quinton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq6uKuQsbshnOEVlh-dC_O3MizvtB4chDBDbFcE3ubI9518w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decent Cantonese food and service is depending on the day just like a woman's mood. This visit our tea cups were constantly being filled. Thank you. Price is worthy because the portion is huge. I'm especially impressed by the clam with black bean sauce. I enjoyed our visit with my friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1iC-2tLeVi-srhJIiJ2Dh39jbMA5UiLzOlchh&fid=0x0:0xc1f6ac8a64b53386"],"When":"2022-6-4"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Yina Gao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW49Hy6Bp8pgGjMI1XWIH9uReM84LVSL1N5nI7rtyE5exbaPXix=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious cup of coffee, so happy I was able to find a well balanced cup after craving one and going to quite a few meh cafes in the Vancouver area during my stay here :) Very cozy and quiet atmosphere, perfect to do some studying/work :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPat-K8_NpOu-cpiCSAmWZVyLuRMjG-Ec8Euxcb\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Zelda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYDa9MsXj-ICvwW_hwqh-GHSWiDMqwu8Za_3wuFz1DE9IB99aK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Coffee is superior quality, it’s definitely noticeable. Would recommend that you check out this spot over a typical Starbucks. I got an iced caramel macchiato, way too sweet for my liking but I forgot to say half sweet. The taste of the coffee itself was really good. I got a chocolate croissant and it wasn’t that good, buttery croissant but weird type of mild chocolate drizzle on top. Other bakery goods looked good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOq_CCdvmt6ZLdQ18TSKVQE3_c4-cuRiNfMwjeV\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice and cozy, lovely atmosphere. I ordered an iced chai which was so delicious and refreshing. Parking around it is tough, very few spots on the street and all 1h, if you’re not lucky to find one you’ll have to go around and park a bit far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYr0p8YRDFKjOB7f6QndvwJUMpJEdV0kF6O5pk\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Small quiet coffee shop that roasts their own beans. Americano was all right and their baked goods were fresh. The only issue I had was with their service. It gets a bit awkward when you walk in and are standing at the front counter but the baristas see you and don’t address you. We were standing for a good 3-5min before the barista finally came up to serve us.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuY8NcxbBBOIeDOgADyPM8gQKaA7vX_dHYzyyK\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Karen W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZZPfpr3QNA42Rvf5GRma8e9wVZe75RxS8Wiz-RehL8Z3PSw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a nice coffee shop. Great atmosphere.  London fog was delicious. Very reasonable prices","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPbfz1KFg3_aYnTQS3Jeksa5XX0nrMEDcR67iD\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Hamed Soltani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJJZvsAhr4w9D1t84C4qF44R0bN-d5cVp4LaJ8auICZqpChXPs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I found this coffee shop near my work and wanted to try it out. I tried to call, but there was no connection. When I got there, I immediately enjoyed the charming and relaxing interior design. I ordered a couple of the savary pastries and an iced hazelnut late. I usually don't drink flavored coffee, but this one was sooo good I went back for another the next day. The pastries were just okay, had a lot of room for improvement, but the coffee tasted amazing! I could see the coffee is roasted there, so most probably that's why it was so good. I will definitely go back to try their esspresso as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFpVieX_7OQn6q_dhBPDsFtQLq57ZiP4HNGqr4\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2023-8-10"},{"Name":"Da Wanderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gUX2zsQKdIE8uVzYWBnKKtvYQAJfEKJppzMJqd4hE4TuUun8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What I love most about this coffee place is the cozy and aesthetic atmosphere. It is very quiet in the mornings and I love to sip my coffee while chilling out watching the beauty of Fall across the street. Their cofee is tasty and tasted like premium blend. I still haven't tried their cookies which I've heard are good. So I will keep on coming back to this place for sure. It is a lovely place to catch up and have a chitchat with someone close.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO47bUzVRxV3LRMAlkVGcnqpEp38s7fpOPvVpPD\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2022-11-1"},{"Name":"GREGORY WELLMAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAW-s39raxpX32XWGDc3RqF-M7I0dQKwlbBPlBwLcZxi7lzkq1Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a gem! To be fair, I wasn't quite expecting a city-center quality coffee shop right here, but here it is! The owners were friendly and respectful, the flat white was perfect (no need for an extra shot-always a good sign). I tried a croissant and it was delish- even though it was later in the day. The design and space were also great, and very relaxing. I've been back twice now. Recommend for sure!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMP0FBV_ywjtdr_vVRMfw6z7nlKtxIvgwFpwVw_\u0026fid=0x0:0x169f315d6c757c61"],"When":"2023-9-13"}]

[{"Name":"Hillbillytc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV833YeKMKJfxtYeKhRHVRSrikZoFOcCapKBwyEFBOnxiCMeXAZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere is a little loud during rush hr. The   food was okay a little salty. Lots of GF options. Charlotte was amazing. She really knew about food allergies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjgDRMHYhBVv-aah-OeLTGeqPMr1GwRvKTHi7N&fid=0x0:0xb774fd12cddbe3f5"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"The Wandering Pianist (Lee)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUBZsAZ9EIBNq_deJHz3XkOMnrx0qKLTX4AxUFQWwPgJ7rvtDl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was great, the service was fast, and the ambiance was A-okay. Special shout-out  to Ayushi for looking after us. She explained the menu very well, patiently answered our questions, and  checked on us. A great asset to the food industry!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcXjF-xt8y-1PPkpnECYUzjEmeaZ8lAAKvnQFo&fid=0x0:0xb774fd12cddbe3f5"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Enrico Buenaventura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC-_JhiSZzA_lg6KL0xNy2Misew0rTke-JdRRIj1tbTzVbK8tN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A must visit whenever I am in the greater Vancouver area. First time in this location. A compromise but perfect location between downtown Vancouver and Langley for a small gathering for a lunch chat.
Had craving for the clam chowder and a bacon mushroom burger with fries. But a colleague ordered a strawberry milkshake and on a hot day, that seemed like a really good idea. Unashamedly ordered same.
The place was not crowded and the service was relaxed but staff were very friendly and responsive. Food was what I expected and remembered.
Facility was accessible and washrooms looked well maintained and clean albeit felt a bit dark. Though it seems to fit with the overall design of the restaurant.
The booth was reasonably comfortable but recall them to be a tad more roomy. This maybe more related to my increasing girth over the years than the furnitures themselves. Appreciated the thoughtful details with the hooks to hang a jacket or walking canes for example.
The staff let us linger awhile and just chat and reconnect. This was very much appreciated.

Cravings met. Expectations met. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl2DHDSKR1uuJkmxvKLaG8ZXqou_IbbCBHhV_F&fid=0x0:0xb774fd12cddbe3f5"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Amit Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQ4BWWOt-MFNnYLuIrS2NwWeJ6KyjNkjkl1nXIyIhTmr_T7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent all around service.  If your looking for beverage suggestions or something to snack on, my server Charlotte was very helpful in my past few visits. Manager Michelle is always greeting customers with a warm smile 😊  If you need a sporting events up on tube, don't be shy, ask Michelle!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbQ9h_xFkDKV5MugBtHSZVcfdrFsOlw5vrdYFY&fid=0x0:0xb774fd12cddbe3f5"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed a lovely family dinner here - delicious food, friendly service, and overall great experience! [{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem. Stumbled upon this place because I had a meeting. The Korean food here is legit as are the sandwiches and fries (they are very addictive!). Everything is made fresh so they can accommodate a variety of dietary needs.

The owners are super friendly and go the extra mile. The seating is basically shared seating with the school and there’s always ample room.

The portions are very good. The spicy pork on rice was especially good and much cheaper than anywhere else.

Definitely not on the beaten path, but if you’re in the mood for lunch and willing to take a quick drive definitely check this place out.

Protip: You have to pay for parking on the street.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtlHqahc6sGi7684OYN9hTPX35k9hbPcv-0YUK&fid=0x0:0xe414e2be58e8336b"],"When":"2023-4-28"},{"Name":"Sarah L. Had Cafe Namu catering individual lunch kits to our womens group lunch and it was perfect. I had the Chicken BLT and it was delish! Will definitely be ordering again for other events! [{"Name":"Niroz Shrestha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJghDn9Kb2GCoIggtbpTwWJGmiIzjHwDY5-gKsGAKuT6FKBTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My gf brought a starbucks tumbler which was 30% off. She asked the cashier to confirm if there was 30% discount on the tumbler we want and he confirmed the discount was there on the product. And also my gf wanted to redeem her membership points on top of that which he agreed. After everything my gr paid the bill. But in the bill there was no discount only my gf points were redeemed. And when she went to ask the other cashier and the cashier said we can only do either discount or redeem the points. They looked like they had no idea how to solve this issue. It took them more than 7 minutes to say we can either do discount or redeem points. Being a regular starbucks customer this was one of the most bad customer service. They should have been clear before they bill us. Very very disappointed. This big francise but so poor service.Never coming back to this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBjUuApT8BsCx2EBXHSiWBdDqTofoDlEK1CilM&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Melinda Barringer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMbz2QWFu4QJzdE7n9ProtMkQYFtVCa04KvPw_-0iR8s6QhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My PSL - Extra whip came with 0 whip this morning, super sad 😔 This is how it came, lots of extra room, and no whip even though I’d customized for extra 🥺

Really disappointing considering it costs almost $7 for a Grande.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1j3_fmpTY5WPT6SQLxDya7uOgoHEkBZxRP0R8&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Eva Zia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJp1CScTOq-jdIBVBA-K4f_r74TZU-kRd9MclConVIiSCPfy3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Here

I can't belive someone would put this in the bag
Careless. I can't even get a refund from doordash.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnUbiBi1J09DdyLQdkaz2fKJT3U1LB5QDfa8cq&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"John P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOLEey5pWbPcCOqx9sg-y4vw9M5MDtmVtgnTOrgv66qfBow7F3cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff are very friendly and great. Forgot to tell them that I’m redeeming the rewards they ended up refunding me and made 2 drinks for me","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO57RuPOw4CVGGttxSNLPwpHW-we5gpUxRK_Uxr&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Jas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUc2XzaWoORvCfwmNLRcPylDaR2PbIHKV5pYWFPJfGPffnyOp1arQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to this location many times.
Non of the experience was bad.
This afternoon there was a buy one get one free promotion. I used the mobile order on the app. The app shows it needs 20+ mins. However after I make the order it shows 7-9mins and I couldn’t cancel. Unfortunately, was waiting at the bank for too long. When I finally arrived the shop it’s over 30 mins. The shop was packed of people.
I asked the lady with glasses(she looks like manager) I told her I was late. Even though it was extremely busy, she was still kind and professional.
She asked me to check the counter, I turned around and saw 30-40 cups of drinks on the table.
A staff (his name was Louis) checked with my order, he explained to me my drinks were stolen.
He explained that the system was not functioning, they couldn’t shout down the mobile order function, so the order was overloaded. He went to the manager and tried to help me out. 2mins later he came back and he asked me to show the order details. However my order was complicatedly customized, I felt extremely sorry for making issues for them.
He wrote down the order on a paper bag and give it manager.
5mins later he hand the two cups of drink to me with smile and gentle attitude.
I leave some tips and walked out of the door.
During the whole visit, I was served by a wonderful team with perfect customer service. It’s Friday afternoon, I really appreciate I can enjoy a cup of drink after the long week. Thank you.🥺💖","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzaG75AV-D5crQ3ZzNs7zs3NFsGbFPvNE1WSlq&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Super slow service, I waited 14 minutes for a matcha Latte which is insane. End product also tasted extremely rushed, bland, cold and tasteless.
Avoid this location at all costs, washrooms are also out of order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON2hLnY-T52nuSlFjZK6rRmfGDkIBEsYM9LrbD&fid=0x0:0xa4c0ebde223c331f"],"When":"2022-11-22"}]

[{"Name":"Wonhee Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoCOt5jbxJbvMaUbcfQc3wt3qabbAkIzZYCCUFmiyeVy8J-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New grand opening with a revised menu, items, cost and owners.

Their baked products are made in-house! So it won’t be like Tim’s where you’re out in 30 seconds, but I got 2 drinks and 2 food in <10 minutes. The in-house made cream cheese was to die for, and the servings are huge!! Couldn’t finish my sandwich and packed the rest to-go.

Great atmosphere with cute music, cozy atmosphere, caught up with a friend here and left with full stomachs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOb8YiDI1KmVAhjdNqz8M68SHwiSLjCBlTUtuWt&fid=0x0:0x4c562d0a545796e4"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Lucy Ryu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVlYJAwtyCqvzYzo7JOhYj6ms93lt97z37dpv-F5-XKZIKH0YZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This has become my favorite bagel spot🥯 They offer a variety of bagel flavors, paired with different kinds of cream cheese. The green onion cream cheese is absolutely the BEST! I also loved the iced matcha latte. The staff is friendly, and the recent renovation creates such a cozy atmosphere. Highly recommend👍👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNk_tBT-Rn8xZjipX_FWaDgsWWKaWyr-jhCHF4-&fid=0x0:0x4c562d0a545796e4"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Esther Kwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfdpF7dFCtHdwz3oC_GissPgRLED_4eZuTowrIljNcSr1_Ww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a smoke salmon bagle sandwich with coffee. I can positively say that it was the best coffee ever tasted so far, and the New york style house made bagle was better than the famous bagle shops I ever visited in Canada.
The cafe is very clean and the service was good, too. I packed some bakery goods home, and their blueberry and white chocolate chip scorn were the best, so soft and delicious. Everybody should try!! I got addicted.
I live in Langley, but I will go there often with my friends.
Good luck with new ownership.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVdCHNQgFkA1f7_Yzx12PPEWMJ6WEFw7tTqQ_x&fid=0x0:0x4c562d0a545796e4"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"TJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP67IcecqWmj25EDB9TYR1oWgWdW_kvUh8kXe9Bcllki-tpXa4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We only really come to this little strip mall when we have to pick up a package from the post office, and my goodness do I love those days. BECAUSE OF SEASONS APPLE CAFE. I absolutely love this cafe. It’s a family run business 😍 that serves up fresh, delicious, quality made food and drinks, made with REAL ingredients. Their drinks are what really reeled us in, as they always have seasonal ones (and they’re friken superb), but after finding out they make their own specialty cream cheese for their variety of bagels ~ we were hooked for good. They are such a kind family, I love even just walking into the place. You’re greeted with smiles and hellos, a beautiful quaint seating area, and just overall great vibes. 10/10 I hope this place is in business forever ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXypNQyfJ0ARQVqfii4fNTfTcMFtMIYWx3dgPbqOiXLt057xhtI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little cafe with the nicest staff! Egg sandwich was super fresh and their brioche bread is so soft and fluffy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWFj668bcrngFu3J838zIZ7wXXHgpZh9dFShjI&fid=0x0:0x4c562d0a545796e4"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Brandon Bae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQ-4cwPUiokO54GNq1abke9LRCH3BSDzh-bt7nmNqcFwNyug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The new owners were sweet and welcoming. I really enjoyed their matcha latte, smoked salmon bagel and COOKIES! Prices are reasonable and scrumptious! I could feel the warmth and love as they prepared my food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Ryu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV68zSh1lxB6HsS7074RKXN2GiMmK-sGj_qtzcG2_-NaTsxnD4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Winter Bagel sandwich was sooo good. All bread, baked goods, and cream cheese is made in-house. You can tell because they constantly remake it throughout the day and it comes out piping hot.

Drinks were really creative and delicious!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elaine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3sByrBumaUTi4SsjcCOqzuNL-H25OBzqdKkk5bQB9PSzxRg4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I come here almost every week, the food is so delicious and the service is very friendly.
The vibe of the cafe is perfect for studying or hanging out with friends, with classic music playing or you can sit outside and they  will bring your food out for you.

I have been trying out their Panini menu and always get it with some soup.
They have great price points for their food at high quality. My favourite Panini so far is the Campanola, but all are so crispy and flavourful. While it was creamy and delicious - I can’t speak too much for the price gouge. The location is nice and clean. They offer other items like cookies and loaves (in a refrigerator) but overall the price was enough to do me in. Try it once - great, but I likely won’t skip back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOh6ukktWH6_LakVP_ACa_Q3LkiYdzX3IBik7w-&fid=0x0:0xe79a3a7efbdf13de"],"When":"2023-6-21"},{"Name":"Joey C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVONws43kRXQQZVKUY_4MVYuG_XVH3tG7L-3VGHgoEAT3rINBjk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped in here last night after dinner with the family.  It was a nice walk from the Japanese restaurant we ate at.  The kids all got a kids scoop abut honestly I would just get the regular scoop because for $1 more you get almost double the amount.  Kids scoop is $7 and the regular scoop is $8.  Only complaint is the chairs! They are so cheap feels like it’s going to break.  I’m pretty sure there are already a few chairs broken as we switched a few when we sat down.  Lots of seating chairs inside and very well lite.  Definitely an upscale Galato shop and perfect for that “First Date” 😂

I ordered 4 kids scoop and when I saw the price difference I felt a little ripped off.  So get the regular scoop.  I got the affogato with vanilla ice cream and I enjoyed it.  It was a single shot on a tiny scoop of ice cream to fit in the mug.

Give it a solid 4 star ⭐️

The Strawberry was really Good!!  Give that a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjP_ZxDZd2958bU0qjOJZXQydRnBihiBiMKJBg&fid=0x0:0xe79a3a7efbdf13de"],"When":"2023-8-2"},{"Name":"Danny Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7uIYz7vEyRlzc_sXf7AZKfTfm0JEbWhx8kEmQrYQim7HLQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very creamy delicious gelato - buy 1 get 1 free for kids who dressed up for the Halloween 🎃","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-dt2hIxO4-JdNZemLCUNZ0P2Xi0Wpg5t11udO&fid=0x0:0xe79a3a7efbdf13de"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Zith Yap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoyNVRM4dH3Q0wNOHrEXaw_mPkMvEWUeUxxZD_GXoOM7ucJ2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best! We got the Chocolate Belgian Brownie, Ube, Matcha, and Mango.. Taste soooo good! ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRfTRc9a6zwOCDKMwpWPk8V-zQ_N90DGtn6Nj0&fid=0x0:0xe79a3a7efbdf13de"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7fOULsNBD7ywsif3r5rB-KotQY_oseavKrgE1jKlbkLP31_eI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place knew and not many customers yet I would say. [{"Name":"Da Wanderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gUX2zsQKdIE8uVzYWBnKKtvYQAJfEKJppzMJqd4hE4TuUun8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the matcha goodies in one place! I love their matcha daifuku. It is very soft and smooth. The cheesecake is also good but I am obsessed with the daifuku and the ice cream. I always look forward to my trip tonthe grocery because I always stop for my treats here. Guilty pleasures for a foodie like me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNecmxXSWF14u2NrTu5rf3ohObBrw6tf5Fmf9kR&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had the Yuzu Citron Parfait (with Houjicha) and a friend had the Shiratama Parfait (with Houjicha). Enjoyed the roasted green tea flavour of the soft serve! Nice contrasting textures in the parfait and refreshing on a summer day. With my parfait, it was supposed to include a sakura monaka. However, I just received a regular monaka wafer instead. I'm not sure if the sakura was only seasonal, but it would've been nice if the staff mentioned the substitution given the change to what's in the menu description!

Price point is a tad high at around $11.25, but Tsujiri does use high quality ingredients with their matcha and Japanese green tea. Unfortunately, no seating in the small location, but the wait was short for our order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAZUr3YALKiY8cWiHLqx7JtzvGh_5ZMGPQYvKq&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Fuzzy Nemo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhjGNDhI-RZYgIiVRXnRDEQCiyyP-dsVjb7EhBkcymNr9MvYi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place was not outstanding,  but pretty close.   For a mall quality,  I thought it was very good.  I have gone a few times and feel that the wait for the ice cream was rather long,  especially when there wasn't a whole lot of people, but they were very friendly.  Would go back and try other stuff,  or try their other locations as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaMb968Vv4N3lNqul4_Yv8v_GOJAj1BALDBR8U&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Evan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItqym_b8p4Y-FW9783yYhbbkXgbWq5yo1i3Fyi_bB9_Q1tlIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The matcha soft serve here slaps so hard, more then any other matcha soft serve nearby. It has the perfect texture and level of sweetness , only thing is the price keeps going up , please stop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgwGkj84GQvppMY-UlQihWRYf37VamO9tz-raV&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Ellen Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOLwp1YuZHFAfe5TfBAETM7Gfw006WNpu6CMM0hXfmB4HVpR97=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Everything is pricey and the portions do not seem to correlate, but somehow everyone, including myself keeps going back. For this location, it's a pretty unique store...you can't really find a similar menu elsewhere in the mall. And when you're feeling stuffy in your winter jacket after a few hours of shopping in a crowded mall, their cold drinks and soft serve seem the most inviting thing in the world. I also appreciate their service. The staff seem genuinely passionate about their menu and happy to patiently explain various items to help you choose a drink of choice. Embarrassed as I am to be consuming a modestly sized $8-9 drink, I might just do it again if the opportunity arises.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrEAqR4qQQEK2yzWMVZZUPy2U5TjT4QSmsdeqS&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2022-12-31"},{"Name":"T L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTjGpJOWlNfflTgg48Q0TQwFIEqYhwqYrycQjwBD2MWV9bYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Hojicha latte had no flavour. The milk was also not frothed properly and the hojicha was not whisked long enough. Not worth the $9 price tag.

I would not recommend getting a drink from here.

However I've tried their parfait before and that was really good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMX5C9IcYqrTPbK51tseNvnBzXkEk5XO6z4xSrw&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Angie D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTl2uG_14A-KzOiwcEdOB4qUiCIiQjMr0sBwCPk2QLQTM3zxxp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"dec 20
~1:30pm
I went here to try a japanese matcha drink. The girl working with long split dye hair was very helpful to help me decide what to get, and I ordered a matcha frappe. I’m a long time lover of drinks like bubble tea and I can see she put a lot of love and effort into making my drink. It’s delicious. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjM4k0COB4xchV3FcU65GC9aYiWw5C0Eg6Ug9-&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2023-12-20"},{"Name":"S K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA8crG_Kej_AlW0Buxi8inYMaqvIWjPmeH973uES3cM0V9rLnd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The matcha is of good quality, and the service was great. However, the prices are ridiculous. I paid $11.25 for a parfait with barely a cup of ice cream in it. I would come here more if the prices were lower.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyJuPSNYrMDSOnN2G-smiNZiQG7BZ40VnfCX4S&fid=0x0:0xd018ac8be1e46952"],"When":"2024-4-20"}]
