[{"Name":"Mia Duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPAUy0Htbh5FTHA7CrcyalmfPE1fNra4l4o1y3j6EQjpz6Sdhn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw this place on YouTube and never knew it existed!!! It’s home cooking and note it is a hole in the wall but if you don’t mind that and are patient with the service as it’s just Yasser cooking and serving then you’ll love the soups and the sandwiches.  Be sure to ask about the special of the day as it’s not on the menu. It’s the only place where you are full and it cost less than $10! He often has 3-4 different types of soups and Tue & Fri the special is the Yasser burger. Monday’s special is the seafood on rice, Wednesday’s special is buttered chicken on rice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9keeXRUR7inMWvfAxGGlYiZjdVTOLGk4cGLJQ&fid=0x0:0x85ea87b0993e9161"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Phil L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLP8vblWOjxfvpOcXTu84a5zJqXMSlg1A4A-FK4spzf_Xtq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing corned beef sandwich! I had heard about the food here from people in the neighborhood, fantastic food and amazing prices!  They were right! The owner is busy, really really busy, place was full but it was also lunchtime, it's a very small place, but he was super friendly and I got my order quick!

Sandwich was hot, perfectly toasted, loaded with meat, delicious!  And 7 bucks! Crazy! Did I say delicious? I didn't have cash so I had to pay with credit. I wanted to leave him a tip but he didn't even put a tip option on his credit card machine!  Now I MUST go back to try the roast beef sandwich ...  and also make up for the tip I owe him :-).  You want ambiance? Go elsewhere.  You want great food, great value and a guy who's so friendly you got to love him? You come here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nalinee Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo10huSX0dX6mUo_p-98vcDKFsNu-pbqmp1FOUHibmggCI0smK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very homy. Feel like having food at home.
Simple but tasty. The chef / owner s sense of humor and very kind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtMC4sTd2ZBHFx99NM7MYn1Al7CvvsU_nu7hJu&fid=0x0:0x85ea87b0993e9161"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Zain Sattar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWEo6_UefMH2p3Ku-wHAXW1J2rnlXth6ibHpgLSDsaqUEIsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing place! Yaser is so kind and his restaurant really feels welcoming. The food is so well priced and absolutely delicious. Try roast beef and corn beef sandwich highly recommend!!
Love the aura will definitely come back
10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMp9Q3kJE4_mTQhpQbKV5IgeBZjn_rL4prbxHq2&fid=0x0:0x85ea87b0993e9161"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Kalvin Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWigZZon5lBY8bc9dUGdaabXIExS8McY2oiiSA9kIAGljo1SdJC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely warm your heart homestyle spot. This is not for someone looking for an upscale experience. This is home cooking. This is a stick to your bones hearty soup and sandwich Spot. It's like stopping by your favourite uncle's place for lunch and he wants you to grow big and strong. Always ask about the special. 10+visits and counting. There's a reason it's always packed for lunch and after work. The value is unmatched.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"To Ching Chan (Raymond)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_JNaVYtt5g0NGwmOn0CZ8D3OYXoGeQEAGHictSSpxFK2__U6u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beef and beans soup with toast for only $3.5 with tax included! It’s tasty and you can’t find it anywhere nowadays. The owner is very friendly. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhD8JPVlZ1bO9sq8mNY0aGKFjYuqKtu6LChhVH&fid=0x0:0x85ea87b0993e9161"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"S. Reid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISNPb4BJnzu5cUcXQUpH68kYmzAE_Gfom8zWU0pQUNlbL1UQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a fun little cafe! It’s a place you hear about and just have to take the time to seek out. We were told about it from a dear friend in Rome!! It’s homey, the food is delicious and the prices are unbelievable!! Yaser is one of the nicest people you will ever meet! If you’re in the area of Burnaby General, check it out!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frédéric Losson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2KnjnrbKb3XwyfTBDFXqRxfL_hY_P11HN7dsyuMPaChWyaMme=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually don't review, but this is just a really good place. All is fresh, homemade, and delicious, and very low price. The owner is very nice, smiling and welcoming.
It is not fancy, but you won't find such a level of quality for this price in 99.9% of Vancouver area's restaurants. Soups and dish of the day are a must.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mahima Gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHiXWFFF3Oi5iW9lt7RTeW0lR8DtRfAKfYJFDdEoFTNXdru9MraA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love their Rib eye steak eggs (very interesting fusion). It was yummy. 4 of us went in for brunch and everything was so on point other than them being so busy. Food itself tasted good but I took away one star for service because we had to ask fir basics (cutlery,sauces,water) and the table we had was a little higher than rest so I give them benefit of doubt of not seeing us and hence not checking in with us more often. But all my friends loved their burgers, my friend is a picky vegetarian even she loved the food. I particularly LOVE their Ube Lattes and go here very often for that. Even their desserts hit the spot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3VGvc-rSQc_42gM7ui76_Up5hatm7SvFnf3ej&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"M Vince","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINswVKcv_7HP6hXe_zVU1zoGZNgim_-GL6O41VCeXNWV7WGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my family had my bday breakfast here, it’s our first time here and had a great experience. The friendly Filipino server (John) very attentive and always smiling. The other young Filipino too serious and not happy working at 8am, Lol. Over all the food was amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXmP2mjzK0WfcNnJ49SfzT-fuRt2TFxDNPIijg&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"April Leclair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8qOXvv_VFz9O28tbAgGBZmscDvFGiww6mmYiYZ2P1x6yNFbIH2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience, flavors, and service! It’s rare to find a restaurant or café with such high standards, and I’m so grateful to have discovered this gem after hours of research (for ube 😂) during our trip to Vancouver! As an ube fanatic, this place was absolutely perfect. Here’s the breakdown:
1.	Waffle: Perfectly crisp on the outside, moist on the inside, with distinct ube flavors throughout. Highly recommend pairing with ube ice cream—but don’t place it directly on top to preserve the waffle’s crispness.
2.	Chicken: Golden-brown and perfectly crispy with the right temperature and thickness. Slightly salty for me, but sparkling water balanced it out beautifully.
3.	Salad: The dressing was too heavy for my mild palate, so I’d separate it next time.
4.	Fries: A few at the top had the ideal crispness and temperature. Slightly salty for my taste, but overall not bad. (Note: I’m not a big fan of steak fries, so take this with a grain of salt—pun intended!)
5.	Ube Latte: Stunning presentation, but tasted more like milk to me. I added no sugar, so that could be why. It paired perfectly with the waffle and ice cream, though, as I found the ice cream slightly sweet for my liking.
6.	Ube Bun: Loved the cream filling! A touch sweet for me, but balanced nicely with the ube latte.
7.	Service: Absolutely amazing—friendly and attentive!

If you’re an ube lover, this is a must-visit spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiEz_v4YmHxJETzQ5wqBlhz4X0tU1VKFhZtSuJ&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Casual cafe located just off a busy intersection of Kingsway and Boundary. Affordable prices and lots of menu options to pick from. They have free underground parking available. Staff are super friendly and attentive. Came here twice and would definitely come back again!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqGnwOqwWmhg-wsaWNlu4RQkDIrKBI0FXV5hYh&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPnAaaLFjZaycZQzsGkYKqDFLkgmP-Pd2h4uf4VmS2SPCnyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a delicious brunch a couple weeks ago on a weekday. Located in a residential area, it is probably a busy spot with the locals. It didn’t seem very busy inside the restaurant, but the food and coffee came out slowly. Perhaps they were busy with takeout orders. Lots of menu options and was yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDEuKZqkZzqjTOZFdvGqgN_Wg1EcrhoVHX7Sec&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Annie X","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIY0aKsdF3LNL6DZxF0791CDOZXJ3wetT_k2aNtk8nE9Sczxo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s a neighborhood cafe that has pretty decent food and drinks. I loved the ube component in the dishes (ie ube waffles and ube latte) and that you can order lunch/dinner style dishes at 8am in the morning! The only qualm I had was the curtness of one of the servers but maybe I caught him on a bad day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtU8VdFDxmUAcAMQFAG-LZVvxOAB2arXKPxRHI&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Diana D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3IZJmhCCOBAZCJcU7Rs13GHMwpWoWC8_agNI5jWh8VfwaBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a delicious meal to celebrate my birthday at liberté café! John had amazing customer service and made it a memorable experience! Thank you for the yummy food!! (:","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMr04fu956SUQYMsAFPHOpkMqSAmHAqN75B6GL&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"shams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2gzPl410bUkkl0oAVJ_Y1DTGQs2MixAYmW42QAK5ZRUtm-kl4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Walked in and was seated immediately. The waiter gave me water and a menu.
Called her over and she took my order and omg unfortunately, they were out of the truffle panini at 9 am already - must be very good.

So I ordered a chicken omelette, Tomato soap and a coffee.

The coffee came in less than 2 minutes and she also brought out ketchup and utensils.

The soup came in 15 minutes after that and looked really good. The entree came like 5 minutes after that. I loved how they spaced out the meal very nice. Also, soup was amazing.

The Chicken Omelette was delicious. The Omelette was soft and flavorful and the chicken was very crispy. The salad had a nice vinaigrette and I loved the little cranberries. The fries were normal kind of good and had a nice crunch to them.

Took half the soup to go. It was a lot of food. The price was also very reasonable for the amount of food.

Overall 8.5 / 10
Would definitely come again. The service was amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqWUg7lyPSyPdUvhSLcpYPUZe96zhTB3HuvTTu&fid=0x0:0xf7e0479c8fd0cac9"],"When":"2024-9-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Carlos Ajoy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj56wBY1xLPQ20bqQNpwgjeSO2V5tNX7g2abXXBavTb3s8Iinv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cafe Ricotta has a cozy vibe and serves delicious food with a unique twist. I tried a few dishes, and everything was spot on:

•	Sandwiches: Perfectly toasted with plenty of filling. They come with a fresh salad and orange slices, which add a nice touch. The bread was crispy, and the melted cheese was just right.
•	Pasta: The creamy pasta was a total hit. Well-seasoned with lots of parmesan on top, and the garlic bread was spot on.
•	Smoothie: Refreshing and smooth, the perfect addition to the meal.
•	Ricotta cake: A must-try! It’s creamy, with a mild flavor, making it a great way to end the meal without feeling too heavy.

The place is nicely decorated with neon lights and a modern vibe, making it super comfortable. They also have a station with utensils, water, and other essentials, which adds to the convenience.

Special shoutout to Linda—make sure to ask for her! She has excellent customer service and really enhances the experience. I’ll definitely be back. Perfect spot for a relaxed meal or to chill with a good dessert and coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB2UqZaGkBUYPSUsQYSGYdj8DQpZLEfB0I1YwJ&fid=0x0:0xaa5bee63b265c4a7"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Seungmin Cho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLCM83Uh3Cp9TN7b-FrhBI1PwhRDQ2eZhBWrJ3SK-RV-9RNIU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their pastas are so creamy and a great value! The ricotta cheese salad, potato soup, cakes, and cookies are all delicious too. 100% recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxkOegaGDqiPPU7S0K8i5FEP1JwgVpp-jW5qE1&fid=0x0:0xaa5bee63b265c4a7"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Dayun Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCQLvvertq1avLFZKHl5apTEDOSO0lUZ81qFHBYAX6TLaFmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been here with my family today. I already knew the food was delicious since I've had it many times, but today was the first time I tried their drinks.
I loved the variety of coffee and non-coffee options. Every drink we tried, from the coffee to the ade and smoothie, was really good. The staff is always friendly and the place is clean. This place never disappoints. I will definitely be visiting again soon.
(If you like spicy food, I highly recommend trying Mala Pasta or Mala Tteokbokki!!!!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbpVSsyoUT7Dm1z5PgtQTNrc_B6Y30nmVAdL83&fid=0x0:0xaa5bee63b265c4a7"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Michelle Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVS6JaWJYqU3FE1DCDneingvSI7iVb6EiQQlNzc6uOkBGU-hZx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the cream pasta and a large ricotta salad. The salad was fantastic—the ricotta cheese was fresh, flavorful, and generously portioned with a big chunk on top. The latte was also delicious and satisfying.

However, the cream pasta was disappointing. It felt more like a cream soup and had a sweet taste. Even the garlic bread was sweet, which didn’t pair well with the dish. The dish needs more savory flavours, personally. For the price, it was okay, but I expected more.

Service-wise, while the staff were polite, no one checked on us to see if everything was okay. A small gesture like that could have made the experience more personal and enjoyable.

Overall, the ricotta cheese and the portions made up for the misses, so I’d give it a solid 4 stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin Pak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWawP6h5FHOMfa8ZuQwLzoBM7e_krAN0BBa5lEAONbqOUlt2g4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was great, chicken club special was not bad and was decent. But the portions are a little small.

Now something that I want to clarify is the wait time. I waited over 30 minutes for the food. It looked like everyone was eating, and I was the only one getting food, yet it was slow.

Overall

7.6/10

[{"Name":"Milangic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVopPvYZNMyoMCZnSPr3vsLdqdKB7J9OKjxv4He0cY0RManHvU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A comfy and great place to enjoy a delicious cup of coffee. Little quote on the mirror to fall cushion covers to tiny Halloween candles during Halloween season. Worth checking out the cup and bun cafe. ☕️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMerqDL5Fun32SXcK5IpIftBhXXoOUsheqd1dVN&fid=0x0:0x1295592475bcc5a4"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Farzam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIooZPCPPfH5D4G1f5pX_06Fqf4UZb5reyqU1DQAFjZqgdcZ04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love Cup and Bun Cafe! The atmosphere is cozy and inviting, making it the perfect spot to relax or catch up with friends. The service is exceptional, and staff are friendly and attentive, ensuring a delightful experience every time. Their coffee is top-notch, rich, and perfectly brewed, and the pastries are simply divine. Every bite is fresh and flavorful. This cafe is a true gem, and I can't recommend it enough!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPt1qN1BG3FpU7VwWED2euVA17apyHCaU-hd_hA&fid=0x0:0x1295592475bcc5a4"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Hassan Mk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn8XljJKUWtM5hZCcrws3Ntw3dFgRbwi5l6-83UHe5aX-z7xYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently visited with my family for a quick walking break, enticed by the promise of aromatic coffee and sweet treats. Our order comprised an Americana, a cappuccino, a lemon cake, and an apricot jam roll.

The coffee and pastries were decent but nothing extraordinary. The cakes seemed a bit overcooked and past their prime, which was a bit disappointing. However, the staff's warmth and friendliness more than made up for it. Their welcoming attitude added a pleasant touch to our visit and made us feel right at home.

The atmosphere of the coffee shop was inviting, with tasteful decorations that added to the overall ambiance. Despite the minor shortcomings in the food, the overall experience was enjoyable, thanks to the cozy environment and the lovely staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDtPhcoFMVMKqz4bQaUvvZp6YQbwKeHIqYUrjr&fid=0x0:0x1295592475bcc5a4"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Phyllis Tee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtHTl5JLpAHiaGIa8m_bWtHrZ84dJMWFq9MtMaT4ZwV6hFBwY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Chicken pesto sandwich was good. Happy with the side salad - made it a balanced dish. Tuna melt was an interesting one - loaded with pickled flavour, which sort of overpowered the tuna taste. Overall, nice little stop for a quick bite.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDRXU-RI9XUweIlPu9xwP3JLaK0VejGRNJHRel&fid=0x0:0x1295592475bcc5a4"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place, quiet on a Sunday afternoon. Rad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfBUNblWOkfhuZ7eOom2I6QeDxjIPkmldUrIixQCHkYaA3j6L-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere and the variety of seating options is great and the staff is friendly. Prices are reasonable too and you have quite some options form pastries to sandwiches. The food and drinks although are decent but nothing really special. Overall, we will be back for sure and I’d rate this as a 4.5/5!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0IFIFaftvdFn-GJ2O0pwOSxNwgTPdxipdyYGy&fid=0x0:0x1295592475bcc5a4"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Maya Florey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWsd7ZlvUoZqLpY-itDvhiZhkJ33_uzwGASGl_tvJHxJbLky4r=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly high quality house made baked goods, sandwiches and traditional coffee! Had a salmon sandwich and a Macchiato, the sourdough bread was fresh and soft and the salad and salmon was very flavourful and lemony. The coffee was very smooth, rich and fruity, with notes of pomegranate and sage. I didn’t try any of their baked goods, but wish I had! They looked incredible and handcrafted, unlike a lot of cafes that resell from Costco! My only complaint is that we went on Sunday afternoon and it was so busy that we could not find a seat! Staff were very helpful and friendly! Seems like a really wonderful community hub!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jamie Coo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMtT8SYH3ODglSdZyhsIz5N_cesns6jNpwE2VJCXq0WPBgF9EA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the Cookie Croissant, Earl Grey Scone, and a Mocha Cube Loaf. For drinks we ordered a Spanish Latte.
We are really impressed by the quality of both the food and drinks here. Starting with the Cookie Croissant, slightly difficult to eat since the cookie part was quite crumbly, but the filling was generous and the flavour was rich and delicious. The scone was a big surprise to us - it was served a little warm, and the inside was super moist. The earl grey flavour was also very pleasant and strong. The Mocha Cube Loaf was moist - the texture is quite like a banana bread but mocha flavoured, but this probably has the most subtle flavour out of everything we ordered.
The Spanish Latte came with a very cute bear latte art. Coffee was strong and rich, and is easily one of the best Spanish Latte we have had.
We will definitely revisit this place for the rest of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHsy3VXVWPc0EglzzV1sjQYMnCz-1qh9Jff_8D&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Jack Bi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ4Bsv7wnjfj756aRVvVyi5fPfQhBIMCe6kqNdp4pTbIyytg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Discover this little hidden gem that boasts an incredibly friendly staff ready to make your visit unforgettable! The relaxing atmosphere invites you to unwind, while the quality food, beautifully presented, will tantalize your taste buds. Come experience the magic for yourself!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPo3cdEHEaE146TNPhCu_Puo1iHKPtRxhC_8Zts&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Josh Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwN2UTX5SU22zHdtHwOol-T1Tx2CdUZ3GytOPSGZ_wa4QkAjU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to many cafes, but this one really stood out. The macarons were absolutely adorable and tasted amazing—each one was like a little work of art. The sandwiches were fresh and full of flavour, perfect for a light meal. The cozy atmosphere and friendly staff made it a great spot to relax. Definitely worth a visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0rPepiaI_U5rtdcULMftT0ij8QcobtQmcnexZ&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Kate Oh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-qqECY5zyYXmAqCj-k4FLrMuqdLUFPr-e1buJmYYfmvaZsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is like a hidden gem. I found it while searching for a place to have brunch. The mushroom avocado and salmon avocado sandwiches are on another level. The ingredients are so fresh and plentiful that it's hard to take a bite. The balance of the sauces and the crispy bread is excellent. I ordered a combo, which included a fresh salad and tomato soup with the sandwich, and it was a perfect match. My daughter's choice of the ham panini was also delicious. The vanilla latte was smooth and had just the right amount of sweetness. I'll definitely come back when I visit Vancouver again. Thank you to the friendly owner and the staff for creating such wonderful memories for our family!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzAIiFiNAlD-yA9l7Okn-Z-V_SbAP9AI3UriNO&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Kenny Poon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCkKTuOESfGudPEm0-BDzQVkIamalgjsSUzE_II9VRplB0iEEX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Visited this cafe in Aug 2024. Fancy little bakery. Good selection of coffee / non-coffee drinks, with small bites available.

We had an "iced latte" and a "real lemon tea" (but there wasn't tea I guess?), a cube loaf (Earl Grey flavour).

Drinks were decent, cube loaf caught us with a bit of a surprise. Warm, moist and rich in flavours.

Good alternative for chained stores like Starbucks or Tim Horton's. Likely to visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMApsVR7WXUTaE8Q_xKvvHp4jLrmmYNMx_k_AHE&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Mattisse Weyler-Hubert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9gJNuDMC-TgqAXQXLf7KWHT1ycRW5rq4CfBrHxm8LTiT_0fjDNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very cute cafe with some delicious looking baked goods that I have yet to try. I had the cranberry chicken sandwich and my partner had the salmon avocado. The presentation is beautiful! My small note would be to cut the tomato into slightly thinner slices and spread them through the sandwich so I don't have to unhinge my jaw like a snake to take a bit. Also my partner mentioned that her's could have used a bit more salmon, but that being said both were delicious!
We also ordered oat vanilla lattes which were very tasty. The service was great despite being busy and we'll both definitely be coming back to try more of the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-VPi7f563T-CLwYFmWIgklnAoArFHSI0RuXSw&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Jayden Goh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfxPbqGM6eAJPan1ykBxu1WdZiDSJ5H4jU_Lmw66QM6XcLJ4I0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a cute cafe! You can tell they put a lot of effort and love towards every baked goods and drinks they serve to their customers. They have the cutest looking macaroons, scones, loaves, cookies, and croissants🤍🍪🥐🍞✨ friendly staff and artistic owner🫶🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqEk5Nm5-1PdV-HbjabRHq2f5bM-pbKiZjTMp9&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"BR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKvHcZB7xb4n8CF1jxejOIwoYqPKN4SdZc0qIjcZcbAYMjdkneNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Bacon & Avo Grilled Cheese Sandwich is a must-try! I highly recommend this meal. The combination of crispy bacon, creamy avocado, and perfectly melted cheese makes for an unforgettable sandwich. The coffee is always very good as well, making it the perfect complement to the meal. And if you have a sweet tooth, the cafe offers a wide variety of delicious sweet treat options that you won't want to miss.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFN9BgyPk_ssXzmXykwMaoqJVfEUF_ALsbK_4D&fid=0x0:0xbefc4217b6347d6"],"When":"2024-8-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food are solid. The price is about the same as other similarly popular cafes.  Coffee tasted pretty good and barista was friendly and informative. Only complaint I have is cleanliness of washroom when I was there. Plenty of seats and fancy lightings provide welcoming vibe for a small sized cafe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMab82X-Q0gOXATGt2iYsoGPS9QlEejoF8ZuU12&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Jordana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJvxqFr8nGL8vok-SCRwxhp2_EJmOiFDFc3qAUH70xw1rrHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is great. Had the Ham and Cheese Criossant and Japanese Hot Dog, and both were delicious. The dough wad flakey and baked just right, and the price was reasonable for what you get. The Rooibos Latte is delectable, highly recommend if you are a tea drinker. The only thing I didnt like is that it was busy but only 1 person behind the counter taking orders and making the orders, so we had to wait quite a bit, otherwise, lovely place. Clean and cozy, great place to catch up with friends and hang out over coffee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSx2yuz7LPmqpdYXNlzXTgK4YAfZ5YQVxoAvxD&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Angelica Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs8Rl6i0PRUB6_vIudko9K2nv_lt0A7oW9FSvOVZiLCVaSWMgL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice cafe with a large variety of baked goods. Their staff is always so kind and the ambiance is nice. I enjoyed my matcha, I just wish they didn’t charge so much for oat milk when dairy is a dietary restriction for many people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHDm0mjUXAu8QYUpecGd-bswC6Z9U0ZUEp85cL&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Naved Quaiyumi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfaJqW_7xDMkt7owQPld9jTBvQCckh2hsX_7RQEdqPvMD2bHPc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jonathan and Rona both provided great service to us. We ordered the cake n coffee ( Spanish latte). Coffee was the best I have tasted in Vancouver however the cafe need to work on its ambience more ...it's not fitting to it's delicious pastries cakes n coffee...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPatezFk2kKnvNs6A9euxNrLACMRHN1XF5NdeFb&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Cute little cafe, gets pretty busy in the evenings because of the icecream/ gelato they carry which is cute. I wanted to try a few drinks but they were out of so many options which was pretty disappointing. So I just went with a latte (which tasted like a straight espresso shot ) and my friend had a green tea latte! Which was very delicious. I tried their Nutella swirl and it was also very delicious! Highly recommend! Next time I think I’ll asked for it warmed up though so it melts more in your mouth ! Will definitely come back to try out the gelato","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2_97X8nACU7-mm8sElw4ea4VFrYs3podIWTih&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Jackie Fiedler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrH5-QVsgBWyB1jTrOwnjnmXPjBownlPqvtu2BmzJx6OHq1yuItQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Charming bakery with a ton of options!

The sausage croissant was fantastic - buttery and flakey croissant was delicious warmed.

The chocolate supreme croissant wasn’t my favorite - very heavily filled and the dough was a little tough.

The mango royal croissant was also heavily filled, but tasty and the dough was excellent.

Friendly service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCimW-EJ95TwikSqB8QYmW8j_ChmO0u_H2Px53&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Melinda W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqFa91nGQX9-WVxFZ-rAUul10GF70bhWZFQZe97ymoPVUZrvFxnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both my husband and I love this cafe. Their baked good are fantastics in taste and great in variety. The downside of it is that it makes us very difficult to choose (joking!)
There is a see-through bakery area. I was sitting next to it and really enjoyed watching the chef working on the dough.
The vibes are very chill there. We just love everything about this cafe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4tXVMtR9mDLcEsPaQFSIY2kyY9ZWQqHPaoOsw&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Lạc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpO8370_7RDhjsqnPt6c35t5mMarMGN54u0eeSrhk9ZwWK5CU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Fior De Latte. They have a crazy pastry selection. Their drinks are decent. All the time I’ve been there, it’s always so busy so sometimes you can’t find a seat. But it’s a very nice cafe and it’s local.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNO-QvZDaTUmIXk-xywn3dL1_WnkUBB7lYh3Ry&fid=0x0:0x529a45d5bbfbcdfb"],"When":"2024-11-28"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kenny T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe7zwS5sOu0N7dgULna7sR8kdK1ezF--5qTVCwIZgwgoxHFYu9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Coffee fan and espresso fan here. Tried there Soon Traditional Cappuccino as it's one of their signature drinks.

Taste: 8.5/9 Coffee beans are not as strong but caffeine kick was there.
Texture: 9/10 Creamy and not watered down like other coffee shops out there.
Flavor: Good balance of milk, coffee and texture.

All in all it's a good texture and coffee made with passion and care.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAaO6gj36l2Jns6ZMDJyG11oi0iZy3jto7lLIi&fid=0x0:0xfb43f5ae2eb7942c"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"tikki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzV_Y6bQFjodBKC8anq5nBVFmCTC7hA6Nh7xklFQuKGefK40A_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've visited Soon a few times since the opening. The vibe and the design is very cool and the coffee is pretty decent as well. It is located inside the food court so it might get busy sometimes but still one of the best options to grab a coffee in Brentwood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzt0NuZ5C5d5bc1_NRCGwtbtI-3bQitloiPFOf&fid=0x0:0xfb43f5ae2eb7942c"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Jessica Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOeC5VCbc6g3HH3dxXpDS9bE993HEKMDVI3SjHX2aNdHbQOJHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Nice to think that there's vegan drinks but still hurt my stomach. The roasted green tea slushy was too sweet but coffee slushy was not too sweet so it tasted fine. thankful for the promo from the farmers market today to try it though","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNc3dUQDXFp2pSa9VTpxEe9Pp-7n-N5aeZcmRjm&fid=0x0:0xfb43f5ae2eb7942c"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Convenient coffee spot inside Brentwood Mall food court. Friendly staff and great everyday $2 coffee. If you want a fancier coffee there’s also Small Victory nearby, but I enjoy the fact that Soon coffee is in the food court where there’s ample seating and a much more efficient ordering experience vs Small Victory","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abhay Verma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrV_6i4dbcDuraV7ft63f2m_fuGbXlt4ooiSAA_Az5gxTkAzw0Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the hometown favorite latte and an iced Americano and loved both drinks!

The barista was really friendly, great at making coffee and gave us good service when we were not sure about our order. The drinks themselves were unique, the hometown favorite had a great, simple twist on a latte and the spring menu's vanilla cardamon latte sounds incredible too.

It's located in the food court in case anyone has difficulty finding this location, definitely worth trying.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNq9OW75IttmmWMwaO9l8U5XVzeKKylNHPo4ua4&fid=0x0:0xfb43f5ae2eb7942c"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Anna Galak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-GNMtmtasDEXBqbed64O79xvbj0wj1dwWfO1CrNYc-cF1UA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best coffee in town.

Always excited employees, recommending what’s good with passion for coffee and what they do. Not a single staff member is pretentious (like at Nemesis👀). If you need your freshly purchased beans grind - they will do it for free and ask you how exactly you are going to brew your coffee to make sure you get the best flavour.
The green tea slushie - out of this world!
Brand and merch design - absolutely delightful.

They are located on the second floor at the mall’s food court so the community vibe there is hit or miss.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3lBylmGoglvD3qVOBYMvlo7RV2UX6ZEPZKmoj&fid=0x0:0xfb43f5ae2eb7942c"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Shaianne Casasis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVflTGm8iJItU5OIi2vvnAmt0aeNAsLE9-Rruq437_EqjqkFaHH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A quaint little cafe tucked into the Brentwood mall food court, Soon Coffee caught my eye with its charming combination of blue, light pink, and white decor, adorned with adorable illustrations: a visual treat that initially drew me in.

The space, though small, was well-utilized, creating an inviting atmosphere. I opted for an iced americano and a chocolate chip cookie, simple items that were hard to mess up. The staff were warm but seemed slightly uncoordinated. For instance, I ordered a small iced americano but received a larger size instead. This wasn't a problem for me, but it could be concerning if another customer experienced the reverse situation. Although I was the only one waiting, the barista had to call for me from across the counter and ask me what I ordered, which was strange. It seemed like they were new, so I'm inclined to give them the benefit of the doubt. As for the food, the chocolate chip cookie was mediocre. The center was unbaked and it tasted as if it were missing an ingredient. However, the iced americano, which was unexpectedly sweet, balanced the bold, dark flavours of the coffee beautifully.

Overall, Soon Coffee is a really cute spot that I'd like to visit more often should I find myself at Brentwood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jyoti Mann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4iOqEqhynUij0PCQiBi1OzMmu6YLmwWZcNK5VEPw9Kgk92w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great, super affordable stop for caffeine! I got their iced americano and it was great. The price to quality of coffee ratio is fantastic, the staff really care about what they do, and the signage is really cute!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"V Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-Qz_zR8NAjeqpRnuANXJcQGSLJzNuS-ETk_THk3z82H5rG6U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall a solid place. I ordered a cup of latte. While I feel the flavour and milk steaming could've been better, it was still a decent cup. I like that they have no tip as a default so you don't need to press anything if you don't want to tip. I'm sure people are feeling more fatigued these days with tips and would appreciate it. The bathroom could be cleaner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjOouTPehfuOKCJ5QRuWCOalChnKTdQnz5-PCi&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Conor Whyte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMdI4_ZGUMJFwplOdkinu1I_usGONki2DpQ6wr_spSbc4yhe2F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent cafe with a strategic location nearby Brentwood Shopping Centre.
Food was expertly prepared, and coffee was super freshly roasted. Highly recommend this cafe! Today was our first time to visit.

맛있는 치킨브리샌드위치와 모카였습니다.

Note for the previous commenter: It is important to open seating for customers that are coming in to eat. If you are spending excessive time in the cafe, it hurts their business as it limits available seating for arriving customers. This is not a large cafe!
There are signs everywhere explaining the 2hr limit. This is more than fair in my opinion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuA-marRZTavANuOGqkJ3naD1qW0n8VpZk89yo&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Lin Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-AOGsPLTQGmNweeMhJKvZ5lorslTGkT0xLfg-fKE2grd81A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Have this weird policy going on: 2 hours limit on weekend and holidays. One of the servers just dropped this tag on my table and I hadn't even finished my cup of coffee (dine in and tips paid). Understandable, but still feel it's a rude policy and make the customer feel bad. Never saw this kind of policy in any cafe I have been, just a warning to those who want a place longer than 2 hrs to study /work. It's a good spot in brentwood, but will never come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxArbsw15FxaRyST2ulNHhnatYFMb6gTwvGJ_g&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Maxim Borzenkov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5du_PkAVH4Z1D5yn5ceof8nx4Vb5Gh-oa_Y_0G13tOUKmBqAiog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent coffee and tasty sandwiches, the chicken brie being a standout favorite. Cheesecake is absolutely delicious, though I wish the slices were a bit larger. I miss being able to order the sandwiches on DoorDash. Overall, a great spot for a tasty meal and dessert!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeaVVfDOeEwlk_63rdT45vESLd8iugZh1J-uoB&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Vic Yung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjSUFpvFSwHsCrywPzGZzN7WDhV8Ljlj3YECw07iwjqMR_leW5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went on a weekday afternoon and most of the tables were occupied. Ordered an iced matcha latte and the staff made sure to ask if I wanted it sweetened or unsweetened. The ice melted a little quickly but the flavor was strong and not too sweet. Started about an hour and staff didn't rush anybody out.

Would recommend for a casual coffee meet up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp4AKcSCITqptgpgL6kivA1850i6Hr18B-e7x3&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Joey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJl9szXFCvkqiDIj8ffgxhpU02VBcZUaH8smB2SMyI4TIXdsaA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious matcha latte, refreshing iced tea, and perfect Basque cheesecake. sesame tiramisu surprised me! Cozy and delightful cafe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPr2FtWRPH8lg9ErCfR3Tmz6rKb-yKeT4wTSdAR&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Marcus Molina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0VJnjNpbeDzNmeiSJg9kR2Htb5wEtrtRAu317vPzeMfxaeoo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The cream puffs were great but what they're really known for is their basque style cheesecake. It was incredibly creamy and the perfect balance of not too sweet but not too bland. In my opinion, this is one of the best cheesecakes in all of Metro Vancouver.

Also tried the apple grapefruit sparkling lemonade and that was so refreshing and good.

If you're looking for some high quality desserts in the Brentwood area this is the place to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSiv_KihY1Fe3T4ViIhGFkf_0-15QP8wJgewP_&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2023-1-16"},{"Name":"Nur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1DGcXSlt3DOKh1OYTYqaVlGYlWM6GjkdmrWGlG1XOHSx5g-8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is a nice place. We tried Tiramisu and cheesecake and velvet cake. Everything was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdRmI1Eauv8WyMEZWWZV-eJmU1aUJFYABa_Z-F&fid=0x0:0x778986f5635d3347"],"When":"2024-11-18"}]

[{"Name":"Alan Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-QmMYfw75kgf5vonVt_7RAAdUJRl5hAF6Ijht6iC6ZE8aPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying out this brunch place in our neighborhood. The ambiance is nice and restaurant decor very warm and comforting. The staff was super friendly, especially the younger girl that served us throughout our dining experience (didn’t catch her name)

All the food options were yummy. The espresso martinis is a tad stronger on alcohol than I’ve had in a few other places. Some may love this though so totally your individual preference. The mixed fruit waffle is quite sweet and the fruits are definitely needed to help cut the sweetness. If I were to order this again, I’d ask for extra fruits.

The Benedict and pasta we ordered were both yummy. Worth a try in if you are in the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCDXR74cJvkaxlcW38jlSeaHSLHxk9yDecQcXx&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Peter Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMSeHRAtGk2XdalqRXihpRRMhie3ny5793uAdd9iw_CYpSb6O7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I didn’t expect such a special brunch, but wow, the place is definitely a hidden gem. Great atmosphere and service with amazing food. We had burnt brie cheese with figs, California Benedict omelette, buttermilk crispy calamari, coffees and a mimosa flight. Every dish was delicious and I would definitely go there again soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOh09mlBVvZP8p6KjDLVB7Cni3cF5KdY_XZF_t8&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Tricia C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS8jxdORXKJaAWhct8yqQ3gE8qhWdlJFJL5jsz8u98jLVDfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This cute cafe on Hastings in Burnaby North has taken over the former space occupied by the Kazu Japanese restaurant. The café has breakfast and lunch menu items as well as cocktails, tea and coffee.
The favourite on our table was the chicken and waffles- the juicy crisp chicken was perfectly cooked.
Parking: free street parking out front.
Staff: Friendly and helpful servers","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMILqQy5598y3ErdXutlS0Z7PL_bcHkx-MJUsxu&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for brunch and had a pleasant experience. The staff are super friendly and a great selection of menu items to pick from. Definitely try the minestrone soup - super hearty!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl7RaZwHiSYdczv_ZlqkSJ-nXRHzO8HC3CSWA2&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"John Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnQcmQk5zXvH68j5FJSO-DZt_bNb-sv4XDWST0oWFFOK2Ke2-Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to check out a cute cafe that just opened up in the neighbourhood. Was surprised at the cozy interior and how good the food was! Service was quick, food was presented well and tasted great, and the price was pretty average for eating out. Lots of interesting drinks on the menu, including the Bumble Bee drink which I’ll have to try next time. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON2vi_RyNfnJXV4XWvSDzlCvVWfNgbazWn-Kxt&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Jennifer Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnElfGUrwJdErhJahkLSaanNvX4G1k3-WZt2a4a57CwIQsqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow I’m so excited about this new brunch place. The best chicken and waffles I’ve ever had, especially the waffle. The pancakes were also delicious. This place is definitely a step above your average brunch quality and the ambience is lovely. There’s also a whole menu of brunch cocktails I want to try next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4hcuWJSPiJ-mCj0udw_Ye_GRltL_e4uvkdF6Z&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"Reza Alaghmandfard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmMkMx99Qu99Z6EErgZuCHvUU2hEB5SXpcaLhvC4R0a2HkgjROTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Brunch was so delicious and employees were all respectful. The only complain I have is the level of the noise. I had hard time hearing my friend’s voice from the other side of a small table. If that is fine with you, this place can offer you lots of fantastic options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5RBPblQRO6wbBil06FlxGGeMRsM6EwB94AIAc&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Sharon Biscoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0-x1SooYgKJay2fzwX2BNXcCc3n8J_jzAtgfKGfItx1uYGGwGFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the rigatoni bolognese and crispy calamari. The bolognese was so flavourful and filling and it was just the right portion! Calamari had a strong flavour and kick to it, and crispy.
Staff are extremely nice and polite. The restaurant itself has a very nice look to it, and is clean. Loved the little pumpkins they decorated around the place, so cute! Definitely recommend this new brunch restaurant and will come again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-Y6QblEEvCMiRhm-vN53FRYLXO_taapj6mlWy&fid=0x0:0xaabc56b7c30c946"],"When":"2024-10-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Wong Irene","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7sp41wGQuueC1lDn3CqM9IATBJFCPj_h7E-EhyDPVkJBCmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An exceptional dining experience! Rita provided service that was nothing short of perfection—attentive, professional, and genuinely warm. She ensured every detail of our visit was taken care of with precision, making us feel truly valued. The food was another highlight: each dish was expertly prepared with fresh ingredients and full of flavor. Whether you’re looking for great service or memorable cuisine, this restaurant delivers on all fronts. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKhxEiYRaNvgCE2sZTdbIorfj2gKpcLESbXR4O&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Ana Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB7MTy6hJzRER5Lw64do3j-FVTSb3sI3u-0kGStMwjecZMBBKwWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great meal here! Lovely service from Rita and the food was amazing. We got the Tom yum fish hot pot, pad Thai, and an appetizer platter with a couple of Thai milk teas. Everything was so good! Would definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3TatcypZevqgetWe3bso1LZkajBt8Y11Ohi6H&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Ann Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvn-xEzewwzi5MnaSg9fqfqC8GocNLnb-uO3tOtU-odVbwqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Loved the atmosphere and the dish presentation was great!  One of the coolest attractions was definitely the coffee robot, which manually pours your coffee, adding to the experience. We ordered the coconut chicken soup, pad Thai and beef green coconut curry. Loved their coconut based dishes, especially the soup. Very clear winner for us! For drinks we got their pour over coffee and Thai green tea. Ruby was our server and she was very kind! Overall, it was fun and tasted good. We will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZQq6fHRD1tAg75Za1jSxA3pD3d6IE6UpaK77z&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"马尔柯","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4syA-Xl9wGd2fBI-MP9Hvp_Amxw0QMFGRxMFKAtkG4OfWZE1JQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Friendly staff, food quality was great. Tom yum soup was delicious, not that 🌶️, suitable for most of guests who would like to try out. Seafood was fresh. Seafood pineapple fried rice was okay, fried rice was not too surprising me, however the quality was matched with the price. Mango sticky rice was the taste that I have in Thailand which was a great after meal dessert. Recommend whoever is interested in Thai food.
Parking was easy, back of the restaurant or side street parking is available.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyw-XO-FZnfBT7th4oCsBzhi_yyftgEiRKV9nQ&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Paola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4XrimCFm4PtK_mrrS16PbwFF6YoSh4YLs5FG7yP-UkHhGyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"MJ was our waitress. She was very fast and efficient. Our food came so fast and everything was absolutely delicious! Absolute perfection! We ordered: pad Thai with chicken, a platter that had chicken satay skewers, tofu skewers, papaya salad, pork spring roll, taro chips with a side of different dipping sauces; green curry chicken, and vermicelli soup. Everything was fresh and savoury. Will definitely go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPt7sMClTRPsRudqgBbS-1wFXRXRHKmLXQfgIgG&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"CLARA LEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0ILRTJhVLrSGhNhbP7yLnUG5OOKMdOcp0BMxOGRysjByVFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"“Today I went to RENS, which many people have praised, but I was very disappointed 🥲.
1.	Ordered the Tom Yum fish hotpot, but the soup wasn’t hot enough. I asked the waiter why there was no flame, and he said the soup was already drinkable and didn’t need to be heated 😪.
2.	The curry soft-shell crab was okay.
3.	Stir-fried kale with shrimp paste didn’t taste like shrimp paste, and the vegetables were tough 😢.
4.	Mango sticky rice with coconut milk was very ordinary.

The bill, including tips, was $142. After eating, I had diarrhea twice.”","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUEyNsDjBA1-893gKFMlSmJwKiikJ2hgClf4s_&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-12-26"},{"Name":"Michelle Zhou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVIvGyONprhS-fV2IjnaoygalX1P8-qAn8vawz8ML1gD0fJBE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this Thai restaurant, appetizers are a good portion and not oily, Tom yum fish hotpot is fresh, soft shell crabs are well marinated with lots of flavours. Additionally,  I was also super amazed by the coffee making robot. 10/10 experience. Huge thanks to our server Ruby and Simon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfl0vWP_7dSysX9l5IlFUJ6P-bzI9KMG8L0hIY&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Daniela Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMB4YUQU0RvmyKQwqA9boDszayPHnBhKRgH704hw0ct-9BCx-l=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a lovely dinner at RENS with family tonight! Simon was a great server providing us with excellent recommendations. The curry grilled fish hotpot was incredible! Super aromatic and flavourful. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO55DT5iiXQWqCzjriKH6GB3jqcklNAk1vETTjH&fid=0x0:0x28438971892ecfbf"],"When":"2024-11-17"}]

[{"Name":"Remia Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmpY-11b6uW1ElYcP-MQ3nN5fllulzAmTZx7kDqDgJ0KRRYIkH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very nice and warm welcoming cafe. The lady working here was very nice and gave me a wonderful cozy vibe.  As if you’re visiting a caring relative. She was very kind and made sure we all found a drink we would enjoy.

The drinks are very delicious and I was very pleased. They use real fruits for some of their drinks and they were very refreshing.

We got 20% off our drinks. The lady told us for the winter months there is 20% off for the season.

I will definitely be back!

I recommend either of the two drinks we got or something made with real fruits!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhCAL-p93nFT6zGlEASc8nJwztaVAIkamNqQpF&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Sam Shop","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL00zVIViQ27vvP18FEhx25H0o_EIIlmqibePozX8gFaroS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Our bubble waffles were nice. Sweet, decent whip cream, but very little fruits. Strawberry was served frozen. Would have been nice if the lady had defrosted it.

Service took a long time even though we were the only ones there.

Taro bbt used jasmine tea so tasted very different. Because she blended the ice, the bubbles became super hard.

Ambiance is not great. It feels like an order to-go place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOF-ZblyBJML0kbOI_6gMjBjqumGsN1NkG2iw&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Allan lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeLeKCCWzGG31UN4u7PVDpcD5nilEIt_OcjsD3MjiLwJogDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a frequent customer at Gathering Cafe. They offer a wide selection of high quality drinks (lattes, milk tea) that are made organically on the spot. The owner uses fresh fruits and ingredients instead of syrup for their drinks, and still maintain a very, very good price. I highly recommend a honeycomb coffee latte and pumpkin latte as they warm you up on a cold day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPE36rzNNT4PbPMRrUYuDUO6HrBpsXCehI019O&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"April Dong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-EJWeyLZl-J46LDopap4-qjdQdaukUBxAWy4qdIzEb8Hgrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very cute and cozy place to sit and enjoy. The lady is warm and welcoming, just tell her what you want and she can recommend to you. All drinks and food are come in great portion, that are good enough to feed you up. I highly recommend the iced fruit tea and green tea with salty cream cheese foam. They are fresh and delightful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQRU2smTJTxvrDc9phK0e0GiWFbp_tFmL1e0Rq&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-4-4"},{"Name":"Samantha Newbery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMwh1oZxhiPpLD2ehTemDe8UpvHDKim9u6YzgoLrrEJoQrabZz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad we stumbled across this super cute cafe while our car was being serviced nearby. It was the perfect place to hang out for an hour. The chocolate bubble waffle and blueberry smoothie with salt milk cover were both freshly made and delicious, and so affordable!
We will definitely be back if we are ever in the area. We were impressed and there are lots of things on the menu we want to try.
Cute place to study or for a quiet hang out with friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Came here for bbt and they definitely have affordable options 6-7 dollars for a bbt. Facilities are extremely old - the building interior had an unpleasant smell to it. As for the drinks themselves, pearls were extremely soft as if they’d been sitting around for days. I would not recommend coming here. Sun Tea within the Safeway complex is a much better experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMswmdei6UWklCfmLwISBSmrU2S9MU-u9BJWa9l&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Su Linn Myint","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEH0QETeDUsAuNdaL-G3MXThYHvHFGOtEiMjaO_gQ0TBWXgz0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to try this cafe for a while and finally tried it. I tired the egg and bacon crepe which is really good and full of fillings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAs-LRfmD0Y5j2m7dqt4WZOsm0T3qGmlHwlgvr&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Lucian Nedelcu (Teddy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQWs20vZVv-WjmKExQoFbz4NhIegHkfZEv7UasxD9lUs_8TMWcoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place, quaint, low-key. The food is very tasty and reasonably-priced. They have an interesting selection of both, food and drink, but nothing crazy.

The wifi is 10/10

If you want a quiet afternoon to study this unassuming place is perfect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfJwwFyQocbbMRpw8TK2wUpj1agA2qrP1o5yuj&fid=0x0:0x25dcc58228ed4dbf"],"When":"2023-6-24"}]

[{"Name":"Mrs. Leci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFUu7tIDGHhiFP61EOIZLCOSzvwJkGN10CXxqa6MRhYpyxpm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can't believe that this cafe is this pretty when we visited the other day for breakfast. I drive past this place almost every week and didn't know it till the other day. Try their Meet Sausage with 2 flavourful sausages, eggs, waffles, fruits, potato tots and green salad with almonds. It was a full plate that's just perfect to make your tummy happy!

Thanks to Olivia for a great dining experience. We'll be here next Sunday Morning again for sure!

Can't wait!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFrtA8YmtifaL7kZ24YBMILFBaHS8xWj-_tmPh&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Joanna Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWolcjmld9gF3v6DkaAWVH8shgENhbGrrRuqb_2RSUD8H4muTAvMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time here, and it's a cute, cozy restaurant. The food was really good, it was fresh and delicious, and I wanted to eat more. The drinks we had were also good. I had strawberry syrup and ice cream coffee. Haven't seen it before on a menu, but glad I tried. Service was really good as well, they were very nice and kind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb9cixLhdHyRQLqj5ycfGJTEHitIZX4nEgVs9J&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Vem Fell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwkPSV3Go5MeUNG2num_FvOxxkl2soaYDTRAJLJyvuZfHkM2xy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Last-minute decision to come here for Sunday brunch (we're visiting from Seattle) and even though we had to wait for 40mins for a table, it's all worth it! Can't go wrong with smoked duck breast and basque cheesecake--made extra special by attentive staff--for a post-bday celebration.  Thank you for extending a positive dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPqKMImmJtvu8kB5l3Xo3jUWIUEWwyRhrGxvoL&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Heyam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQm9BhjOHMjC7GcWrHn68t1cIzjRHFnDfgXZNgHLdz2uOG85st=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing cafe and staff. Very beautiful cafe.
We were looking for a place to have breakfast on Sunday. Some of the cafes had big lineups, but I didn't want to waste our Sunday morning in line up. I found 1003 on the map, and we headed here. It has very beautiful design and decor. We ordered 2 dishes with coffee and tea. The food was very good. The bread is fresh. I felt like we were in heaven for our breakfast.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1xfOay1A6YbrZ3wA7zDzYNv2r_K861bg3wde3&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Nikki c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTEI07jnFTAEaLsFO0c2_mPPfnmG0XKKHuolSSFqT8Xlgj-nIi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The sausage was juicy and delicious, though the waffles were soft and not crunch (which i prefer) it tasted more like pancakes.

The portions are not as big as they look.

The decorations are cute and overall comfortable dining atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpyvGWGINTnl9f3nub4EaJkHMbyvZ3H8uOJ7hG&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Elle L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUA6uiZPrLU9bl4EujMU3r0rYnUtrFGP8wi2uc18VoJ8Udh_FGB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We decided to check out 1003 Brunch and Dessert and ordered the pesto chicken focaccia combo (with a side salad and tater tots), the bacon croissant sandwich, and an Oreo iced latte. Unfortunately, the experience fell short of our expectations.

Starting with the pesto chicken focaccia: the bread itself was disappointing. Focaccia is typically known for its airy, slightly crisp, and flaky texture, but this version was far from it. The bottom bun was soggy, and overall, the sandwich lacked the fresh, well-textured bread that makes focaccia so enjoyable. The chicken itself was even more of a letdown—boiled chicken breast with no seasoning. It felt bland and lifeless, lacking any of the flavors you’d expect from a pesto chicken sandwich. We found ourselves reaching for the ketchup served with the tots, which speaks volumes about how little flavor the sandwich had on its own.

The salad that came with the combo was unremarkable as well. It consisted mostly of plain greens with no standout flavor or dressing that could complement the other parts of the meal.

Service was another area that needed improvement. After our food was brought out, our server didn’t check in with us, and we were left without basic essentials like salt and pepper, which could have helped improve the meal’s flavor. It was surprising that we weren’t offered any, as it seemed obvious we needed some seasoning to bring out the flavors of what we’d ordered.

The bacon croissant sandwich fared slightly better but still wasn’t impressive. The croissant was decent, though it didn’t have the flaky, buttery texture that a well-made croissant should have. While not as bland as the pesto chicken focaccia, it wasn’t memorable either.

Finally, the Oreo iced latte was another disappointment. We had hoped for a drink with a unique twist, but it turned out to be just a standard iced latte with crushed Oreos on top. It tasted like a quick gimmick rather than a thoughtfully crafted beverage. We would have preferred an option to have it as a hot drink, which could have added a nice contrast to the flavors.

Overall, this visit left us underwhelmed. Between the subpar food quality, lack of flavor, and inattentive service, we don’t see ourselves coming back to 1003 Brunch and Dessert. There’s potential here, but for the price, we expected a much better experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUH29NlM-CmBLD_LOmlcSeukanEn_fDcv2d-TP&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"cat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOpJ0p_oeAe5MdNgkzgRlfQlHruhwSqcfe0RoRC2l6Ja8sIdzz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was great! It’s hard to find places like these for such a cheap price. One of our knives came dirty, and staff replaced it without request. A 3-course meal with drinks included ($10 CAD) was $48. The bathroom was completely clean and had no noticeable spots that were dirty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPORUpC7oMzhcTNjtzX539QuXZ45WalnP-A3t1a&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Khue N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVhVKylYAtr_zgjEBMuypkuJBrSM3sCJT_8EE6YWBCFfnw53OL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super cute place for brunch! They don’t take reservation for brunch but no wait line either, we got a table rather quickly. Food was excellent. Will come back to try their high tea. Also really reasonably priced!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLwWA3jBwwJLX1K4BFHx4G9iXUwmaAvG34_j42&fid=0x0:0xd6f82a5318716098"],"When":"2024-7-31"}]

[{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZuen6azAZaeBPQC6XtvXbgUcHlZFPy1xD9wav_8Z186L2bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best new brunch place! Choice of Italian or brunch menu. The food was good and the service was great. Free 2 hour parking across the street and free no limit weekend parking on Albert. Games section if that's your thing. Great patio with treed tables and under a canopy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpPP7IzTza4Ip-JE51GJhuNyO2I34koQyh1zsr&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Derek Shek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP9Pjija1abf8rOsOgAPBkesWOZ8sALAjyQJKt0I-DTaykDkHV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great spot for breakfast with plenty of options to choose from! The hash browns were especially good—crispy and flavorful. There’s lots of space here, making it perfect for a relaxed meal without feeling crowded. Whether you’re in for a quick bite or a leisurely breakfast, this place has something for everyone. Definitely recommend giving it a try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2JVQgCl9OsottKSRyre_Bvdj3SzyQcLZmiJhu&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Farzam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIooZPCPPfH5D4G1f5pX_06Fqf4UZb5reyqU1DQAFjZqgdcZ04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I would rate Reverie Kitchen 3 stars. The cafe is simple, not fancy. The food was tasty and made with good ingredients, but it wasn't exceptional. The service was just alright; they served our foods (also coffees) separately, which is against basic serving rules. The cutlery wasn't clean, as shown in my pictures. It's worth noting that they have a few tables outside. Overall, the food didn't look amazing, but it was alright. I'm thinking about giving them another chance for a lunch or dinner and will update my review if I have a better experience. I'm very fair when it comes to rating places, and I'm very surprised by their google overal 4.7 review!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpVTirLImVaeFWeZSPzCfl5HHmg837TI4A80Sk&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Renee Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjpu7xvxzQuz7mPhbIfCUN7BEUO3RMAXobynBrvl_suLC61AA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Had high expectations after seeing the review but sadly I can only rate this place 2/5. This restaurant is more towards a casual cafe, nothing fancy. Menu has wayyy too many items although some are fair priced.

Food: ⭐️⭐️

🍝Shrimp Carbonara with Homemade Fettuccine ⭐️⭐️

Tastes like something I can cook at home. They kinda overheated the Carbonara sauce, making it clumpy and scrambled, which made the pasta very dry. For it to be $22 (shrimp+fettuccine was additional 💰) was disappointing.

🍝Chicken Alfredo with Homemade Fettuccine ⭐️⭐️⭐️

Definitely tasted better than the carbonara, everything was good. Although I can certainly make the same taste at home.

🍕Margherita Pizza ⭐️⭐️

It was a bit different from we imagined, the crust tastes like those frozen ones, but the topping was good. The tomatoes were fresh and delicious, there was decent amount of cheese. $11 was fair, you get what you pay

🌯Tuscan Chicken Panini ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

Honestly the best looking dish out of everything we ordered. It had lots of cheese and meat, $16 was fair

☕️Drinks ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
Drinks were surprisingly good! We have ice-frapp and italian soda, both tasted really good, although a small frapp is $6 lol

🍽️Service ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
The service was amazing, staff were very kind and attentive. Willing to make fresh fettuccine when they ran out 🙏🏻 I appreciate that!

Overall:  2/5

A bit pricey for what they served, maybe order their drinks and breakfast. Pasta was disappointing for the price we paid, we might stick to paninis only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpdJcwuLITEB0xEq51prxonrPo3YFDa-VJVefX&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"Westie Masks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImIpX9gcj-rBam5pQsTIWhZNmKHdi6lOhnIkMHVwcRXdVlRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Casual fare with solid breakfast options. I had the Salmon Eggs Benedict and my friends ordered The Standard. We aLeo ordered the hash browns. I absolutely loved my meal. Hash browns were so good with hot sauce and ketchup. Service was excellent. What a nice spot! Wish I lived closer!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Val Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXkNc5CFidDvCL6ggfjfAKrG0er-5TyNmVe1yZFGc2n0YAtMVp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seriously best breakfast around. The bread is baked in house and has the nicest crumb. Crispest hash browns. Was blown away by the French toast. Not normally a french toast sweet breakfast kinda person but I crave this now. The savory French toast was topped with dried apple slices and “not too sweet” oatmeal crumble. Best value breakfast especially since there is so much care taken in making the food. The owner always comes out to say hi and the staff is so friendly and work quickly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs-S-NsLPnkdIVbkNkCIj7vRIe1zm2Yn6tCpFw&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2023-9-28"},{"Name":"Jackie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvUQ9aJ1wSufelDKgqON2H6lO7iMGLWM2g-QyJYoOznHaBLkrZTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You order off a menu taped on the wall counter-service style and then pay and find a table (inside or on their humongous and comfy patio.)

The furniture is dated but the vibe and staff are all awesome. Very laid back and kind.

Prices can't be beat and honestly the food knocked our socks off. All 3 of us loved every part of our dishes, the bread was so high quality and the shredded hashbrowns are *chefs kiss*. The Italian espresso they use was also bold and delicious.

This place is so unassuming but what a gem for the community. I can't wait to come back and try the homemade pastas and other breakfast/lunch options!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5hLWvEss7xua6fjsAugCVuDxJu294LBLId-ey&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2022-9-25"},{"Name":"Justin Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIphX3IVdB6bYFyvRnGuBCpwkqSRxWlxdh1LxRlF-KLcXAbeHmLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Easygoing spot in a nice location… used to be La Fontana. Food at this new Reverie Kitchen is solid, tasty, a little pricier than usual, but not excellent: it’s missing a little bit of “soul”, if that makes sense. Service is a little lacking - long wait times for both drinks and food make it hard to give full marks for this area. The space, though is comfortable, easy to find seating in, and feels homey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAogmnSTCxPJP-DAzCGzbJWHfo62RwHc7dM7hQ&fid=0x0:0xd5fbbe326624ce2d"],"When":"2024-5-12"}]
