[{"Name":"Ss W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLO2c5mKnbli1BnGAmVNeFTG8cuiptGfaoGASzlUNOFP4ApJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An Aussie bakery serving up a pepper steak pie topped with mashed potato, green peas, and gravy—how could I resist? Even though I’m not much of a meat person, temptation won this time.

It was my first visit, so I asked the staff for a recommendation and decided to give it a shot. The layers of flavor offered a surprisingly complex taste, and to my delight, they balanced everything really well. Definitely worth trying!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcmY5L3hXCwB1fZLyVwa0EkUI5OSglkOUNXgTM&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Mona Zad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMR4E2eGeCM0YXIbpTdTSJbxtosgSXZZMVun99jHaxXCgVa1_f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience for my first visit to this Australian café! The Lamington cake was excellent—perfect texture with a delightful coconut flavor and whipped cream on top. I also tried their white flat coffee, which paired beautifully with the dessert. Definitely planning to come back and try their famous pies next time. Highly recommend this spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM73zPphxadziv6e0HxBYRErT-1szIzCcVStpCt&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Karl Flanagan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhtirzD0mdP9P2x8hQPRsaXU_3_5DCvt1LrUd3FyFx6TUTYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Traditional peaked pie and long black coffee for brunch hit the right place. Couldn't resist trying out the desserts and opted for the lemon meringue. Both were so good. Hightly recommended anyone who's driving by or simply curious. I'll have to return another day for a pie flight lunch. From humble beginnings......","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_-id6_yuatUiG3yk9KNW-rNI71pivbc3-bCVQ&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Iced mocha was extremely sweet, would recommend asking half sweet. Bright spot with lots of sitting. Haven’t tried any food since I’m not into pies, just happened to be in the area and wanted something cold to drink in a hot summer day. They also sell beers and have a cute patio.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMocOpZLFwutLUEoruSQibXHR57ymR5ewSt0mjT&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pie flight!! Came with four mini pies…chicken, veggies, Aussie, and peach coconut. Great way to try different kind of pies though I still liked the peaked Aussie pie the best. We also liked peach coconuts pie.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8CDkQlgYr-LmaiUP1wwU3HqqsLvW7lv6zhLy7&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Olga O.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeV9paF7MActTa0K4EXEhpSsxLDjI8EhLGL81BDcMklmCzJ_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I don't blame the business for the soaring prices, but $8+tax for a single sausage roll... that's insane.
The food is still delicious, however, $18+ for  barely warm peaked pie where you need to dig for filling (ordered butter chicken and only found a piece of meat when was halfway through it) and $8 roll is a bit too much.
Also, asking for tips that by default start from 15% when you have to wipe the table with napkins, then pick up your own food, then take away your plates, discard leftovers and put empty plates into the trays that are not emptied by staff is not right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFzV9iZuVhujl6I8BHoEAVGSnyN6fGqC9u9V8H&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-3-26"},{"Name":"Judy Liang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFW5Hsaw-gYHcFvxWIOBaJ5LzgvsAUy5D69g2t3bvT5LGqVv8z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven't had a good meat pie for awhile and I'm glad I finally tried peaked pies! The savory pies smelled so good and the taste was UNREAL! Not too salty even though the pies were filled with sauce. The black pepper flavor really hits (chunky pepper steak)! Also, it is fresh and hot so be careful when you bite into it! My friend had a cinnamon roll and she was obsessed with it as well! Will visit again soon! And they have a bus stop right outside the door!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSAiMW1jvawKm2dIQmu0uOjjOquu9ZhcU7CCjo&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Viona Halim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5PMLEtvgkAwv2IjmL8XXm0-Ly_XpBo5Kd0Hv2pxoQ26_Hfy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really satisfying savory pies perfect for lunch. They're not cheap pies by any means but they're definitely tasty pies with flaky crusts.

Highly recommend to get them "peaked" which adds mashed potatoes, mushy peas, and gravy on top. The filling themselves are already moist, but gravy makes everything tastes better!

The mini lamington cake on the other hand was alright. It was slightly dry imo, but we'll definitely come back to try their other pies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2BKG-dUSb7AxjUvXy0TK7xyBqtYUKfif8XEoK&fid=0x0:0x964d742028f61058"],"When":"2023-10-2"}]

[{"Name":"YVR Duke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbrjJ5U6gKw7Gn1zE_GlxhUndims9WHlh7sVaHLXVrjOFlYd_B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Typical food court’s Hong King style breakfast.  You can get beef rice noodle, Two-egg HAM (choice of luncheon meat, sausage or ham) and toast, and a cup of Hong Kong style milk tea or coffee.

Staff are friendly and very efficient when it is busy.  You can get your breakfast faster than when you are at McDonald’s.

Two-Eggs HAM and Toast

In food court, you cannot really choose how your eggs can be done.  Ham sausage and luncheon meat is not anything particularly high quality and the toast is typical Asian style white toast.

Satay Beef Rice Noodle

There is a expected taste on traditional Hong Kong style satay beef noodles, and it doesn’t really meet that standard.  There are two other healthier choices on menu.

Milk tea

The Hong King style milk tea served here is, i would say, quite average.  Not particularly good or bad.  it is authentic in a way, not the best type of authentic but average.

For under 10 dollars, here you can something somewhat fulfilling.  Somewhat comforting if you are from Hong Kong missing some home-style breakfast.

Nothing more you can ask for when tax is included and there is no tips expected.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuXjf1i_IA1cKnShEnuKm31NLDO1eg7oQo9xWv&fid=0x0:0xd18f33afebe493d6"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Cole Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOU6XCX3s_R0vWndse-P-J59JZDVGZbi6kfyG2pJARhX4qsYzZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My go to in crystal for Asian and asianized western.

They have good food here, the ladies are friendly. Kind of.

I think they've been serving with the most consistent food quality and prices over the last decade.

I recommend their salted fish and chicken fried rice, a classic.

I'd likely come back again, because it make a great bite when you're finished buying groceries.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrr6mVl0DSzU3S_cZMhazZK0zwtK9K8AzELJu-&fid=0x0:0xd18f33afebe493d6"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Lister Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWbNvO55wOzkDRxCcJ-fMoCcdWyut5hlx-H_zUreRnwso9_V0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very delicious Chinese food. $13 combo two choices plus rice and soup. Had spicy chicken and chives","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv_lMZo1cf9TIgHxJkByf0vPJ0ke_hbmMHY2Hd&fid=0x0:0xd18f33afebe493d6"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Daniel Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrVd67d7uU974eU_qTUE2z9HO_CgJZEmwGwQZmsR3nz_Sy-AdO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I considered my self a Cantonese cafe expert and always love trying curry brisket on rice everywhere, this is really disappointing…

The “real deal” has a good portion of brisket and potato, mix with fragrant flavourful curry

The photos you guys see, have significant imbalance of beef brisket! 5 pieces including tendon and a piece of fat, the rest are just chopped bell peppers and onions. Curry is nothing but a yellow sauce

Do not recommend this for $15🥶","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXUONtxExyIZ22ZfbjdhkQkkm4e_dOwcyohIOY&fid=0x0:0xd18f33afebe493d6"],"When":"2023-3-3"},{"Name":"Phone suzanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIovxXGSBbpRujzl74kbCvFOzJp7e0ULCdZBLR9HoOP6p92ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible attitude from the older waitress. Had sweet sauce chicken noodles, got a small portion of meat with lots of noodles that tastes incredibly bland. It's obvious that they are trying to lower the cost. I would strongly recommend against eating here. NO THANK YOU!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cyrus Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdRQimrQeVWgdU6NaWMloGGT9KPecvYQutRiBNNLVEWoWjyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The service was largely subpar, in the sense that they speak to you as though you owe them something. But what really concerned me was the food : the food was also rather disappointing. The curry chicken wasn't spicy and as someone who grew up with that dish in Hong Kong, I know for a fact that it wasn't suppose to taste like that. I really do hope this is just a separate instance, but the chicken I had that day was bland. The curry was the main source of flavor in the dish and unfortunately, the curry simply wasn't up to standard, whether in Vancouver or in Hong Kong.

As a redeeming quality, the portions were big for the price and you can split them into two meals, but I personally didn't do that cuz I think one meal like that was more than enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John lender","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkcpQ1MYMsPpPJ3JDffI_rwr5iRvTie5E35hqQo57LwH2qf8Dv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I usually love this place but getting more expensive for breakfast now day. I bought combo A & B total $24.00 include cold drink

But for lunch item still ok $15.75 come with cold drink","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNI_D0SGN0sBsaQhJH3ppY1Tvd_n9oY7J9-sxcN&fid=0x0:0xd18f33afebe493d6"],"When":"2023-5-14"},{"Name":"Jade Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJWSVoZW1CCY-_xhdgdeWOnL28P_e39FAE_t38PKZ_hYo17g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered take out. Beef brisket with glass noodles. The noodles are transparent and thick (not like Korean japchae). It was alright. But the disappointment is only 4 pieces of beef and one of them is utter fat and inedible. Also ordered the soy sauce rice noodles with beef. The noodles was good. A bit salty. But beef was so tough and inedible and few pieces. Giving 2 stars for the cold drinks, added 75c each. Had the milk tea and "Ying Yong". The drinks are good.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Kevin P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkDBk3e1Ip_bQRNhdYV04jXqFUg3jOtnLdryylvdelhRMP-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing double espresso macchiato ☕️at a location only nearby locals may know.
I personally didn’t know about this place until recently but wish I had known sooner.
Small area for outdoor seating is also available for those rare sunny days in Vancouver","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTZWu0PMlHEPgCqcqZkkAs3rbQxQGz5oIUApAe&fid=0x0:0xd88620a72c11dfbe"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Martin Matahari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAn1gLSlBMeGXZBHUnKkSJRx9LUQmHP9VKEpiPVA6PU8EOwPbl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Got a takeout coffee here, latte, and the roast was not too bad, not super bitter. But the quality of the milk wasn’t good. There was a plasticky aftertaste that I could tell it was cheap milk. There was ample seating and the ambiance was nice. Just wish they invested in better dairy products to improve their products. Staff was ok, average.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMttTPnl3bSvZNc1htjegwW_nIGj9l0kFMd6gfG&fid=0x0:0xd88620a72c11dfbe"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"mehrsa kazeroonian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM1lLEqmMksgol23r92UT7tstgmJXGUfF_daWvZHX2f1OtKqhq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious drinks and sweets, Nice and kind people and clean surrounding🌹🌹
Negin is so friendly","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgc9rDwj0NHbp0z7CbxUKy-Nrpx9HTRqSwFgi4&fid=0x0:0xd88620a72c11dfbe"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Aaron G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKstDhbd58MjtbnCrT08KosG0qF__vGcLbau-yPNhc06Pj5bg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"If you're looking for a spot to grab a coffee and get some work done, I'd think twice. There are other coffee shops within a 5 minute walk that won't:

-Interrupt a work call to ask if you're going to buy a coffee. Yes, I'd love x, can I pay for it when this call is over?

-Have someone else interrupt you 5 minutes later to ask if you're going to buy a coffee. Yes, I'd like x, but I'm stuck on this call -- can you help me out with that please?

-Have the owner come over and tell you this not a restaurant and you can't just sit here using wifi. As I've told your staff, I was late for a call and couldn't wait at the counter to place an order.

Note, this wasn't my first time at CuppaJoe. I've been grabbing a coffee there at least once a week for the past few months.

At the end of the day it's a great way to lose a customer that lives nearby.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Esra Kırbaş Kırdı","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcBbZ5SjcOv3S9fKk0tsJLEbWeh-7338zt4bOWFv8nMbg0rTjS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Italian style coffee in Burnaby, awesome breakfast wraps, vegeterian options available. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Chris Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6WjhE7O_z0dL-4WeNoLevaXaY3DBcdBlBeszJiK--UOXjTJcw2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time having weekday breakfast here. Very good fresh egg and bacon. Like the crispy hash brown. Unfortunately the servers said no refill for coffee but the menu doesn't say it. I only asked for a little bit more and I would think a good service will still fill some more coffee and I was the first customer.

My feedback to make it clear in the menu for no refill because I always have refills for coffee there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjrhWht4HHO3nQHXLRECYUCfOs7BMntP23yT74&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"kitty phung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9z9Rf2ykwBl2eDGDQFqS7fubwPLZRMljGtMyo1LWNQsxLfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I came in with a few girlfriends for an early Christmas get-together. This was my first time, but the others had been before. Everything was excellent! My favorites were the lemon ricotta pancakes and the chicken and waffles. The crispiness was perfect—no sogginess at all. The hash browns were also amazing, so delicious! And the Hollandaise sauce was incredible.

The staff was very attentive and always ready to assist.

We'll definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNI2GT7w4Vuyb3gYeyxYiwvXJQ-LhiUzaEIw8TW&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Cindy M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGKoLguedM393K_wR1xMOVrvE3ThWeh1Ms4feKswKRb-YaoDvm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We ordered the truckers breakfast. It had nice thick slices of bacon and tomatoes with a good chmichurri. The lemon ricotta pancake has a good flavour but a bit of a chewy texture I was not used to. The pulled pork eggs benny was okay, but nothing special. The Thai iced with coconut milk was tasty, except there was an additional piece of raw onion in my drink. Servers were apologetic and replaced it. The orange juice was the same as they serve from the IKEA cafeteria. I expected something better. It was busy and the servers were helpful.

There was a  lack of air conditioning which made for an uncomfortable meal. The place was alright, but the perhaps other reviews had set the expectation high. I’m not running to come back. Maybe in the fall when it gets cooler, or not at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjXjZnNHHRzfPDTEQ62Nqxja81-5jDeOe68ysN&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Anna Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEcZfbsoWDqf9VhDccjUC6lp_alTzUBelHIC9wioqUA2b2fS4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is fantastic, really love their bacon and staffs are friendly enough to share the source for their food. The venue felt a bit empty and décor won’t match up with the food quality. Overall, very delicious, no wonder some people think it is the ceiling of Vancouver’s brunch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNm_Xcs1X8e3u2jAXvHtd2ltW1rEy3_ipdaVqMy&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"Tanisha Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-xx3K0iGw_qb-ltTzaUMCTALn9JE9E7NPAbbzI4HTpiMZBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here today with friends and everything was delicious. There were six of us and between us all we tried:
- chicken and waffles (regular and spicy)
- the kitchen sink
- veggie benny
- pulled pork benny
- trucker platter

The portions are big- the chicken and waffles came with three large thighs! Just a couple things to note are that the spicy chicken and waffles wasn’t actually very spicy at all (and it’s an extra charge), and the bacon was lacking salt and tastes kinda more like ham.
Their iced matcha latte and Thai iced tea are both very good.

Service was fast and surprisingly no wait on a Sunday! Even if it gets busy they take a waitlist online. This is definitely going to be my go-to brunch spot in burnaby from now on.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM46-8rIP_DJhtq_0zT0fiyfTkSaoN4BugDpP_m&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really miss the beet salad they used to have here.

UPDATE July 2024: Finally revisted after they expanded into the neighbouring unit. They have a lot more seating now which is nice because it used to get busy during peak times before.

They also have weekday specials now. When we visited, it was a bacon, egg, and cheese sammy with hashbrown. Good value. We also got the crab cake benny complete with beautiful runny yolk. Make sure you order some dip to go along with the super crispy tater tots.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgM2H8s9WcLswtIjzjSEqCLq1WH4XXKSKt8d0G&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Lukas Schroeder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdptCACNz82_PtG4Bt8mi48TwfvBwhyqsr_zrww4ds0RG0AzMM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious, hot, fresh food. Wasnt very busy at 12pm on a friday, service time was standard if not pretty quick. Our food did come out about 2-3 minutes apart, which I didnt care about as it was so clearly made fresh.
Hope you have an empty belly for the fry/hash portions!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO076GM7JSBOJD3ClW4OGplHTBg4gsvVm3f_PJr&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Jenn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRm654M6WEPKpMVyI_-_CuYSSnZvfd29M3aYNWNqYhiLyRGrBS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"These were the best hash browns I’ve ever had! So crispy and well seasoned. The avocado toast was disappointing as the ratios were not good and it was overall quite bland. Service was also really bad as the server took our order, brought it out then never came back. We tried to get her attention 3-4 times to pay and finally another server noticed us and brought out the bill","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2ZHu6fLWZTX6K3w_Tf0bFQRHdOL8y7eSrh4LX&fid=0x0:0xfbccdd2c95c1cb47"],"When":"2024-10-2"}]

[{"Name":"Fady Daniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtSa8909Zvb8JHUTGGVcRXnet67ACdiu-ilSLWe7UkrDATPic=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"very nice place they have very good service. I love this place. I come here a lot. They have fresh ingredients. There is lots of parking around it.
Also, very nice music reasonable prices
We've been today with my daughter. She got a hot chocolate. I got iced tea.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuTfHg6F6bnm06K2PHh-rpx1QsGPSxOn19Qos&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The vibe is super cool, modern, cozy and laidback. A very new and upcoming chain location and is by far the nicest I have visited beforehand.
Im an avid fan of this fantastic chain and awesome coffee joint so took FULL advantage of grabbing a To Good To Go haul and boy did I get a surprise! A filo'loaded Pastry army equipped to take down anyone, fantastic value and great, fresh products made from natural and minimum ingredients. I managed to pickup:

Spiced Apple Pumpkin Muffin
Candycane Muffins
Cappuccino Loaf
Pumpkin Orange Scone

Everything was super yummy, wholesome and fresh with great flavors of home baking style goodies.
Definetely recommend and will always return!
Support Canadian businesses!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIxg5JbLCzHviJ3cmVLRZPC0dgDkO9PBxREx0W&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2023-12-30"},{"Name":"Jasmine D H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEb4caEP8q51G4Q6FltQZ0tzjgp9nyrYClLo_WuTzcS_aoUd4-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's really cute and spacious place. Nice and bright as well as friendly staff and very clean. The coffee is much better than say other chain coffee places too! More flavor and way more options. 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDYFHw1xAxGkOFgdXvjtmNwtlQ5O5eaK85X5kv&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Al","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJke_H51lEVtqmQ6Mwhj0R5MqDW7L2xLlIdf0sg4kPFJFF0D9I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly people and super cozy location. Treat customers good and look after you.  Place is a clean and welcoming atmosphere. Free parking around and after some shopping close by you can have hot drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwMRsVNoVQshBUM7o0VEj91QaZ_CCpqfocWP5Y&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2023-11-27"},{"Name":"Destiny Sloane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaUBiTJOQoYgRBSbpDJgBjbHyLPSrLFsH_OrtvYNZfQDoymA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My recent visit wasn’t okay, especially because the drink tasted very milky and the way the barista handled my feedback. This is probably going to be the last time and maybe it's good for them that they don't have me as their customer. The drinks are okay but there is no customer service at this place, especially this time when they made me walk back with the drinks. The person who made my drinks doesn’t seem to be okay with my feedback based on how he reacted, but I think I’m entitled to give feedback as a customer. The reason I give them 2 stars is because they at least made a new drink and up size for me this time, it’s wed anyway, otherwise I would rate them 1 star. I know that he may think he's very good at his job and probably believes he made the very best drinks, but if he put his ego down and listened to customers, he would understand that the drink tastes different this time. That's all I wanted to say. He wasn’t rude or anything, but his facial expressions and words sounded ironic. He seems upset when his colleague’s asking what’s going on. In the end, I just walked away with the new drinks he made (which actually taste better, saying this with no bias). Though I live a block away and this place is the closest coffee shop to my house, I still consider not revisiting anytime soon, as I think it would be good for both of us not to have bad feelings toward each other.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Molly Boucher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_QcVS348jkCoM0SQ_B1NoeQ2o5lrwZ030Mr1UKH6paS362Qd63g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely LOVE this Waves location. Morad and his team are always so welcoming. I am greeted so wonderfully when I come here. I Cannot recommend this Waves location enough!

I am really grateful to this awesome team!
I wish i could give more than 5stars!

All the best team!
- Molly","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pat Waslen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkC-Tyq5Sy6eH64VG6FwtcQj-OJYnSvli4ZLpkEY8S6PBvQxBoIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Well in a neighbourhood full of coffee shops Waves at Hastings & Carleton makes the effort to stand out.  Always clean, bright and airy.  It has its own little meeting room for customers to use .  A welcoming environment with a cosmopolitan clientele.  Ash the manager is friendly and kind. Food is your standard coffee shop fare. Lots of options for warm or cold drinks.  A nice place to visit and to stay awhile.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTk9Ko7XTOk62HQWBZPgR2_2QprR_4UaBg-tYk&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2022-5-10"},{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Picked up a Too Good To Go order from here! Satisfying bag with 4 coffee house baked goods/treats. The cheesecakes were moist and nicely packaged so they retained their shape individually. The loaf and muffin (white chocolate) were nothing special, but did retain a decent flavour when warmed up. Waves is reliable and quick stop for coffee and simple baked goods.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNls6ukrH7Z3ZM3MkSlGuo1E7sRVZc1SnKtqWcs&fid=0x0:0xa9375dfb83c12bb6"],"When":"2023-3-29"}]

I especially like the story of Muhammad Ali behind the coffee shop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM64UWaRfUrOq3LKQukOMGoWf77tqtIDGJMhgLf&fid=0x0:0x686f1b477ef30aee"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"B F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1OW6_5mWq5T5cXzcmpwoGkYLBwInikRzneyVxV3WvtCyYWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"since new owners in 2024, qualiy has gone down alot! [{"Name":"Esther","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWm4MrcOMcE-MmdjBoKAjDTfZHS26hzehvqwvBxROz7rHTb9kPKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their spanish latte is so good! In the future I’d get it a little less sweet. To be honest, I think this coffee shop is a little on the pricier side. But overall the service and vibes are great🤩

This place is probably one of my favorite places to study and hangout. There are plenty of seats and charging spots.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4xqEZh0djdJFdgYSMpyBmUdblzZ7A1bzScngD&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Arun & Jayati Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1nRUaNnMhfrJXEHRAsLmucE76xhX7zjbHxTwvQuVl2h1215pD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a delightful place!  Large comfy areas to sit around, chat, read and feel the calm and genuine atmosphere. It feels like home. The baristas have a fabulous sense of humor and always welcoming. The food is clean with vegan options too. Extremely clean and well kept. This is my favorite haunt. I buy my coffee beans from there and they grind it for me with a ready smile. Go and enjoy this friendly place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1dnMFYxdD-9t8xZJzaEDOsCi5bk6BIQCuxDgA&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-3-28"},{"Name":"amy s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYgcyWpyGHBvYuOaRvvIYCZkZrtJGCDEvJz1JjzjSgkvyuf1tM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I enjoyed their caramel macchiato very much,, 9/10! but the lavender latte was pretty bland :( I loved the atmosphere though and their service was nice and quick :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4GslEoNBWvgbbZ6UxqAGDYJ-iATzyVjzA21uD&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Tsui-Fang Hu (Tracy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_ro0txUL1mG25heVUuoyMTMpTlXMMMT4-dXmn5rgUocYrBx5y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved the atmosphere there! It’s spacious and relaxing, air quality is pretty good (which is my top priority when it comes to a cafe as I usually spend time doing some work). Barista was friendly which made me feel comfortable and welcomed ☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkJlKMUr73kT1zcsnPskdBFwO7Mko5TbxidfN-&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Melinda W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqFa91nGQX9-WVxFZ-rAUul10GF70bhWZFQZe97ymoPVUZrvFxnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my second favorite cafe after Nemesis. The decor is chic, the staff are friendly, coffee is pretty good and the pastries and bread are delicious.

The barista is good with latte art. My friend got a swan in his mocha which was absolutely gorgeous. Sadly I forgot to take a picture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN74gXfZ7x24_tI8Jv-40O0N0gmG5h6iRw-lVL6&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"tm2cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUz_jeSUR-1dFOa4r3dihZ4MBKQB_6kbIY15uMhq9G7Flg1HsA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Freddo’s are nice blended but headsup cofffee are pretty strong. I like strong coffees so I dont mind :). I took pic of menu for update. This is Oct 12, 2024","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPN32Xhujs477gcXFNdLXSBOILBwVRbsZdKSNIB&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2024-10-12"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A nice coffee shop in this area. The staff are friendly and helpful. The decorations, seating, washrooms and space are bright and clean.
My wife is so happy with her earl grey tea with pot and cup. They use the loose tea and the quality is good.
My coffee is little cold since it sits in the kettle. It makes me give the 4 stars not the 5 stars.  Anyway it's a nice coffee shop for meeting with friends or just have a drink.
The outdoor chairs are not comfortable enough.  Maybe the busy street sidewalk is not suitable for some bigger chairs there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdL8qWU73XkqWIR9rivlwgbb-YJEJDxVuXkHg-&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2022-9-26"},{"Name":"Dhrumit Sheth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9r95Es3YQAlkO6Yw2Yg4R0kNpVi-5oWmckdwTw51wptlXqgTS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing coffee and banana bread! Croisant was one of the best I ever ate. I ordered a drip coffee and my wife ordered hot chocolate. Both tasted delicious! There were vegan option like Banana Bread. It was delicious. I would definitely recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQKX6xkNU6a4hUUrPL0fZ1QqfSkNE7Nh2FZFDi&fid=0x0:0xf448061cd198dab3"],"When":"2023-2-12"}]

[{"Name":"Nadezhda Bogoley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXViJlc7Ezrz7eVF7KUG_I5Hb-Ew_10mP0vESIupkLM97sa73E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very lucky to live within walking distance of this wonderful bakery. I really love their baked goods, most of all the whipcream donuts, moderately sweet and tender, and all the other products as well. I especially like the atmosphere of the place and the friendly staff, which makes me want to come back many, many times. Success and prosperity to your bakery💖","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHwluGotjanqZ6edvioy_Sm_0Q33xtlUQLU48&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Євгенія Загадаєва","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb4if_bhRyE6F_-h06OXfCe1VGQxxk77kcyF0lKcETdukilzpR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Got 6 different pieces of cake from there, only two turned out edible. The rest was smelling like a dirty socks. Buttercream is extremely fat and not fresh. Wouldn’t recommend this place for dessert!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNTo7WYPsEiq8OmQvQhzJMtwIe8qkXcgUV04Sb&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here since the bakery came under new ownership last year, but it didn't disappoint! We thought the variety of pastries and their quality were not compromised. Ordered some sausage rolls, cookies, their pear tart, and pistachio roll. The sausage rolls had adequate meat filling. With the cookies, we're allowed to mix & match when purchasing a dozen or half a dozen. Good nutty flavours for the almond and caramel crunch cookies, and the jam shortbread still maintained its moistness! The pistachio roll still tasted great the day after when warmed in the microwave to allow the inner filling to melt.

The only issue we had was with the pear tart and separating it from the outer wrap/paper. It was stuck and we had difficulty peeling it off, so had to basically scoop and eat the pastry from the attached paper. Will return to try some different pastries and baked goods! Hopefully they update their website in the near future, as itemizing their products would be valuable for new customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM36NfE9WfhwfylF5fG9IiAnE_sUOMMyq3ZnlUZ&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"Priyamvada Trivedi Bajpai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD2R3z5XCnn6iN0aOD9S1uFgt3ZJD1eBRZcFk0NYAQCECfbXW5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been to Valley bakery many times now and it delights us every time. The bakery items always taste so delicious and fresh especially all the cakes with whipped cream icing which feel so light. I love their surprise baskets too. I recently got my daughter's birthday cake made by them, a tall purple cake with vanilla sponge and nougat filling and I'm finishing it off greedily, not offering the leftovers to anyone in my house LOL. This place is a gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzAq0T7BBuPFo4RaexbtMhssrwl6czqyoVrEH2&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-3-11"},{"Name":"samira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwkQGMre8jgbaip4E0o2r4QwZ6hsRUFGFhUhbAr4O--khz6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the snowflakes and eclairs here! Will definitely visit again. Everything was so fresh and tasty. Not too sweet, just the great balance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0Fze1ejrkw8Hvya-fCfYE5nsZWKw_a-AxzJpA&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Misty Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiOIsbeMdPLGZQQq4tbfnigd9rxmZvr3zcyJYxR7sCOyju702f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing bakery and price is so good too! $3.95 for a big cinnamon roll! Also they gave us free cookies :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPPcCDwAGcusJ6wYdcuEdV5Dl6qXMbu4DvNJ0h&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"cgmc70","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzXD32DfRqqvnrxut0qW4Xp1dRXi1jGQ41udzAPASAQpd5iacc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loving the new items @The Valley Bakery !!! Mixed fruit galettes (yummy!!)
Daily colourful selection of delicious donuts, nice selection of HUGE & tasty croissants, etc. You have to try one of the delicious pear or apple French tarts too !!!
AND there’s a friendly barista waiting to serve you a tasty latté now as well …
Friendly service tops it all off !! 🥐🍩🍰☕️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLzaoYeikFZS5jww2GV4HUWOC6MNsv1camKvW0&fid=0x0:0x65bb04d84aa344a6"],"When":"2024-1-27"},{"Name":"Trina Swami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBMHGUNBomopDFw_AEySRbNEfOaYI6CylUOLh7Q-e-N38Z4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Bakery is hit or miss with the customer service, I always get something here when i do come in(I miss their vegetarian sausage rolls, they stopped bringing them back.) but find when it's busy they don't want to help, lady who works there said she isn't working but yet helps someone with an order meanwhile I was behind a guy gonna order but the boy who was working was gonna help the guy after me? I Don't get it, I worked customer service in a bakery, if you want your customers you don't denying service, I confused about this bakery, better off going to Kandell bakery which is a couple blocks away instead because at least I don't get turned down for help or for ordering. Maybe fortuna is better.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Rein Belaza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViGnLySeh-SHnUMUXJryDRxEmnF4Doki2bgbyScLG4Jp6atxb6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"awful and horrible service! would've give it negative stars if i can. i kindly asked for a container to transfer my beef noodle soup as it's hard to eat in the paper container they gave me bc the soup is overflowing and i can't eat without the noodle splashing all over but the manager said that they don't have any container to transfer it to even if i can clearly see that they have one at the back. he was rude and was not providing me any good service. would definitely not go back here. they need to fix their manners!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIPqtqv_bHscQ6uLlj0HilM-ConTJJY4J92tGy&fid=0x0:0xa02e98c76e68b849"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Rajat Painuli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEEoWoiBmIfDXeBCI5AbNk2-JU_9V5bjlvxQp92GYfjt8jaw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited Bubble Waffle Cafe and decided to try their sour spicy chicken rice, and it was a huge disappointment. The dish arrived cold and dry, making it unappetizing right from the start. The chicken lacked flavor and seemed overcooked, while the rice was clumpy and bland. I expected a vibrant mix of flavors, but instead, it felt like a chore to eat. To make matters worse, the cashier was rude and dismissive, which added to the overall negative experience. I wouldn’t recommend this dish or the cafe to anyone looking for a satisfying meal. Overall, it was a letdown, and I left the cafe feeling unsatisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyndra Puntanar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcwGTTVTFb6bJqnWpAaQonGTghsZedQOs7TWs5ebDTnXXt9grC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Listen to the other reviews! DO NOT GO AND EAT HERE. We love bubble waffle cafe because of their good food. But wow the customer service in this restaurant is horrendous. The guy in the counter is super rude. As in super!!! You will really have a bad day when you encounter him. I suggest to the guy to change his career if he's always looking for quarrel.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1xaMBvf-pw29Vk5Yt3peEcF2MXeCjfGYNq3X5CClmNs-i_44=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am a huge fan of this chain - this location is a complete let down. Management for this location needs to be replaced or retrained. The portions are less than half of other locations. Drinks are smaller than the other locations - even if I ask for no ice, the cup shouldn’t be half full only. Completely avoid this location. You will have better luck in the food court if you’re looking for Asian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOid8POSSuq35eKVdzTXPkk3DCeN2SG-vjnXUQ0&fid=0x0:0xa02e98c76e68b849"],"When":"2024-3-24"},{"Name":"Vivi Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIokdCA9t79WcqMQW_PpuhXv-LCk0OQTU7Io2_eGyShdvPzBzM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to like this restaurant. But I went today and I can’t even give them one star….
Food wise, the chicken was good. But the noodles was all broken into little pieces. I can’t even pick it up with my chopsticks! And we ordered one chicken soup would taste full of MSG, and one fish soup which has no taste at all…. The bubble waffle came before the meal, by the time we eat it, it’s all soggy and cold.

We are a family of 4 with a 3 and 6 year old. Order 2 noodles, 2 drinks, 2 bubble waffle, extra side of Chicken. When we asked for 2 cups of water for the kids, they said I need to pay for the cup!!!! I have never had a sit down meal where they charge for a cup of water!!!  That’s just ridiculous!

Never going back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tasfia Ahamed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoYBDXI-OrwM8tJ5g6NuHO70If1PIQgmcVEXkYJfo_BmwFRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Attitude of the employees are not good.I asked the girl 3 times to do less ice on my drink as I had scratchy throat when I saw she used a lot of I asked her again to make it less she gave a look and just removed one cube of ice and started making the drink.More over waffles are made way ahead of your order.Waste of time and money","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7cowBwGwSRhkAZyciKdOuDz72ZQUiFKe-Pc0T&fid=0x0:0xa02e98c76e68b849"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"C Liew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPZ8c66MjpgdxIU5mRxsOhQGiJpZMMGoKhRn3-1sa-o6bq8q4f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Always love their waffles and bubble waffles.  Glad that this outlet opened!  I’ll say it’s definitely good place to hv a quick meal, tasty and very reasonably priced.  Will be one of my favourite eateries for sure!
Staffs are very friendly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEYQl9q4XtVo9tIAneY_VurTCGw4zm8x_aZ2du&fid=0x0:0xa02e98c76e68b849"],"When":"2019-7-15"},{"Name":"Earl Flormata","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHEYR5crfzT5mFZF5yY6PmVwTawXCmDPm3U8WVZUqH5mb8rOP9MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location for bubble waffle. [{"Name":"Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCDMUY42ah4aAgta84ssT2DYa3PFsR3r4fbxhBdcs3AXShIgTOYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A fun neighborhood spot for ice cream and sundaes. Counter seating and a few tables available. Lots of seasonal flavors available. Takeout pints and ice cream sandwiches are a must try if you’re buying for the road!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWc7P31g7ggOOAvcZPM4yp6I30hRknYcxBztPk&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Yumi Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPFqDkxESWXC88SASBBMb5TodqjqiFWci9IiQVgmoclWTpAqs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love love love the ice cream and soda at Glennburn. Been here several times now and their ice cream is ALWAYS solid. Whenever I visit Vancouver- Burnaby area this is one of the spots that I must visit. Recently tried the FOG & the fruity loop flavored sodas with vanilla ice cream on the side. Would highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbjvC6eI6T0VMmrZblBOy85imxDCF_L-j0HLoH&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"L Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQvIh5w41NvNm69uuQ6fEFfx4_xCLgbz-lb793dTjac89L3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An old fashioned soda shop in the heart of Burnaby BC.  This place is always a staple and we drop by every year when we are in town.  Wide range of products including ice creams, floats, milkshakes, sundaes and other desserts.  We ordered a chocolate milk shake, hot fudge sundae and scoop of ice cream.  The chocolate milkshake was rich and creamy with whip cream on top,  the sundae came with whip cream, cherry and walnuts.  The single scoop of lemon sunrise was light, zesty and refreshing.  It was a pleasant experience as always.  They have dad’s rootbeer here as well.  Hands down always a great treat for the family","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfuI7ZUkPqTLkLL2VJcvCjqi4i83JjpT-sjJhg&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Amar M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBQWZODVOR5EgW_ud4WGBoPZzS3E7_T_DuyVRfFsnuGSHVIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First timers here.  Tried a bit of everything.  Banana Split was the clear winner - worth the cost - not a drop left.  Lime Rickey was refreshing and as advertised.  Small spot - bar seating is ideal in my opinion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOj-Pr1R0F2YRo5Jwwc4CPR63G2aTXCadvPsiF3&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Spike Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-bYH0S2j8q9mpEz9LWcLeOJc9r39CdWCQQyEHN9RaHr3ZaKJV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really great place to go for homemade soda's, floats, ice cream, and shakes. They have a great selection of classic and new flavours. There's normally a long line up on a hot day but the line moves fast. The staff are very friendly and very helpful. They also sell doggy ice cream!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbKO_TgQfbezolZzrzr9TG0F6AMLeOR5CCI6xe&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Keith Eastcott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk5BCUEJh42hOpsF-_OoCCbmyygcrHIJcijMiuq6slKML49qmN0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So absolutely beyond amazing. From the time you walk in you can tell this store is gonna be good. They have an old time soda shop vibe with glass containers of candy and old school milk shake machines and other decor to make it feel like the 1950's. They have a large list of flavors and different options like sundays, milkshakes, and 2 different kinds of banana split. The portions are ridiculously huge and could easily be split if you feel like sharing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpSLTLynC6Wr5XQETb2HlmeMa1IObtGMhOJrlk&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Ognjen Stajic (Ozzy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkSSU4eg1VXAeLi1fHS3IroDB794s-Cx1rfGJubYTxg0uZj5k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hear me out. Their ice cream is great, sizes are awesome and the place is really cute and retro.

What's truly great is their cakes. My kid had a birthday party and a lot of parents choose something like DQ for a birthday party - please don't.

Glenburn's ice cream cakes are amazing and comparable in price. Best thing? You get to support a local business and enjoy delicious snacks.

Order it, you won't regret it.

Do I sound like I'm advertising it? You bet, they are great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNL2tiRbiyDBZsp-zQrjCiq_AIzFVhR4vc0CFXn&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Jimina Almero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVHqAiyaVguwyrjIKIrFauUQ4ck0nbY7blKjG9gpN9m4eZsl4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Glenburn has been our go to for a delicious treat for the past few years. We always look forward to trying their seasonal flavors","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPc55YMu9nydqUykL3KTFAj38FcYhqxlOicNEHv&fid=0x0:0x858c5e898fdfa3c"],"When":"2024-12-10"}]

I enjoyed it! and I'm definitely coming back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9tx4v9J7XRV6V9IWP2j1GKNuNyMLBB4zcFIXK&fid=0x0:0x9126dc9d4eed48c6"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Allen Bakht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgPoVBGaUgzmRUqHXReJW1JnHL7TdotuxPSKPOAWiZsThJWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"What a terrible way to start a day by visiting this so-called cafe.
The breakfast sandwich and wraps were tasteless, and the coffee was terrible.
To make matters worse, the service was equally disappointing. The lady behind the counter was incredibly rude and unwelcoming. She seemed annoyed by any customer's presence and made no effort to be friendly or helpful. It's no wonder the place was empty.
I would strongly advise anyone considering visiting this cafe to think twice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Naomi Kragh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZLUAmyQRHAJJOvAgnTAMFOCBA9leIrpEFbTsp7S0XsUBWx9lRKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to have a good meal with real ingredients. This place definitely provides that "home cooked" feel. They made my order fresh and it was delicious. I would definitely go back again if I was in the neighborhood and hungry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt4St7H7tw_-aojTPlCP683VjLknTUoMzYgcxp&fid=0x0:0x9126dc9d4eed48c6"],"When":"2019-4-30"},{"Name":"Deirdre Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_Oc8v6QrILyrJI0L83nUelBdCqYYlUlerOucGglpTJbHj3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"love it. I happily  ate the same meal for a week in a row.  Great  food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNAX4IZiHBId_qyHSyeVsfuES2H42U8Lcz98wI&fid=0x0:0x9126dc9d4eed48c6"],"When":"2024-4-11"},{"Name":"Yuri Faenza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIxgHjemJViIUq8LqCJr1gtDtmnsS-uceO0ebfTBKpL0dt2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"You are probably considering having breakfast here if you are staying at the nearby hotel. We did not enjoy our experience, and after the first time we ended up going to the Starbucks at Gilmore station. I always try to shop local and avoid big chains, but here it was not possible. The breakfast combo for hotel guests is very rigid and it is not possible, eg, to upgrade the coffee to a cappuccino by paying extra. We asked for an extra paper cup so that our children could split the glass of milk. They refused it and told us to use the big glasses, which a toddler just can't use (and may quite likely break). All this was communicated to us in a not so nice tone. Food was average.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Convenient location for a quick bite if conducting business close by in this industrial area of Burnaby. Decent coffee, good soup and I enjoyed my Spicy Beef Bulgogi Korean Paninis. Interesting flavours with sweet onion, green pepper and tender bulgogi beef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXYzGtixm72w4fop_z77EKcZ6WzEoVoZMS5euc&fid=0x0:0x9126dc9d4eed48c6"],"When":"2021-10-9"},{"Name":"Marisa Castellano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP_e-6SpCCWpUAwHDWQrxAduKxHge5i2CmcBNDknsEiY6NcY0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Elements Café is a delightful gem for food enthusiasts looking for a unique culinary experience. The café boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect fr both casual and special occasions. Their menu offers a fusion of traditional and modern flavors, with a focus on fresh, locally sourced ingredients. The standout dishes include their artisanal sandwiches, vibrant salads, and a selection of exquisite pastries that are both visually appealing and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGp4-5zv7GtRDW52hdDlQh10zbNAZ2bDyY4If5&fid=0x0:0x9126dc9d4eed48c6"],"When":"2024-1-9"},{"Name":"Mahmood Naw Rouz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv5JlLlFL5c8x5Lao81Orts42VO1JtAth2aUb0neJMtl_2Njif=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cafe is awesome!
The lady was perfect!
I highly recommend it!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Mehdi Emamifar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY88Drfz_FNswLf99CbARyK9hbyH5mYT-OVIIdYcWQYUQOoWFG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Starbucks next to Gilmore Station is truly an exceptional place to relax and enjoy a great cup of coffee. It offers a pleasant and tranquil environment for customers, making it an ideal spot for studying, working, or simply meeting up with friends.

One of the standout features of this Starbucks is its friendly and welcoming staff. The baristas are always ready with a smile, providing excellent customer service and making sure every order is just right. Their warm and approachable demeanor adds to the overall positive experience.

Whether you’re looking to take a break from a busy day, need a quiet spot to work, or just want to enjoy some quality time with a good beverage, the Starbucks near Gilmore Station is a perfect choice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpGLLoyHjaYLZJWqSZBu8jKX0ZSx0-bB-uAUga&fid=0x0:0xde3d1317dab606a7"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Hamid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZeCAMeEgy6nfEH_q_cdx_kw6M9nQkJXu6z624ESesXG758gNKQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always got great service here. Great people and convenient location. Can accommodate 20 people easily inside and there are some seating areas outside too. Medium Late with a lemon loaf is my usual order which I enjoy the most. I have tried the chicken pesto sandwich before and it was tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOG5eRJGXKJR9NF1va0oerYwKbZH4vS5IxxNJut&fid=0x0:0xde3d1317dab606a7"],"When":"2022-6-13"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very convenient location right next to Gilmore skytrain station and very handy to grab a coffee on the go!
This Starbucks unfortunately seems to have a limited menu when ordering via the Starbucks app.
Staff efficiently make great tasting coffee and you get consistent results.
Coffee joint also has outdoor patio seating available which is pretty sweet!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1TXN2nDhZIrBp2MZaQckQU0AqTjkBEpmnIDxd&fid=0x0:0xde3d1317dab606a7"],"When":"2021-5-7"},{"Name":"Zareh Megerdoonian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsbPOIrk2Yl1yDK3I29z7I2dPVaKmhP3xib1VAIDZlyuslZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Doesn’t feel like a cafe walking in, very sterile - like a medical clinic.
Cream is behind the counter, cinnamon is behind the counter, always at least 1 person in a mask.
It resembles nothing to a cafe vibe, and their snacks are never fresh and come from some warehouse. No active conversation between clients and employees, and no customers talk to each other too - just stare at their laptop or phone. Yeah, nothing like Paris or Milan here - lol - zero soul here
Service is ok, employees just doing their job, they are nice, I don’t blame them","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurpreet Thind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFQfD_dLnMNqrkRe_Ns7EzXbGEFLaqjV62f5GMLazrBlWq_BU2sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pretty decent Starbucks location. Parking is definitely an issue. Being right across from sky train , should not be an issue. Staff was very courteous and quick in their service. WiFi was little slow but the place being packed and everyone on their internet machines, it was understandable. Overall the place was very reasonably clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWi_1Kj9l97vgArdvJ7x0TkdVVM4eRp0mCfpVi&fid=0x0:0xde3d1317dab606a7"],"When":"2019-11-24"},{"Name":"Angela Shen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLWS0WaWyf2U7mCiVLrIAfqTCkssR3Y-o6KP5Oy_aU5hwUXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have this Nitro Cold brew that richer than normal cold brew the staff is also so incredibly nice and kind. It's a great place to sit and hang out with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJJ2lBRP1ekFrRFLrye_wRX3LQ9dR-wWx2Y45X&fid=0x0:0xde3d1317dab606a7"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Dreaming Day","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu1_3uTnc4J6QMjMJInT2xcanxZtWP7H_9hgzhCFZ0KjHsEO2UCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The Asian woman in her 20s and brown hair is an extreme dog police! I had my small and well trained dog with me to pick up a mobile order - two other baristas were helping me with no issues (said my dog was cute and even gave her a large sized pup cup) and suddenly she pops out from the back and demands that we go outside in an unnecessarily authoritative tone. It’s 5:30am and there was one other guest there who was completely unbothered. WAY too overkill and enforcement-heavy on the dog policy. I just need 2 min to pick up and go. Why would Starbucks have pup cups if not to incentivize dog owners to come? Needs to chill out and use discretion to read the situational context.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miss Cinz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrAcR0nWLDdtNjX8gao3i1bs8jIVXL168fbuQfyx2lMrg64PuWUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This location just feels like closing whenever they want. Second time coming here on a different week and they’ve decided to close before 2 pm with no explanation. I’ve watched others walk by in disappointment when there’s never any warning they’ll be closing earlier.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX11ANDfpnFU7GmCeaVtU5cBwuWRqquWAK3F9_AUyciKpah0H5L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The days of finding a Starbucks on every street corner have long since gone. Imagine my surprise when on a rare trip to Highgate, I encountered this one.

I have never really had a bad experience at any Starbucks, and this visit was no exception.

I grabbed a Peach Green Tea Lemonade, and it was refreshing as a Summer's Day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6x-O9f7Z91fydu6FWgossKW93kMfoLLF_ASux&fid=0x0:0x74ae1c621c14ebbb"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"jonathan LY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpY4Nr1JwSro6nuX1ki1aFhJYT1oO-9jxVPyNHEFXbrHLECQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Don’t you think ice is too much? They almost give me the full cap of ice😅 she could have just given me a full cup of ice, but she still alms me some matcha in it. WOW very appreciate that my gratitude is beyond words👍👍👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsSX_KzulacUf7ZYPOk60MuqpwOKLy42GkJlQi&fid=0x0:0x74ae1c621c14ebbb"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Albert Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9Fv0yNGvtbx8QHQOR-NQBojnSXy-wOnKr-1lQp3bSnESE8g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's never available when you ask for a dark coffee around my break in 3pm at this location, only Pike instead. But today when I mentioned my concern, the friendly stuff told they can make a fresh pot for me. I am so impressed since I love strong and rich taste.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNF_0dc2TCG8hqp2vivQTKaW88LX2DhMytK6guHgklhLqRCCgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Subpar at best.. This is the closest Starbucks to me since I moved nearby. I often come here so often and I used to like the friendly barista. Now I’m noticing more and more issues with mobile order. There is huge amount stack of mobile orders just sitting on the counter because no one is calling out names on a timely manner for them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ember N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOVVSRZSBJ6e5O5jUUtiBAq23q-FcEx-8tVq1hmthlfDRNYcfgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"go to place for quick grab and go. don't stay here too long because it will be busy. best to do mobile order. but you need to also tell them that you are waiting for a pickup bec they will just continue to create drinks and not mind the mobile pickups not unless the order has been sitting completed for 5mins. just keep looking at what they are making so you can monitor if you have not been called for 5mins.

good washroom but again dont stay too long, too many people. staff are fast but very busy. would come back here if i crave for my dragon fruit drink again in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTAGsXubf0M6kksPB_H4yvAByBRW5J5GCoQBXb&fid=0x0:0x74ae1c621c14ebbb"],"When":"2022-8-3"},{"Name":"Ivan Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1Zv5EiNZ9X9m5kbuLRJRxtWgFATVzCOiu8e12Zt_UAwwmxA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Do not come here. 5 employees and only one of them is actually working. Service is super slow!

Following is actually my second review to emphasize the poor service! I made a mistake and came here again hoping that things might be better, but actual it's worse! Extremely slow and inefficient service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"H W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiEtu-Pfzzd7vMmnC1lRzmwYGQeuaGu_8hpE004heAd4NBbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location with a really well maintained space. Always clean and staff are upbeat and efficient. Part of a larger shopping complex so can get very busy at times and quite loud, but the good part is that means plenty of free parking around.

Washrooms are clean and small, but they have 3 so less chance of that awkward washroom wait. Place is also quite crowded but overall a nice hangout spot and great place to grab your coffee and go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwiYoTCxlbof59QcYCeMbUHEXxyt6UdA0lrpjf&fid=0x0:0x74ae1c621c14ebbb"],"When":"2019-9-14"},{"Name":"mdcuenca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU8SadqV3cVNy8Y10ZpTx7ICBswPazLwcB9e-OKg7mOGmtQRs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Star bucks coffee crew has no team work, no initiative to have good customer service. Not friendly and has attitude. This location at Highgate has very high turn over of crew. I got the coffee at 6 pm, Saturday December 16, 2023.  The group of hired people there seemed not friendly and just focus on doing their stock ups.  I even asked, “is there anyone going to help me?”

What a thumbs down crew on this location!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTR45p9w6VQzwXv0DdEOvtGDPPy_iNOEolDF2h&fid=0x0:0x74ae1c621c14ebbb"],"When":"2023-12-17"}]

The food was fresh and very cozy; i don’t like cheesecake much but the earl grey cheesecake was quite nice and worth a try ☺️ Servers were also lovely and the whole atmosphere was stunning, could see the sunset nice and clear 🌅","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmhz1EQYWvp7oC_PWCgpjGQMrObGSBypb9kyhA&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Johnny C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMH8aFZIGB5a7CFStbNQ6JGT0sYgxOttD7xMtIebcz8N9tnSzq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food quality was good.  Service was good.  Plenty of parking but maybe difficult to find a parking spot during golf peak times.  Overall I would have given them 5 stars.  A star was deducted because the seat was dirty with food crumbs and the burger bun was too charred.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRIIr6YONpsjnFCThRI2VFJx5FMqmqWcxGNVmU&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Tiffany M.H Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEEILPLKkaPpClYcrh-pqQr9Qp-ChcXOXh_6gWcHTjnAC6d-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was here with family on August 17th 2024 for dinner. Our server provided wonderful service and was kind to adjust the curtains so that the sun wasn't shining at us. She was also very attentive! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPz1NiBHaLnWU0J1sZO7hpmUWM06krwZ9evZ-HG&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"sterling lans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIvenuetfEWn36IEiriFUPO5kWX_zzj7sHU6kuq1Gz6fGRZZ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was absolutely spectacular!!! I ordered the Steak and it was cooked beautifully! I have never had a better steak experience in my life! I highly recommend eating in this fine dining establishment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTcWm2g2g6DCyqAk9k6FFBLxV0JqAZR4RQbDzW&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Nastassja Dorotich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn3xVQllagWYXZP_5pYQUbA_9S8FifHN2FImREt6v5HUwEzIUh5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our wedding was a dream, the absolute perfect day! Ella was such a kind and helpful coordinator. She answered all my questions promptly and made the planning process so easy. The chef was able to accommodate our request of a fully vegetarian wedding with vegan options, which was delicious! The team were all so kind and seemed to be having fun during the event, as well. The indoor and outdoor space offered the perfect flow. Gorgeous ceremony area, beautiful dinner area, fun bar area, and lots of outdoor hangout and conversation spaces with the front, back and side patios. Highly recommend Burnaby Mountain Clubhouse for your event! Thank you ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaIZbIfOza8oifP4B3yTat8R4OAdfZwcTxgaHy&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Betsy CT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQGGIyc_AHsnDVRkUQkbSnV2yECP14J_GFVoTan8z9D8GO3iLAQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visit. 5 of us celebrating a family birthday. All the food was tasty and service was friendly despite a bit of learning curve from new staff. Mistake orders were taken off the bill so it's all good. Such a a nice quiet pleasant location. Definitely will tell and bring others.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTffXP-mlv7qT6_2dqT86LGeNx5SNYsGr5K4kC&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"Katrina Stavenkos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu8k31K8bLBb3gU-CZZko7AdWW-2Kcangps-MS6U0qeb28LGs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"People are posting reviews and pics of wrong restaurant lol this one is beside a golf course not ontop of Burnaby mountain …

The restaurant smelled funny lol not sure what it was but yuck . Food was ok , the big full potatoes were not smashed as advertised , I smashed them up , no flavour , eggs Benny was ok . Daughter enjoyed her lobster grilled cheese . We shared a dessert hole in one something , was so small , should have two little cakes on the plate .
Service was good but never asked if we wanted another drink once we finished first one . Such a lovely area , and could be such a good restaurant , more appetizers offered , more sandwiches etc , if you ever need a over haul hire me lol","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORAAjuqpR3I4qgUkea_s7Bhhj9uQp5HSn9cUUR&fid=0x0:0xbde5969106292e16"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Lola Bradfield","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWurG33EZqdt6uDU7HAJsd_fp6jKSUDSbuLYzXg6oaLHuo7XC0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here, the server was amazing . The food was good, but not excellent or something to come back for. However, the atmosphere was not what we were looking for in a nice, expensive dinner restaurant.  The lights were way waaaay too bright and more appropriate to a cafeteria type of setting, which was too bad because the fixtures themselves were beautiful... the bright lights  gave the location a cheaper ambiance and very cold instead of a warm and welcoming feeling....","Images":null,"When":""}]

Starbucks is lucky to have them","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sunshine R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmBq-vH672PNgunu5-hqzLHWS3eOIQdFKljX4uInov8xpiYwDU_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dear Starbucks,

I’m writing to express my appreciation for the excellent service I received from a member of your staff on 12/23/22.
Although I don’t remember his name, the boy who served me was extremely kind and patient, and he made a difficult day much easier for me.

I had come into the store to order a tea, and I mentioned to him that my daughter was feeling sick. He listened to my concerns and provided me with helpful information and recommendations with a smile, which meant a lot to me at the time.

I just wanted to take a moment to thank him and to let you know that he is a valuable asset to your team. Please pass along my gratitude to him and to the rest of your staff for their hard work and dedication.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ekta Jassu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIlITNNt00Ak8A9MPzVynO2i3ZNkWqKAWqkUgV3tmu2wZ-mVs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best drink service and great customer service","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lexie Arellano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKN_aswGxUe9kXhkC2mgvxhI8VzeZckPaB-LgdLneBYVZZy2VQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Girls are super friendly, even under pressure the service is always great :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN70wNoBiriJ9SuIwJWtKNus0OxkdNz3li6Z99z&fid=0x0:0x207f8f135a2c4c2d"],"When":"2022-3-21"},{"Name":"Lisa V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcml9rZKlYEVaT3FpgYj8R5N6aYmItCEAddOhlJHNYGRuF5A2l=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Katie is literally one of the nicest and kindest barista at Starbucks. 10/10 would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristine Baril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNvvc_yQ7LurbtxlQTwx-5LkZMSLDsJzAd1js9OFDcGYvxXu8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Was really disappointed to see no one wearing masks behind the counter, as they handle food and drink during the Covid-19 pandemic.
