The store's operating hours are also accommodating, and the staff members are consistently friendly and helpful. They have consistently fulfilled my orders accurately as per my requests made through the app. Since it is inside the mall, it's convenient to visit while shopping.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZy_XHnSLfD6FEclZwtqzNitb3RstmWaUO67Hl&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Clean, spacious, and modern store on the corner section of the mall with some seating on the side. I ordered a drink on the mobile app and got it within 5 minutes. Staff is efficient and gets the job done. Location is on the second floor right across from the food court.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3TfM6Uzxk5GHFiF0HmJrx_gZHJlk2llXZnzM4&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2022-2-11"},{"Name":"Veronica N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaEZZcukGThSmHA881UMjlshS09D0BtOAEz9vsdpXKxEW84w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I asked for a refill with the exact same previous order, even showed them the sticker to avoid any mistakes. Of course, there was a mistake—they replaced my oat milk with a CREAMER. Now I'm stuck in the toilet for the rest of the day.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mandeep kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5-aAr05P2hI2GAfB2fGoYiVjQycm1ruTfhS13F8mvruplauI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Always had my favourite drink on weekends. Always tastes better.

I got chai tea latte with matcha foam on top. But the tea gets cold very easily just after 5 minutes.
I like to enjoy my coffee sip by sip.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVaZazr95L3TcaULaTYE3k-dbJF_sTTtfTzug1&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2023-9-10"},{"Name":"A Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqWf7PP6Ijzi2lzQvv5gHfc8J8mJWT5kt0bKPkTr45FanVBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"often have issues at this coffee shop. They frequently misspell my name, get my coffee order wrong, and when the coffee is finally made, they don’t even call my name to let me know. The service is really frustrating, and it’s disappointing to see the same mistakes repeated without any improvement.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn1tdfwXfRnZVszKV8bZBNwooyRqfHv0VT8T0EAQWyUrqTrrO6aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don't understand. I feel cheated.

The app notified me of a BOGO free event for frappucino® products today and I got so excited. I started researching and it was legit.

When it was finally 3pm, I walked a few kilometres to the nearest Starbucks. (lougheed)
It was raining pretty bad too.

While I was ordering, there were only two non-caffeinated Frappucino®: Strawberry Crème and Vanilla Bean Crème. I was let down. To make things worse, whipped cream was mandatory. I couldn't change the setting.

Then I checked the condiment stand. The carafes were all empty except two. The customer support was supposed change them every so often. During my 30 minute stay I didn't see anybody replace them.

When I finally retrieved my 2 items, nobody called my name. Usually they do before they leave it on the tray. And when I took it, nobody even noticed or acknowledged me.

The worst part was that when I walked back home, I realized that there wasn't any BOGO at all. I was charged full price for two frappucinos®.

I feel like I got scammed.

I don't believe Starbucks would do something like this! My heart wants to believe in them. But my wallet doesn't. Those drinks were not cheap.

I'm so crestfallen that I don't think I will buy from Starbucks for a while. A long while.

Until we settle what happened.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMD-N1uVaKafR74wPHS0yr7GmcVINSPzzN1-RgL&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2019-3-15"},{"Name":"Shu-Yuan Yi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGyDlWWSl0QxqBP7BMgLBJUPlYaBBAGfJRaXnZRaQGHfhFNHhn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"When I got my large coffee it feels pretty light, and after I got home within 3mins and opened the lid it shows 1/3 were bubbles... feel cheated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_UAydN6pInfatIsimWmmjpxkX_HVaw0fsJegC&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2022-11-24"},{"Name":"Joseph Liang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKl9MhDPy8EY7RScMPhpKoWbPpWdnatgpmX48XB_InHQxZUBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like most Starbucks, this one does everything pretty well. It's also nice how early they open (6:30am on weekdays as of March 13, 2021). Line gets pretty bad late in the morning though, so try to go either before 9:30am or after 2:00pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6qwAXs3cID_ELTzWJQ5fAa4fF9GLDXkW15uF7&fid=0x0:0xef2836b8d631efd5"],"When":"2021-3-13"}]

[{"Name":"Scott Gardner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAtcJicC0R9IQuYc_EQKkOcP-sHAeMKi4grD7YdbfSUxo3AB8k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Starbucks and had an excellent experience thanks to the outstanding service provided by Sarah and Igor. They were both incredibly welcoming and attentive, ensuring that my order was perfect and that I felt valued as a customer. Their positive attitudes and professionalism really stood out and made my visit all the more enjoyable. Kudos to Sarah and Igor for going above and beyond to provide exceptional service—I'll definitely be returning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-NjOqeiKKBIKYuXncVHCxmhgnBrRVCHYU0hgL&fid=0x0:0x6ead6e17f1100b2c"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Agnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyqJcbJDbElC-RwU1sBP46by6tVeVGdJmv6s9B0kjpjwDghjdVVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wish the stars you accumulate didn't disappear.
Busy location right before school start at 830am.
Staff handling the high volume with dedicated staff calling out all the orders including mobile ones.

Red cup day November 16 extra busy. Great day to pick up a free reusable cup with Christmas handcrafted drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFP9QOgQvtpbCflSMlX61DS2X6DOls4ZJLoN_K&fid=0x0:0x6ead6e17f1100b2c"],"When":"2023-11-16"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The last best coffee stop in Burnaby before you hit the Barnett highway. A usual stop for me in rush hour traffic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjC-1Q95cD4c5ZNnvXzHOpPe747O7gZ1HyQXZZ&fid=0x0:0x6ead6e17f1100b2c"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"İskender Pehlivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6VcFI0OW4_Uhp2tRcJmKyywysJgJn2d5ke-6arDdi6Q2W3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Is unhappiness contagious?
I would like to share an incident I experienced at Starbucks 6568 Hastings Street, Kensington Ave, Burnaby, BC V5B 1S2 store, which I have been a happy customer of for years, on October 2, 2024 at around 9 a.m. I decided to write this because of the friendliness and polite attitude of the store employees. Recently, I have seen an employee named Jackie behave in a very disturbing way towards both colleagues and customers. As a psychologist, I can make some guesses from Jackie's perpetually aggressive uncomfortable gaze and perpetually sweaty face. Anyway... In the morning, while he was interfering with a colleague in an unpolite manner, I said with a smile that this was Jackie's rule, not Starbucks'. He angrily kicked me out of the store. I asked him why he was so rude because I hadn't seen other stores charge extra for the milk added to the coffee. When it started to get uglier, I said, why are you so nervous and making people unhappy? From the way people were looking at me and because I wanted the topic to end, I showed him my phone and asked him if he would fire me once again to dissuade him. It started to look even worse because I was calling the police, let alone being quiet or polite. You wouldn't want to see the gaze of employees and customers. I wrote this with the thought that maybe Starbucks officials could save customers and store employees from Jackie. Because I don't like people who aren't kind and make other people unhappy just to be happy themselves.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wall E Bush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsKYOEr-emRnRDMvQb4Fe50cosacwOYlXOeUFcUM1BL-i4pEI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The baristas behind the counter always seem like they’re having a good time & every interaction I’ve had with them has been pleasant. They make the atmosphere of the cafe enjoyable, as it seems they care for what they are doing. It can get quite busy there during rush hours, but they are able to maintain stamina despite sometimes rude customers. It’s free to be nice to service workers!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SharonMelissa Shawn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIj697oj8NKE8wzKphJ1nB6MrB4S4kNdUYzQf1XRQMR-ueSoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am very disappointed with the recent management changes at this Starbucks location. For two consecutive days, there was no coffee available, which is unacceptable for a coffee shop. If corporate advertises a promotion, such as $5 coffee and pastry, it should be readily available for customers. Under the new manager, the service has significantly declined. They micromanage what customers can order and seem more focused on maximizing profit (even charging for no ice, etc) than providing a good experience. I will not be returning to this location, and it’s no surprise it’s not as busy as it used to be.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Azya Estiqlal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOYBu1npG2EZSM0xMjnJjkp78nuTI2ynw1dM3WINwKVUpRqXf9TA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This morning I went there for get coffee I pay by cash they ask change they don’t have small size money.
and also I order two Cinnamon cake it take almost15 min to bring my order.
bad experience not satisfied.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alessandra Marinkovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTm6Ln4GHA8MCGhRY6-YLk5FPvhvx6ihvur4dcaB-AfDq9Rca1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hannah is the most professional, kind and helpful worker. She is competent, and provides great service. They need more people like HER. I had a great experience with her.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Derek Shek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP9Pjija1abf8rOsOgAPBkesWOZ8sALAjyQJKt0I-DTaykDkHV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ended up at Ha Cafe on a whim when our original lunch plan fell through, and what a delightful surprise it turned out to be!

Nestled right next to the closed Mui Garden Restaurant, Ha Cafe offers a genuine taste of Vietnamese cuisine. I savored their BBQ chicken and pork rice, which was exceptionally juicy and flavorful, truly capturing the essence of authentic Vietnamese dishes. My friend enjoyed their beef noodle soup, which was equally satisfying.

We tried both hot and cold Vietnamese coffee, which were average, but the overall meal experience was wonderful. The staff were welcoming and friendly, enhancing our visit.

Definitely planning a return visit to explore more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_uBFdZIpPoSWJt6oDj6po-4RLGU-ZxHfmD0Zd&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"NC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUi7i4NwNpNEzIszjhbxKRN43HbVvZt8x4BOGr2pmqSj3ZKyWTz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ha Cafe never disappoints. We often dine in but do take out more since we live close by and like eating at home. The portions are great, and the food is delicious. Not salty or under-seasoned! Take out never takes more than 10 mins to prepare and dining in means we get to see the lovely staff. I wish they would turn on the TV or play some music for ambiance but not a big deal :) my favourite item is the short ribs on vermicelli!! I could eat it every day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpMIbdzszxmabJ6n12OfSCx5VmbcUXU0ggo5jb&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Maxim Borzenkov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5du_PkAVH4Z1D5yn5ceof8nx4Vb5Gh-oa_Y_0G13tOUKmBqAiog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lemongrass chicken on rice impressed me. A bit sweet, full of flavour and grilled to perfection. Noodle soup was also very nice, recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVOJfZ0iUV4sbpnMsvNo8Zn9jOKC2RBn86IyT7&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Andy Chiang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6Ytd6jvLjiUIKjc2DLdidLuwgHbgPUD4GPhFuPOLEoqlZ2vbh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a staple for pho near Metrotown mall. It does get very busy and there isn’t a lot of seating available so you may need to wait during busy periods

Parking is a bit tough as it’s street parking only.

For pho, they make a tasty broth and it’s very flavorful. Definitely the highlight of the meal. Not all pho is made the same and they definitely have the right mix.

This review is mainly based on the food as its interior is similar to most pho places. Definitely worth stopping by for a quick bite before a movie.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMliWr_Vy4B9Ui1-PNqS2pFJa4jRvq-emhszqTx&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Thompson Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvT3wthkscBk1HzmAVpiCVTNOTk83aoXGxP-0_pyQ35kgZaBXq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Impressive dishes! Definitely coming back for more! Great price for all dishes!

Well used of sound absorbing material, so it is quite quiet even there are many people. Very kind staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSasWgZ1_lbgH_az9GklLv-Wi1IvmVRVvgL-6i&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Elton Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_SVkVqkNe3SvSFwaZ1xrBYHObNVkTiTTXXYykf58guqGIk3qy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t usually go to Kingsway nearby Metrotown for foods but this time I felt like having lunch outside rather than eating in food court. I searched for Vietnamese cafe and I found this place. They have pretty good reviews.

I went there with my wife and we ordered grilled half pork and half chicken on rice and pho.

This foods didn’t disappointed us. I was surprised the broth of the pho was gracefully rich and tasty. The beef balls had natural beef taste. The grilled pork and chicken were having a nice smoked flavour but not burnt. Well done!

The owner was there serving the customers and he is friendly and welcoming. At one moment the sunlight came in from the window he immediately went to pull down the bind so the customers won’t get the sunlight directly into their eyes. He kept serving tea and refilled frequently. I’m happy with their service.

In terms of foods and service quality, this is a place I will definitely return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLqlCIgO5YHf_JEwpY5LJKStuN00vrZZJrXyk&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"allan duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGxUcchxgL7ckWobz0D4SkQX2X_-MUEClzpOhSJ32Qd5j6TA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything is great here. Big fan of the bbq pork Banh Mi. Neal, the owner is such a nice guy and knows how to run a restaurant. Affordable and delicious food consistently. Hes also a great tennis player!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7LBEi0UhrngaOXC2ApOj8jWeEDNDrrhKIpxEB&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"MD Ziauddin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXodMgQTYeurui5Akz5ecfFeI0koeX15uE51SyfwtR2iW6qd7bI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Special beef broth pho was excellent 👌  with price under control will go back
3 star for atmosphere cause it was painfully silent inside , maybe soft ambience would have been better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU6S3yiQ1KsdN0NLB8Z1u7NLVoWF9lCvjgkjHY&fid=0x0:0xe0d2ff6b5cbae9b4"],"When":"2024-11-6"}]

[{"Name":"Sophia Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxLQXfwQJahPezKI3zYgYADGK8JbtfxdLhB3lBNb80NltDMBh8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You guys made our day😊👍🏻✨
It was special treat for my husband! Solo District Starbucks All Staffs are warmly welcome to us with great taste coffee. I really recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2zitnwGed-w5IzCKATle8kC_ZPYILdhr4mSZ7&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"HL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSqAWPJXpOlqUn852Q39EE_iHsFkq0EJ_Y83_M8oqs5b0eF2KT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I love visiting Starbucks, especially for your seasonal beverages and oat milk options. However, I’ve noticed that more often than not, the store is out of stock on both the seasonal drinks and oat milk. It can be quite disappointing when you’re excited to try something special, only to find it’s unavailable. I suggest paying closer attention to inventory management, so that customers can enjoy the full range of options you’re known for.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyHxisBuRQx5A0DZ5o66_7l1Mt0bIDj1TL4GSF&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Efficient, no-nonsense and simple ordering in advance delivers cup to hand upon walking through the door with a smile and friendly barista!
Nothing much to report apart from your average Starbucks joint. Very friendly staff, nice cozy coffee house and convenient location near the Skytrain and Whole Foods.
Unfortunately no indoor or outdoor seating at present due to COVID.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRy7Nj_KhSCm3cmo9T36tJNYpSSULTVq5LVZ6f&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2021-7-7"},{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favourite Starbucks location. I frequent this one often which makes it easier for me to get to know the staff, however - the staff themselves make this a delight! Easily one of the nicest workers even when they are slammed with happy hour or morning rush or the afternoon pick me up. They take the time to speak with every guest courteously and have their drink or food ready for them quickly. There is seating inside and some tables outside. They also have a nice variety of merchandise for purchase.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQP0NJshXgxEseWiL36Vql5k6ghh7TbKRnQo9v&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2022-10-27"},{"Name":"Kayla Ok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2ZPW-HOTvhKWxZVs_tiGZng-PPQOf1u70Mg0ytQnqF8DWQ4ac=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is my go to order everyday (Irish cream cold brew) but the presentation is definitely the worst at this location:( also the cream is usually not so foamy. I have gone to this location a few times but I prefer The skytrain station location across the street. That one is the best in this area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzWkcu_p5fPMAZy_z6BQ57BScZ9xFrgsKy84I9&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2022-12-2"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Efficient Starbucks location with drinks made as expected. Tried the Iced Trenta Passion Tango tea and it was light and refreshing. No complaints.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlT8Z79CjYZ-6NfjgiVxZJLPT7_UcJLee1JqMJ&fid=0x0:0x34b30f04a9d38c2b"],"When":"2024-3-15"},{"Name":"Annie Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL51p-8tvOS30ipWZ1RjfIfghES9nK5xP6AURpBT6uJJTLRLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here on the Thursday. The cashier was unfriendly and hot helpful at all. [{"Name":"Nate D. Suppanade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT5GIFT3fWisDu-ffUjuVaDyKrj5NqWSJjl9Ok7m5pMmYxWgpmJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great coffee spot! I came here one morning the line was 7-8 people long but it moved quickly with 2 cash registers open. I ordered an iced latte and the double smoked bacon & egg breakfast bagel. Order came up quickly. There were plenty of tables available despite being the morning rush. The latte was prefect, not too sweet. The sandwich was exactly what I wanted, nice and toasted. They are very efficient and move through the crowds very quickly. Overall very happy with this place, would definitely come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpSteKEI2pggmWzHYZy-DQjcYasIseOSQ8Qnd6&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"eyup tunc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrtzpD3MBavlYkqs3CO6hRXMhruzBfZ-lAQJz-enOjNpKXo_yRJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This morning, I went to JJ Bean with my family to buy coffee and snacks. We bought 2 Americana misto and a blue barriers capcake. There was a long rope for the capcake and when I showed the rope to the officer, I received the answer "Let's give you a free coffee". Neither an apology nor an explanation. no. Good luck in your service and business life at JJ Bean, which we visit twice a week.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHFT1DuzxY1pgqe4nWMCfyD9oml9D1OgmJE0qU&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Looking for a down to earth, minimal fuss and true grass roots coffee joint? Then look no further. One thing of many I love about this chain, is that they don't charge extra for dairy free milk options, have a huge bunch widely available to help yourself.
JJ Bean is awesome and totally underrated, this is my new go to coffee house around Hastings. All their locations are aesthetically well decorated, have yummy baked goods and talented baristas whipping up tasty drinks! A great selection of Espresso ranges for any kind of tastebuds. This was an awesome soy cold brew to go on a hot day.
This specific Roasters also has a phenomenal plethora of both indoor and outdoor comfortable seating. Full honesty, this is one of the sweetest coffee joints you'll witness for a long time and is dope.
I just wish they'd setup a loyalty scheme reward program would be awesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvf5s0S45j6_T5-eH4YusHJmvn8AT9rNN8nTh-&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2023-7-9"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A good location for good coffee and some baked goods. The staff are friendly and helpful. The place is well keep and tidy.  There are lots of parking around.
I'm so glad that they still offer mugs and plates for eat in. It has a good patio outside too.
If you visit this area, this is the right one for a break.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlXqJPMRj9Gajim9uXVLV02HaMm_N9ubr0cUHO&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2022-9-21"},{"Name":"Julian Tu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUccbSC4ghmImblBXURerAc5in7hUNzwjywsW9q13-eiHpFJ49c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time at this JJ Bean location ⚠️ 📢
Went for late night with boyfriend and family.

Couple notes:

- Very large open concept coffee shop.
- I enjoy there design and the lamps looked interesting with fabric material.
- Lots of selection for bakery/breakfast/snacks
- Many tables where this could be a study spot along with outside patio to enjoy coffee
- Be nice if they had more than 1 menu. The menu is just at the front where you pay though if there's a line up be hard to walk in to take a look.
- The coffee shop did feel quite cold though so many temperature adjustment in the evening is needed
- The lady taking our order was very nice and offered us some snacks since they were about to close up shop and it would be thrown out.
- Staff was great felt like a good environment
- I has the Blended Vanillla Shiver and enjoyed it. Can definitely taste the espressoo~

Would recommend others to come to try it.👍👍 J approved ~","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP99xDzjbvpkx3ZrLqiucqz-3HW1vphi7nDWMq1&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2022-10-9"},{"Name":"Coshiela Bote","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnR1wEd2-LKD6S_sbHbohcbHkNlg8IBHyRGFP-Xh6kx8lMXFlG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"my boyfriend mentioned that this is one of his favourite jjbeans to study at. i came by tonight to do some work, and he was not wrong. interior is really lovely, and very clean. good music and lovely service. variety of seating areas. glad i live close by i will be coming more often. bonus points for long hours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jodine Morehouse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkI3ILmstAY-XeAWqv2CETEpjWiJVODW602jRpnYogrvfslqk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best coffee shop in the North Burnaby area. You walk in to see clean and beautiful decor, and a great display case. I ordered the Spinach and Feta breakfast sandwich and a cappuccino. The sandwich was very flavourful and felt homemade. The cappuccino was extremely smooth with zero bitter taste (just the way I like it). I liked the coffee cup lid - easy to drink out of and you can see the latte art! 5 star service as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeZ6L8mWDTk3HX1YvUiOultmghHiCdw6isk0Tw&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2021-1-22"},{"Name":"Kit Yee Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUy4hyLjXryzPjKJf4N3DUJBAsHtZSSuk76pvxFtVmwfHSV1Gtd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I chose to come here with my family, so I could sit outside, meet with them and enjoy a cup of coffee. I found that JJ Bean here has a big outdoor seating area. It was awesome!

I had coffee or latte at other JJ Bean locations. I loved their beverages in general. Before I visited this location, I hoped for the same good experience and having good quality of beverages here as well!

The size or interior of this branch is very big! After the pandemic or when the restrictions were lifted, customers could enjoy indoor seating. That would be awesome! I love their interior design. It’s very modern, contemporary, white and clean. The outdoor seating areas has got many tables and chairs comparing to other coffee places. That’s why I said it was awesome!

I ordered latte with soy, milk and almond milk as well as a cup of black coffee and two cheese muffins. All of them were very delicious. Pricing was reasonable considering the good quality, presentation of everything and the environment.

I would love to come back here and enjoy dining inside the coffee shop one day. There is lots of street parking right on Hastings or small streets. Don’t need to worry about looking for a parking spot. It’s still free parking in this neighbourhood and I am hoping city of Burnaby will change the rules and laws here 😁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTelPMsDYcIJHnbB-lrymlwdc-Z5wk25okOia4&fid=0x0:0x6a09e91dfc4e8e22"],"When":"2021-5-25"}]

[{"Name":"Derek Shek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP9Pjija1abf8rOsOgAPBkesWOZ8sALAjyQJKt0I-DTaykDkHV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"On a rainy day, I found myself seeking shelter at the Café at Mandeville, and what a delightful discovery it was! The café exudes a cozy vibe that made me feel right at home, especially with a fireplace near our table which added a touch of warmth to the dreary weather outside.

The food and drinks were a hit. I had the picnic, which was great, and an iced Americano that was certainly above average—robust and refreshing. The daily soup was another highlight for me; it was rich, comforting, and exactly what I needed on a chilly day.

The café also boasts a charming outdoor seating area that I took note of for future visits. It seems like the perfect spot to enjoy a coffee and meal outdoors, especially with kids. The ambiance of the café, combined with its tasty offerings, makes it a fantastic place to chill with friends or enjoy a family outing.

I’m already looking forward to my next visit to Café at Mandeville, to enjoy not just the ambiance and company but also to relish their food and drinks in the lovely outdoor setting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCucD3E4Z1C6Q9i-NFQJr961PEfp_wyO9KrYiQ&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Shirley Ann Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTufZ1O7YNqmevegFQNEbK68BixarB9ooeJyWD92O9OkSBiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to Mandeville gardens multiple times but have never eaten at their cafe! Initially I found it pricey but today I decided I would go ahead and have something there. For the price you get a lot of food and it's very delicious! I had brie and turkey breast panini with a cranberry mayo. To my surprise it came with a lovely fresh salad and the most amazing dressing on the side. It was so much food. I had the rest for dinner. The atmosphere is quaint, the outdoor space was beautiful. The service was pleasant and quick. They have a selection of decadent treats, drinks, and a lunch and breakfast menu. I would highly recommend this little cafe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8hLB8EGZuAVnVfTiScV0BB4hnHs8E1_z5CdBq&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Little Journey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlNkzOJynLpgqJCrPnrmAAn5viwim-B3Uir-26DOWxIzwcnZ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A cozy cafe in GardenWorks. The food was not outstanding but the beautiful sunshine made everything look better. We had an enjoyable breakfast under the relaxing vibes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6yUUXV2zMEjiKMblzI8g-sfn4leqaKtBKeN3_&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Agnes K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlACFBOxAwIK9p5cFkOHFik2vVrT3D26L4whxKFJwcdFUtLb7U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing eggs benedict, good coffee. Really enjoyed very calm and relaxed brunch in the patio. Good prices, plenty of parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1eviwwFwk3SCneY7aiEOz-IGC0IuAQWIRUivx&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-9-9"},{"Name":"Kayla Ok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2ZPW-HOTvhKWxZVs_tiGZng-PPQOf1u70Mg0ytQnqF8DWQ4ac=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I came here for lunch the other day with some friends. I ordered the chicken and waffles which my food came out very late and the waffles were undercooked… this cafe was nothing to write home about food wise but the atmosphere was nice as it is located in the Garden Works.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5e8-dJbs8CuzGyOQYQRzLmwbKu25jyE5RiJNM&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Chelmeda Nidhi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYwVJJmtKtLPsuxSuNB1Sn_QaYLUkUUW8uyt9KVhvgH2EQmwyO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loveeeee visiting here. Great great ambience, lots of flowers and plants in the dining area as well since it is combines with a nursery store. And lots of home decor, plants to buy. My favourite place in Burnaby neighbourhoods.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuAHRzYXT952-5fMwID9TL_BGNjDdqrA0y53Jx&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Melinda W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqFa91nGQX9-WVxFZ-rAUul10GF70bhWZFQZe97ymoPVUZrvFxnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to Gardenworks a couple times, but this time I finally had time to enjoy the cafe.
The lovely sunshine made everything look much more beautiful I must say. The spacious indoor area was lit up by the sun coming from the skylight. The terrace was radiating under the sun and  has such a relaxing vibes.  All customers were enjoying themselves in their own ways.
We ordered a BLT and turkey meat panini with coffee. I loved my BLT as I could taste the freshness of the veggies from their crunch. The bacon was crisp like chips. While munching his panini, my husband kept praising how much turkey meat it was in the panini. He complemented that he has never had such a "generous" panini before. Lol.
I think we will soon become regulars to this cafe. It's one of the best activities to us on a sunny day.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfF9RlVOnzVofo3T-PvIuR9ZCHV2Mh3kXYXBXC&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Hed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUcEJ_YnqWzTiAa8-5IAPYFK-uDFbxXkSKxsPhKg8FnmJCsH0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a fantastic experience!
The staffs, food, decoration, and the peace of the atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjdqTru3xpEK2VI9HSSLxvN_7571zEiuDxgS7L&fid=0x0:0xf13d8715535fd701"],"When":"2024-12-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dave Munday","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaNS1DZd97spwQGogwfE06SDoDiGtYHmZ-fIsxivv-iLxnAtq3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This business is a wonderful place to take a break. The staff are adorably friendly and as an even more delightful surprise, randomly deciding to try out their chocolate syrup waffles ended up proving to be a deliciously unexpected bonus factor I would definitely recommend.

If you're in this area, don't even give it a second thought.  Take 20 minutes and stop in here to treat yourself.
I'm sure you won't regret doing so.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgtJ8-PoPE_OkO2R1YESoWbdv_gETXpPfkMJGs&fid=0x0:0x844acb6955e8473c"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Viena Bajic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdi91GoxwP9yFVcNNB0Tzapbiyob2wrd2PZVKhJUUjrwtSA8y9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven’t been here in awhile, but as I was scrolling amongst photos in my camera roll, I’ve realized the most consistent thing in my life has been Tealips. I’m a senior in high school graduating this year, but scrolling back, you’ll find I’ve been going here since I still went to elementary school. In all these years, I cannot recall a single bad experience. My friend who lives next door told me her entire life’s story at the table by the window. I’ve stared at the same cabinet full off bubble-tea related gifts for years. I’ve watched as their decor changed slightly, adding plushes and cactuses, and the small changes in their menu. I’ve genuinely saved money through their student deals, and the amount of toppings they offer is top tier. I don’t know where I would be without a small, comforting place nuzzled in my life like Tealips. Coco’s mass produced pearls got nothing on my love like Tealips. I’ve sat at those tables as a child, with a mask on during COVID, and even now as a struggling student. In the grand scheme of all things of life, so much is moving, but not Tealips. Tealips understands you. Tealips welcomes you. Tealips is you. Not sponsored.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUAGt19q0htQKNIblnURKVozUunhdcg_arpi5h&fid=0x0:0x844acb6955e8473c"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Mina Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoNAB2Isfin8N0jYjVW-M4q31NlZ9H-TQZeTegsCy6YwExT74jTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lost Wallet, Found Hope

Last night, panic set in when I realized I’d lost my wallet. Thankfully, my partner used the AirTag inside to track its location. I rushed to Tealips and, to my immense relief, the staff had my wallet! A kind-hearted individual had found it and turned it in.

I’m so grateful to the staff at Tealips for their help and to the person who found my wallet. This experience has truly restored my faith in humanity.

Thank you for being such a wonderful cafe.

But I have to say, I will not let the same mistake happen again. Please look after belongings, not everyone willing to keep and return. And the cafe has no obligation to keep other's belonging, or do anything for lost and found.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyKlcBIrKejAFH6-6XW8pXRp4BJb8EW-o7r827&fid=0x0:0x844acb6955e8473c"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Joaquin Ofreneo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrNPnxzQyA7bFu4AlcXFBuPYzU-63dEkarSgw0BNUHG6-MHPo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This sandwich was AMAZING! My mouth watered at the sight of it, and I could tell by the design and beauty of the sandwich that I was in for a wild ride. And boy, what a ride this sandwich took me on. Tealips produces the finest of sandwiches.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtyHiQzv-Ce__FR8317U-Jf45a1UB3dzxoJcaQ&fid=0x0:0x844acb6955e8473c"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Mahak Mithani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIVq4rklNDW7_SN4ilTOdPr2MBnf1pznAUl4g5o3uReAbojEaIOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super cute spot with a great menu - looking forward to trying their waffles and bingsoo soon! I got an avocado smoothie, which is one of my favorite drinks, but next time I’ll definitely try a milk tea!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwl6e9hUyVNp5RUsLXfAwfdP4gBfGE-R_e22iy&fid=0x0:0x844acb6955e8473c"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Channing Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW326VL4agCltUTEqgHa6HKz_qvHT6y6Rid0jNN2xdoTQi2u7JT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very scrumptious and yummy, I love Tealips with all my life. [{"Name":"Neha Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOAFVq8Z0ZGxqdcHyQUNR3mUQfrl34aqa6y4TgqK9UdFHM4ko3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great customer service, staff was polite. Excellent menu potions. Mango ice cream was good. I cant stop myself to recommend banana chocolate ice cream drink with complimentary coconut jellies. It was delicious and filling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNakhEZLCLBX6QzqZizFpgZOnJStrnBMrqJal2n&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Qiongyu Chong Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWssGm9ujB4PRrGeL3vqwFdAgcQ2HleVBiKNDuYibWaXLNdm2Dr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is such a neighborhood gem! We had avocado , red bean and mango milkshake, made with fresh ingredient, really tasty and not too sweet , we love it. They also have food options and open until midnight , such a good spot for after dinner desert/drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyJrNHIzOXr8koDqOnyHGJlvxl11kqm1rNE1jR&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"AH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbSDTBRb0i5Z-O9Llx_f4jUDvaC36Rpc_Ai8VCzOt_tM08rlqM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favorite bubble tea places in Vancouver along with Hot Cha Cafe. They usually have special drinks which are pretty good. Prices are very cheap and their pearls are great. Service could be improved, as sometimes the people behind the counter seem annoyed. However, the quality and price make up for it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2NjbH7GR9YR3b3dmh1WYl7ZWOX99OxH_ZQpfP&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"eddy wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8Fjpj3y8teHQ4LqbC4PHR8whbU4-XOrTXEwklI9bGRqZLRD20=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The owners are very very hard working. They rarely take a day off and I've been a loyal customer since I was 16 at their original location on Fraser street across from John Oliver high school. They raised 2 kids and work long hours everyday. They also own the laundry mat next door.

They have daily specials posted on their chalk board outside that attracts crowds daily, even during the winter months. But if you’re a fan of ice cream or cheese cake bubble teas this is the place. My personal favourite is their green tea ice cream with coconut jelly.

They have a small dine in area and tv. You’ll see a lot of young students here.
Cash or debit only. Pay cash and get 5% off.
I just noticed they do e-transfer now.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvdZFC-jqLLx2zkvPUw8bXN-MjLewcSBBGmkBP&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Alick Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUqZ-BRlpWhxpGIkligB7NDQbnz-lNKkuIZsGRSdDfseOKcvE5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going to this place for years, but tonight I went to grab a drink with a friend  and a snack. The drinks are pretty casual as always. but something caught my eyes on the food menu tonight and   I had to try it!
The creamy durian balls aka “golden durian mochi ball”
I didn’t even know they had it, it’s a must try!
😍explosion of creamy durian on the inside and a light crispy outer shell with a soft mochi middle layer! The sauce top it off and gives it just the right amount of sweetness!
It was perfect the durians treat that hit the spot

definitely going to get them again next time
thank you👍👍

it’s not for the everyone, but for the durian lovers out there it’s definitely going to give you a durian tasty time!🤪","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWoO1aWj3rVXJ7tQTtH88tEkOTFDWX5GrKBkrb&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Bryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgQOyucobzp1WHcgAwkWVFUg6T8jAN7HsnzLG69-m-S2SOVkUy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The bubble tea was great. The atmosphere is as expected for an older cafe. It's fine but come for the tea not the atmosphere. My only complaint was they didn't take MasterCard. Without Visa, cash or debit. You are stuck.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Bennet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvYdpdn1NxF637i3RhyQP9PtiVF9jOCdDNyEHmcaA9tMpwkZI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Milk & Sugar Cafe offers a delightful experience for anyone looking for a cozy spot to enjoy a great cup of coffee or a delicious light meal. The cafe's atmosphere is warm and inviting, with a charming decor that blends rustic and modern elements. Their coffee, sourced from high-quality beans, is rich and flavourful, perfect for coffee connoisseurs. The menu, though not extensive, includes a variety of pastries, sandwiches, and salads, all freshly prepared. The standout is their signature vanilla latte and the avocado toast, which is a must-try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSmT3cMxbNrRVm7PyYF2tut6c8D_9L9TMCzbB5&fid=0x0:0x97925fa58174cc94"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"Liam Rider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPX4DDrtiUNyDL1r03MV7uHEDVU-v1k00_ry1glHtcrJFAttnq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Worst fried chicken I've had in my entire life. And it was 14 bucks for 2 drumsticks and 2 thighs!!!!! Beware. I'm sure their bubble tea is great but stay away from the fried chicken.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kadin Hurley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-WuG4L3Bfuwv__aplBnTqxkiXkxFc3mU7e8oYoPyFy8JfJsae=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found it driving around looking for somewhere to eat that wasn't a big chain restaurant and was not disappointed. The free parking in a real parking lot was a pleasant surprise to find.  Someone was quick to assist us and allow us to take our pick of the tables. My wife had the butter chicken and I had the bacon Swiss burger and wow the butter chicken was amazing with a homemade sauce with a mild spice and the burger was well cooked juicy with real bacon. I would recommend trying it out if you haven't and feel the friendly atmosphere at this small family operated business","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"B W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJp85P5JohieEKJOfTMzyjH1aTNit_eIhBL3dFVyxf0xS2BxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The Missus and I had a craving for spicy food on a rainy Friday evening.  We had eaten at James Street Cafe many years ago when it was located on Joyce Street.  The food was only okay and nothing spectacular.  We asked for medium spice but it was more at the very spicy level.  The lone waiter (from Nepal) was friendly, offered suggestions and served our food promptly.  However, the restaurant lacked any ambience as there were no other dining customers for a Friday night.  This led us to wonder how fresh the food was without any turnover.  We will be trying other Indian restaurants in the area for a more rounded dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNE61xaqUEYmARVyhE1pJd4dK3EXxg1cmKtyEn&fid=0x0:0xb3311ab1d2946d99"],"When":"2023-3-7"},{"Name":"william winslowhansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs6UFthdNPb2nMPDzj8Fn1ahJf-ni1YT6iOWaJXFBL1czXpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely horrible experience. Came in hungry. Was acknowledged by no one . A scowling person did bus tables passing us by several times. This was highly recommended by ismali friends as a good to place for ismali food lauded for it's great food and service.. Went in expecting to at least be acknowledged and give it a try but no. After three passes by staff who seemed extremely unhappy ..why are they so angry looking? Almost ten minutes passed at the front door waiting .Obviously James Street grill has its fans if you are in the ismali club but for me I'd need to question if I was ignored because of my skin colour or something else . I hate to say it but I think when you enter a restaurant and it's empty and there's staff present scowling at them is not a good way to make a good impression. Try hello maybe .

I will not return and I will never spend one cent in this establishment.  One of the mainlands greatest disappointments. How low can you get

You're obviously far far to important to serve the infidels . Oh well

The restaurant overall looked dingy and the smell of old grease permeated the air . It was off putting out of the gate . I’m unsure as to what people would find enticing to eat here and I just won’t give one dime to any restaurant that does not have the human decency to acknowledge new faces coming to patronize their establishment.
Not sure what bequeathed you with such large and mightily chips on your shoulders .
From the response of your staff it would appear that you are under the impression that somehow being miserable and impolite are marks of good service .
They are not.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Moyez B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6Eamn5ca8yTbck8IWNLNrD9ZeZUGnCTcQ08dD3UxDg2X-UdoJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Following our visit to James Street Cafe on New Year's Day, I observed that the overall dining experience differed from my previous positive encounters. While acknowledging the possible impact of limited staff during this period, it's notable that the cassava, though palatable, carried a distinct oil aroma, hinting at excessive usage.

The Pili Pili chicken, unfortunately, deviated from the usual standard, being exceptionally dry and lacking the customary sauce. I understand that special occasions like New Year's Day may present operational challenges, but consistency in food quality remains paramount.

Regrettably, I'm inclined to withhold future visits for the time being. It appears that the establishment may be unintentionally compromising its commitment to culinary excellence, leaning towards a model that prioritizes quantity over the renowned quality I've previously enjoyed.

This feedback is offered constructively, with the hope that James Street Cafe continues to refine its operations and maintains the high culinary standards that have characterized my prior experiences.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcPxy3ghlGKJJ4mZRniHQCqv7csAvh-fWLOoQh&fid=0x0:0xb3311ab1d2946d99"],"When":"2024-1-3"},{"Name":"carly reinbolt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVERp_D9BYOlNXkOO_bEBcw7v9exKrXOeb3L9lXXum6mmX8fxBPmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So welcoming! Placed a take out order and they offered me chai tea. I drank and watched the football game until my food was ready. So friendly, will come again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dela Hoorfar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPbxCeFi3lnx1yOZ4ebiZIces3jNhusrHsnNn4bhbxMOfetXWidA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today I ordered from skip to pick up a burger from this place. I have no idea how they have a 9.3 rating on skip. The fries were clearly old and microwaved. The bread was re-used? From the picture you can see that the corners of the bread were missing.

Ended up throwing the food out. This is just insulting.. i will make sure to get a refund from skip and will never order from here again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwqwXFLjdsChNs6hjmkkzE6UwWuQM_bPkof7Tw&fid=0x0:0xb3311ab1d2946d99"],"When":"2023-4-23"},{"Name":"Belinda Jin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQN2pGhoNzK76Clox_ElaIbflMT40WxZHUMqKpCiI5FtnukLZ6Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It was my second time having Indian Food with my Indian Friend. We had a lunch at James Street Cafe & Grill. My friend is an Indian. She knew the staffs who work there and how to order the food. James Street Cafe & Grill is located on Canada Way Burnaby. The location is not very convienence for people to find, but it has a decent Indian Food. The restaurant is middle size, divided by patio and inside restaurant two parts. Traditional Indian Culture decorations design inside the restaurant. The staffs were very friendly and helpful. Service was great. My friend ordered all the traditional Indian food for us. The food was very fresh and tasty. We also had hot Chai Tea, which was fantastic. It was a great experience to have an Indian Lunch at James Street Cafe and Grill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOawBEkNP2jAhG34eRDuPg8KD5LgOa_ti7iBKSX&fid=0x0:0xb3311ab1d2946d99"],"When":"2017-8-10"},{"Name":"Saadiq Daya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3DKqBF6FlfD1uoJFijv1AasTE7x1Yai7PIt8hzShJr7eE_dUr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall experience was decent, service was quick enough but did forget to bring utensils, called ahead of time so the food would be ready, and it was ready. Ribs were decent, not the most tender cuts, and the falooda was good but missing something. Personally food wise I prefer Jambo Grill still.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNb0yn6rfcOYVBztUmrju0HcQpIU8wDUpW3JLcP&fid=0x0:0xb3311ab1d2946d99"],"When":"2020-7-6"}]

[{"Name":"Nina Sound","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYQTTl1OUoEfYxAd7_EZGpQHJbjbDQIITtXcowNIlFfrK5rca8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a dark ice chocolate there today and the barista gave me a full cup of ice with some chocolate stuff. I asked her to remove that full cup of ice(nicely) cuz I didn’t know they’d gave me extra extra extra ice, after removing most ice cubes it looks like there’s much less portion of the drink, I supposed she’d fill it but she just retuned it back to me lol, she said cuz they’ve got every drink measured for the taste.

BUT the drink she gave me doesn’t even look it’s the right color for their “right measurement”. And I’ve no idea what she put at the bottom.

First time ever I was treated like this in a Blenz.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJEpjcIgjcHRCaaOAxedQMfjBBD-JlHkPHk36n&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"In all honesty my purchase and my sister‘s purchase was a bit expensive for what it was, but the staff interaction that we had was very kind, calm, and concise. unfortunately we could not remember his name which was our fault however he was a Japanese staff and I really wanted to give some kudos to his customer service. We hadn’t been to Blenz in a while So we were taking our time with the menu and he was very patient and explaining some of the fan favourites and different alternatives to get. The interior was clean and nicely decorated with some holiday items. I had ordered the bacon and egg sandwich but it tasted pretty bland and dry in my opinion. I also ordered the turmeric latte which was fine. And my sister had ordered a cranberry mocha drink which she really liked. In general I do not know how quickly I have to go back to a blend however if I had to recommend a nice place to grab a coffee, sit down, and relax from shopping while having nice customer service I would come back to this location and it is located right across from Winners.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFNTCVa-0_7gDO6yTtVYg8XrOR6KwoPYhszCX1&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2022-12-6"},{"Name":"Da Wanderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gUX2zsQKdIE8uVzYWBnKKtvYQAJfEKJppzMJqd4hE4TuUun8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favorite coffee shop. I love all their chocolate drinks but their dark chocolate ones are the best. I like to pair it with their famous chocolate hazelnut bignet. I just wish the rewards app is more worth collecting like points redemption is as easy as the other popular coffee shop chains.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8lT7GtxmI0BKqJ4-FTOx9RHx2mphk9DZtJrL8&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2023-4-25"},{"Name":"Cheshan Jayathilaka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZnrVCAI3Y_puq6ZNh8ssXubtO30jQ6uoEfxcRtUDQU7GV8WQU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately, my experience at Blenz Coffee was far from satisfactory. The staff's rudeness and lack of friendliness left a sour taste in my mouth. As a first-time customer, I expected a warm welcome and guidance on ordering, but instead, I was met with indifference and impatience. Even when I mistakenly understood their promotions, their response was less helpful.

To add to the disappointment, my parents' order was also mishandled. Despite specifying two sugars and no cream, their coffee arrived without sugar, and when we requested some, we were only given one pack.

Overall, Blenz Coffee failed to meet even the basic standards of customer service and quality control. It's a shame to see such a renowned brand fail to deliver a positive experience. I would not recommend this place, especially on a busy day when patience and efficiency are paramount.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqVo89zHwnNmL6-R3N92ooLlre7v0ItQ2HnSU&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Louise Boilevin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrbB57nz9izpshPwn7yH-SAdWr6iO_LJBZM25eopW2F0ZElrXPDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Its a small   coffee shop too small for such a big mall . Its right inside the mall at the entrance of the mall on lower level  were the bus/skytrain transportation  area .  Its has some seating but 98 %  always full hard to get a seat . Staff is decent  . Coffee is good etc . The seats are comfortable and there are tables  too .  Its very busy this boxing week","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUIVfbxkeAH9sT_VmknhXFih6zZLDNBAR6-jKm&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2022-12-30"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Blenz ain't half bad! Grabbed a Large Soy Decaf Latte which was pretty yummy, I like their plant based milk alternatives and house coffee blends.
Whilst the service wasn't exactly with a smile, this is a nice joint to chill and pretty much the only place you can sit and chill in a relaxed and comfortable vibe within Metropolis.
The rewards are super useful and a great option.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2jL4br3ykgOShTf09R_hTRf_hIXC8sl_J1sNf&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2022-7-19"},{"Name":"A. T.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDPNdOkM5E2lrC8VtQDHpS8O3UNg0sOaVobrSHrMLcsHst7sVSHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Since I always order a Matchachillo at Metrotown's Blenz Coffee in front of Winners, I really liked this coffee store. However, today, I ordered the same drink but there was something wrong with it. There were bits of plastic pieces in the drink and was confused on what it was. It was until I reached the end of the drink that there was actually a whole. Plastic. Lid. In my cup. Blended. I was baffled honestly.
I just want to warn future customers to look out for what they have in their drinks even though I know it can be difficult.
Also, I want to inform the workers there to look out for and be careful of what they blend in the drinks before serving them to their customers. Because we all know that plastic is highly harmful to a person's body if consumed so please be more aware of these potential harms.

Thanks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOW2cL3Oc6i0DbkkpKDXvlMlKCCa19pgpHHkp-n&fid=0x0:0xa1b50b597a7352e1"],"When":"2023-12-3"},{"Name":"sri harsha reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ8st-jAWWTB1wYuSv8MLrDGfhlPtnBRoTeFes744mRp1EX7Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited Blenz Coffee and had a disappointing experience due to their poor customer service. The staff seemed disinterested and unapproachable, offering no greeting or smile upon my arrival. The barista was rude and dismissive, barely making eye contact or acknowledging my order. Her name was Franchiska.

To make matters worse, my coffee was prepared incorrectly, and when I pointed this out, the staff's response was unprofessional and lacking in courtesy. There was no apology or effort to rectify the mistake promptly. The overall lack of friendliness and attention to customer satisfaction was disappointing and made me feel unwelcome.

I hope the management addresses these issues and trains their staff to be more attentive and courteous. A little kindness and professionalism can go a long way in making customers feel valued and encouraging repeat visits.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"David Durango","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_2PesKmt-cFSjzAWF8ZpvzKFIQfYWeYB7sfNc7YronxWjhwaDKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The burger and fries were good. Menu is alright. However, the offering should be better than this given they have enough people and students around to support the inclusion of higher quality of food in their menu. Nothing but sandwiches and burgers here. Then again the kitchen seems very small so I get it. There is a nice eating area right outside too which is very pleasant in sunny days. Prices are reasonable. Service was quick and good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyAwheQ9t1Ao60qBM-ZrrqTdFPM_c0zVtW_eTG&fid=0x0:0x19f9b8fb8520e293"],"When":"2023-10-12"},{"Name":"meshkat hoseiny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM57zWMm0vZk-l-96leEq7xy88YmrSkMBKFp6CxsNaLy-u4CVb5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This café is the only option on Floor G for the people of Burnaby, but it’s often crowded during the week with high school students from across the street, leaving little room for others.

The service could be better. On multiple occasions, I’ve gone for coffee around 2:15 PM, only to be told that the machines were already cleaned and they couldn’t take any orders—even though they claim to serve until 3:30 PM.

The food quality also doesn’t compare to the café on the other side near Deer Lake 1. Unfortunately, I can’t recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jimmy Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmaQe2WLp7herqsSS6Qbb3TdkPTjO2rKeO4tgMEL6Gag0kIT7k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bacon Burger: the bread is just right (in my opinion) for the burger. The patty was properly seasoned, and the ingredients were fresh.
Caesar Salad: Good lettuce size, with adequate salad dressing added, and basically what you can expect from a Caesar salad.
My thoughts: portion size was great, and there are specials throughout the week on the menu for a good price. Can be busy during rush hours, but overall the café is well managed. Thank you City Hall Café!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5rSeGpCqVnOrsOexvCz6hJwKFwGLfoYQILCoS&fid=0x0:0x19f9b8fb8520e293"],"When":"2023-9-13"},{"Name":"Zach Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsLTwWkK_Fl6ZtyZLDA-tn1qcA6hBmyVudtUY0B35fijDakONNOA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The line up can be long at peak times, even extending beyond the door of the cafeteria. Food offerings are very reasonably priced and affordable. Food is not bad. Staff are helpful, but not out of their way friendly. Very crowded during lunch with no tables left, however, there is seating outdoors. Food is prepared within 5-15 minutes, depending on item and time. Disposable wooden cutlery is available, self-serve.  There is a coffee machine, but it is sometimes out of service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvwlyjB4u92gNs2XkVMCtEEv1bbhznwa-XyALuorQtBg64Yw0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Had the chicken burger & fries, not bad for the price. Just tried the bacon burger, that was a huge mistake. First off, the meat smelled of "fish" and tasted like what could only be described as an old tuna  fish type taste. Which is disgusting to say the least, the meat looked like something I could really not describe as actual hamburger meat. Just sad, the kitchen staff reflect the products you get.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"VonosGaming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnR1nRw3YgsCeiYWmvwq_6_wCyhE3U2TiFUi0pItdAKDMU749q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Can't  believe I paid $9.00 for a disgusting chicken burger.

I paid $9.00 for a burger I could've gotten anywhere else with quality and it would actually taste good.

Secondly I was not provided with a seat it's only for adults. I paid a lot of money for their food I should get a seat especially waiting twenty minutes for a chicken burger.

I wanted a Caesar salad but they said they didn't have it but five minutes later a customer asked for it and he got it? What happened to equality in this world.

They kick out students right when they get their food when the whole place is empty.

Lady at cashier provides rude attitude to students even if you're nice to her she'll still give you attitude unless you're an adult.

Never coming here again.

More to add but I won't waste my time on this rubbish cafe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connor Tung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlElm5ceiiu07TKDWKhYg9BP84KThPVOpnnHGJdykNdSUlc01v=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The cashier is very rude to students even though they constantly buy food from there. Students aren’t allowed to sit down even though there is no one else sitting down. They also hired a security guard that is mean and asks you when you at lining up for food if you are going to buy. He has also harassed people who obviously bought something and waiting for food to leave if they didn’t buy anything. Overall would not recommend going to eat at this poorly ran cafe.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbhd2sAGh6YdWTSnS0ezKbeHKIzRo9oLgml0KIMw6fBXjChK3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good burgers, good fries","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwFHs6eFHwIesXhbVCWrgYNYlRcAGqRzR1rKk3&fid=0x0:0x19f9b8fb8520e293"],"When":"2022-6-16"}]

[{"Name":"Mike W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlIImTOV3nnD9V7iWkW3eVhXMba-8CAFPBMRprUEsLOepZgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am not sure how the food is because the service made us walk out before we ordered.

We were waiting at the counter for 2-3 minutes to order, and then once the employees finally acknowledged us the cashier told us to step aside so they could take the order of the 6 people that walked in behind us. Absolute BS, we went to the Park Crest Diner instead.

They obviously know where they make their money, off the people who work in the area and have no other options. If you have the option, go somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mathieu Youdan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXEuoZHKSGbJGQ2ZyS4stjHw5WfmXQiL083_lG5w4MfbQWhHqjwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The portions and quality of their beef dip was pretty good. Priced a bit on the high end but what isn't nowadays? Overall I was pretty impressed, most of these light industrial area restaurants tend to be pretty good. Self serve plate to table and back. But as we were about to order 6 people walked into the restaurant from a local business and we were pushed aside to take their order ahead of us. We left and will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danny W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT8CSSxZNnwa0JLa1bCyCp0sp9ujWayFM_dlh2SoTL2Jd0Dug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice little cafe, but a bit disappointing that there aren’t many vegetarian options, and the specials almost never have a vegetarian option these days. Would be nice to have a vegetarian soup at least once a week or something.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marc Bains","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVB1uNpfNLHu9WBRTgIqWySVYIGXymnfeeGQike9UtJF-LmScGfdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you've read the reviews you know I always go for the Traditional Breakfast. This day was no different. I tried Chefs Cafe as I was in the area. Good choice if I may say so myself. It was a big meal that tasted great. Eggs and sausage were the stars of the show.  Price point was a little high for a breakfast. Pro tip: syrup with sausages.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMTbOdHGcCgCY_O15NvPEP4IZodcHEbss8CUY5&fid=0x0:0x4b0dc94cee4ba99c"],"When":"2022-2-21"},{"Name":"Mojgan C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNQdX0o-yiYGAfPntN7LgWcnsDUW0pZ6gq07bo-q0bNGM-MX2TVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered food via Uber for the first time to avail their offer of buy one get one free. Very disappointing! The pork sandwich was very greasy and doesn’t taste good. No salt in fries. I also received a card to leave a 5 star review to get a $5.00 Amazon gift card. Is it even legal to ask for a review in return of a gift card? I got two cheap candies with my order and a thank you note on my food package which was nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOu4Yit_Burv7qZKbkaIzW_rdbsmROXko3joQSW&fid=0x0:0x4b0dc94cee4ba99c"],"When":"2021-10-5"},{"Name":"Bat Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsHrMF1U97M_AI9bk2xNb41tFGVAPF-s0krNV-O3nZrEGmgtwk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a nice hidden gem. The pricing is good and you get very filling and tasty portions with fresh ingredients. What more can you ask for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONVN9Ei8CUFPauMEYVq9kLDJHy1Kpxc7ihKBxs&fid=0x0:0x4b0dc94cee4ba99c"],"When":"2020-10-22"},{"Name":"Diego Cortina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJBxC0cJ1Q4wbEz6k2cij82ffRb5IoZx4nhoiMzINR5NsU8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place is beautiful, the staff is so friendly and welcoming and they have good prices for the food which is pretty good. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Brad Woof","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOikOWWy3FFvrMZb5HocaqSzvdkVEsop6bS7a63EMLwSmSTiHj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I noticed this place a few days prior & made a note to comeback for lunch a few days later when I was back in the area. Neat to find a 'hole in the wall' local restaurant that serves good food for reasonable prices. I checked out their reviews before attending & was happy to see that they have high reviews. Their website lists all their menu items & current prices. Parking is Free in the Parking Lot outfront although a bit busy because there are quite a few business in the corner complex. The restaurant doesn't look like much & the atmosphere could be better, lots of room for more tables etc but the food is really good quality, price is good, & service is quick albiet a bit of a language barrier. They did bring the food to the table & gave glasses of water without even having to ask which was nice. I ordered the Chirashi Don, + a side Miso Soup. For the Chirashi Don was happy with the presentation, size of the peices of sashimi, & number of pieces was pretty good for the price. Basically 10 pieces for $14.50, lots of tasty sushi rice below too. I would order again but next time will probably go for the Deluxe Chirashi Don to see the difference. I grabbed 2 takeout menus on my way out & will tell people to go & try this place when I can.

*

Came back with a Friend on SAT JUL-27 & we both had Bento Box A which for only $11.45 was exceptional all around. I highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvHuVATDU5d3Nw7upe0OD6wFPnkjPILNGFcz-T&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! What a pleasant surprise. It’s definitely not gourmet sushi but they get 5 ⭐️ because for the price point to taste ratio, it’s perfect! Their sushi tastes amazing! The sushi rice was the perfect texture and flavour and still fresh and warm tasting. Their BC roll was a true BC roll bursting with salmon skin. Highly recommend their combo C for $16.95 which comes with California rolls, teriyaki chicken, sashimi, assorted tempura, salad, miso soup, and an orange slice. It’s the perfect mix of a bit of everything at a great fixed price. The portions were all generous too and would definitely have sushi from here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvuMdX8hOKTbyzdICifqVoypqPJNiVLySDez-O&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Jennie Gaeun Jeong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdBsJcaFPd0UawfEbpKsScTiEnTsmeN_7DVjYHJnuxnO7dvHY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Sushi Q used to be my favorite place. I’ve ordered more than 7 times, but I was really disappointed with what I received today. I’ve ordered the aburi sashimidon more than 4 times, but today’s aburi sashimidon was awful. There were 3 tacos, and only 3 pieces of sashimi. Before, there were at least 5 pieces. The quality is getting worse, especially the aburi-don. I recommend ordering the sashimi-don instead of the aburi-don","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrknyAr6H_fATuEwQneJsMxDLnDGV4pBvqX-_k&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Lizzie S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5qIG1VmBASZQRSYXsIMifm6rtLhZA6xcKTGDs0bvXyJT2pXkmsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Local gem sushi shop 😉 very nice quality sushi with affordable price. I love aburi series, creamy and great aroma. I'll definitely come again when I visit Burnaby.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4fYhB6YhXB3qnh4sutOO_j1ujLkgKt5XD_fWA&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Dru","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcIUWhXu36DJooUJ1lpbYjpqIkYmzEr706B1kzk2ckCpk9YfWe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my favourite Japanese restaurant. The photos are from a few of my past orders. I always order bento box A and it comes with delicious miso soup as well. The food is always fresh, affordable, and made with love :))","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFh9sXOG-jhs-IICs1mBQgc4I38AFWIOLu5dOJ&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Kalvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYzAZd-0_JeniSNljNxgImCwzlXWbe6PzaDeAXT6_nhg5vP5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Portion were generous, quality of food not there. Sushi, tempura and miso soup had no taste. Good price for what you get.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnERr9NWv2sr26_j-e0lypwJayJmJLFxSnX1Xi&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Popular eatery, more so for take out. The interior and ambiance is very simple, with minimal tables and chairs for dining in that felt more like an office setting rather than a restaurant. However, the food was reasonably priced and decent! I had Bento Box A ($10.95), which came with teriyaki chicken on rice, assorted tempura, a side salad, and a California roll. The tempura tasted fresh, the chicken was well flavoured with the teriyaki sauce, and the salad had ample dressing. The California roll came with 8 pieces and had a substantive amount of imitation crab! I may not dine in again, but would be happy to return to take out.

Extensive menu with lots of cooked and raw items! Service was prompt and our food was prepared quite quickly. We had to pay at the front counter. The restaurant is within a commercial complex that has limited complimentary parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzROliJYk6T7MlLhhvNksx7ty1jyLQmL2FHlfF&fid=0x0:0xe102f9ac29770d63"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Chelsea L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeNrEgqwcoT_dQPlVSlYzahJemcNKWPa8MpMYyDTVBOPId1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sushi is good and the value is amazing. Can’t get over how generous the portions are for the price. Everything tasted great and not low quality or anything. It’s nothing fancy but it’s the perfect lowkey meal that’s fuss free and delicious. Defs will be returning!","Images":null,"When":""}]
