user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Beverly Ilaine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOfKPZbMvb42_xrZF5ClhSC5jdqhApu7E9LUpCeuCFmvWbiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so happy we chose Riverway as our wedding venue. Everything went perfectly. The whole process was very organized and the staff were all awesome to deal with. Bradley was our contact through the whole process and he was very kind, professional and patient with my million and 7 questions! All my quests were very impressed by the food and many said it was best wedding food they have ever had. The desserts were also delicious.  I also received a lot of compliments on how beautiful the venue is. The staff were very on top of the buffet and making sure food was replaced as soon as getting low and the chef was able to accommodate the few guests I had who had special dietary needs. One of the reasons I chose Riverway was the very transparent pricing as well. I compared several venues before choosing and I especially liked how straightforward the pricing structure is at Riverway and it made it easy to plan my budget. I have zero regrets or complaints and could not have chosen a better place to share my special day.

Update:  Two weeks after wedding I am still getting calls and texts about how good the good the food was. Many friends shocked two vegetarians had such good meat dishes and said the prime rib was perfection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNijlofkhNX_GDeBA9kazvfftJynyKSbVD_ZLsD&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Gloria Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDAFqPWRWeT53N4LeEy3NovGglbPNXMDbhXHfakPDm-pA7Xgc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There is no doubt we picked the perfect location for our big day. Riverway Clubhouse offers a modern venue with a touch of rustic charm. I love how the reception area is connected to an outdoor patio and leads seamlessly to the ceremony area, right beside a small lake with a fountain and overlooking the lush greenery of the golf course. The facilities and landscaping are impeccably maintained. I must also mention how stunning the sunset was, casting its glow right above the fountain in August and creating a magical scene for our sunset photos. This is something we will never forget!
We are so happy we chose the plated dinner option, which was a crucial requirement for us. The food was amazing, and many of our guests complimented it, especially the dessert buffet. The serving staff and bartenders were professional and fun to talk to. Supervisors Bradley, Laura, and Tegan were friendly and accommodating with all our requests, making the wedding planning process smooth and worry-free.
Thank you for making us feel special. Your professionalism and effort are truly appreciated. We highly recommend couples to check out Riverway and consider holding their big day at this amazing venue!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnsMqKS38ge5dj7bNn8fazBvtKtAAnW5-cFxiJ&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Ivy C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJI-0DKHrbq9cwyZtdxoyTslChz-bW4i6IP-K3UiX51ZmB2O262=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can not imagine myself having my wedding anywhere else but here.

We hosted our wedding here in September and couldn’t have chosen a better venue with such an incredible team. Bradley Binkley guided us through the entire booking process and handled all the details for setting up the venue, showing great attention to detail and quick responses to our inquiries. We needed a customized menu to meet Buddhist vegetarian and allium-free requirements (no onion, garlic, chives, leeks, or shallots), and both Bradley and Chef Mok made sure everything was perfectly tailored to our needs. Our guests raved about the menu Chef Mok created, and many said they would return just for the food alone. Laura, who supported us during the tasting and on our wedding night, along with the entire Riverway staff, was friendly, welcoming, and accommodating. If you’re considering Riverway Clubhouse for your special event, you can be confident that it’s a fantastic choice, backed by a team committed to making your experience truly exceptional.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHEHXfY_B0gq6V3tIlVbQ_QZfUBtNq2yT_-Pma&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very disappointed
Quality of food is horrible
The AAA New York steak ( Steak  and Fritz)  was super chewy its as chewy as puppy’s toy for almost $50/pax meal I was hoping for something much better
Poke bowl is another nightmare , rice is hard and cold , salad was dry and tasteless
Atmosphere was good and relaxing but server not friendly make the whole stay rather awkward

Free parking though

most golf course restaurant that we visited mostly have  nice environment and great food today really caught me by surprise","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcyuKI3ORTMtOry20T_EAR3gtlo5gjTWzUIhKg&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"JR Wedding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLft8D7bIDwDyi3Q6WmFcD4HucbpHTggcTCsUbJdmUGFT9NHdM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First and foremost, thank you for providing such an amazing venue and making our day so special! Our family and friends couldn’t stop raving about the delicious food, and the staff at Riverway went above and beyond with their professionalism and care. The Riverway Club made our wedding a day we’ll cherish forever. Wishing you all the best, and thank you again for everything","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvZEwEVTqJkuXh4UsCGV-8sFaBtW_ywAWKlln1&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Kathy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiyb_IZpx_WoUpDbNVrKDpyLmD7_rVs6LOSYuAzIVmUAcA7Ma7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We have reservations for 4 people at Thursday 5:30 PM,  I was thinking I am early but it was no parking at all and I have to park out the road.

I saw the manu it was different at Web site and I am kind of disappointed because not much to choose from the manu.
(Please see attached photo)

Therefore,  three of us were chosen for Roast Beef set dinner with lobster. ($39+15)

The set includes soup or salad, roast beef and dessert.  The whole set was very delicious especially the beef very soft and coffee cake 🍰 too.

The service I only give 3 star because the waitress didn't come check on us at all after she delivered the main dish and even we don't have water any more.
The food I only give 4 star because I didn't try other dishes yet.

I highly recommended to try to eat here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5F1sjg11lQjtg4gdBzQwjDaxI5z8Riq_FpipE&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2024-6-15"},{"Name":"Jason S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkCj-jc2YXNtXhtWIHMiswaQLIS5bwxc3U-1qEa51OCIRs3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bradley and the Riverway team did a fantastic job hosting our wedding and reception. The venue is absolutely perfect and the food was excellent. Our guests were raving about how much fun they had! We looked at many venues before deciding on Riverway, and we definitely made the right choice in being patient. If we had an opportunity to do it all over again, we would definitely go with Bradley and the team. Thank you for making our wedding day memorable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMu693kmMFcHWCNmj6psGQUrwPFOrZPrlABHzfZ&fid=0x0:0x6b1815483dcb77f4"],"When":"2023-9-1"},{"Name":"Dyanara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcxZLR5VMCB7ueLiR8tj3DedCkVF2BwHv9NAr_y4ni6uQ_6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the wedding of our dreams at this hidden gem. Riverway is naturally beautiful where decorating less is more than enough. The sunset in their patio is stunning, the natural lightning is what a photographer’s dream! Me and my husband had a very positive experience ay Riverway especially to Bradley. He is very professional, goes above and beyond to meet your needs and is always happy to answer a thousands of my question during my wedding planning. Food is so amazing and so good! Our guests have enjoyed the buffet, heard all positive things and they kept on raging on the dessert buffet! We are so thankful that we found Riverway to have our wedding. [{"Name":"Lisa Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFZLErRYeOTAavlFqDGw7i_a8AnnXc6Slji12tOqwEY2XQBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They had no food!  It was 11:30am - barely even lunch time.  The prices were outrageous and the service was meh.  Look up from your laptop, acknowledge customers and have conversation!   Don’t think I would spend $$ here again.  What happened to this cute little place?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqELq_vZiyoP-YTtjCvZ023BM0HMq7aj-KaFZeBSqn4YfZtiVj_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was hesitant in giving a five star not because of their coffee or pastry, but their interior decor doesn't justify their "image." Not sure if it was because of the Cafe's location but inside, it was not what I've expected after visiting their other locations (McArthur Glen & Downtown). I truly thought I was in the wrong cafe at first! 😂

But with all that aside, their coffee is still amazing and their "Pain de Chocolate" was so yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4yFmEQaAv54e6NJDZ4SlQE5CzDkrtqZsFjLap&fid=0x0:0xf3bd561ff3a002b3"],"When":"2021-11-5"},{"Name":"Ahmad Fallah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYf-wJx1un_QduvzbSzJPNGg6vPBLmGDZO1qjv-pZS71mm8709=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible customer service. The barista was careless, inconsiderate, and appeared angry. Avoid this cafe if you value friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNL84Fc6D_dC7B1wXsUO5HHMZmjE2R_wEOR7Dgr&fid=0x0:0xf3bd561ff3a002b3"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"KeepinItPG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbHTWkFYu0nhmrOjlNjJHnFrR3dgmIrN6Q0ugwayQ9K8Izi3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Nothing will ruin your day more than a first sip of terrible overpriced coffee. No wonder no one was in this coffee shop when we came in. Overpriced burnt puddle water coffee can’t even get passed 2 sips; save your money go elsewhere","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Leon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVndOYFwwmQ-UqHE_W_8GKWZH4QazMnMojFUZvBAoSUBuZLLcuhRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The place looks nice, heavily understaffed. Customer service could be improved. Coffee is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8qud1gvERgXDzNQbOiIu6YopiGnYwQ3ETB7iv&fid=0x0:0xf3bd561ff3a002b3"],"When":"2019-12-24"},{"Name":"Ryan McLeod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUPms8M2hY6Qxj68Tle5U0l_wxcvQ9ju2T6HgxIsmvnftNxgp7OQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have a problem. I am basically obsessed with the ham and Swiss wrap at @CaffeArtigiano the potato, the red peppers... Mmmmm just so amazing and a very filling breakfast. The staff is super friendly and the tea is always piping hot. Best place to come hang out when you're at work and need a chill moment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP79Mj9hsEqazIC1sXmbT_Wc_ZHmcRkP3i6ThG-&fid=0x0:0xf3bd561ff3a002b3"],"When":"2018-6-28"},{"Name":"Tony Durke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2B-yxtEwsN3VC5I0agH_oArdXi55oh_OiwFVSsJVbk0zRM7sR5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Been here lots but not anymore. The only reason I went there was because I was working nearby. Service was meh, coffee was consistently mid and it's kinda run down and worn out. And the food, if there's any left at 930, is usually dried out served to you as if you asked them to borrow money.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blake Vanderheyden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGlmqcVwH7QPhsHY2ED_exjlWnztAquqtp7a3YtRzw8FKOSVw7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"$10 for 2 half full Americano’s.
(I know it’s just hot water on top, but where am I going to top it off, I spent my money here to get a full coffee)
No lids, 20 minute wait, microwaved food.

Not sure when this location went downhill but, not really an Artisan Coffee shop anymore.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_tR3fU-Vt-0YyL7rNtIDNuBMrlI8pEi_aF26X&fid=0x0:0xf3bd561ff3a002b3"],"When":"2019-11-6"}]

[{"Name":"Jessica Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOeC5VCbc6g3HH3dxXpDS9bE993HEKMDVI3SjHX2aNdHbQOJHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Café I've ever been to with the best menu. So lucky they were part of the Vancouver croissant crawl making it easier to discover them. The vegan chicken croissant was delicious and flavorful with a touch of refreshing lemongrass taste included too. The durian croissant had a great filling 🥐 I'm not sure why it was called moissant because it seemed like a normal croissant. The iced Ube haze latte was amazingly full of ube flavor with the perfect amount of Vietnamese coffee ☕ and best of all it was safe for a dairy sensitive person 👌🏽 The staff gave thoughtful suggestions like to try the coffee jelly dalgona drink too so would definitely try that next time. They packaged everything so nice and seemed to be with care. Totally worth coming out of your way to this place. It was cool to be able to order ahead of time through the broyecafe website too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkgrvROuPqP9MwOQfxMnpI5YXxcV4N7H9oqR1o&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Tam Bui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBT5ncDfh8bnFPF0txL6LoKmGGJNZbFO5rGsUaWCMegaQw5A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favorite coffee shop in Vancouver. I love their mango matcha latte and moissants. It’s croissant crawl today so it was quite hectic compared to normal but the limited edition items are worth the wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqcQqdrw7JJhVkihEb63DqbbFZjvOro5_O3ICk&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Mrs. Leci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFUu7tIDGHhiFP61EOIZLCOSzvwJkGN10CXxqa6MRhYpyxpm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a nice dining experience on a gloomy day here at Broye. Visit their cafe for a yummy mochi buns and coffee!

Made our day!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTn12E3cNk3WaOK_DuS7JG7ZZuHFMUYdkJ7NT_&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Tay Cun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVISvV4V-lNqhgBJaNaxP5l32SM4_qpYYBDmmefTcVji7eDYTQz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a wonderful cafe. They offer plenty of seating and the staff very friendly.
They have plenty of delicious hot and cold drinks options
And the mochi buns are cute and tasty
They also offer Happy Hour BOGO on select items which was definitely a plus. I highly recommend the location on Fraser Street.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX68VKFKNYCqMYirfkLtUb1_bO9dbAiD7d3dPd&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Tiara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOGTnVSprrRfKnl8HxlMWqGPfK-EAnduRxsmD5lBjFitcsiWe8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I got their egg coffee, which was good but I expected a more custardy taste to the egg cream. It still had a great taste to it and got me awake enough to get through the day. They had a wide variety of food and drinks that I should try next time","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPkS67XeVinZ13d9B_OUDdrXePUEELM59-sv5G&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Tammy Hoang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-yEBkQVFHvEWZfuLZqbeoOB7DXxgT7uhpXL_VVia-4TbHCTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: we had a great experience re-visiting this place recently. Customer service was awesome. The owner even gave us the mango yuzu croissant when we were leaving 😊 the coffee was rich and had a nice fragrance.
It is a cozy and well decorated place, parking can be a bit hard to find. I'm looking forward to trying other items next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObq0DOElOTukyEgvy_9hXf-ngI8T-HLSLSl94&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2022-4-16"},{"Name":"Mariam Ashraf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdm9Z3aKH31BAMEdQch46HgK2OKNKcqEP3WPF-lmoLHMZV7xONvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I read many reviews before trying this cute Vietnamese cafe… and I was pleasantly surprised! There definitely is an odd, plastic-y smell when you enter but the decor is so whimsical that the ambiance is still pleasant. I ordered a Viet coffee mochi croissant which was really nice. I wasn’t adventurous with my order due to the mixed reviews but I did try a salted Vietnamese coffee (cold) which was interesting. More ice than drink but still enjoyable.
The service was ok- I asked about mochi croissants “moissants”, if they have multiple flavours and just got a “yes”. Couldn’t see the flavour options so asked her to list them and she slowly named a few. Eventually I found the listed options but it was like pulling teeth to get the info from the cashier.
I would go back here with a friend since it’s so fun and unique but I doubt I’ll go out of my way again solo.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiWxqS3SxmAu7fEFj6j-Sw2HnLn8STH6SX1Ldr&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Jim Fong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3tXWnX8xFhA_qZcSgIAVcjedjNVtb5Riz6aB4ltUNzTkDmgfU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What is there not to love about this place. Everything from the sandwiches to the mochi bun were great. Will definitely be back to try their other items, YUM","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPE4TekCuGADlb0RFDxIJ8DAFB27cbRyDwfS-IP&fid=0x0:0x413f53b7b34d8ffa"],"When":"2024-8-20"}]

[{"Name":"Kimi Lala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmGcf79-dtKD3mqW2FhkIlnFicRE1wE9HVbysDOFNCUkT9CLE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Came for a bubble waffle and she gave me a cold one. I’ve had them in the past and if it’s fresh, it comes out hot. The point of these bubble waffles is to have them hot and crunchy. She told me that it’s cold because they move it over to cool down. It was ready right after I paid which leads me to believe it was already made and NOT fresh!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5_01voTVpSIMy4RXpMAR8768FSpLJQ89cFuWZ&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Adam Bauman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfaGVPFirvJH5TTW0hpJUDtsQIvJc1wzx5QTvb4pIXxvFP7dQJ-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered the Szechuan duck noodle combo #18. The images on the menu were completely different from the meal. The images showed broccoli, tomato, and few other ingredients. I got 1 rubbery peppercorn covered duck breast and cabbage with seemingly some tofu skins or something. The broth was decent but could be better.
I also would prefer if they had those buzzer units like every other store in the food court. Their order ready screen is not updated and I had to check back often.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoeNQXIa_kBqWYkKC32xQVQShcgXkvny7JhV4z&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"A M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWvg88cxFi-Whpi-QZRwC_wprIJbtdrq1L_DgKg19Cb1WnKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered at counter few times in the past.  But this time, ordered half chicken by UBER.
I knew it is boneless, but it was skinless as well.  70% of the chicken had no skin and tasteless.  And it is so small and no wing.  So much space left for a 6" takeout container.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKJML4VDLHOX6hDVfUJP3_bAgis-NfBMgcfc9z&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"James Inouye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGMUsvXLijMfgZydLJhU2TpG1bqPFbrelq3iJSQAmmOzYoUfG8Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for noodle soup and rice dishes. And a very great deal since it also comes with a drink. The staff are friendly and accommodating, and they are consistently excellent.

It's good to go when they open. During lunchtime, the food court can get pretty busy. There are a lot of seats around. And it's very clean.

I recommend coming here if you want noodle soup.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvqrv-ZBYJxMHDwrUosrcKfGVoNjYFLr5EHs-jn5iLo41Zmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great price and good portion for lunch. We purchased lunch and ate at the mall. The place was busy so we had to wait but it was quick for customized noodle dish and tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpy18wV_cv5qp668qjkc1_GxIjf7wnQILin_-R&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Frank-E S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuQqGrhmSMvK5d6i8DZca-5U01rmiJHXM6e3jvV56tTRuvGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As this location is situated in a food court, the atmosphere is good. I've ordered their Salty Nuggets with Rice dish in the past with no issues but today was something else! It felt like it was reheated and toaster oven-ed as the texture was off; the chicken pieces had a hard exterior and the inside was dry. It must've been from the day before or something...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsKxdmbVz9766ZztDJnsgFAAvTegG4aVO7d-qG&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2023-12-1"},{"Name":"AVRIL SWIFT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRvQ0rnf0weuFVtehTeOvTJk0mIQSuYAF9GhuU8TZzAegLoo3u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered the Hainanese Chicken from this restaurant and the rice they gave me was fully burned. I believe the staff notes about it, and they try to hide the burned rice in the middle.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2jelzYysMtfanQQsTWiAMSc3BAROxQc0yABqD&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2023-12-29"},{"Name":"D Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4D0pnJRuugp7xtOoI9Okhc1IdtNuzKocuzhsSBj3gUdos57g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Feeling like something soupy? This is a new bubble waffle location inside the brentwood mall food court. Staff is friend and organized. Menu is very extensive.

I think the bubble waffles chain does really well for people who want to have a really complete combo (food, drink, snack) at a reasonable price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMY59yCahcb2K5MkLIZ3JBL_ngKmwmb_4HOe2Rr&fid=0x0:0x7198d2bb4bb10f49"],"When":"2022-2-1"}]

[{"Name":"Yui K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUp3HCV4DpRLjcnqAeASD3s3A4WGKgCnNbyVQ4WVfzXV-fapuB-FA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"No matter what you eat or drink here, you won't regret it. Everything is soooo delicious.
My favorite is the pistachio croissant donut, but the scone I had here the other day was the most delicious scone I've ever had in my life. I think scone is my new favorite.Everyone should try it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbCLDrtxaO5KDtPjBlkRpFhp2ZnD6O0c9exInM&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHTcuSM-4ly1uIP3q2-jgQ_2Vqi7GhBmGO9JykCcOlnN1NYOmqYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super friendly staff helped guide me through the maze that is the line + million pastry options! How does one decide! I could go back a couple dozen times just to try something new. Adorable & delicious, will definitely return!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZj5sxsHQOj8DjrcuSEofX52tol_dA9TtqT8Go&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"David 04 Make the World a Better Place","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkrAyRsAwad4uDl0EKEwpsCVMLq51IOxmbley55h_iwJzGo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This is a very iconic coffee shop.
It’s great to see this coffee shop at Brentwood Mall.
However, compared to the quality and atmosphere of other locations, I’m slightly disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6Rs1yvD02BtiNqmLsa39bALf3Htj_N1nfwho&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"MeganMoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIqNrocluvebctUWQfv5il3VHeKMDGxr_n3l4nFY1oEA-JBEG8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend the chocolate almond croissant… best I’ve ever had. Flakey dough but soft and chewy alongside the almond and chocolate jam. It’s quite sweet though! I also ordered the iced hojicha latte. Real tea and perfect amount of sweetness— unlike  the matcha latte which always tends to be a bit bitter.  but I guess it’s to enhance the flavour. Pretty cafe interior with a unique barista bar in the middle! Loved this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4TiIshjSo-5_WQb8fSlhtxOyyWNFoOC8C9aeK&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"All the flaky pastries such as croissants are very good… even better, go there at breakfast time and try fresh-out-of-oven ham and cheese croissants. So good!
Cakes and breads are good as well, but scones are not my favorite. My fav today was banana bread with chocolate chips!
Located in Brentwood mall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyQRf-BKF85o3Dt9P8tBnpbIu9zhIEQnko-k8u&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Karlee P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKcogQ6RORYiMmSspqCcqCmyIrc0-pWDzMzKeIGrxpNySqDxSl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The SV Almond Croissant is the best Almond Croissant you’ll ever eat within the lower mainland. We recently tried the Birthday Cake and it was seriously a dream, so light and not super sweet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAs4UHsMLuy3KnU-Ua6sKZC3Ak9pmr8QplwcuL&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Little Journey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlNkzOJynLpgqJCrPnrmAAn5viwim-B3Uir-26DOWxIzwcnZ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I just need coffee, it is always irresistibly attractive for me to grab a pastry. The croissant was divine. I was blown away by its crispiness and softness, even though I went there about their closing time. The cafe is small though the vibe is good to chill out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTUPcQu-AXbreQ7xiC1G-NtsDO1CevyHPAvoON&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-1-30"},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"tl;dr you must try the chicken sausage roll. Also the pastries > the coffee.

Quite a busy location given all the condos that have gone up. The line moves fairly quickly and the drinks come out without having to wait too long.

The chicken sausage roll is my favorite item on the menu, and generally the food seems to be better than the coffee. The sourdough loaves are quick good.

I ordered a bone dry cappuccino but I ended up getting a milky coffee. The baristas seemed like they were in training.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbqM36N67tD5kWSNluoQ5vL6FFwtfdC2F7lwcI&fid=0x0:0x82fb41dc599ae45b"],"When":"2024-4-7"}]

[{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wholefoods offers a fantastic, wooden-feel, minimalistic and easy going seating area with plenty of options which are mostly sourced from local companies or made in-store. They have a great facilities area with microwave and water refill station as well as compostable water cups.
I opted for the Large Soy Cappucino with some whipped in cinammon, great value (20oz) in size compared to other coffee houses and the Allegro coffee is super yummy from local roasters. They also have an awesome range of all dairy free milks and their bakery contains a plethora of delicious tasty goodies to cater for all tastebuds as well as vegan and gluten-free options.
I wish they would extend their great offer for for coffee and muffin to other baked goods to offer a bit more variety and the fact these things freshly served bad boys literally sell like hot cakes as their so good, but is one my only gripes. Therefore, if your there late morning it's hard to fight for any of the good muffins left.
I always opt for my go-to Banana Bread as it's incredibly scrummy and as most of their stuff is made from wholesome, fresh and locally-sourced ingredients.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYXCMkClpNlXzHafPVARzE66T9tdSh9zKU9-9H&fid=0x0:0xb5bc03ac5aed7fe5"],"When":"2022-2-27"},{"Name":"Darren Michaud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXu366do_xG8Lw5b8D75tAo0g_tIJTZ9UOqpDOvK-QaCUG5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Advertising branded Bulletproof coffee with MCT oil and grassfed butter, what they sell is generic coffee mixed with Bulletproof Brain Octane Blend and Nanak Desi Ghee - clarified butter with a very distinct taste. It’s not grassfed, has no nutrients (boiled down to milk fat), and does not blend. No measurements were used when mixing. Love the rest of the store, just need to correct your ingredients here please!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Spencer K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxeBmVkRYpoUg4BPGwvjRaID79B_HB-klvBsfuzD5gqqYIkTN_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Muffin and coffee deal for 4 bucks is a great deal. The coffee by itself is too expensive for my liking but the combo with the muffin is well priced . Coffee is tasty","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDLNdVaubv2aakSebPOyG_UmGiEWk-Kn9ElvILTaVIxhWZUmU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Way better than the typical chains. [{"Name":"Mehran bakhtiari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX52_I8QBEvpbwP2DsvccLDQ1hUjTB0qEjwNL_660Q7Wjozcaqk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"3 months ago, I gave a 5-star rating to this Tim Hortons branch, because the few times I came here, everything was great, but in these three months, everything has changed and it's not the same anymore, and I had to change my 5-star comment today.
I will delete and replace this comment.

I ordered a pizza today, but after 15 minutes, no one served my food when I asked if my order was ready.
They just realized that they forgot to make it and without saying a word or apologizing, they started preparing the order and laughing.
This is a disaster.
I hope the manager of this branch sees my comment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcV-3a6hA0LrEar-vKdLfjNpjYtw9EqwUkVTZy&fid=0x0:0x3243319e59291cc4"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Mr.J'S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-e8rjz6kQF92n1F1aire7WYQoeTlkimsRuRCMV5xPWerPo6IPuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They never follow instructions… poor service, shelf is always empty…. I ordered double double … taste like nothing .. there is no sugar. They don’t stirred the coffee just fill it and throw it on the table. Customer service is very bad in here… always out of stock especially no pastries. Why to waste the time in here","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVH6kwe2wQeqCVBHeASxVOVyvvLfU6-7YRaP93&fid=0x0:0x3243319e59291cc4"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Mariah Pascal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUL9JSELKsrgtMS0rHzeE0njrDPLVGqYa0zIuek5QC463CbJdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Staff rushed us to order.
Asked for a cookie, and she broke it when grabbing it, didn't apologize or grab it.

[{"Name":"Soner Kalayci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyFA9nFJv5HZ_bIMNLk9Z9eDkiKHwZPIyuAppLzuVMKInn_oSR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Environment: Pretty decent, clean and spacious. They have outside seating which I appreciate a lot!

Food: Just tried their Jupiter sandwich. I had high hopes but it wasn’t able to deliver. It lacks any and all texture, a mostly haphazard construction of very mushy ingredients. A well soaked beef dip is still more interesting. The taste is not for my liking but it is not bad. There is not enough harmony between flavours, and zero texture is making it even more apparent. I believe having a better roasted beef that has a bite to it would elevate the sandwich at least one star!

Cost: It is not a cheap place, and with the lackluster sandwich, it is quite low value.

Overall, this is a nice looking place with nice people working inside. If they improve their sandwiches, it’s well worth a visit. For now, I will not try again for a while :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Filia Kumala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIovBEwl6PBaxcHXI6oAWL3Fe_Z80KMUMDVq-6oVkti2S1wAdxa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy cafe to chill, free parking as well !
And the sandwiches really good. A lot of desserts as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiqZo5KABeYVYqlPVle2JJUxmP3QP7AescBDE_&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Jack Yuen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhRPpXHdrFGpSfFPj2Llvg9rACCkMWbpnKawexr7OBRxKhKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"After checking the doctor next door, we dropped by the cafe and try having some breakfast. The portion is quite large and taste is good. I loved the onion pickle right next to my sandwich. Bread is also fresh and crispy. Belgian chocolate that my kid have also taste very good","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM433fRhlsNQsCyYahjxae2ahlXGrDFvuPnIwdN&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2024-1-21"},{"Name":"Anita Rahman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbYGrDbp0-pEtutp2LMOGSJJItl9mWCgkE4IHACE4014Vmc94=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful place for a hearty meal. Already visited 3 times in couple of months. Everyone working there is super nice and friendly. Their grilled cheese with soup combo is my most favorite and also the lava cake. We visited with our year old son and he was always treated very warmly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jinchen Cai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAkTaGuIBaKsnqPWu-_2v9e15t_xkadDsddRx-i0U3GTJUait-Fw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Cafe, amazing food and drinks! 🥪☕️🍵

Even though this cafe has been open since 2020, I've haven't tried it until today. Interior design and atmosphere is great and welcoming. Food and drinks are great for the price.

The juniper sandwich is amazing. It taste just as good as the all the Italian sandwiches I've had in Italy! I'm quite shocked. The deli cuts was juicy and tender, and the bread used is perfect. 🥰

I ordered the caramel macchiato and it's so much better than the Starbucks one that's my go-to. Idk what it is about the caramel that was so tasty with a smokey flavour. Unfortunately, the espresso in the latte cannot be compared to expresso in Italy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMROyzs-D1V-_3dtGCiFhJWmQVMYD0Xij26812L&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Vienna Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1Ta4lwNnbpbXRflsTPdhZ5BFLfHHNLQU8CNBUiA018milklt7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute study spot. I spot an outlet! Food is decent but the latte was extremely bitter. Calm in the morning :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhUKgVff1MphEC5VvK9QRmDOF6T3EPYMnKhANM&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Stefan Rees","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVygWTOmYHF6xzlHi-VSEPhK4QTFBEMEA4EzI875uDMDccdlZ-d-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Breakfast sandwich was tasty but a little salty and poorly assembled, really slid everywhere. The breakfast wraps eggs were an interesting color of grey. Blueberry balsamic pastry was wonderful and I enjoyed my black coffee although the iced coffee lacked punch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtJYHzBYn5t06aVvU0MF1errgNlg8i1ko4m68i&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2022-6-21"},{"Name":"kristina harvey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEiYWpqVelO0tFIKk8FvQvgQXtUL5ZH3j1tq-L7jd9piQsTybW7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time eating here. The Jupiter sandwich was tasty and just the right size for me. My friend needed 2 sandwiches. The London Fog was well made. I'll come back next time to try the desserts which looked amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOW-y2bYtdiFnGVI08AuaocpAGJMw41A35w721&fid=0x0:0x6d04a162b9761b1a"],"When":"2023-3-29"}]

[{"Name":"Emily Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEvwebxzOOvHfn2UnHwr4i_lsQ_4WBBcdmwEUmGOtZoyfwO9Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decent happy hour menu. They make there good fresh and they all come out hot. An ideal place for a bite in the afternoon. The chicken tenders were great, and of good value too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHFoPGen8X3pQiV7rfjV85Neq77JlklPXaUqxE&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was surprised I'd never been to Ricky's before, considering how many locations they have, but our usual spot across the street wasn't open yet, so we gave it a shot. The place has that classic breakfast diner atmosphere with decent, attentive service. The food didn't exactly blow me away—it was okay. The tomato in my brioche breakfast club was so thick and unripe that it overpowered the rest of the sandwich. However, I noticed they have a Famoso pizza oven on site, and usually great things come out of those, though the items weren't available that early. I might give it another try for that reason, but overall, it's a fair breakfast place—nothing special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtTUSYAf8KVzpqLjy3DsWUMZkHF9LktDccolpy&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Kumiko Murakami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrzaF6KRvUp_QuDlErcjgBgm4H4mGAcgrFn7sjBqNDAMqeO3GY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We come here regularly, usually for Sunday Brunch.  We usually get Susan as our server and she always provides great service and is very sweet.

Food is consistently delicious every time!

You can park in the underground for $2 and they will reimburse your parking on your bill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPO2pSBwzb1eA-GIBc_ogSDqEHqrY6asePff9yA&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"John Bruce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuV5ODBnNIimWAyoZ_GtD_Id5KnjSp-Jr-bHjiZST2Bk9M_N7G7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy to eat at Ricky's again after the closing of the boundary location. The food is much better at this location and service is top notch. Pretty bad when I eat at a restaurant twice in a week but the food was that good.  All your favourite food plus they will be adding a pizza menu soon.  Parking is not bad but it is pay  parking. I recommend the burgers as I keep coming back to eat more of them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrzknWReeDqyrQfkjaekKXTgpSVI6iR1Dk1EzS&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2023-8-14"},{"Name":"w chia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUECfNq4GDhAHqSZk9LQfVl_xZjJJSUJUhAKYJ2tSWdkFZEIuPF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decided to go for eggs Benedict on a Saturday morning and found selections around Burnaby to be limited if we wanted to eat early. Ricky's Cafe was close to where we were staying at the Delta hotel, and the Benny choices were tasty. We also had pancakes and that was a nice breakfast. Great service with lots of seating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_ddbLVboH0Skowd5nEsyc-z0hCtQjHBwNMAU7&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Isabel Azem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAI18212pL7CSJLNLPKvOXEaRTwWnC_4nz2HDZ32m45n7oz4c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I was so disappointed with the service we received . We were meeting friends here that had not seen in a long time and were looking forwards to a nice dinner with friends kind night.
… we came in for dinner at around 7:30 and went in because we saw on the doors their hours were until 10pm. At just about 9pm we were told the restaurant was closing and had to cut our plans short.

The food was so disappointing too. My fiend ordered the chicken parm and the pasta was most definitely cooked with jarred pasta sauce. Most def not worth the price. My kids ordered the fish and chips but the fish was so greasy they just couldn’t eat it.
For desert we ordered cheesecake and tiramisu. We had to send one of the cheesecake servings back because basically the bottom half was missing. The server noticed for sure but she still served it that way anyways.
The tiramisu was definitely not tiramisu. It was basically a layer of thin cake with piles of cream and a chocolate drizzle that tasted like cheap chocolate syrup .
There were things on the menu we wanted but they were not available.
It’s too bad, the restaurant was actually nice and clean but the food was so disappointing and the service not great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Turnbull","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb3y-xYzCVR6N_Ai49HYr4STDQ454gU7LeU-LpiQKvRGfVZTU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had such an amazing time at breakfast. The service was above abs beyond most places we have been with plenty of times being asked for extra water and coffee and checking in on us. It’s funny how few places give refills. Our meals tasted great as they always have and definitely large portion sizes too. This is a great place for breakfast and would recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGpCa6POEZHhfwBjgJiKO1vN1QHskm4B0nCZv4&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2022-5-24"},{"Name":"Jana Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFjmUvyv_D0C928LPFmDlM7xtJSop1GTxh4Yhc54LmpKCsxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and i went there for a dinner.  My husband and I ordered their famous beef liver and onions and my kid ordered tender chicken and shrimp platter. Everything was delicious. Liver onions meal comes in 2 sizes. I took smaller one and it was still a good portion for me. Staff was very friendly. I enjoyed the view. We were sitting near the window.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsUp-4eRJ2S30lPaifu2Y7GKmdQJjQxeEcjqyg&fid=0x0:0x5e97e7c7e5a0d559"],"When":"2022-3-29"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Gurpreet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSpy9T1fE8WtvvfcCp0G99t9accekp5Do74O8zp60Z4pvRaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited this Tim Horton many times and had pretty much very unpleasant experience every time. But I have never given any bad review as I tried to understand the situation every time. This time it went too far and I couldn't ignore. This acknowledgment is much needed for the staff that was working in the store during my visit. Last time I visited is on 13 November 2024 at about 5:25pm.

I went to pay for gas inside the esso and thought of getting something to eat and drink as well. Tim Horton was the place to go. First of all, there was no one to assist. I guess the employee was in washroom. There was another customer standing in front of me. The guy working at esso called the Tim Horton employee to let her know that there are customers waiting. I heard her saying to the guy "make sure you don't call me while I am using restroom". I suppose she was in restroom and responded this because of that.  Once she came to take order, she repeated the same thing to him. Then the guy working at esso replied that if I see customers standing, of course I'm gonna call and let you know and if you don't like it, you can block me.

Now she proceed to take order for me and my friend who was with me. I have asked for coffee and grilled cheese melt. She said that the grilled cheese panini is still thawed and she can't serve that. Then my friend asked if she is able to microwave it and we are okay with that. Then she question back if you have worked at Tim Hortons and thawing take time. My friend acknowledged that she works at Tim Horton as well and we are okay with if you can microwave it. Then she said actually we have it but it is only for uber eats and online orders. Then my friend requested it's just two grilled cheese melt if she can give it to us. She said sorry she can't.

Then I was like okay, leave it. We are not going to order anything at all. As we specifically wanted the grilled cheese melt. As I was about to go, she said please don't give bad review. Then I ask her why not ?

Give me a reason for it. She replied you can do it if you want. But i was just saying.

I was leaving the store and wasn't thinking at all to give review as I mentioned I have been here many times. Got disappointed numerous times and never ever give any bad review. I also work in food and it's been 9 years I have doing it and I understand customer service very well.

How she responded back to guy working at esso?
If you did have the grilled cheese melt then why we were denied?
If it was only for online order then why acknowledge it to customer at all?
Then integrity to ask not to leave bad review. Wow amazed.

Whoever is in charge to this location, you might need to retrain your employee and it's much needed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ricardo Arreola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpnoji5QwbP2Y-m4nuNzbvrIrl1FghE-nvkvtONtITGVJF_vhm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately I have to go to this Tim Hortons location every day for my coffee. [{"Name":"Gabriel Souza (Blart)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSnVx7ZTOwrxOmzkyk8g-x4LBtDbZDjqUNRBwPSfW5OfbG78V-Vw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of dining at Brown Social House and left thoroughly impressed by both the cuisine and the service. I ordered the Butcher’s Block Burger, which featured a perfectly cooked, flavorful beef patty topped with crispy, smoky bacon and crisp, fresh lettuce. The attention to detail in the preparation was evident, as each component complemented the others beautifully, making for an incredibly satisfying and well-balanced burger.

What truly set the experience apart, however, was the outstanding service. Erin, our waitress, was attentive and genuinely friendly, making sure our needs were met with efficiency and a warm demeanor. Her professionalism and positive attitude contributed to an inviting and enjoyable atmosphere. It’s clear that Brown Social House prioritizes both the quality of their food and the experience of their guests.

For anyone seeking a combination of excellent service and a delicious, thoughtfully crafted meal, I highly recommend Brown Social House. It’s a standout choice for anyone looking to enjoy a top-notch dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-GTQolz2yVh8m8-O0cuxlHiL_XEtitwMVy7jl&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: Thanks to Sarah and the team for their response to our first review. We returned for brunch and had a wonderful experience. Special mention to our server, Ella, who was very attentive with our food, dietary intolerances, and hot water refills. We had the Angus Beef Hash and Blackened Chicken Wonton Soup. The wonton soup was great, but a tad spicy for my taste buds (in the future, I'd ask for the chili oil on the side). They have large TV screens as well, so it was nice to catch some morning hockey while dining! Looking forward to returning to this location in the future, given the exceptional service.

Came here with a group of 8 for an early dinner. We were sat at a higher table with barstool seats, which were hard to move (as they don't glide on the flooring). Being middle-aged, some in the group needed help from others to be "pushed" closer to the table. The food was good. I had the Crispy Cauliflower and Crispy Yam & Avocado Roll (which was average for the $11 price). The cauliflower had a nice breading and was flavourful, and felt like a slightly smaller portion ("social hour" portion).

We had some concerns with the lack of service. We constantly had to flag down our waitress as we wanted to place part of our order before 6 pm to take advantage of the social hour pricing. My glass of water never was refilled during the meal. For a large group, it would have been nice to get checked in on from time-to-time, as a courtesy. Because of our group size, we still had to pay the automatic 18% gratuity, but we didn't think the service warranted that amount. The food itself did come out in a timely manner and was done correctly with some diners' special requests. When asked, our server was able to take a group photo of our table.

Ample parking in the parkade below with a 3-hour limit, which I was told was a non-factor after 6 pm when I called the restaurant ahead of time. Overall, we had an average experience! While the food was decent, the service for our larger group left a bit to be desired (3 stars).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRMdbceD5gvubL_XIV_xZyV73uBO4uvNPN8nFX&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Chris Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcT6Z40EZW4C3yt0N7VoX3tM1V1mzzAe7xxRrgBiMmtInx7b7I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Brown's Socialhouse Brentwood to celebrate a friend's birthday. We ordered drinks and had dinner. There are multiple TVs to watch sports. There is also outdoor seating available.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1r7v6eFGHx_TnjDH5PaLYUNDgz2ep4pV7bVSN&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"chaitanya gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP-Cx-tNwiu90cNABgEGrEB8sTBdVTRvK_y-kZN0OvutQ-s073wg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Brentwood - Browns Socialhouse, and it was an incredible experience from start to finish. The food was nothing short of amazing. Each dish was prepared with great care and bursting with flavor. The menu offered a fantastic variety of options, ensuring there's something for everyone.

The ambience was equally impressive. The atmosphere is chic and inviting, with a perfect blend of modern design and cozy touches. It’s an ideal spot for a casual lunch, a lively dinner with friends, or a relaxed date night. The staff were friendly and attentive, adding to the overall excellent dining experience.

If you're looking for a place with delicious food and a great vibe, Brentwood - Browns Socialhouse is a must-visit. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO08_3FEcFA7aLMz3TTzE-yN9qQ1G4lgr-Xgjkf&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"virlla devi soothar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ87VSdNOiBHZdFVAOCWbky5_aTwGfKrpQhbWlqGppEwSWfH8BSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently celebrated my husband's birthday at Brown's Social House in Brentwood. The ambiance was pleasant, with just the right level of noise and activity. We thoroughly enjoyed our meal. For starters, we had crispy chicken and pickles, which were incredibly flavorful. Our main dishes included blackened chicken with Alfredo pasta and a crispy chicken sandwich. The Alfredo pasta was my personal favorite. Our server was friendly and even surprised us with a complimentary dessert for the occasion, which was a lovely touch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIllIy92gvjbjUVuQKImk_VX6LjKRVNilTMJGN&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-2-20"},{"Name":"Hembie Ashwe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKO9rJcuK7rmPLT51WDXVZEmLuIpTCZNMBqR345jXFZISUciQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brown’s  is always a hit and today was super awesome because we had a waiter named Jessie who took care of our huge group really well. Food came on time, she was very welcoming and cordial to us. Great Blackened Chicken Alfredo too! I wish they bring back the Butter Chicken though!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maggie M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdc14i8-MYTGVgNkeFp_8cUvOSr08TU9llw-YCHcXvGaMtrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to dine! So peaceful to go sit there and enjoy lunch alone when I have writing or editing that needs to be done. Food is great! The music is on and there are people there but my mission is always accomplished.zero interruption (except to check that *I don’t need anything!) and I can accomplish more in a lunch hour here than in my office with a bowl of cereal. I come back feeling refreshed and accomplished! 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kai Vancouver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5heIFDkKoC83IFbA65C6TMLRjWTHbqDpbnlW25A9H1S6DBNo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"You can enjoy a reasonably priced happy hour from 3 p.m. to 6 p.m. There are many big tables and large space, so it's good to go with many friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWhfOrI1XqkBgw-_Pgximn5U6pHeiALjX-MWc&fid=0x0:0x1f96fae1d97e6d13"],"When":"2024-3-16"}]

Previous, sandwich was wrong.
Is this a good store???","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8GheJPqCEXcY259S-0r8UUe1byAX9fvOwDNtO4xjd15N5WrQG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Mobile ordered 2 bagel belt WITH EXTRA EGG. Waste of time and money","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K ZM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbQQH12gwY2goqP6VKtbLbGoabpUsQzHxFXsEZVAeSh-CWDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"For a gas location, I’m pretty impressed.  Kinda safe too late nite if you know what I mean.

Off the quieter part of Lougheed Hwy.

Ordered online, busy for a Saturday morning.  The Farmers wrap is my go-to with extra chipotle sauce for 30 cents more, sure why not.

Ended up buying a lottery ticket while waiting.  This Esso is a gold mine with the traffic in and out.

So obviously no seating area for those looking to hang with their friends.

For a local gas station it’s pretty big.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raveness Sss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWvT4opHGYIYG4-tYSmgn9RLP7BTF0_G_KYcxxIyYdHnGGfCHWUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Please put donuts on the skip the dishes order menu. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Annia Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCmNf-6kVgoV3z2v1rhLUKPIXQtdwZxPsOxdlb6pZhbXP-BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Typical food court service just with unexperienced and unprofessional staff at front counter.  It was the only boba/bubble tea option kind of decent.  Nothing fancy.  If one still is training or don't like people they should be making the drinks and not at till or counter in my opinion","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkztQK-6BIyfxpIYEKTDuIsufPHm1F-PYWjMSP\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Bill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWN9zwp7xv0imGZck91UiXUA_5sub2NWtj0XbXLIIDzsUyGLI6_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm extremely disappointed by the lack of customer service professionalism at Chatime Brentwood. On December 19 at 3pm, I was ordering some milk tea and saw their Thursday $2 drink poster. There were 2 staff taking my order, I asked them some questions to clarify because I wasn't sure how the deal works. While I was asking my questions, the 2 staff looked at each other and started laughing at my questions. I'm very disappointed in the customer service and would not recommend anyone going to this Chatime location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODXUNpfjtm9PAE4VHw4u8e2yZlU0pjquv1WlZ9\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVePuoaXXyM0dJKn-ODUhhmFE4_3a2_ph2wNm5FbgL2HboE4I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a very mango slush and noticed the employees making it kept looking at the mango chunks and talking to each other in Mandarin. It looks like one of the workers was inquiring to their co-worker about it but they just decided to go ahead and make it without really caring if it was spoiled. I found that interaction suspicious and to my surprise I was right, the mango chunks were indeed old and not edible at all. I knew the taste was off as soon as I ate it since it was way too mushy so I took a piece out and it was brown meaning the mango chunks had rotten. I contacted chatime customer support the same day of purchase and it says they reply within 10 business days. However, is been over a month since the incident and all I got is dead silence. I have both proof of purchase and pictures of the mango being brown and gone bad but no reply. I had gotten sick from consuming just a few sips fortunately I threw away the drink otherwise I would have probably ended up with a bad case of food poisoning. However, the lack of reply and accountability of Chatime has soured my experience with ever going back there as someone who used to buy it once a week for $10 each time I expected at least something edible and if the employees knew something was up they should of spoken up and asked to change my order. And still waiting for a reply for customer service but got nothing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHYMLtSTmJRijuElaMt4_y-FMKNr9NA-n1ueSA\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Chatime is a chain located within the Tables food court and serves bubble tea and other fruit beverages. I ordered the pearl milk tea and it was very typical with less milk flavour and more tea flavour. Service was ok but they didn’t provide a straw for my drink and I had to reach over to grab it. Lots of tables and seats\nnearby to drink your beverage on.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmHqBPaUChw-7NydEfvz-btgwAPJytVzOwy2-G\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-2-9"},{"Name":"joey dai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7bJJzMZHUu9DY_uckxy80NObPKXoK4JkITvzIewsfcupqT2E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The matcha milk tea here is absolutely delicious—rich, smooth, and perfectly balanced. The staff are friendly and provide excellent service, making the whole experience delightful. Highly recommend this place for any milk tea lover!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5tVqcuHwMoYSsDUNLiok6NQrqhQ0QxiYZDc3c\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Panda Paw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0Ug2xYBGS0Dokq2ocby3rrBMBNp1ieVmKFLBuDIrNHmNX-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered QQ Lychee, watched the staff made this drink with syrup + water, which I'm fine with, BUT it tasted awfu! It tasted like bad tap water or water that went through dirty filter, had a bit of pool water taste too.  I was super thirsty so I still drank 1/4 cup, then I threw it away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkmf58wgCDq1kXJ6z9fJBMD7hl-fygjiQ8n1_Q\u0026fid=0x0:0x719ccfd1a7b24f1d"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Kieran Purewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpsPXqRQa5lSQQbUcJ-pLRyGzdXE2MzyreRO2yhH26kI4Ucg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered a taro smoothie and she mentioned how they use the fake Taro. It was indeed the real one when we mentioned that we did not want that. We went back to complain and we were denied the opportunity to get a new drink or a refund. Don’t waste your money or time coming here because the people are clueless.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paludarium Terrarium Aquarium love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISoh6osPDwcCz5V8SxeYnxsZCuyibAPKvdm-8ik1PkJhHspg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I bought 3 drinks but wanted one more. The front girl was really nice and helped me out and told me that there is a current promotion of 5 CAD off if spending 25CAD. She cancelled my transaction and reordered it for me with promotion despite of the long lineup after me. I really appreciate that customer service.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"B W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJp85P5JohieEKJOfTMzyjH1aTNit_eIhBL3dFVyxf0xS2BxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Took my folks for a quick lunch at the ParkCrest Diner. It’s typical diner style, friendly atmosphere, family run and efficient table service. We had the clubhouse, bacon breakfast and the fish & chips. The food taste was nor scrumptious nor bad. Just okay. The prices were slightly lower than chain restaurants.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyNsuhY0A1yKWqhDX0gmu8sbA29Fm4_v6qvl9Q&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Kevin Louie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyd1cWI5-K50M1BsfFNavSiBRGYn0MuSSZ4ltVgrMUnHnWWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Peak nostalgia. If you could time capsule a restaurant this would be it. These types of establishments are a dying breed , so if you’re looking for that authentic diner experience to take you back in time this would be it. As for the food , it’s tastes exactly how you remember it. Even if a more modern or fancier restaurant tried to replicate the food they would probably fail. You can only get the taste of diner food from a diner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQTwghgFpsoo3qi_7FfMw6CYhPj15pFUjTN_2i&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Amanda Lawrence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrm3ZMxoLF2CG9McrTgRAQudtSzxhvJWcA9JJgJsq1W-v6tmez=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute little vintage diner, family run and very friendly. It felt like having breakfast at my grandmas house, we loved visiting here. Prices are super reasonable too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqdFafUNaPNwlMb4pA3eXYA6E_oSQI4Trc8ce8&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Johnny Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8kuvggl1b5n8mcnQaYPPw3eDKW2LyleXkOlCYUlDcd0LxcPXH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a gem!  A definite throwback to ol’skool diners of past Vancouver times…but in BBY!   What I say - authentic, value, greasy spoons - so good!   Had the Cafe Hash - awesome, will def be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9MNun2kmVA4D2Cr6jApX3mNlYSmr22eIJ3aMV&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Brent Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYSM0_7rmQIvuRgwYvvqbzjo_qKvSImbFN7n8plIZlijT85g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I loved the retro 60s feel of this Chinese Canadian greasy spoon, from the sunburst wall decorations to the green chairs!

I ordered the breaded pork cutlets (14.99). They were very thin, lightly breaded, juicy and crispy. It came swimming in a bath of tasty gravy! It also came with a side of vegetables and a choice of mashed potatoes or fries (I choose mashed potatoes). The mash was chunky how I like it !

They also had daily specials, like a hot beef sandwich, hamburger steak and more. These were the same price as the regular menu item but they came with a small cup of daily soup.

Service was excellent here! Cash and debit only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEivMVSe5R012UsRKbfHUVC1cMJTw0g89Y05ST&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2023-10-19"},{"Name":"Eunice L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQkzUZXfdvXjIof6QNpWT0Clt0HQWO6_tic3KMTC1-MnvOY65-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I really enjoyed my experience.  The Cantonese-speaking owners have a really well-run operation for a small team.  The cafe is well-maintained and offers a vintage vibe.  I stopped in for breakfast and my coffee was constantly refilled, condiments
were brought without needing to be requested, food was reasonably priced, quality was so-so with the hash browns.

What really impressed me was the community vibe - there were a lot of local regulars right at opening - one of their regulars helped set up the patio set outside and they were catching up with their friends for a regular meet up.  The lady who was serving everyone remembered multiple orders of her regulars and was very warm and welcoming to everyone in both English & Cantonese.  She never stopped moving - getting coffee prepared, taking orders, delivering orders, checking in, gossiping with her regulars, coordinating with her husband in the kitchen or manning the till.  The husband chef was constantly cooking and also managed to step out for a quick chat with some regulars while grabbing some coffee.

Came for the food but stayed for the positive vibes to kick off a busy weekend.  Overall, well done!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfYe6gT3AjGrpInaPA2AoIzp49Tcms2VCBZsAN&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"Kerry Blouin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSW2DH-eKrJvoqT2G0RRXWJ8bJjxcIzafk7pVuJ5f2_f1-WV9R=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always enjoy coming to this place. Love that it’s not a chain and is run by some salt of the earth types. Bring cash or your debit card. Keep this place busy! We don’t want it to go away! Now is the time to come; when the weather is cold and dreary it’s a lovely place to spend some time and grab a bite.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"LP Suk Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZZWhLTBiNnFdEmOz0oWyNSiMsKoKbYJ0F8gVklQ8QmSRWi9TF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A hidden gem that takes you back to the 50’s, this Chinese Canadian run restaurant is charming and the music is piped over a tinny radio which just adds to the atmosphere. The pricing is reasonable, the owners greet the regulars like family, and it is just a solid place for breakfast, burgers, and other diner fare.
Oh, and the coffee is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVbz5iZxoxYfn_t6TAQs7AhYNtOlJSwzqQd3jg&fid=0x0:0x2a7b38f9b045e4fb"],"When":"2024-5-25"}]

[{"Name":"Sehee Yoon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtOXp5lxWEEk6SCncJwz6gk0H92Eqk9W2JcqIkFNIr6VZdEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is my first time at Timholton today. I've been looking forward to going there, and today was "the day". And I had the worst service experience of any cafe I've ever been to. The staff threw me a cup of coffee as if it had come out, and as a result, all the hot coffee came out through a hole in the lid entrance, making my hands so hot. For that staff member, I may be one of the many customers she meet during the day, but I hope you don't forget to be so kind as to know that the experience of ordering Timholton's coffee is a one-time event for someone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtRIEOc8wW23upc_xEXyY1KtOtZ8n0Jut6JCCK&fid=0x0:0x1d48c823da32659a"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"You can't complain about Tim Hortons in North Burnaby. A place I like to grab morning coffee and treats heading to work.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNC5aXOJs0Ljlbj78NCthTfkZcjONEpoJ407mND&fid=0x0:0x1d48c823da32659a"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Mỹ Linh Nguyễn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUPGdlACpkT-8Ix-ricYXzDX8HyxXIsza9fz1ZfUm6lYyn9xc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I brought icecap here almost every day, for sure some worker here know me very well, it’s nothing happen in summer, but in winter time I think not much people buy icecap then the icecap is go wrong, taste is like sour, over date. It’s probably not many people buy then they keep it in machine to sell for next day that’s why….

I drink almost everyday so I know the taste very well,
Today I really upset because this is second times I got this experience again 😡 the first time happened to me I came back to complain… I told with worker tell your manager don’t let this thing happen again pls. Then I got Food poisoning and
Feeling nauseous for two days.
But I still sympathy for them because I thought after I complain with them I think they will get experience, so I still came back brought the icecap for next few more times is ok, but today the taste sour happened with me again I felt mad then I throw the icecap right away. This time I don’t want come back the store to complain, I went another store brought again the taste is not sour like this… I got so mad because wasted my time and money, gas, have to drives back and forth then just throw it… the store in Lougheed they don’t sell icecap in winter time… if you don’t have enough customers to buy icecap in winter time don’t sell it is better. At least I don’t have problems with health… or manager should check it every day… this fault of the manager, this business will lose many customers because of the manager.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alvin Ou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2JjEF2ENbfZsuNNdlqVZy4pe0bKqoNU0AIPG5sjI4WpOnmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Staff are nice. But I don't know since when I will have to keep asking for napkins for my take out and sleeves for my coffee. Every single time. I have no problem in other locations as they will just put them out there self serve. Even when I asked, they gives you one or two pieces of napkins. This is being cheap to the next levels. I live nearby and I visit almost three times a week. This practice gonna drive me away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ivana Sabljic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSSptmK3sMr38ueSxakMdGefpm0sXA1btpmQ6x2gPwxTUJSXDf0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Truly deserves zero stars. Wait time is absolutely ridiculous. Why does it take 20 mins to toast one damn bagel. Meanwhile worker are walking around in a daze with no sense of urgency what so ever.  Standing around doing nothing, not helpful at all. I don’t even think they knew where they were. Must have been stoned or something. By far the worst Tim’s I’ve ever been too. Do not come here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sakar Paudel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVQdmNpknmolQZ3RjAzn5nM2nfditbGmNxcp1zWFKf_U_Cm9oY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had an extremely disappointing experience at this location around 2 PM Sunday dec 8th. The employee working the day shift, particularly a white girl, was incredibly rude. Despite the store not being busy, she behaved as though she owned the place, throwing tantrums at customers left and right. To make matters worse, every employee there seemed to be fighting with each other, except for the thin white guy who actually appeared calm and professional. The overall management seemed poor, giving the impression that this is one of the worst-run Tim Hortons I’ve encountered. This kind of behavior damages Tim Hortons’ reputation. I don’t usually write reviews, but this was undeniably one of the worst customer service experiences I’ve ever had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Riya Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJceQwZz0Alt9B9HgGFAcU7e5mJIoBgRScSzUbWA1-Ofc2dzA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I worked here 2.5 years ago, and I quit in 2 days. The manager Anny is a horrible person to be sitting at a managerial position. She was so rude on the first day itself. She doesn't want the employees to talk in their own language amongst themselves (which is acceptable) but she kept talking in her native language with the other employees. She did not provide any training, or any sort of learning. She mistreats the employees, the customers and everyone around her. Tim Hortons should take an action or this branch will not see any progress with the kind of leader they have (Anny). Terrible terrible manager.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Norah W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsnf3xJOpMipfvIUwj8oOqg_s4HtxC2hxaAVVZvkqRsCJyJmjP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This location has good parking spots right outside its doors and a cozy ambience inside. We came in on a Saturday afternoon and were happy to see a good selection of pastry including the new Timbiebs. The service was quick and easy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODqzPaEkcLbzkSjV1AWNWprBsFc1aK3qiTx_Zi&fid=0x0:0x1d48c823da32659a"],"When":"2022-6-18"}]
