[{"Name":"Sinyo ganteng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVK6DhObLW3StVcJ_e9Ph42mdmAq5cSoW-d536hao-jSu7WAn8I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried for the first time. Their salted egg deep fried wing is okay, pretty crispy on the skin and juicy on the meat, but  barely taste salted egg on it. prices are pretty expensive. Also bought the durian spring roll. This one is good. but also bit expensive.
Service is okay, atmosphere just regular food court.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPe3oWdLqPMANiPLEmXPdMjVVygzPvQLXKxTUxR&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Eden Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNLi8pjkdjqmlxE1IFEGaNATKSxVgmuUgcclrgx3Di14AqjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was just really disappointing. Pork chop was deep fried so hard prior to baking it was tough and dry. Sauce flavor was bland and watery. Rice was soggy despite it being a baked dish.

I get that this is a food court, but for the price, you gotta get more than this right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqDPAilAkbqz8aJjdcEn_hcOw44QxE1VclG0OO&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Casey Ye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEApUDalFbqPMkPa848Ez6bzcTZugbIf9CdQT67iXdNxdfBiDr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Decent size Baked Chicken Steak on rice with cheese for $17.75 after tax . It is quite salty but overall good. There is real tomato in the sauce and chicken thigh meat used for the chicken, cooked well and very flavorful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO78Us056UsuYbePctkn9vCl13c09FXc4LC-sit&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Echo Mak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8zfKESf24sBrD_u2JQbuoTpzweQhnIu3TX_XPmjomDVnkQ6DbKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is not bad for food court, prices are reasonable.   However food does come out quite slow, especially during the lunch rush so go early.  I was quite thirsty after my meal though...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5zsoPKsPLN8-bnwhG_rsK92t_Cya-NGPJ_1Ty&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhlRzWDXzdsN5IEg7ILK_EQ56zA9jcQ-fPPr3cS5cgV1YVlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This place is located in the food court of Crystal Mall. It has been awhile since I last tasted any fast Hong Kong cafe food on Nathan Road in Hong Kong so this as close to me being a poser as it gets.

Here were the food I ordered;

1. Iced Hong Kong milk tea. Tasted pretty watery and weak, missing that nice smooth rich taste.
2. French toast with salted egg yolk. The picture on the menu looked amazingly good; the salted egg yolk oozing out like lava. In reality, it’s a badly pan seared French toast smothered in condensed milk with a dried up layer of salted egg yolk inside. It’s like a dried up 100 year old cow, nothing is oozing out.
3. Intestine noodle soup. The intestines had that strong gamey smell and the soup was a bit bland.
4. Brisket and tendon rice noodle soup. The soup was hot, the tendons were tender, most part of the briskets were tender but a few were stringy. Over decent but definitely wasn’t work the price.

Overall, always an adventure to enjoy the lively atmosphere of the food court here especially during peak hours.
I would say most of the uncles and aunties running the food stalls are pretty nice and friendly.
Unfortunately, Nathan Road cafe here is nothing like cafes in actual Nathan Road in Hong Kong. (Really looking to travel to Asia again)

I am off this road for now…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtOmsFOzU6qHh9kzKllHWFi_tweYzDe7eP22RV&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Mandy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5mEmihbLMNbXayRaHIlQjiu-swJc8Muackys6qwrAKQ_9K-xI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered the pineapple iced lemon tea. Very good, a little bit on the sweet side though, wish there was a sugar % option. There were big chunks of pineapple and lemon & lime slices.
Cash or debit accepted. Short wait time","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOw3529AoM3Dndi6fXrJp_glh9iwBqFnZ06gKQB&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Addi L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTnlR5MICiGE73IqW2NSDmuc0wN6jbCQTqUiu6siIFiacFuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They accept credit cards! Seems that most of the workers can understand Cantonese but speak Mandarin or English.
I ordered the (Egg and Pan Fried Chicken Rice) and was quite surprised at the sheer size of the chicken. I waited roughly 15 minutes for the dish to come out.
The presentation was beautifully done, and the pictures on the menu do not do it justice. The chicken steak was crispy and soft. Because they use omega 3 eggs, it was incredibly heavy; the rice, with the sauce, egg and chicken made it quite oily. Definitely on the pricier side compared to the other options available in the food court.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaIP-dsNszCnkT1UNf01fL5TnRX5lxDHt15q_C&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-3-18"},{"Name":"Pongo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXT-qQCE1uUwfmES1FGLIpAmkroUlDIcsJZMXejhRkO1uA9CxO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I thought this place was a lot better than what the average Google review score indicated. The tendon + swirl egg on rice hit all the right notes. It was hearty, inexpensive, and filling. Beef tendon was thoroughly cooked, and drenched in flavour. Swirl egg had a decent, soft texture. Wait was approx. 12 minutes. Credit cards are accepted here btw.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkGKSufBIK5j1kJR7-LaBlCDvU9-ssUAFfesZX&fid=0x0:0x5401e882e7ac4dd5"],"When":"2024-5-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Anthony Plaxen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0TosyGAQWTqM_XvTHaXfq2jDGHv6ifKWBgTGcJKYnap3ceipL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A lovely and quaint neighbourhood cafe. More places like this should be nestled into every neighbourhood, it’s homey and has lovely calming vibes to it!

Excellent service and very friendly staff! Ordering a coffee here is great. Also tried the carbonara for lunch and it was quite good! Has a good creamy taste and the ham matches perfectly with it. It’s plated really nicely and elegantly. Coffee has good flavour and has strong depth.

Will come back again. It’s a nice nestled neighbourhood cafe in East Vancouver and worth checking out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSi_Z_N5qD4BJkpfBJh5CN05rxbLeLCydGu94c&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Dana Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQIw-0oOUNgoyniYugTscGkgpKJS8tpx4V0tAajn3ZGkNIfqEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy and intimate cafe in a residential area. Unsurprisingly, it wasn't very busy mid-afternoon on a weekday (save for a pair that left shortly after I arrived, I had the place to myself), so it was nice and calm. It was kind of chilly inside because they had the door propped open despite it being cold out, but I can imagine it might have been stuffy for the staff in the kitchen area. The barista was very nice!
I got the Sooyo croissant, an egg tart, and a milk tea. I loved the Sooyo croissant - I'm weak to the brie/fig combo and this had just the right balance of all the ingredients on a warm and soft croissant. The egg tart was also really nice with a hint of cinnamon. It was bite-sized which was good for a small treat. I also loved the milk tea. It was very strong, and the brown sugar syrup enhanced the flavour!
It was worth the trip for me for a relaxing snack stop!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdGU7v21ZyjAaMqmB-AdwzvlmYdde2hVURBX4e&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Hondro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdA5EfEJGFE_Wqw6SKvif7X44Sj0EvL6330umFVx4wThQmgqDI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sooyo means “awesome” in Taiwanese and it does not fall short. It’s a cute quiet, and calm coffee shop that reminds you of the lofi girl you used to study to in university. The food is off the charts, staff is lovely, and has views of the downtown skyline. Unreal spot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-x0n66_CecYUFyw1S9t_BrspirFAavkP1p-Oi&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Billy Chai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjhTx3gNatyYGIEmlgcisi5HNSS4K7xZ4IsKIZeODtjx3TiMG_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the ham carbonara, mushroom pasta, egg tart, latte and peppermint mocha. All tasted great. I think portions could be a tad bigger for lunch but definitely would come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHSl1jZvfm_gY4UOEt92_TPXXHLx3VHQf2OI0L&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Pat Waslen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkC-Tyq5Sy6eH64VG6FwtcQj-OJYnSvli4ZLpkEY8S6PBvQxBoIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every neighbourhood should have their own little place like Sooyo Cafe.  It really is a very welcoming and it has such a varied menu once could visit it every day.  I believe that have had it now for 3 years and it still remains one of my favourite cafes to visit in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPk6ZOdxFG3osr3LLugeCVg52eUt0otIQ_kjUwt&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Rachelle Castro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTlI_8fSUkEtqgb_5bBSWzSZp2YkIdHUSFuATMaujZtmSbf34x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quaint little cafe in the middle of a residential area. We ordered the carbonara pasta, egg salad sandwich and a London dog. Everything was delicious. Have been here a few times and never disappoints.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7YRR05OgJyrWwamhQU04UCGrTuB4l228Khe6W&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Jordan Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFsjfnS-oiBTX7iRzPhMh-PXM_FEBemeI_C6-8CDhB4SzDFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the carbonara and wow, I was not expecting the depth of flavor that it has. The plating was also great, and definitely gives fancy vibes. With that being said, the location is very homey and down to earth too.

Will 100% be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5gPOUc57dQv7LHkDOZwWmtRgQ6WeDlmcRvQoc&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Josh Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkkyxhPTEpUzQ5foRkJncedrUI9-aKVkl-8bPKd9pTC4acuQRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cafe with homey and calm vibes. Dishes are creative and plating is classy, not something I was expecting but was pleasantly surprised. Seems like they are constantly innovating and improving their game. I definitely recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNW_HxSBJNdZzmakqhmP6LtfyQSZ7Xm2cW6CIFb&fid=0x0:0xd592b069ec18dfa2"],"When":"2024-8-12"}]

[{"Name":"Daniel Mendes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWfyNEj2hAlFDhso__VBFi6FvULT81eYCfgh0tEG1hfmmiLO46=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful experience today! The coffee and cream puff were absolutely delicious, and I was really impressed with the customer service. The young lady working the 1pm shift was handling things solo during a busy time, yet she was incredibly attentive and made me feel welcome. I truly appreciate her excellent service and the effort she put in to make my visit enjoyable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXn7wYh6umes38pZEQcWVacJj_sqruOklMJ8mq&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jen Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlaZ4jVI8-MGK8N3Ennssxj3Am6YAlBQiLzRukb1hoeXq6X_3y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The tiramisu croffle is so delicious, the basque cheesecake is very good too. Lots of nice seating and good AC if it’s a hot day outside!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO68I7-f1hOXl6Q2u6_5Qvt55-VYdMt5L1qbuF-&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Yeshvi Mehta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVHHFZUwt0pnim38TVGVDQUhu3Obi33NtK1Ek9rBbru761t74M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I remember this place for having $.99 crowaffle during Covid time!
Stopped by again for their delicious crowaffle, and I would totally pay full price.

I got the tiramisu crowaffle, earl grey cream puff and hot chocolate. Totally recommend all three, and can’t wait to try more.

The service was a little slow, but they were surely busy. There was a small issue with my dish, and I went up to the server, and I told them and they promptly made me a new one. The ambiance and aesthetics of the restaurant are adorable, make sure to dine in!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoy0thZJ-h80vcEtiYflTyORrqceKyi5gG01eP&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Bnj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNh4WOBtEBrNeXTtCvPPHoOi2fCnIWYUSsxvGCqPlNVWcYg71G=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered the Dubai chocolate from uber 😂 omg! Disappointed. The photo you are using on uber it’s fake. Liars!
Do not order Dubai chocolate! Idk the rest, probably worst than chocolate","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdKJXoioXvLkuE6DpJNrS3_yutdXk4wOUe_dgw&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Sandy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKzWmD3yqDm1j3bPcX4s2bAnSxyGdM67eMohhq5y4VrF_zJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice cafe with lots of space and seating. We only tried their desserts, didn’t order drinks. All the desserts were super cute. Husband had the giant toast and he gave it 5/5, crunchy on the outside but soft on the inside. Ube fans will love the ube cake, soft fluffy but not over sweet. Kids enjoyed their mango bingsu and the strawberry pot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2P1YWgen-_dGgkkJko1MfQjSTzhZT8Mgc0wt6&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2023-7-9"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I quite enjoyed their croffle even though I was full from dinner. It was crispy on the outside and chewy and warm on the inside. I got the combo with hot americano and although I couldn't fall asleep at night thanks to the caffeine, I would say that it was worth it. The croffle also came with whipped cream, slices of kiwis, strawberries, and bananas, and extra syrup. They didn't skimp on the fruits which I appreciated.

If you're ever driving along North road, it's not a bad place to check out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlUT8gBaJUK9tLKG_6EZOtNONBo60BpzzjvutF&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2021-10-23"},{"Name":"Winnie Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6fPSN5uI4FuY8CMxX9v8QU_1VDEbPbmppdovszprfj2819A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall is good. Waffle was very yummy, but drink was a bit sweeter than we expected. We had tiramisu waffle and corn latte.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_deZLBqpw05BMgL878v8eAqiBHQFnUF4DKCLY&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2023-10-11"},{"Name":"Alan Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-QmMYfw75kgf5vonVt_7RAAdUJRl5hAF6Ijht6iC6ZE8aPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was in the area shopping and thought I'd make a pitstop here as my wife wanted to give this place a try.

Quality- the waffles had a nice crunch to them on the outer coating and the inside was nice and soft. I bought their original waffle paired with a dalgona Frappuccino. The drink was delicious. It was very sweet though so for some people it may be too much sugar.

Service - although it was a bit on the slower side for speed of service (working by herself) she was however super friendly which is more important to me. I'm willing to wait a bit longer if the food is good and the people serving is is friendly :)

Cleanliness - the Cafe was clean and organized and had all of the proper social distancing stuff for COVID and staff was wearing PPE.

Overall I would definitely come back when I'm in the area again :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSoPVqo3vxY4gPQyPfTG-a4GKwL83Pn90cTFVW&fid=0x0:0x96d1d3dedf1eba06"],"When":"2021-6-27"}]

[{"Name":"Paul Hong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRpKduqb19k8iOlDvRrDxtR1LkmMQ3f1St94M3vXnwpoCFnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food, calming atmosphere! Highly recommended brunch cafe!

I often go out for brunch before my work, and this place is one of the best brunch I have had. Also the price is half the price than the other restaurants but the taste is the double.

Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPf6MrEBf3LWRBeITK8-WmBNDnl-98702d3n_Ml&fid=0x0:0xcf4e3e5cc2c10b09"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Sienna H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfhHxUPKbC7hlXVnIXxiki18h9_gWhjRPm0mx4UPtxir5JCbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s the newest cafe where will be my go to place. Brunch dishes are simple but fully tasty. Absolutely delicious and perfect! I love all the homemade sauces and drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCj8IORBDATef79s9_FZOY7-jueyntWrMZViTj&fid=0x0:0xcf4e3e5cc2c10b09"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Jason Jeon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3SP6Vm6Ilg74I-qLhK3q0RUKW80d9mhVRGt3xFJlFCkYil5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For.Rest Cafe is a solid spot for a coffee break. The pancakes were well-prepared—light and fluffy, with a nice balance of flavor. The iced americano was super fresh and had a refreshing, tastefully bitter taste, which I appreciated. The atmosphere was comfortable and low-key, making it a nice place to catch a break or get some work done. I’d definitely come back when I’m in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIQ4eo2NyypowBArtpDjMN4FpPEwCpR5JMcZdk&fid=0x0:0xcf4e3e5cc2c10b09"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Michelle Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPVfuzgO-NOUBaWnfwRHvW2NjF4_Yy-SPBCC_ZGs5F5Icb7_6frw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a cute cafe! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Iris and Scott Wedding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjUefdZRNJMcCgmMMfLYQWeR_K3UNo-piHulpCkZYKBV6iOBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sonja, Gen, and the rest of the Hart House team are absolutely amazing. I had my wedding here - specifically inside their event tent - and even with the rain, it was beyond magical. The bartenders were on point, the staff were super friendly and accommodating, everything was set up and in complete sync with my coordination vendors. The food itself was divine. Guests kept complimenting me on the food selections and dessert choices! Overall, Hart House is the perfect place for a lush green and quiet lunch and dinner, for exploring the grounds and Deer Lake, or for a major milestone event like your wedding day. We don’t live in Vancouver, but we can’t wait to keep coming back to Hart House over the years!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFP7vDzX8oIYxooeOgTFgxMEWq_fOdtNlvrGqW&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Megan P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmpi2Cjy1ZUv7EQnoPBoHx8RHeeUNY6hzlrkO_zclHA7Z0LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've loved this place for a long time and have been coming at least once a year for our special events.

The food was even better than before, since the new executive chef joined. We were very impressed by their appetizers, and main dishes. We had seared scallops, mushroom arancchini, ricotta gnocchi with mushrooms, and halibut.  They offered a amuse-bouche that was very tasty and pleasant.
Everything was well seasoned and delicious. Gnocchis melt in your mouth and fish/scallops were perfectly cooked. The scallops and the mushrooms in ricotta gnocchis were AMAZING! We felt the care that was put into cooking the food by the chefs.
Would love to visit again to try other dishes soon.

The server was very nice, friendly and accommodating.
The only thing we missed was the overall service was slightly slow. But the quality of food and great ambiance of this place make up for it.

This is a real gem in Burnaby. You get better food than other casual western restaurant franchises for similar prices.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXy7i1BpIUiadKaj5xeo8AtN-p0st1PH9_v6TQ&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Alessandro Salaris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrrAFhZ0DWxEznML-_6_HmJZtHRgzEa3bJxENt2tNnWIMlGRMK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location, exceptional service. Dined outdoor, surrounded by plants and flowers everywhere. Our table was facing a giant green yard used by the owners for a wedding party happening at the same time. Lovely atmosphere. Food was great, and service was really top class. A bit too expensive but overall is worth the price. Thank you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-vTj-bSHLiFzNYXKnItLYI6MFtistWxOECKWe&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Norman Farrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOKauCUm-k2P6JXZbVaCjI514xmAUd8cPqhMzakFQdELGnjKWj0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Busy afternoon with a large wedding party on the lawn overlooking the lake. We enjoyed the outdoor dining area. The “happy hour” menu was offered until 5 pm when the dinner menu was available. The happy hour menu was limited but adequate. We had mussels and clams, fish cakes and Caesar salad. All nicely presented and tasty. Desserts were crème brûlée and fruit Pavlova. Both very good. Service would be 5-star except that my wife’s plate arrived more than 5 minutes after my shellfish dish. A couple normally expects to have entrees served to them at the same time. Young woman serving us though was excellent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjJroRJs34SVkyC6BtXuJsBdF3DSweNAFvMRb8&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edit: we returned for our anniversary. Excellent food and service, and a wonderful night out!

We visited Hart House Restaurant for a work function. We were seated upstairs which offered a cozy meeting room with technology for the PowerPoint. My husband had a view of Deer Lake and commented several times about how pretty it was. Buffet dinner was tasty. I’d love to go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlCoBnkkEq4aVMwgRO5YEx4yp0roA9_EC1rJLr&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Mrs. Leci","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFUu7tIDGHhiFP61EOIZLCOSzvwJkGN10CXxqa6MRhYpyxpm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our dining experience in this restaurant was nothing short of exceptional. This feel-good-and-charming restaurant was a delight from start to finish. The dishes we ordered was really delicious, the plating is beautifully done. It's charming ambience is the cherry on top. You can walk outdoors and if your lucky, there might just be a wedding ceremony going on with all the flowers blooming. It's a great scenery while dining in.

Love, love, love this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfcOig6lBzZReEK-le2YMVUTawL8XutJcU9tHx&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"G C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW20QuW__IfaK4FwuvG_N-_l9xiiBSDQFOta_GyQe9BNR4mDQU3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were greeted by a friendly gentleman as soon as we entered. The fireplace was on; warming guests as they entered. We tried the set menu with wine pairings with each course. We were given a pre appy snack which was a nice surprise. My favourite dish was the steelhead. The fish was perfectly cooked and the flavours worked well together. My husband enjoyed his roasted duck. The servers were attentive and sweet. We were happy and full when we left. We’d definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNk1FDX496YJPPsMj-mpi7JFIVMOhXqimacP6AB&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Michelle Kienzle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEPDzRZApZ0TVs_lWHFpNjZ0-OB0yjGNDbbsAlhpoWQYWs0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful lunch. The food was delicious, excellent service and beautiful Christmas decorations. Our group was in a side room so it wasn’t too noisy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQqHqE-1c4hme9ck52j0Uoq-XtlKZUflqDGpPV&fid=0x0:0x373c4eea0847305f"],"When":"2024-12-18"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Monica T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfTcr7UpZvrmvtqWfFjBeZIhFRwKW8QZ4OivzWAS6rOFQreQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place used to be good, but I had a different experience today. I ordered seafood and vegetable chow mein, specifying crispy noodles, but the dish arrived with a lot of sauce and soggy noodles. The sauce had soaked into the noodles, and I couldn’t finish them. I’ve had this same dish here a few times before, and it didn’t look like this. It seems like they may have changed management or the chef. The portion was also much smaller than what I had last time. I understand that food costs are rising and don’t mind a smaller portion, but at least maintain the quality and taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_z4cBSY9YT1ABDkdunH1Xa3VpzmouU6Qo45qX&fid=0x0:0xcfda3bd0a6e99e70"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the dinner for 2 and couple of other dishes.. the waiter let its swap one  of the dishes out of the dinner for 2. Which made my wife and o happy they did that.. all in all the meal was very tasty.. the workers are friendly.. can’t say anything bad about the place..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmjzLXNefPSofBkjf-FPr_YohOItvVyB4x_1cG&fid=0x0:0xcfda3bd0a6e99e70"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried their honey garlic spareribs and their sautéed greens with garlic and both were pretty solid, fresh, and tasty. The honey garlic spareribs could have been a bit crisper but it still tasted good. The price for the greens wasn’t cheap and a bit high in my opinion but the portions for both dishes were good. Tasted much better than food court Chinese food and up to restaurant type Chinese food standards.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyg8t2rbAMAHjKVX_288aDk6wYA1amQN-TAwYG&fid=0x0:0xcfda3bd0a6e99e70"],"When":"2023-10-20"},{"Name":"Jon Noj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6QnxMhGdN39gi_BJd3q4T2iEf3nn8TbjBOu-4vbFHvGKuQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"New management again and they raised all the prices by 2 dollars and got rid of all the lunch specials/dinners for 1 and the specials with rice which were a good cheaper option for one person. They also got rid of a couple of dishes I liked like the Mapo Tofu (although they had changed the recipe to that one and I didn't like so I guess it's for the best)
Probably still good for large group orders of multiple items and for parties but no longer a good option for a quick lunch for one person sadly.  If the recipes didn't change I recommend the Beef Brisket Noodle Soup and their sweet and sour pork.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PicTsao2","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgSrP8Bsph_CXWaSZ44qGamDFBzT8JaOtpAu46eC9jo2Kzkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't know why there are people giving them bad reviews, seems to me they are just expecting Michelin level service and flavour. This is a family own small restaurant not a fancy restaurant. I love the food here. Always great portion and taste fantastic. I'll come back every week!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Acacia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfZtRyvS02Y-nirNA8KmFkYuuXc-nQka6l-WTTFRPvtHXJYHMv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"it was our first time ordering from this restaurant, so we were hoping it'd be a nice experience and we could make it part of our rotation of favourite restaurants! we ordered take out sunday morning (about 9), scheduled for the same day at 12:05, since we were having people over for lunch, we wanted the food to be ready on time. however, we had to wait a whole 30 minutes after arriving there at 12:05 despite having asked them to prepare the food in advance. as a result, we were late to our own lunch - isn't that ridiculous? when we expressed our disappointment, they didn't even respond with an apology.
we ordered 6 dishes, and the 2 most expensive dishes we ordered they swapped out for random cheap dishes without letting us know - we only found out after we got home. still, the receipt says they made us pay for the dishes we ordered but didn't get! they scammed us.
the food was slightly below average. no one touched the two dishes that they subbed in randomly because it was not what any of us liked or wanted. the 4 dishes we ordered and got, when compared to other chinese restaurants, is mediocre at best.
extremely disappointed in their poor service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terri Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdHMQamP6ntk6cmD8m9VHj4cLgJWNXVSwfy5Jk1_ks8LpnASP1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is legit your go to authentic Chinese restaurant! If you know what wok hei is, then you will get it at this restaurant! (If you don't know check out uncle roger haiya 😂) I think it's under new management. The owner works both front and back of the house. I noticed lots of takeouts (10% off pickup) I ordered several classic dishes a d they did not disappoint. I got the scrambled egg and shrimp on ho fun (flat noodles), honeymoon fried rice and deep fried tofu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJE78eZDG-VNOiLsA4u8TugMEW_6R3SRtMr6xB&fid=0x0:0xcfda3bd0a6e99e70"],"When":"2023-9-19"},{"Name":"Cadz0027","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIFUNNJs7scwbkY4PZ16V1bA3H0RJA79HbuipNxcT7YzukKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could give six stars for the service That we received today I would. Lady was working alone, but she kept a smile on her face and gave us an amazing service. Amazing food as well.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Joel Adimathra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU-GI6mpr6xG9dwqsNu_gX6OTWh-qfSwtdeT_CEmMj8mboLR0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We found this place by accident. My wife and I were really hungry after visiting the Burnbay village museum for the Christmas Tree Lighting special. We were so pleasantly surprised at how authentic and amazing the food was. It felt similar to what we were having in the middle east. It made us feel nostalgic for a restaurant we loved to eat at in Bahrain. We will definitely visit more often! It's our new spot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_PdjFpt6NbfT0le8PiS0dVeThxGKvDnTwBGg&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Shabnam B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINmhU8uS2Zsvl6JqLYduWdVvBF_JzgRelqj_9FWdHGPySXHjI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got take out on October 13th. They gave me this half of the lamb vindaloo dosa even though they charge full price for it. It has very less filling as well. Very disappointing and tastes terribly dry and bitter. I called the store and they don’t take accountability of their quality of their food and aren’t honest at all. Definitely never going back or recommending this awful restaurant to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPteTxw9I1lCsCWfNBw15l_UCXsdAeYwO9FdJxk&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Jayanand KV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ300Yeb4iZG-kKuVhK9gX6deBVBJYl5e792S9p7AKCEsTgpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We stopped by for dinner on a Saturday evening. Got seated immediately. Medhu vada and cauliflower 65 were good starters. Onion tomato chilli uthapam was tasty. So were gun powder dosas. It comes with masala, we requested the dosas without it; price was same though.  Veg kothu paratta was not tasty. Mango lassi , falooda drinks and coffee were good.  They seem under staffed. The lady serving us seemed overwhelmed and tired. We had a rather long wait for our food. There is not much of an ambience; very basic and old fashioned interiors.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtUunKmWiGAlCYKIedsvofV79GL-XibzvkTBBq&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Nick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGjptqH3FdoeLfdSjPWQygL5KEsM_ui4pClg77BekGUD0E-Q_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I'm being kind while giving away 4 stars to this restaurant, and that's only and only due to the fact that the food was extra spicy, the way we like it. We asked for the food to be made extra spicy and they delivered. Otherwise everything else was going against this restaurant. We were the only ones in the whole restaurant during their lunch service and the food still took over 40 mins to reach our table. Imagine the wait time of it gets busy. The atmosphere is very basic with ventilation being an issue. Go for the food, not for the atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpxSY6GRJyC5V4mZfFB0Ii3gTJWww0hCZoe20N&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had Chicken Kotthu and asked them to make it spicy.
It was super spicy and fresh. A little bit of coriander leaves were added on top. It came with a tasty gravy.

Great portion that I shared with another person.

The other day, I tried their Rasam, awesome in flavours and heaven on a rainy day.
Poori and Parata are a bit oily, but tasty.

I was eager to try their idli, but they said that it's not available.

Update : On my second visit, tried Chicken pepper fry with extra spicy. They delivered it as expected high level of spice and tasted great with rice.

But be prepared for many No No.  Rasam wasn’t available. Rasamalai and Faluda drink were also not available. So left the place without any desserts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6wBeBuD-GsvZgRyhS5dosNDVXnSdc-6h-g14v&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"S Ramesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWq93P1v7Q5LEZs1NfgPNPQHNhO82zc2MQImRPuuKzwZ46QhAaZzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to explore South Indian cuisine.  The food was excellent quality with fine spice level and authentic flavors.  Variety of food selection with reasonable priced.  The tipping option are enormous.  The customer service met beyond the expectations and pleasing with accommodating nature.  Washrooms are clean.  Amble parking at a great location.  Definitely will come back with my family and friends.  No hesitation of recommendation to the food lovers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Radhika Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqhivsBGfuy4Hh4Ikya7TYc3M3f3ax5pRlJEKTGryuw2nE44wF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food experience, please try there chicken pepper soup reminded me of home, Rava onion dosa don’t forget to tell them to make it with ghee.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPDK-CIlePG_zXf95WGKtnRGsErDCPmb4IGavV&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Darlene B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJEzkJ_Cm9j6nle9JrD7D2YVUuFX857_POLo7FiF7FYoLYxKrd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was delicious! And the server Sahil was so sweet and fast with service. We got our utensils and waters immediately after being seated, and were even expedited an appetizer earlier than expected. Cute little spot, I really appreciate the art they have up on the walls. It’s a little run down, but for the food, service, and maybe a little bit of privacy and intimacy w your introverted mate, this spot is perfect. Oh and they checked if the food was dairy free for me beforehand which I really appreciated. (Worth the price it don’t break the bank btw! A dosa is like $10)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNx5VNt2Y2GeO8XNw5N3up6GV0nYQuMniQhXghL&fid=0x0:0xf59903adc47f1060"],"When":"2023-8-26"}]

[{"Name":"Bernie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPXTBFQGy4UZogf6r0hGxUGZ8fvtwePPN5iicbAtQksaWtpwOP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tim Horton is my favourite place for a snack.  Over the weekend, I visit the Metrotown Mall for shopping. Took a snack at the Tim Horton at the food court. I got the crispy chicken sandwich but freak out with the taste and the very thin chicken.  The food quality is not worth the price I pay. Other Tim Horton stores do not sell this quality of chicken sandwich.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6UAfsXTV2B3W3Bw8tZLgilhAXFYzgLxgvjjqq&fid=0x0:0x96c719804df5cb2a"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"jaipreet mangat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURqP3P2UKzU6KpvWiT9K5qrCL97HEQ0NYd6T6KWSLD7Jeetxgi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I generally like the experience at Tim Hortons – the food and overall service are good. However, I was disappointed with the lack of proper facilities, specifically washroom services. Having a clean and accessible washroom is essential for any restaurant, and it’s something every customer has a right to expect. While there is a service available at the door, it is not sufficient or convenient for customers. This is an important aspect that needs improvement.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJf9ph-45InWTgP5YzC1LPv-Er9tPe_gghVw5wVNsaZul3lTlM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The manager in the morning and a group of mom-like staff served us and always gave me a warm smile. Now that I'm leaving Canada, this is my favorite coffee donut shop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBCEj99xQnzjQXYsknRyYUq8OLXS3PpCn8ORFB&fid=0x0:0x96c719804df5cb2a"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"24k magic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMqzXmjPoF_Fv-8j-usHWDZVV1T9lPRoMrcBkpWnSlckMkXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I prefer this location than the one Inside the mall as their service is fast and the ladies are friendly n have a warm smile :) they’ve never gotten my order wrong too and their online orders r fast too but sometimes bins r overfull but I understand they might b very busy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harman Sanghera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIN-1mivi_zLpQILEtIwiSzkey_JtcHnckUR7t2dmtq4M9ZrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pretty standard as far as food quality goes. Can’t expect much from Tim’s. One of the better locations when it comes to service. Location is always adequately staffed and trained and I have never gotten an order wrong.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catherine G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT8Nn6t_2yVpeVu_W5x-yj8B3R40JhCwbXMGSdq6kgF5-krF5H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The weekday morning crew at this location is great. Always seems to be properly staffed and everyone working hard! I usually mobile order, but the staff are always very fast and friendly. The Filipino manager or supervisor (I think her name is Gladys?) is really nice, remembers me, and always helps expedite my order.

This must be really difficult to work at (close to skytrain, lots of unhoused individuals, and mental health/drug use), but the staff seem to treat everyone with dignity and respect. I've never felt unsafe coming here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nisha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMwhePHas7hihMtxSKZDLq9ZTJgsVKHXO9oR2k5xH15205fE8WPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Have tried this location several times for breakfast and lunch but really disappointed with the cleanliness of the place. The tables are always dirty and the trash bins are always full.

Some of the food items are really good like Habanero chicken and veggie bowl, honey cruller & boston cream donut, potato wedges but their coffee is never consistent be it original blend or cappuccino or cold brew.

Although the service is real quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbHnfp0OxEsCklqDQWTmKx9R_Glsr-yFVt_uv2&fid=0x0:0x96c719804df5cb2a"],"When":"2023-2-26"},{"Name":"Varun Jayavel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNMFGegqUwiJxsTUXzUpDG-GUmy0qJyqPfPuKZhhsVGbbvvjXU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a very disappointing experience at this location. The supervisor or manager who took my order was also making my coffee, but she left it half done to take more orders. This caused unnecessary delays. To make things worse, two other customers who ordered food after me also experienced significant delays in receiving their orders. The entire process felt unorganized and inefficient. Definitely not the standard I expect from Tim Hortons.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Majid Taherinejad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViDPiXU0JKzH_zVow85jmOX5CVYRWsJheQX5s1ReerMFEgHGH43w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Viva Sue Pizza is a true hidden gem! It’s incredible that this place has been around for over 30 years with the original owners, and you can taste the tradition in every bite.
The thick crust is topped with tons of toppings and flavorful cheese.

For Iranians: Chef's Best is just like makhsoos pizza ✅
Super Sue feels like makhloot ✅

Sue, the owner, is so kind and generous. She has such a warm attitude and is happy to share stories. The place isn’t fancy, but the food is all about exceptional quality and that nostalgic taste. So glad we found this spot! Highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFCX_XS9iHJf-bosxWAm9bMc_ajZanR4XXXaXe&fid=0x0:0x4ff907ccb4f9a3ef"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"TIMOTHY NG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN2gSiOaEpoGCNqpejeNlvBx1ORB59GTGiaGiQ4L8w_ZeW5g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience here. The pizza was excellent and crunchy. The lady was so nice and smiled all the time ! I will definitely come back again ! :) However, one small pizza for 1 person was a little bit too much so I will probably bring more friends to share a larger pizza next time !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONKtFKa7N4x-hHKuz6dcTHbiUUPkaXzimcQdxs&fid=0x0:0x4ff907ccb4f9a3ef"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Zuhal Akay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg1GgpOURu6iroxmZvkn1xIHAzW9h3eAvSkLgL5SlOyjxqMwldWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loaded with ingredients, topped with a delicious homemade marinara sauce, and simply excellent pizzas. The best pizza we've had in Vancouver so far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7enJ4DawB-GH_M1Y0pp79bHP-Lay_6MAOqT1A&fid=0x0:0x4ff907ccb4f9a3ef"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"Eric Sahrmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKDVPpEOav4bcliJ1B-9dSabhVsGjEASsG_60KBpYSm99uWBGv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic pizza.  Friendly family run business.  Comfortable small dining area. Ate with my mom, the topping are amazing, they made it instantly after order so it was hot. The crust was crunchy and it was so nice. I ordered a Spanish latte and basically it was just all condensed milk and milk and a dash of coffee (came out as a very light beige). So you can just imagine how sweet that drink was. I have never had such a BAD Spanish latte in my life. You're basically just drinking condensed milk. And it wasn't cheap either $8.50 or something like that. So I asked if they could just dump a bit out and add more coffee and they wanted to charge me MORE for that bit of coffee, even though the drink was UNDRINKABLE. I didn't want them to completely remake the drink because I thought it was completely unnecessary. At the end I asked if I could have a full refund or even a partial one. I would have been happy with that, but they refused to give me one. Basically told me I just had to deal with it or spend more money to fix the problem. Ended up throwing out the completely  full drink. Customer service took no accountability for the problem and had a hostile attitude towards me when I brought up the problem. Almost as if they were blaming me for their mistake. NO APOLOGIES, NO NOTHING. DON'T RECOMMEND. BAD SERVICE. OVERPRICED. UNWELCOMING. RUDE. MONEY HUNGRY ESTABLISHMENT. Definitely NEVER coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitsuba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPTokkJ7B-7PXzC1asSVZYKNDX01MAmrvmPdKoBlxIra8E3U0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place doesn't serve coffee only water. When I asked for a new one the owner scolded me and said no?

This was after I bought another one since he threatened to kick me out, if I didn't..

Which is hilarious since the couple next to me ordered a cake and shared it, and yet they could stay.

This place is a joke. And I would recommend people to not use their hard earned money here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgDV8VX0Secg6OQbF936OGg_yVP2aQjNr7x5xP&fid=0x0:0xf83f0ad361f89b31"],"When":"2024-3-22"}]

[{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m pretty impressed by how the staff was able to churn out orders and take plenty of customer orders in tandem and made sure that any pile up of people waiting for either were cleared relatively quickly. One of the donut glass case was covered by the Tim Horton’s sixty years banner, so not sure if they have less items than usual or that you can still ask for the items not shown. The person at the counter knew how to process an order where I had filled out the survey for $1 iced coffee without additional assistance from the supervisor, which doesn’t always happen. Didn’t stay in to eat, but happy with my take out order experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXNfQU2t4rMKsMbhmQS71ZbGg84CrAjKocRGur&fid=0x0:0xf2936acf0d72beed"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Shubh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFfsAESA4cnJr_oE8kPQ9x02VZlmqcrgL8nGk69JpCeZNwxk0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tim Hortons never disappoints! I had a fantastic experience with both the food and service. The staff was welcoming and quick to take my order, and my meal was prepared perfectly and served right on time. The breakfast sandwich was fresh, hot, and delicious, and the pastries were soft and flavorful. It’s always a pleasure stopping by here because they really know how to make you feel valued as a customer. Highly recommended 🎉🥳","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blaine McDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaj5l5jRzEJPL23Cnc0i6apZq-RiY0Ze04YDbrQBJiGywNoZiB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Late night (after supper) visit only one staff that we could see and seemed to be run off his feet a bit haggled. Nice ambience large customer eating areas, outside patio with picnic tables. If you dont mind a wait it's a great location","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZMPSxp2p8JBpb0SqbUn7RdcP6G0s0ykNw6iM4&fid=0x0:0xf2936acf0d72beed"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Aman Khotani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0TdsVKvGvZSdb_3B1sz-HZ2EeCweqKRhy_Vsw3GH1R6B-MA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Tim Hortons and had a fantastic experience! The service was prompt and efficient, with my coffee served perfectly on time. The staff was friendly, attentive, and clearly focused on making sure everything was just right. As for the coffee, it was of excellent quality—rich, flavorful, and brewed to perfection. Tim Hortons continues to deliver a consistently great experience, and I’ll definitely be back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoHd5hTCH_qL1CIrJbRfTreD5Cb9V5OGdEBFylMdqYYezaCqKj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This was a gross Tim Hortons 🤮 The floor was extremely sticky, almost as if some hadn’t cleaned it in weeks. Shame on the store manager and staff for letting it be a gross mess.

The simply cheese pizza was extremely disappointing as well. You could clearly see that the person got lazy, and piped the tomato sauce onto the pizza. Also there was barely any cheese on the pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQMw2DuCX80r6c1fk5jo0Wk7jTftSQf5hLEnaF&fid=0x0:0xf2936acf0d72beed"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Leanne Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkClBAXb_Dl2U1kkiGW5NLQhayIfds0ClddqhB9HmKKMkQKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Based off the wording used and a quick check at the accounts, it’s pretty obvious the positive reviews of this place are fake.

This is without a doubt the worst Tim’s I’ve ever been to. Unclean, always understaffed, the workers are rude, food is inedible. Ridiculous wait times, they’ve constantly screwed up my order. Whether it be overcharging me, giving me the wrong drink, or missing an item. They’ve done it all and I’ve only been coming here for a few months. I go to this one because the smaller Tims in the gas station nearby has some kind of a bug infestation problem. Seen the same staff working at that one so I’m guessing same owner/management.

I usually come around 2pm and the baked goods I’ve tried ALWAYS taste like they were made the day before. So dry and disgusting.

I now stop at a Tims in New West to get my order. Avoid this location at all costs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Blanks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8t6ZCmVJRAcSXFetCTGRT1rWGtaSTTetuNMT87h4YEzRLtP4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went in to make a purchase and asked to use the restroom. They told me all 3 were out of order. Pretty sure it was a lie as the staff member said"we don't make the rules. I will be emailing a formal complaint to corporate and the city of province whoever regulates the rules around washrooms in restaurants.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Mackie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlMlVpi0_E4BxSLJkes7MhJzdYdAznf41U_NpiapfFZ1ym0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately this location’s employees seem to not deliver on the simplest of requests. I only order dark roast from Tim Hortons as that is my preferred coffee. Multiple times they have tried to pass off original roast as dark, simply because they didn’t want to. I called out the worker after tasting it, and she said “oh ok, uh 4 mins” this type of “customer service” I will not stand for. If they had told me that it would be a wait due to brewing, then I would wait. But instead I guess it’s easier to lie and forget.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I have ordered 2 everything bagels and they gave these mostly burnt ones. Do employe sleeps during preparation?that girl gave unnecessary attitude but no attention to the order. Ridiculous behavior as well as service. I would have given 0 star","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoJi9i6jKGVQCP9sJkhnuT8CTSuqFRkaS2tqFC&fid=0x0:0xef66571b2102ad9e"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Ck Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3MWDSpnvfbSfIcMPQemcrDj851pfPR-fjVN54Tw48l4WrAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited this Tim Hortons and unfortunately had a disappointing experience regarding customer service. I waited at the counter for over 10 minutes without being acknowledged or served by the staff. This was surprising and uncomfortable, especially since the cafe was not very busy at the time.

My concerns grew when two other customers arrived and were attended to immediately before me, despite my prior arrival. This situation made me feel overlooked and discriminated against, which may have been an unintentional oversight by the staff, but it was distressing nonetheless.

I hope this feedback is taken constructively. I believe that prompt and equal service to all customers, regardless of background, is essential in hospitality. Improvement in this area would certainly enhance the experience for everyone.

Thank you for taking the time to consider my feedback. [{"Name":"V P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIxj8yENCKwdvGgfIR4uDA0bh65erhq2TGJESneOu_P2sA-HA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered 2 Grass Jelly Roasted Milk tea through DoorDash. Neither had sugar and one looked and tasted like they used water. Just disgusting!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBbhyeqhf-0HQAIBgeojvjYZt2HzCcSVGNNOiV&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Roshni Sarath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_Mhsw0X5KywwYv3vY8x0c2kA5Hbqo3Y1IIXwrT4V3UMjYiKgr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"UPDATE [Aug 29,2024] : The Manager / Owner , Hugh reached out  to me . Hugh seems to be very sensible person . He collected all the information and acted on it and assured staffs will be re trained on customer service. They gave me a refund for the affected drinks. This gives me a hope that they might not kill the experience for another customer next time. I understand how google reviews affect business. Based on Hugh's response and action , I am updating the rating to 3 starts from 1.

[ORIGINAL REVIEW , AUG 25 ] : Service is way below average! They messed up 2 out  of my 4 orders.

They missed out on an add on for me in my drink, despite taking the order correctly and confirming on it.
I realized something was off right after I took a sip of the drink outside the store.
I went back and informed the staff that it appears that they missed an add on in my drink.

I got no response.Customer service is simply unacceptable!
One of the girls just took my drink , transferred to another cup, put the missing add on, giggled something in their language and put the cup in front of me. No apology/ acknowledgment, nothing!
Very rude staff.

This time they missed adding ice. Which when I pointed out, I got a stare from one of the girls and she said it is there.
I could not stand this attitude and decided to just leave the store.
I stepped out and opened the drink and there was no ice !

The second instance is I ordered for a mango smoothie for my daughter and they gave her a mango slushie!

Staffs are rude and kills the experience of going to this store again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am a regular customer of Chatime and was pretty stoked about seeing this new branch open so close to home, but I was kinda skeptical about visiting when I saw its a newly established joint and the reviews showed the quality wasn't good because of the lack of experience etc. Unfortunately its true, this is the worst bubble tea I have ever had and will not be visiting here again and really put off Chatime now.
I feel awful for saying this as it's clearly a new chain and the staff are in training. However, I don't think staff should be training on the fly and surely they could organize some offline training and tasting sessions or something surely?..
I ordered my go to Large Matcha Roasted Milk Tea which tasted like bath water with the smallest hint of matcha, it was so gross and I felt sick so I couldn't even finish it.
As all Chatime branches, they do offer Oat milk alternatives which is great and the regular menu although I don't trust ordering any drinks from here.
Also the restrooms are not available at this time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv-V2k95ovDIWdRsOELP226v5CpvXG9RYHXrsn&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2021-3-29"},{"Name":"Alan Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-QmMYfw75kgf5vonVt_7RAAdUJRl5hAF6Ijht6iC6ZE8aPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chatime for me for the most part has been hit and miss. However my experience at this specific location has been great and consistent. The owner is kind and genuinely tries to accommodate customer requests.

Quality- ordered their new limited time TRIO cup drink (dragon fruit bits with grape in one part of the cup, mango peach in the other and the last part of the cup was guava) the flavours overall were refreshing. Although I did not have toppings, I'd definitely grab it again next time but with coconut jelly.

Service- the owner is super helpful and was very nice to my wife and my kid. The staff looks like they are still in training but they were still nice during our interactions.

Cleanliness - although the dining room is still not yet open, the space it self is quite clean, they have plexi glass up and PPE worn by staff.

Overall a good experience and will definitely return if I am ever craving chatime.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3J-EMWiATDtkk_ce88yc7ceU1-eutvMYiMovl&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2021-6-19"},{"Name":"Ashley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5kCzc7eRb4jfW7949WUTBpVquxs5hCBGMbV9VKX7WizSYJao=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at this Chatime location. It wasn’t busy when I visited as I was the only customer inside. The staff was patient with me while I was deciding what drinks to get.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQJ3UeoNt_Eb4VSBqSkCdPQCl5RTmtGE8rhK30&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2021-4-20"},{"Name":"Jemma Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXCHgsvEOda8Euj2F1UAraubpKMT6WV7yVIZRrlelmuyGL9zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Expensive just for the regular size which is smaller than a standard regular size bubble tea elsewhere. They are lacking milky slush options. But the flavours are good :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtKrs8uJoc2ybxiHJgsyaehcg1pMk_m0ZDt_Xk&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2022-6-12"},{"Name":"Bob Seymour","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0fRtxv4CszHn4EcW7G0G4cbSaQfULwvKaBFoESMUbanu_Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great environment, staff and quality milk tea. Same owner as previous Zenq. I was not familiar with new selections and the owner was very patient to introduce the new drinks to me.

Will be coming back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb1L34NkBnO4FqfgHhh5Gr1gvKgy5DlI218yw6&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2021-3-14"},{"Name":"Jess Kwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDBzh8dbkC1LzSd7XrpM8gWZ5VmXx8K9kvQQxVQanMubn1WEvT3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff and good tasting drinks (better tasting than the chatime closer to my home). Clean and nice looking inside and hope one day after Covid people can come inside to enjoy the space","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXZFoMiwiBJ7VM83GX2yUVqz3VMh_eq_LJ1qaP&fid=0x0:0xbd21794f7fc07a8f"],"When":"2021-3-9"}]

I don't know,  feed your workers or pay them more so they are not THAT hungry.
And no. I didn't eat some just for photos. Telling lies is for stupid  - I am not the smartest, but not that kind of stupid.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_FctIuPUfHQmNtMgwh2mSvgRzLN7xLEV9Yf76&fid=0x0:0x3f69167dbae48f45"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Guinevre V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJaT8TBmP4FTwLCFRoen_pexmMrkwx21BlciUWGh3YaXljqfV5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered delivery for 3:40am, whoever worked tonight was lacking.  Instead of one fry order with no salt, they added more salt to all of the fry orders. No straws with drinks. Missing dipping sauce. Food not fresh.

Every other time we ordered was great though. Need some quality control","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avinash Pathania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIffNjM14L5v97rrS-cc5UoaQwuYgSzP9tgCdq3gLpqxUEWOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As an Indian, it’s quite embarrassing to write this review, but I feel compelled to share my experience with this particular McDonald's location. Unfortunately, the staff working post 11 PM, especially the individual in the blue shirt (likely a supervisor), exhibit a consistently rude attitude toward customers.

I live in the east and frequently visit other McDonald’s nearby, such as Grandview, Boundary Road, and Cassiar Connector. However, the service at this location stands out for all the wrong reasons. The staff seem poorly trained, and their attitude is unacceptable. It’s not just a one-time incident—this behavior happens every time.

What’s most disheartening is that this rudeness seems targeted, particularly when Indian customers are involved. As soon as this staff member in the blue shirt spots an Indian customer, it’s as if they take out their frustrations on them for no reason. This is both unprofessional and deeply disappointing, especially when coming from someone in a supervisory role.

Their arrogance and argumentative behavior suggest they believe they own the restaurant. This problem isn’t limited to the counter service; even drive-through customers face the same rude treatment.

This experience has been so unpleasant that I’ve decided never to visit this location again. McDonald’s needs to seriously reevaluate the training and conduct of its staff here, as this level of service is far below the standard expected from such a reputable brand.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annia Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCmNf-6kVgoV3z2v1rhLUKPIXQtdwZxPsOxdlb6pZhbXP-BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Too late and lazy to cook 🤣 Last day for the coupons and I got 8pc instead of 6pc nuggets 🙃 McDonald's saves the night for a starving girl.  They usually provide great efficient  service for drive thru unlike the other location five minutes away. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mehran bakhtiari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX52_I8QBEvpbwP2DsvccLDQ1hUjTB0qEjwNL_660Q7Wjozcaqk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I congratulate the manager of this Tim Horton's branch, you are the most unworthy manager in the world.👏👎🏻

I came to this branch today and it was a disaster here, both the service and the behavior of the employees and the cleanliness.

I was the only person in line and it took 10 to 15 minutes for them to take my order.
If they were working, it wouldn't be a problem, but they were standing next to each other, talking and laughing, and it didn't matter to them at all that I was on the line.
The health condition was a disaster, everywhere was full of stains and dirt, and the floor was full of paper towels.
I can't explain the state of the toilet at all.
The photo I took seems to be the best explanation that exists.

The sewage is much better and cleaner than here. I took several photos, which unfortunately I cannot upload here, but I will upload the same message on Tim hortons app.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-4r8GkhezNPdi_roGFT_WGcNp7Hd6cWuniFS5&fid=0x0:0x65dd66a30485068e"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Dat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiWNTb2mj1MMD4SDcDWEj8uG6Ow3gj4UB5x5jY320mMnjkv5Zv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was Oct 19 2024 at 3PM PST. Cup cover had some coffee spilt on top when served. I ordered French Vanilla and it tasted like water with some hints of coffee and sugar. There were lots of  tissues around trash bin area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8G8AoH3ZG19-WT7ijh5VG9nhoEA8StakL6PWt&fid=0x0:0x65dd66a30485068e"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Troubleshooter E.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKzv0x_1DM_uM4g-tecfDvd0I_OBcI5XoixESy1oAFLNQ6QDFW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I visit here often as it’s the closest to where I live. But man is this location disappointing.

Very short staffed and even when foot traffic was relatively low, I’d expect my baked items to take ~ 10 mins to complete.

Hygiene sucks big time. There was litter almost everywhere and staff couldn’t be bothered. Tables were mostly dirty too. Not uncommon to spot fruit flies and the like.

Food is average.

Honestly Tim’s has really gone downhill. All the stores I visited had been more or less the same.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Akwinder punia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJntwqgmz3tJ1KrZzo_ekWFujb9YF83_zrrMUwsFQKy1MhI9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited this location around 8:00 PM today and had an unsatisfactory experience. The employee ANMOL, was extremely rude when i ordered a bagel and asked for it to be toasted, but she said that they don't toast bagels or croissants in the evening.It felt like an unreasonable policy, and I was disappointed by the lack of flexibility and customer service. I hope the management can look into this and ensure a more consistent experience for all customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sevgi Yurtseven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKy2jtPh84jlAwE9lMXPgEJ3y1WVckiKBVKdxsxPJX4kl6LLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tonight, I went to get Timbits, and the male employee was not following hygiene rules. With the same gloves, he touched everything and then placed the Timbits into the box. For the customer before me, who appeared to be of the same ethnicity as him, he used a napkin to place the Timbits, but for me, he didn’t change his gloves. Then, without washing or changing gloves, he used his hand to add ice to my daughter’s drink. I really hope we don’t get sick.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shapinder Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPSb5wfrVXPA41aCFGJp9kls3YT4SHXjx5x0B4UGo_4PlFlQk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""The service at Tim Hortons is always great, but today stood out thanks to HUSAN. She greeted me with a warm smile and provided quick, efficient service even during the morning rush.Her positive attitude made my day, and I really appreciate her effort!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4wK-jqnP5hr2Jw0c7g_77Lz-aJ6zM-bkBiYFP60wFwcUxV2NU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food and drinks usually take forever, most of the time the orders are also wrong after waiting. There's no consistency in anything and you never get what you actually pay for. The staff member Kathleen at the register is basically running the place, she's super fast, friendly and directing other staff. Give her a promotion or raise because without her I'm sure this place would go even more down hill if that's possible. Tim Hortons, have some pride in your places, you have enough money to make them better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derin Geo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbZ9aM_pUYz2yNS_COYstxqJtbGUsUbD6NWXxxh90QeMMACY2N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Regular customer here. I have to acknowledge that this shop has a proportionate degree of employees trying their best and then some doing their worst. I dont know why but i feel extremely unwelcome in this tim hortons most of the time based on one employee’s behaviour. Not the first ive seen this happen and it happened to me last night (dec 12)  between 9 and 10pm. I completely empathize with the fact that your jobs are challenging in its own way but, the bare minimum is be firm with us customers. The lady who worked that shift really needs to work on her attitude. The bare minimum you could do atleast is give me my food just firmly. Stop throwing or smacking the drinks or food when you serve it to the customers on the counter. This even happened the day before when the same person was throwing two little boxes of tim bits on the counter to another customer. Its really disrespectful! And also please be calm and humble with your tone. It really makes me feel guilty for coming there. (Maybe genuinely its just the normal accent and you may not be intending to do that but please atleast try to.)","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"anahita hatami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQ-o6gwcAXOjCJCdPLpBMeXB6iHThpttDoU6zj03rQHgYevw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The store From outside it doesn’t look good or doesn’t have an eye catching interior design but they have the BEST BAKLAVA in whole BC. I tried their Baklava and it was the most amazing the most delicious like the BEST sweet I have ever tasted. I bout two pack to go one small one medium, It was a bit pricy but worth it I would say.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPf60IcXDW-T1XoBUTOuz5VwZSAtjpBhCh2pMrV&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-12-26"},{"Name":"Heyam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQm9BhjOHMjC7GcWrHn68t1cIzjRHFnDfgXZNgHLdz2uOG85st=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here with my date to try Baklava. They have very fresh baklavas, lokim, and baked goods. The Turkish coffee is very good. I really liked the Turkish tea.
Staff are extremely friendly and nice people.  I recommend this place to hang out with friends or family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVNjCZhCBhOwqRWefwKeDdeKgOwmw-ZKePyf6J&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the varieties in Baklava that I have never seen anywhere in Vancouver.

They had dry, more juicy and less sweet baklavas.

They had cold baklava that was unique and delicious overloaded.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKQsVnaHrPlaARnSV9OZb9YxRK6KOOe6BmecKq&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Hassan Mk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn8XljJKUWtM5hZCcrws3Ntw3dFgRbwi5l6-83UHe5aX-z7xYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our visit was nothing short of a delight. On a sunny weekend, my family and I ventured in, eager to indulge in the array of baklava offerings. From the classic to the exotic, every bite was a journey through Turkish confectionery craftsmanship. Each piece, meticulously layered with nuts and honey, offered a symphony of flavors and textures that left us craving for more. The variety on offer catered to every palate, ensuring there was something for everyone to savor.

Accompanying our sweet treats was the quintessential Turkish tea, a delightful complement to the richness of the baklava. Served with warmth and hospitality, it added an extra layer of authenticity to our culinary experience.

The staff, with their warm smiles and attentive service, elevated our visit to another level. Their genuine hospitality made us feel right at home, contributing to the overall pleasant atmosphere of the place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzbes_aknZotcmJM4h5pq-zsHe1XOFT-MQ_2v4&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Atena Razmpoush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDTwnpwsyCMQv83dsdwlkz2BAvureQHzZZxo2_BIzfjtUBCR_R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tasty products, friendly people, clean place, good price.
I will definitely go back there with my other friends!

The pistachio baklava wasn’t too sweet which I loved! And the aroma of the turkish coffee was fascinating 🫠 they make the coffee in a traditional style using hot sand!

These guys make everything from scratch in the shop, super authentic and delicious!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnGWyQ-ZWmhdYwrxLfIKod5LOc_tZq3oLS5cU-&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Jamie Coo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMtT8SYH3ODglSdZyhsIz5N_cesns6jNpwE2VJCXq0WPBgF9EA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here so we had no idea what anything is, so we asked a lot of questions and the staff was really nice and patient and answered everything. The baklavas were super delicious and we really enjoyed it! The place is very spacious and clean as well. Will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSRhQkNQOFTNXjZGIgolw0sW2yXqpKzEK4RocI&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Hakim E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKh-iMj-_rDGQN3VCbzbu_kiuv0nHkHesY5lkxIxZFiLe004Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, very friendly. The baklava is fresh and sweet. I have tried Turkish coffee the last time I was here. This time I tried the Turkish Affogato, which is a Turkish coffee with ice cream. Big thanks to the owner and the great staff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCgA4Ozc_PqtPRi4j2vBGeOV90aTl0ioUKfeQI&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"M K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbi6LJtKWW_2rjs9UHr5Hby-WcnZyGuhY2NPvJWMqZ_P0zVpzO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven’t had chance to have anything savoury here yet but Baklavas are authentic Turkish. No honey in them like what our lovely neighbour Persians make. So, if you are Turkish and homesick or want some good Baklava, this IS the place to stop by! Best part is you can order by piece or bulk if you talk with store owner. Overall, you won’t regret it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqzPLyRYb1vddccFaG7TklxvTR6S0HoxJ5yhbh&fid=0x0:0x7dd1a230462a0e4d"],"When":"2024-5-31"}]
