[{"Name":"Thunder Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdSkmsSZNhQgmdDGKl222cUn9wFQ4eo2ZH5ZKJ65CE7S2osss=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is very good,highly recommended to check out this place while you in Burnaby! The bubble egg waffle is not too sweet and they have stuffing inside of each bubble. We ordered the Mochi one. They make the waffle fresh to order so they are fluffy and crispy at the same time. Best to eat them straight away.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPFfcgVQb5AE3neJtc1_kt4IBiHilN_5WWNv2y&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jessica Qian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMPHnv5ykgYQs8zvHb-zflWJP4NabP5GUcTNQF5f9Hl7NQFW1S=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute cafe! Love the graphics on the wall and the cute designs. It’s not a bad study spot too. The drinks and food have pretty nice creativity and tastes decently good. Personally I found some of the specialized drinks taste a bit odd. Some drinks you don’t see often at regular cafes but may taste a bit different, totally depends on your preference though. Menu has lots of variety and customer service was acceptable. Washroom could use some cleaning","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1e55xQhgSOBjFerQccVgrA5KynYNErWXb0amt&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Michelle Trieu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRUdLsKoOQIbSFHtkcOmbZuj54calmd_Aq93Oh5d2s-U0bc5dT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute decor on the inside, wasn’t too busy when I went in on Sunday afternoon (2pm).
Ordered the catch on fire and creamy shrimp XL sandwiches, did have to wait a bit (~15min) but was worth it.
Bun was soft and buttery, egg was fluffy and not over cooked. Shrimp sandwich only had three pieces of shrimp but still quite filling.
Catch on fire sandwich was good and spicy, but possibly recommend getting more sauce? And there’s only a bit of noodle just on top to cover the top.
Otherwise not too bad!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBwZjhIDNeknGp681H80T3MMqxuIYU2J9yMLoN&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Liza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU6psZuYm5issGPqVIywDJmiQmgvYke0cz4aCVVktU9NoaykdJkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere is great and the place is pretty spacious compared to others. They have a great selection of desserts and savory food like egg sandwiches and crepes. However, I feel they could improve their selection of drinks, as everything is very sweet and icy. The coffee was also average. Overall, nice spot for a quick and yummy bite!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtw-TO9LgzZRoWFxZ7Cj4kT6SJ80ueE6qieXri&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Christopher Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVexNzsO8991iK-9EWX-70Xc57sEkVGaaf84klilDJ3qadcoigBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped in here randomly with friends after eating dinner nearby. Was immediately impressed with the decor. Very whimsical and fun, the kids loved it. The fresh coconut jelly with mango (comes in a fresh coconut) was unique and very refreshing. Our friends got the mango shaved ice (bingsu) and it was also really good. The menu online doesn’t capture everything they offer.. in fact the menu online seems limited. There is a self-serve water station if you want some after all the sweets are consumed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-Add8RJtd9lSyH0fUMG-CilGFCL3fzmuAXF_9&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"candy L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgq2OgnXFRsC1icGye-CTgUf_6kEV0cPoOgzI7ANMes5eDT-Xz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Last weekend, I happened to be in this area, and the weather was a bit hot. So I wanted to have a cold drink, but there were very few shops around. I chose this one to try. Interestingly, it had a lot of pictures on the walls, and the most special part was the ceiling, which was decorated with many cute hangings, making it feel like stepping into a fairy tale world. I ordered an iced oat milk Earl Grey bubble tea. The pearls were very soft and chewy, and the tea had a rich and fragrant flavor. Since I had my dog with me, I sat at their only outdoor table. Soon, a very friendly staff member came out and asked if they could give my dog some free ice cream. When she brought out a cute little cup, I saw some things that looked like chocolate chips on top. I thought they were chocolate chips, but she explained that they were carob beans, which are safe for dogs, and mentioned that she also had a dog. My dog gulped it down in just a few bites. It was the first time I had heard of carob beans, and she even told me to Google it .Overall, it was an unexpectedly pleasant experience, and I will definitely return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKMvk3pOl48AVc_yFsdwNHTbx76nbjr3OqEKSe&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Meriel D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdBZiOjd-GeyzGMWsBAXROxAGpgvxnw6omqBMdoCAEl3YzDBX0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a hidden gem in royal oak, this cafe has different variety of drinks and sandwhiches a lot of their items I find very unique!

We were waiting for our car wash to finish so we decided to come here for a quick refreshment we ordered a jumbo mango slush with pearls. Was perfect not too sweet and has the right amount of mango flavour she said she used 2 mangos and I can definitely tell!

I recommend for all your sweets and bubble tea needs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNd-dOqb1oK_mHR8SmYnfExn_KcHe_XT1715Zm-&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"ashley (ash)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVca1AqgmVAUxYl3x1gw4mblzPVNYqkxX-Ca1xloNJPimDcUOmGUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been a customer of theirs for almost a whole year now, and still remains my favourite cafe in royal oak! They always have great food and are changing up the decor from time to time, and the owner is super nice and accommodating 😊

I've also worked with them a couple of times to organize events at their cafe and the process has always been super smooth and fun to organize with Something Sweet, and they have such innovative ideas all the time for new food and drink items! 100% recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPC7P1zufhrY2upoI_cF7_v0xsy75uFGjEL7fyi&fid=0x0:0xb7eba217bfaa74ff"],"When":"2024-5-19"}]

[{"Name":"Paulina K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHESGuv2e44yh_7pNCkjXfHsSmzMLHqmPnws63OHRE0hDZGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Small cafe - extremely quiet. Good selection of tea, coffee & chocolate drinks however nothing extra ordinary. Their mugs seem to be not very well washed. The cafe wasn’t busy at all yet even when there was no one waiting in line, the lady at the cafe bar didn’t take all the mass pile of dirty cups at the front so it was quite distracting to sit beside a mass amount of dirty plates & cups. Seems like a small family run business, but I do believe they can do better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSJwUPQJpKyXxDxamXE1PWHKX18TCVqaMScAT0&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Samantha McColm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKzi-7JNrC_rSzJcOL0zetHy_k8l4rQueMj9Z8lBPXZ0Sd2r7-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food, really enjoyed the breakfast sausage wrap. Honestly. I will dream about that wrap. They had super fresh tasty croissants and the Vanilla lavender latter was also great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVxtqRroB32tNK6zjlezCXpn0lUuCegOh_i6VR&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Rishu Sachdeva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvTBeEbRg-SIO8iQBstzbrCDRm1m4lUsJNaOM5lAiT0XQnNdX4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute and sweet vibe! Loved the drinks! The rose milk tea was so good! I wanted something on not so sweet side and the barista made me the perfect recommendation.....My brother has a sweet tooth and the recommended brown sugar milk tea was a perfect drink!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqnu1yLKXY8PD9aKaPZamA6qAdae5ZQLcdl8h7&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Liana Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBd7Ss8Y7y3H5JQstWWjO4TKz3hKo9b4W72dyZfc4FSDaNq6e4-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small, quiet, and quaint little neighborhood cafe.  Great for picking up a quick breakfast. Enjoyed their apple peach vanilla waffle and their lemongrass chicken wrap was also good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKmjdXLOMSUWHVdQ7lVu5EsXOb1mnIEz3lK7Rc&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2023-6-13"},{"Name":"Janet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYX0KD6zVBb-KVfav12OTiQHpKAX44ciWjj7UwWI7eJLtEUjp_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The matcha waffles were amazing! The kids  and peach waffles were a bit too sweet for my taste. Everything was made fresh and nicely presented. The kids area was a nice bonus.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODVqAbTf4xFZoVZYxhhAx4S4JfO6k9V8dx4Ut4&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2024-1-22"},{"Name":"Joyce Szeto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu5pYboexWdn2AESh0M-GcEvSyoq5MoQrmjhy2r0gsnwHcEiK4XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My go-to for some quality me-time! The food is fresh and made to order, and the drink selection  is good for those who crave caffeine and even kid-friendly options. I find the cup size to be generous for the price, something you normally wouldn't expect to see at a local café. There's a kids' place area, and my kids loved playing there after having some yummy waffles and strawberry mint milk. It's not super busy to dine-in as there's an incentive for take-out orders. I prefer dine-in so I can enjoy my drink while i read/write 😀 Fyi - they close Tuesdays!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_U-Gy5X-x30Ejb4Ie6BAyHPNIsEknEjcYhM1k&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2022-12-16"},{"Name":"Julian Tu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUccbSC4ghmImblBXURerAc5in7hUNzwjywsW9q13-eiHpFJ49c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time Customer alert ⚠️ 📢

- Tried this cute small store for their waffles and drink after work.
- Had their waffle deal where you pick 2 waffles. We picked the Chocolate and Matcha Waffles 🧇
- Drink: Fairy Rose Milk Tea Cold and Vanilla Lavendar Lattee Cold
- The store was quite open concept and had decent music on.

Pros:
- Won't be a bad place to study, but it has limited seats overall. Probably roughly 10 tables 📖
- Waffle was really yummy, I personally liked the Matcha since it was nice and fluffy, and if you look at my photo, you can see the waffle texture. 🧇
- My partner liked the chocolate waffle, which had bits of chocolate pieces.
- Both waffles weren't sweet, which really made it worth it for us.👌👍
- The Fairy Rose Milk Tea, I liked it as I could taste the rose flavoring, but my partner didn't like much as it was more milky. If you like milky with rose flavoring, then give it a try ~

Improvements/comments:

- I think investing in menu per table would be better as people can sit and order. The reason for this is that guest can order whole sitting and can add onto their overall order.
Instead of paying right at the door with the TV menu.
My partner and I would have been more inclined to order another batch of waffles if we hadn't paid beforehand.
- There was only 1 person during this time, and maybe it would be hard to do this, but the likely of someone ordering more is easier than paying everything first, in my opinion.
- The chairs are okay. If you are wearing shorts, just pick another chair as it can cause lines on your back legs.

Overall, I won't mind going back again and would recommend trying the place out 😊

-J approved.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK7RCicdjKvXr8PbNDTnjGvhu_HPvG-cR0yOHw&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2023-6-12"},{"Name":"Yuen Tso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGxQe3CGkaLkRsj4mn2zb12RFye96G7s1qoZk2obkll8HdPJM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It’s a shame they charge a cup fee on uber eats and door dash when it should have ended on may 1st 2023 hasn’t been fixed still . Strange the manager doesn’t read the comments here

Other than that Quiet and cute shop  . I tried their matcha waffle it’s quite dry. Maybe it taste better in store but they have a bogo on
Uber eats/door dash","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNS4Z9B2W8FBoy9V-8XGAo561Yax6CTDfy64ccY&fid=0x0:0x99d5cb2d2a7625d3"],"When":"2023-3-17"}]

[{"Name":"Eva Zia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJp1CScTOq-jdIBVBA-K4f_r74TZU-kRd9MclConVIiSCPfy3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was looking for a takeaway coffee on Sunday and came across this place by chance—it was terrible. First, the coffee was completely burnt and tasted awful. Then, the medium size was priced like other places, but the actual size was like a small elsewhere. I was really disappointed with myself for choosing this place because I usually try to support local businesses, but sometimes they make me regret it. I thought I should’ve just gone to Starbucks, at least I know what to expect there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZ8Ik9kgsDNqRJ-qDzJh6EBeTg13A7l14kRCCm&fid=0x0:0xfdbaf300e9499ed4"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Inci Karaduman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuz90-BI8mkfIOCTJg-bbQh6j_O7R3GEg8I_bf94fV6-m5KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely cafe, I had rush so I took to go their americano. The taste is a little bitter than other coffee shops. I will try apple cider next time and enjoy the atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBDTR4E7UogWeS2mwCiTM-I30vJkBK7W5j8MRY&fid=0x0:0xfdbaf300e9499ed4"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Travelling Daze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7d51ijgGftoX1gC7H0c4HYLCHvNSzmJceM6LdaaqwQoFmfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Probably my new favourite cafe! Thrift store with 5 dollar clothes! And they also showcase local artists.
Food: chicken pesto sandwich was very flavourful and good pricing. Sooo many drink options I was overwhelmed but will be going back to try more haha
Outlets: there’s an outlet at almost every table!
Seating: comfortable and a medium/good number throughout the cafe.
